The company''s innovative search marketing platform delivers insights into market dynamics, competitor activities, and growth opportunities. This transparency allows marketers to effectively target their ads, ensuring efficient use of advertising budgets. Adthena''s technology has received multiple industry awards, highlighting its leadership in the pay-per-click software space. The company serves a global clientele, including well-known brands like Eurostar, HSBC, Burberry, and VodafoneZiggo, helping them enhance their search marketing strategies. Headquartered in London, Adthena employs around 111 people and has raised approximately $16.6 million in funding for product development and market expansion.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '3', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/1218.png', 'true', 'Medium-sized company', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', 'ashby', 'https://api.ashbyhq.com/posting-api/job-board/adthena', null), ('73', 'Kantata', 'Kimble Applications Limited', 'https://www.kantata.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/gokantata/', 'Kantata is a global software company that specializes in professional services automation (PSA) and project management solutions. It serves over 2,500 professional services organizations in more than 100 countries, focusing on industries such as consulting and IT services. Kantata aims to simplify complex project lifecycles and enhance financial performance for professional services firms.

The company offers the Kantata Professional Services Cloud, a comprehensive, cloud-based platform that integrates project management, resource planning, financials, and collaboration tools. Key features include project management tools for scheduling and budgeting, resource planning for effective personnel allocation, and time and expense management for improved billing accuracy. The platform also provides a centralized portal for collaboration and customizable reporting tools for strategic decision-making. Kantata integrates with popular business tools like Salesforce, Microsoft, and Slack, ensuring smooth workflows across different systems.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '3', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/456.png', 'true', 'Large company', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', 'bamboohr', 'kantata', null), ('75', 'Automata', 'Automata Technologies Limited', 'https://automata.tech/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/automata-technologies/', 'Automata is a biotech company focused on integrated lab automation solutions for the life sciences sector. Their mission is to make automation accessible and practical for laboratories, moving beyond traditional instruments to a fully automated, open platform. The company''s flagship product, LINQ, is the world’s first fully automated lab bench, designed to enhance workflow efficiency and data management. This platform allows labs to increase throughput significantly, such as processing up to 250 plates per day while minimizing manual interactions.

Automata''s solutions are utilized in prominent clinical and research settings, including The Royal Marsden NHS Foundation Trust and The Francis Crick Institute. Their technology streamlines genomic testing and sequencing workflows, contributing to faster scientific discoveries. The company provides a combination of hardware, software, and expert support, focusing on areas like clinical genomics and cell culture automation. Founded by Mostafa ElSayed, Automata leverages expertise in design, engineering, and life sciences to deliver innovative automation solutions that enhance research capabilities in laboratories.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/195.png', 'true', 'Medium-sized company', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', null, null, null), ('76', 'proSapient', 'proSapient Limited', 'https://www.prosapient.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/prosapient/', 'proSapient is a London-based expert network founded in 2017 that connects institutional investors, management consultants, and corporate professionals with vetted subject matter experts globally. The company utilizes artificial intelligence and machine learning to enhance the efficiency of sourcing, scheduling, and managing expert consultations.

The services offered by proSapient include facilitating one-on-one calls and meetings with industry specialists, an AI-powered search engine for matching clients with relevant experts, and the ability to launch targeted surveys for primary research insights. Additionally, proSapient provides automated transcription services and a unified dashboard for streamlined access to multiple expert networks, supporting market research and due diligence processes.

