Deel IT offers a comprehensive IT management suite that includes device procurement and global logistics, ensuring fast delivery of hardware to remote employees. The company also manages the entire device lifecycle, covering deployment, security configuration, repair, and replacement. Additionally, Deel IT provides software provisioning and app access management, streamlining IT workflows. Its centralized platform allows HR and IT teams to efficiently manage hiring, onboarding, and offboarding processes, reducing operational complexity. With a strong customer base and a focus on supporting global organizations, Deel IT is well-equipped to meet the needs of companies with remote workforces.', 'The company is not currently offering visa sponsorship.', '2', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/296.png', 'true', 'Medium-sized company', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', null, null, null), ('184', 'AudioStack', 'Aflorithmic Labs, Ltd.', 'https://audiostack.ai/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/audiostack-ai/', 'AudioStack is an enterprise platform that specializes in AI-driven audio production. It offers an end-to-end solution that allows businesses to create high-quality audio content quickly and efficiently. The company''s technology integrates various AI-powered media creation tools, including AI script generation, text-to-speech, speech-to-speech, generative music, and dynamic versioning. This enables enterprises to build complex audio production workflows faster than real-time while maintaining professional quality.

