The group operates through several subsidiaries, including Octopus Energy, which supplies affordable green energy to over 1.35 million customers and manages renewable energy assets. Octopus Investments focuses on venture capital trusts and investments that create societal impact, while Octopus Money provides accessible financial advice. Other ventures, such as Aurora, support children with special educational needs. Overall, Octopus Group is dedicated to fostering sustainable growth and social impact through its diverse portfolio.', 'Sponsorship can be offered for some roles.', '1', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/47.png', 'true', 'Very large company', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', 'smartrecruiters', 'v1', null), ('187', 'Seldon', 'Seldon Technologies Ltd', 'https://www.seldon.io/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/seldon/', 'Seldon Technologies Limited is a British technology company founded in 2014 and based in London. It specializes in Machine Learning Operations (MLOps) and Large Language Model Operations (LLMOps) for enterprise deployment and monitoring of machine learning models. The company offers a modular framework called Seldon Core, which enables scalable and standardized deployment of machine learning models across various environments.

Seldon''s platform provides tools for model deployment, management, and observability. It facilitates the production of machine learning models at scale, supports diverse model types, and optimizes resource use. The platform also allows real-time monitoring of models and pipelines, helping teams improve performance. Seldon’s offerings include Seldon Core, Seldon Core+ for enterprises, the Seldon LLM Module for large language models, and Seldon Alibi for model inspection and explanation.

Seldon serves a wide range of customers, including enterprises that need robust machine learning solutions. The company has established partnerships with major technology firms like Google, Red Hat, IBM, and Amazon Web Services, reflecting its strong position in the market.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/338.png', 'true', 'Medium-sized company', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', 'greenhouse', 'seldon', null), ('188', 'Arm', 'Arm Limited', 'https://www.arm.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/arm/', 'Arm Holdings plc is a UK-based semiconductor and software design company founded in 1990. It specializes in developing the ARM architecture, a family of low-power, high-performance CPU designs that are widely used in mobile devices, embedded systems, and increasingly in data centers and AI applications.

The company focuses on the design and licensing of semiconductor intellectual property (IP), particularly its instruction set architecture (ISA) and processor designs. Arm licenses its technology to semiconductor companies and original equipment manufacturers (OEMs), allowing them to integrate Arm-based processors into their products. Its offerings include optimized CPU architectures, software development tools, middleware, and security technologies that support its hardware designs.

Arm''s technology is embedded in over 99% of the world''s smartphones and is expanding into automotive, IoT, and data center markets. The company has established a strong customer base, including major semiconductor firms like Qualcomm, Nvidia, and Intel, as well as smartphone manufacturers such as Oppo, Vivo, and Xiaomi.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '3', '1', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/495.png', 'true', 'Very large company', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', 'workable', 'carmoola', null), ('189', 'CybSafe', 'CybSafe Limited', 'https://www.cybsafe.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/cybsafe-limited/', 'CybSafe is a London-based cybersecurity company founded in 2015, specializing in human risk management. Led by CEO Oz Alashe, the company employs around 90 professionals dedicated to enhancing online safety through innovative solutions that address the human element of cybersecurity.

CybSafe''s core offering is an adaptive Human Risk Management platform that detects and reduces risky cybersecurity behaviors in real time. Utilizing AI, behavioral science, and data analytics, the platform provides personalized interventions to change user behavior effectively. This approach has demonstrated significant results, including a reduction in high-risk behaviors by up to 60% and a 50% acceleration in compliance. The platform integrates seamlessly with existing technology stacks, offering real-time guidance within users'' workflows.

CybSafe emphasizes a people-centric and evidence-based approach to security, empowering users to make smarter decisions. Their services include advanced cybersecurity awareness training, risk management tools, and behavioral security solutions designed to mitigate emerging threats. The company serves leading global organizations across various industries, focusing on reducing human cyber risk and improving overall security culture.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/103.png', 'true', 'Small company', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', 'bamboohr', 'cybsafe', null), ('190', 'Pelago', 'Digital Therapeutics Ltd', 'https://www.pelagohealth.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/pelago-health/', 'Pelago is a virtual clinic focused on substance use management, providing digital treatment solutions for tobacco, alcohol, opioid, and cannabis use disorders. Founded in 2017 by physicians, including CEO Yusuf Sherwani and Chief Medical Officer Sarim Siddiqui, Pelago partners with employers and health plans across the United States to make effective support accessible.

The clinic offers personalized, evidence-based treatment programs that combine cognitive behavioral therapy (CBT) with medication-assisted treatment (MAT). Members have unlimited access to a physician-led care team, including doctors, nurses, coaches, and counselors. Key features include virtual therapy sessions, remote monitoring tools, and access to clinically vetted inpatient treatment centers. PelagoRx serves as a confidential medication hub for MAT prescriptions, ensuring seamless integration with employer health plans and wellness platforms.

Pelago supports over 750,000 registered users and has partnerships with more than 100 companies across various industries. The company emphasizes clinical research and data-driven outcomes to continuously improve its treatment plans, aiming to reduce stigma and provide discreet, scalable care for healthier lives.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '1', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/1006.png', 'true', 'Medium-sized company', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', 'greenhouse', 'pelago', null), ('191', 'Biorelate', 'Biorelate Ltd', 'https://www.biorelate.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/biorelate-limited/', 'Biorelate is a private limited company based in Manchester, UK, founded in 2014 as a spinout from Manchester University. The company specializes in transforming unstructured biomedical data into actionable insights using advanced AI and machine learning technologies. Biorelate aims to enhance drug discovery and development by converting complex biomedical information into usable knowledge, thereby improving research and development efficiency for pharmaceutical and life sciences organizations.

The company''s flagship product, Galactic AI™, launched in 2020, curates and analyzes biomedical data to support drug target identification and validation. Biorelate also offers AI-driven data curation services and applies predictive modeling to assist researchers in understanding drug-disease relationships. Their client base includes leading global pharmaceutical companies and biotech firms, all seeking to streamline their drug discovery processes. Biorelate is recognized for its strong internal culture, emphasizing values such as curiosity, accountability, and innovation.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/1196.png', 'true', 'Small company', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', null, null, null), ('193', 'Parkopedia', 'Parkopedia Limited', 'https://www.parkopedia.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/parkopedia/?originalSubdomain=uk', 'Parkopedia is a global technology company founded in 2007 by CEO Eugene Tsyrklevich. The company aims to enhance the parking experience for drivers worldwide through its comprehensive platform. Parkopedia helps millions of drivers find, pay for, and manage parking, electric vehicle (EV) charging, fueling, and toll services across over 20,000 cities in 90 countries.

The core offering is a detailed database of more than 90 million parking spots, including on-street and curbside locations. Parkopedia utilizes proprietary software, artificial intelligence, and innovative data collection technologies to provide real-time and predictive availability data. Its services include parking finder and payment solutions, EV charging integration, fueling and toll services, and in-car commerce. The technology is integrated into connected vehicles, with a significant presence in Europe and the US. Parkopedia partners with automotive manufacturers and mapping providers to deliver seamless in-car services, aiming to make mobility more ecological, efficient, and convenient. The company has roots in Moldova and also operates in London and California.', 'Sponsorship may be offered for some roles, and we have excluded any that definitely cannot be.', '1', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/1094.png', 'true', 'Medium-sized company', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', 'teamtailor', 'parkopedia', null), ('194', 'Lick', 'Lick Home Ltd', 'https://www.lick.com/uk', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/join-lick/', 'Lick is a London-based home décor brand founded in 2020 and certified as a B Corporation. The company focuses on providing high-quality, sustainable decorating products, including water-based, low-VOC paints, wallpaper, blinds, and innovative decorating tools. Lick is dedicated to minimizing its ecological impact through industry-first no-wastage manufacturing processes.

The brand''s mission emphasizes environmental sustainability and social responsibility. Lick aims to enhance indoor air quality and support charitable initiatives, such as providing clean water through partnerships with organizations like charity: water. The company serves environmentally conscious homeowners and decorators, prioritizing ethical marketing and customer feedback to foster a positive impact on both society and the environment. Since its launch, Lick has experienced rapid growth as an online supplier in the UK.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/1042.png', 'true', 'Medium-sized company', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', 'workable', 'lick-home', null), ('196', 'Fathom', 'SSBM Ltd', 'https://www.fathom.global/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/fathom-global/', 'Fathom is a global water and climate risk intelligence firm that specializes in flood risk mapping and modeling. Founded in 2013 from academic research at the University of Bristol, Fathom provides scientifically rigorous data to help businesses and communities manage and mitigate water risks. In December 2023, Fathom joined Swiss Re, enhancing its ability to deliver advanced solutions for water-related risk resilience.

The company offers a range of services, including high-quality flood hazard mapping, the Global River Topology (GRIT) dataset, and the FathomDEM Global Terrain Map, which supports accurate flood modeling. Fathom also provides risk scores and geospatial data tailored for various regions, along with catastrophe models and flood hazard maps developed by a team of scientists. Their research contributes to the understanding of climate change impacts on water risk, supporting clients across multiple sectors, including government agencies, insurance companies, and humanitarian organizations.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '3', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/1184.png', 'true', 'Medium-sized company', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', 'bamboohr', 'fathom', null), ('197', 'Anthesis', 'Anthesis (UK) Limited', 'https://www.anthesisgroup.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/anthesis-consulting-group/', 'Anthesis Group is a global sustainability consultancy and advisory firm, recognized as the largest group of dedicated sustainability experts worldwide. With over 1,000 professionals in 40 countries, the company serves more than 2,000 clients, including major corporations like Reckitt Benckiser, Cisco, and Tesco. Headquartered in London, UK, Anthesis also has offices across the Americas, Europe, Asia, and the Middle East.

The firm, known as the "Sustainability Activator," helps organizations transition to sustainable and decarbonized business models. Their services include developing sustainability strategies, providing science-based advisory, and offering digital solutions for sustainability management. Anthesis also engages in carbon removal projects and supports early-stage companies through its venture arm. As a certified B Corporation, Anthesis is committed to social and environmental performance, and it has been recognized for high employee satisfaction, particularly in the U.S. operations.', 'The company is not currently offering visa sponsorship.', '2', '4', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/1254.png', 'true', 'Very large company', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', 'pinpoint', 'anthesisgroup', null), ('198', 'Cutover', 'Godesic Limited', 'https://www.cutover.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/cutover/', 'Cutover is a cloud-hosted Collaborative Automation platform that connects teams and technology to enhance the management of complex IT operations. It supports enterprises in areas such as disaster recovery, cloud migration, and software releases, promoting efficiency and control. The platform integrates AI, automation, and human collaboration to simplify workflows and improve visibility across IT operations.

The services offered by Cutover include a SaaS solution for standardizing and automating technology operation processes, AI-powered automated runbooks that significantly reduce recovery times, and real-time dashboards for monitoring work status. The platform also generates immutable audit logs to assist with regulatory compliance and integrates with over 20 tools to enhance operational efficiency. Cutover is trusted by a diverse range of industries, including financial services, healthcare, telecommunications, and energy, serving thousands of users globally, including major global banks.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '3', '1', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/235.png', 'true', 'Medium-sized company', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', null, null, null), ('199', 'Solvo.ai', 'Solvo.ai Ltd', 'https://www.solvo.ai/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/solvo-ai/', 'Solvo.ai is a technology company that specializes in AI-driven price optimization for the freight forwarding and logistics industry. The company aims to empower freight forwarders by enhancing decision-making through a combination of artificial intelligence and human expertise.

Their main offering is a Price Optimization Engine that helps logistics companies make complex pricing decisions. This engine analyzes historical data, real-time market feedback, and customer behavior to provide dynamic price recommendations that adapt to changing market conditions. Key features include increased quotation efficiency, improved yield performance, and the ability to model pricing strategies and manage KPIs.

Founded by a team with extensive expertise in machine learning and logistics, Solvo.ai collaborates with global logistics providers to deliver tailored solutions that integrate with existing systems. The company is focused on expanding its AI capabilities and aims to become a leading AI engine in the freight forwarding sector.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/529.png', 'true', 'Very small company', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', null, null, null), ('201', 'Hook', 'Hook Technology Ltd', 'https://hook.co/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/hook-technology/', 'Hook is an award-winning creative content agency that specializes in digital production and advertising campaigns. The agency focuses on creating high-quality, engaging content that drives growth for innovative brands. Their production-led approach combines artistic creativity with technical expertise to deliver impactful marketing solutions.

The services offered by Hook include digital advertising campaigns, creative content production across various media, experiential marketing, and the development of creative toolkits. They have collaborated with major brands like Google, Amazon, Indeed, and Mailchimp, providing innovative digital marketing solutions and strategic brand campaigns. Hook aims to engage audiences effectively through technology and creativity.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/1026.png', 'true', 'Medium-sized company', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', 'ashby', 'https://api.ashbyhq.com/posting-api/job-board/hook', null), ('202', 'Binance', 'Binance Europe Limited', 'https://www.binance.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/binance/', 'Binance is the largest cryptocurrency exchange in the world by daily trading volume, founded in 2017 by Changpeng Zhao. Initially based in China, the company has since relocated its operations to various countries and is currently registered in the Cayman Islands. Binance allows users to trade over 350 cryptocurrencies, offering competitive fees and high liquidity.

The company provides a wide range of services, including a decentralized exchange for peer-to-peer trading, peer-to-peer lending, and staking services. Binance also has its own cryptocurrency, Binance Coin (BNB), which is used for trading fee discounts and features deflationary mechanisms. Additionally, Binance Labs invests in blockchain and Web3 projects, while Binance Academy offers educational resources to help users navigate the crypto space. With millions of users globally, Binance caters to both novice and experienced traders.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '1', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/385.png', 'true', 'Very large company', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', 'lever', 'binance', null), ('203', 'VMWare', 'VMWare UK Limited', 'https://www.vmware.com/uk.html', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/vmware/', 'VMware is a prominent company specializing in cloud computing and virtualization. Founded in 1998 in Palo Alto, California, VMware gained recognition with the launch of its first product, VMware Workstation, in 1999. This software enabled users to run multiple operating systems on a single computer, significantly impacting software development and testing. Over the years, VMware expanded its offerings, including server virtualization solutions like VMware ESXi and a comprehensive suite for managing virtualized environments known as VMware vSphere.

The company provides a variety of products and services, including VMware Cloud Foundation for cloud infrastructure, VMware NSX for network virtualization, and VMware Tanzu for modern application management. VMware also offers cloud services through partnerships with major cloud providers such as AWS, Azure, and IBM Cloud. With a diverse customer base that includes enterprise IT, government agencies, healthcare providers, and financial institutions, VMware is widely adopted across various industries, including many Fortune 500 companies.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/452.png', 'true', 'Very large company', '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', 'teamtailor', 'vmware', null), ('205', 'Mintago', 'Mintago Limited', 'https://mintago.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/getmintago/', 'Mintago is a UK-based financial wellbeing company founded in 2019, headquartered in London. The company offers a technology-driven platform designed to enhance financial health and literacy for both employers and employees. Mintago aims to create happier, financially healthier workforces by providing tools and services that reduce money-related stress and improve workplace productivity.

The platform includes salary sacrifice pension schemes, comprehensive staff benefits like employee assistance programs and virtual GP services, and financial education tools. Mintago also assists employees in recovering lost pensions and offers unbiased financial advice tailored to individual needs. With a focus on growth, trust, impact, safety, and transparency, Mintago supports organizations in enhancing their employee benefits and financial wellbeing offerings. Their clients include organizations such as NICE and Ride Tandem, which have reported high adoption rates and positive feedback on the platform''s effectiveness.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '3', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/1145.png', 'true', 'Medium-sized company', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', 'teamtailor', 'mintago', null), ('206', 'Plotly', 'Plotly Europe Ltd', 'https://plotly.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/plotly/', 'Plotly is a software company founded in 2012 and based in Montreal, Canada, with a fully remote team. The company specializes in interactive, web-based data visualization and analytics tools for scientific, engineering, and enterprise applications. Plotly has strong ties to the open-source community, having developed popular libraries like Plotly.py and Plotly.R.

The company offers several products, including Plotly Studio and Plotly Cloud for creating and sharing interactive graphs, and Dash Enterprise, a low-code platform for building and managing Python data applications. Dash Enterprise integrates with various IT systems and cloud environments, supports authentication methods, and connects to major big data backends. Plotly also maintains open-source libraries that facilitate interactive scientific data visualization without the need for JavaScript coding.

Plotly''s tools are utilized by Fortune 500 companies and other enterprises across various industries, including finance, engineering, and business intelligence. The company has received venture funding and provides professional services such as application development and training workshops to enhance enterprise adoption of its solutions.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '1', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/963.png', 'true', 'Medium-sized company', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', 'greenhouse', 'plotly', null), ('207', 'Cognism', 'Cognism Limited', 'https://www.cognism.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/cognism/', 'Cognism is a UK-based B2B sales intelligence and lead generation company founded in 2015 and headquartered in London. With over 500 employees, Cognism specializes in accelerating sales and recruitment leads by utilizing artificial intelligence and machine learning. The company provides real-time, actionable sales opportunities from a curated database of over 400 million B2B profiles.

Cognism''s sales acceleration platform offers powerful search capabilities, an Ideal Customer Profile (ICP) builder, and tools for identifying buying teams and obtaining direct contact information. It also serves as an enrichment tool for outbound data automation, integrating with platforms like Salesforce and LinkedIn Sales Navigator. The company''s services enhance CRM records, stream leads, and leverage AI to surface tailored sales opportunities, improving data quality and compliance standards.

Cognism supports over 1,800 revenue teams globally across various industries, focusing on demand generation and relationship building. Their marketing efforts foster interest and trust in their products, contributing significantly to their new business revenue.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor but does not sponsor SDRs.', '1', '14', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/91.png', 'true', 'Large company', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', null, null, null), ('208', 'NET-A-PORTER', 'Net-A-Porter Group Ltd', 'https://www.net-a-porter.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/net-a-porter/', 'NET-A-PORTER is a luxury online fashion retailer founded in London in 2000 by Natalie Massenet. It transformed the retail landscape by creating a high-end e-commerce platform that features full-priced women''s clothing and accessories from renowned luxury brands like Gucci and Oscar de la Renta, as well as popular high-street labels.

