With a global team of over 400 employees, the studio is well-equipped to develop its innovative titles. Build A Rocket Boy has successfully raised significant funding, including a $110 million Series D round in early 2024, to support its development efforts.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/1114.png', 'true', 'Large company', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', 'bamboohr', 'build', null), ('216', 'Salary Finance', 'Salary Finance Limited', 'https://www.salaryfinance.com/uk/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/salaryfinance/', 'Salary Finance is a financial technology company based in the UK, founded in 2015 by Dan Cobley, Asesh Sarkar, and Daniel Shakhani. Headquartered in London, the company aims to enhance the financial wellbeing of working individuals by helping them manage debt and save for their financial goals.

