Salary Finance serves a diverse range of employers, including notable organizations like Marks & Spencer and E.On, supporting over 4 million employees across more than 575 client companies. The company has received numerous awards for its innovative approach to financial wellbeing and is recognized for its commitment to social responsibility in lending.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '3', '5', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/238.png', 'true', 'Medium-sized company', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', 'greenhouse', 'salaryfinance83', null), ('217', 'Travers Smith', 'Travers Smith LLP', 'https://www.traverssmith.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/travers-smith/', 'Travers Smith LLP is a full-service law firm located in London, with a history of over 150 years. It is recognized as part of the UK''s "Silver Circle" of leading law firms and operates as a limited liability partnership. The firm provides a wide range of legal services across various practice areas, including corporate advisory, mergers and acquisitions, financial services, dispute resolution, employment, real estate, and tax.

