Everlaw''s core offering is a scalable e-discovery platform that enables law firms, corporate legal departments, and government agencies to efficiently handle the entire litigation lifecycle. This includes document review, complex litigation, investigations, Data Subject Access Requests (DSARs), and contract review, all within a centralized platform. The platform features an intuitive review experience and tools like StoryBuilder™, which helps legal teams collaboratively prepare outlines for briefs and depositions by integrating key documents into their narratives. With over 1,000 customers worldwide, Everlaw has established a strong market presence and is valued at over $2 billion.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '3', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/851.png', 'true', 'Large company', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', 'greenhouse', 'everlaw', null), ('224', 'Motorway', 'Motorway Online Limited', 'https://motorway.co.uk', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/motorway-online-ltd./', 'Motorway is a UK-based online marketplace that connects private car owners with over 7,500 verified car dealers, facilitating fast and transparent vehicle sales. Founded in July 2017 and headquartered in London and Brighton, Motorway simplifies the buying and selling process by leveraging technology to provide competitive offers quickly and securely.

