The firm invests in various sectors, including artificial intelligence, machine learning, fintech, and logistics, typically committing between €1.5 million and €3 million per funding round. Frontline Ventures emphasizes building long-term relationships with founders, offering strategic support and resources like the "US Playbook" to help navigate transatlantic expansion. With a portfolio of over 130 companies and more than 35 successful exits, Frontline Ventures is dedicated to fostering growth for globally ambitious B2B software startups.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/907.png', 'true', 'Small company', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', 'bamboohr', 'frontlinevc', null), ('264', 'Lingumi', 'Lingumi Limited', 'https://lingumi.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/lingumi/', 'Lingumi is an educational technology company based in London, focused on early childhood English language learning for children aged 2 to 6 years. Founded in 2015, Lingumi develops the Club Lingumi app, which features an AI-driven curriculum that includes videos, interactive activities, games, and speaking exercises. This personalized approach adapts to each child''s learning pace, making the experience engaging and effective.

The app operates on a subscription model, providing families with daily lessons and content. Lingumi serves over 100,000 families across various countries, including China, Taiwan, the UK, Germany, Italy, and France. The company also emphasizes social impact by offering free daily activity packs for parents and pledging to donate 20% of sales to the Global Children’s Fund. With a strong foundation in research from the University of Oxford, Lingumi aims to expand its global reach while delivering playful and effective English learning experiences for preschoolers.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/114.png', 'true', 'Small company', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', null, null, null), ('266', 'Abatable', 'Zero Imprint Limited', 'https://www.abatable.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/abatable/', 'Abatable is a London-based technology company founded in 2021 that operates a carbon offsetting procurement platform. The platform connects businesses with high-quality carbon project developers, helping organizations navigate the voluntary carbon markets and create credible climate action plans aligned with the 1.5°C Paris Agreement goal.

The company offers a carbon intelligence and procurement platform that assists companies in making informed decisions about purchasing carbon offsets. It provides third-party quality assessments of carbon projects, standardizes multi-year purchase agreements, and features an automated Request for Proposal (RFP) system. Abatable emphasizes transparency and accountability, ensuring that carbon credits deliver real environmental benefits. The platform also offers insights into supply trends in the voluntary carbon market, aiding both buyers and project developers.

Abatable serves businesses and institutional investors aiming to achieve net zero and science-based climate goals. Notable partnerships include the Paris 2024 Olympic Games, where the company sources and vets climate action projects to enhance the event''s environmental impact. The company''s mission is to empower organizations to build a sustainable future for climate, nature, and people.', 'The company can provide sponsorship for all roles.', '1', '3', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/496.png', 'true', 'Small company', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', 'workable', 'abatable', null), ('267', 'Home Made', 'Home-Made UK Properties Limited', 'https://www.home-made.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/home-made./', 'Home Made is a prop-tech start-up on a mission to fix renting for good. Forever. Making it better, safer, and fairer for all.
 
