Marshmallow offers a digital-first experience, allowing customers to easily purchase and manage their car insurance through an app. The company is committed to diversity and inclusivity, focusing on marginalized groups who face challenges in accessing fair insurance. With a distinctive branding and a mission-driven approach, Marshmallow has quickly grown to become one of the fastest-growing companies in Europe, achieving unicorn status with a valuation of $1.25 billion as of 2021.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '3', '9', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/18.png', 'true', 'Large company', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', 'ashby', 'https://api.ashbyhq.com/posting-api/job-board/marshmallow', null), ('274', 'Oyster Yachts', 'Oyster Yachts Limited', 'https://oysteryachts.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/oysteryachts/', 'Oyster Yachts is a British luxury yacht manufacturer founded in 1973 by Sir Richard Matthews, with its headquarters near Southampton, UK. The company specializes in designing and building high-end bluewater cruising sailing yachts, known for their quality and performance. A signature feature of their yachts is the Deck Saloon design, introduced in 1978, which enhances onboard comfort and visibility.

