Mixcloud stands out by focusing on legal licensing agreements with music rights holders, ensuring fair royalties for artists and songwriters. Registered users can upload content, join interest-based groups, and promote their mixes through social networking features. The platform also offers an API for easy integration with other services. In 2018, Mixcloud introduced a "fan-to-creator" subscription model, allowing listeners to support their favorite creators directly, which helps fund licensing costs and provides revenue opportunities for content creators. The platform primarily serves DJs, radio show hosts, podcasters, and music enthusiasts looking for a legal and fair way to share and discover audio content.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/158.png', 'true', 'Medium-sized company', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', 'workable', 'mixcloud-limited', null), ('281', 'London Stock Exchange Group (LSEG)', 'London Stock Exchange Group Plc', 'https://www.lseg.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/london-stock-exchange-group/', 'London Stock Exchange Group (LSEG) is a prominent global financial markets infrastructure and data provider based in London, England. It plays a crucial role in the financial system, serving clients across Europe, the Americas, Asia Pacific, and emerging markets. LSEG operates a suite of businesses, including the London Stock Exchange, Refinitiv, FTSE Russell, LCH, and Tradeweb, and is recognized as Europe''s leading equities business.

LSEG is organized into five main business divisions: Data & Analytics, FTSE Russell, Risk Intelligence, Capital Markets, and Post Trade. These divisions offer specialized services that support investment, trading, risk management, and capital formation. LSEG also provides a variety of products and technologies, such as the LSEG TORA trading system and Millennium Exchange matching engine, along with comprehensive index and fixed income analytics through FTSE Russell. With a diverse customer base that includes asset managers, hedge funds, and investment banks, LSEG empowers financial market participants to make informed decisions and enhance operational efficiency.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '3', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/438.png', 'true', 'Very large company', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', 'workday', 'Careers', null), ('282', 'Hutch', 'Hutch Games Ltd', 'https://www.hutch.io/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/hutch-games-ltd/', 'Hutch is a telecommunications service provider based in Colombo, Sri Lanka, founded in 2004. As a subsidiary of CK Hutchison Holdings, the company offers a variety of mobile communication services, including prepaid and postpaid plans, 4G network coverage, data connectivity, voice, and SMS services. Hutch focuses on delivering affordable mobile plans with reliable network coverage and strong customer support.

