The team consists of over 25 scientists, technologists, and food experts. Better Dairy has raised over $20 million in funding, including a significant Series A round in 2022. Their innovative process utilizes genetically engineered yeast to produce casein and other dairy components, resulting in products that are lactose-free and have a lower environmental impact compared to conventional dairy farming.

