Chatham House conducts research on various global challenges, including climate change and geopolitical shifts. It hosts lectures, debates, and policy discussions, and produces reports and policy briefs to influence decision-makers. The organization also offers educational resources for academia and media. With a leadership team that includes CEO Bronwen Maddox and notable presidents like former New Zealand Prime Minister Helen Clark, Chatham House plays a vital role in shaping international policy discourse and is frequently cited by major media outlets for its expert insights.', 'Sponsorship can be offered for some roles.', '3', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/177.png', 'true', 'Very large company', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', null, null, null), ('306', 'Galldris Services', 'Galldris Services Limited', 'https://www.galldris.co.uk/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/galldris-group-ltd/', 'Galldris Group, represented by Galldris Construction Limited and Galldris Holdings Limited, is a key player in the construction industry based in Harrow, Middlesex, England. Established in 1998, Galldris Construction offers a variety of construction services, including civil engineering, groundworks, reinforced concrete frames, tunnelling, basement construction, piling, and rail services.

