The core offering of Flexciton is its Autonomous Scheduling Technology (AST), which includes several applications designed to optimize semiconductor manufacturing workflows. Key components are Flex Local, a toolset for individual equipment scheduling; Flex Global, a system-wide scheduler for improved coordination; and Flex Planner, which manages wafer starts and bottlenecks. These tools analyze operational data to create optimized production schedules, maximizing throughput and improving delivery predictability.

