The company offers a cloud-based platform that includes policy and procedure management, regulatory mapping, and traceability. Key features of the platform include smart document management for compliance documents, real-time regulatory change tracking, and collaboration tools to streamline workflows for policy drafting and implementation. Clausematch serves a variety of sectors, including banking, investment management, insurance, fintech, payments, and corporate clients, helping them efficiently adapt to regulatory changes and reduce compliance risks. The company emphasizes automation and AI-driven compliance to improve operational efficiency and ensure alignment with evolving regulations.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '2', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/135.png', 'true', 'Small company', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', null, null, null), ('341', 'iwoca', 'iwoca Limited', 'https://www.iwoca.co.uk/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/iwoca/', 'iwoca is a fintech company that specializes in providing business finance to small and medium-sized enterprises (SMEs) in the UK and Germany. Founded in October 2011, iwoca has grown to become one of the largest small business lenders in these markets. The company offers credit lending services that focus on fast, flexible, and accessible financing solutions tailored to the needs of SMEs.

