The company brews a variety of lagers infused with real fruit extracts like peach, elderflower, and grapefruit. Their products are gluten-free, vegan, low in calories, and free from artificial preservatives and flavorings. JUBEL has gained recognition for its brightly colored cans and has won multiple awards, including the UK’s Best Fruit Beer at the World Beer Awards.

JUBEL is committed to sustainability, having switched from glass bottles to aluminum cans to reduce emissions significantly. The company is a Certified B Corp and actively publishes annual impact reports to share its environmental progress. With a growing presence in major UK retailers and nearly 1,000 pubs, JUBEL continues to expand its reach while promoting social and environmental responsibility.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/1302.png', 'true', 'Medium-sized company', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', null, null, null), ('431', 'AND Digital', 'ANDigital Limited', 'https://www.and.digital/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/and_digital/', 'AND Digital is a technology company founded in 2014 by CEO Paramjit Uppal, dedicated to closing the global digital skills gap. The company helps businesses enhance their digital delivery by embedding skilled digital professionals, known as "ANDi," into client teams. This approach enables organizations to innovate and compete effectively in a software-driven world.

The company specializes in talent augmentation, digital consultancy, and delivery acceleration, assisting clients in building and scaling digital products and platforms. AND Digital serves a diverse range of clients, including British Airways, Gousto, NBrown Group, and IAG Cargo, focusing on large enterprises that aim to improve their digital capabilities.

With over 1,000 employees and 11 offices across the UK, AND Digital has experienced significant growth since its inception. The company has also expanded internationally, establishing a presence in Amsterdam. Its revenues have surpassed £50 million, reflecting its success in the digital services market.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '3', '9', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/1029.png', 'true', 'Very large company', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', 'workable', 'and-digital', null), ('432', 'Addepar', 'ADDEPAR UK LTD', 'https://addepar.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/addepar/', 'Addepar, Inc. is a cloud-based wealth management software company founded in 2009 by Joe Lonsdale and Jason Mirra. The company focuses on providing an investment management platform for registered investment advisors, family offices, private banks, and broker-dealers who serve high-net-worth and ultra-high-net-worth clients. Addepar''s mission is to aggregate and analyze complex financial data, offering comprehensive portfolio insights.

The platform features data aggregation across various asset types, including traditional investments and alternative assets like private equity. It provides advanced analytics and customizable reporting tools, enabling wealth managers to gain transparency into portfolio performance and make informed decisions. Addepar also offers a mobile application for on-the-go portfolio management and has integrated machine learning capabilities to enhance its analytical functions. The company serves a diverse clientele, including notable clients and partnerships with major financial institutions, aiming to modernize wealth management technology and improve investment decision-making.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '3', '22', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/1251.png', 'true', 'Very large company', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', 'greenhouse', 'addepar1', null), ('433', 'Journey', 'Journey Hospitality Limited', 'https://journey.travel/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/journey/', 'Journey is a technology and ecommerce provider focused on the hospitality industry, particularly luxury hotels and resorts. The company specializes in enhancing direct bookings and guest experiences through an integrated platform that includes booking engines, experience management, payment processing, and digital marketing services. Their aim is to help hotel owners and operators increase revenue and productivity by turning guest interactions into personalized opportunities.

Journey offers an all-in-one booking engine to boost direct bookings, a management system for efficiently handling guest experiences, and a payment management platform that consolidates resort payments. They also provide website development services to enhance the online guest experience and digital marketing programs tailored for hotels and spas. Their expertise in revenue maximization supports hotel owners in improving their direct booking channels and overall revenue management through digital transformation.', null, '4', '9', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/1143.png', 'true', 'Medium-sized company', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', 'greenhouse', 'journey', null), ('434', 'UNDO', 'UNDO Carbon Ltd', 'https://un-do.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/undocarbon/', 'UNDO is a leading carbon dioxide removal project developer that specializes in enhanced rock weathering (ERW). This nature-based technology accelerates a natural geological process to permanently remove CO₂ from the atmosphere. By spreading crushed silicate rock on agricultural land, UNDO enhances the weathering process, which releases nutrients and bicarbonates that eventually form solid carbonate minerals in the oceans, effectively locking away carbon.

Founded by Jim Mann, UNDO operates globally with projects in the UK, US, Australia, Canada, and East Africa. The company collaborates with major partners like Microsoft, Stripe, and McLaren to help businesses achieve their net zero goals. UNDO offers carbon removal credits based on scientifically validated methodologies and supports farmers by providing crushed rock for free, utilizing existing agricultural infrastructure. Their approach not only focuses on carbon removal but also improves soil health and supports farming communities.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/1287.png', 'true', 'Medium-sized company', '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', null, null, null), ('435', 'Circuit Mind', 'Circuit Mind', 'https://www.circuitmind.io/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/circuit-mind/', 'Circuit Mind is a deeptech company focused on automating electronic circuit board design using artificial intelligence. The company aims to inspire innovation in hardware by enabling engineering teams to create high-quality electronic systems more quickly and at lower costs compared to traditional methods.

Their core offering is an AI-powered platform that automates the generation and redesign of electronic systems in a matter of seconds or minutes, a process that usually takes weeks or months. This platform allows teams to input requirements and instantly explore optimized design options based on various factors such as cost, size, and performance. Circuit Mind also provides services that include electronic circuit and PCB design, drafting requirements, selecting components, and connecting customers with manufacturing partners.

Targeting electronic engineering teams and companies, Circuit Mind helps accelerate hardware development cycles and reduce manual design tasks. The company is led by Co-founder and CEO Tomide Adesanmi and is headquartered in London.', 'The company is prepared to sponsor for all of their roles.', '1', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/493.png', 'true', 'Small company', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', null, null, null), ('436', 'Cohere', 'Cohere UK Ltd', 'https://cohere.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/cohere-ai/', 'Cohere is a Canadian multinational technology company that specializes in enterprise artificial intelligence (AI), focusing on large language models (LLMs) and AI products for regulated industries such as finance, healthcare, and manufacturing. Founded in 2019, Cohere is headquartered in Toronto and San Francisco, with additional offices in Montreal, London, and New York.

The company offers a range of AI tools and models, including generative language models like Command R+, advanced retrieval models, and enterprise APIs for text generation and intelligent search. Cohere supports both cloud-based and on-premises deployment options, ensuring organizations can maintain data control while utilizing AI capabilities. Their AI workspace solutions streamline workflows, and specialized offerings for healthcare improve collaboration and decision-making. Cohere serves a diverse clientele, including notable companies like Fujitsu and Oracle, positioning itself as a key partner in the AI landscape.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '3', '47', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/382.png', 'true', 'Large company', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', 'ashby', 'https://api.ashbyhq.com/posting-api/job-board/cohere', null), ('437', 'Callsign', 'Callsign Ltd', 'https://www.callsign.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/callsign/', 'Callsign is a UK-based cybersecurity company that specializes in digital identity, fraud prevention, and authentication solutions. The company utilizes advanced artificial intelligence and machine learning technologies to enhance security across web, mobile, and physical interactions. Its mission is to provide seamless identification while ensuring a frictionless user experience.

The core technology of Callsign employs deep learning for real-time risk intelligence, allowing organizations to adjust authentication requirements based on the context of access attempts. This adaptive approach helps reduce fraud by increasing authentication steps for suspicious activities and simplifying them for legitimate users. Callsign''s platform supports passwordless authentication through a single PIN and biometric tests, achieving high accuracy in user recognition.

Callsign emphasizes ethical AI and privacy-conscious design, using data obfuscation techniques to analyze behaviors without compromising individual privacy. The company’s solutions are designed to comply with privacy regulations, reflecting its commitment to data responsibility. Callsign serves a global customer base, providing innovative solutions that enhance digital trust and security.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/150.png', 'true', 'Large company', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', 'smartrecruiters', 'callsign', null), ('438', 'Hadean', 'Hadean Supercomputing Ltd', 'https://hadean.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/hadean/', 'Hadean is a London-based deep tech company founded in 2014, specializing in distributed computing and spatial intelligence platforms. The company focuses on creating hyper-scalable synthetic environments that connect physical and virtual worlds. Hadean''s mission is to provide supercomputer-level processing power to developers and enterprises, enabling large-scale simulations and complex applications across various sectors, including defence, transport, logistics, space, gaming, and the metaverse.

The Hadean Platform allows developers to build and scale applications that require significant computational power without the limitations of traditional infrastructure. The Aether Engine supports massively multiplayer online games by enabling high player counts and complex interactions without performance issues. Additionally, Muxer optimizes networking and data flow within distributed systems. Hadean collaborates with notable partners, including CCP Games and Epic Games, and has worked with the British Army to create advanced synthetic training environments. The company aims to enhance decision-making and situational awareness through its innovative technology.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '5', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/205.png', 'true', 'Medium-sized company', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', 'teamtailor', 'hadean', null), ('440', 'DocuSign', 'DocuSign UK Limited', 'https://www.docusign.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/docusign/', 'DocuSign, Inc. is a technology company founded in 2003 in Seattle, Washington, with a mission to replace paper-based signatures with secure digital solutions. Headquartered in San Francisco, DocuSign operates globally, serving customers in over 180 countries.

The company''s main offering is the DocuSign Agreement Cloud, which includes a suite of applications designed to automate and streamline the agreement process. Its flagship product, eSignature, allows users to securely sign documents electronically on any device. Additional features include Contract Lifecycle Management (CLM) for automating contract processes, Document Generation tools for creating agreements, Contract Analytics for analyzing contract terms, and Remote Online Notarization for secure notarization of documents.

DocuSign integrates with various third-party applications, making it easy to incorporate into existing business workflows. The company serves multiple industries, including healthcare, real estate, and financial services, helping organizations improve efficiency, reduce costs, and minimize environmental impact by decreasing paper usage.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '3', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/584.png', 'true', 'Very large company', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', 'smartrecruiters', 'docusign', null), ('441', 'Encord', 'Cord Technologies Limited', 'https://encord.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/encord-team/', 'Encord is an AI data management platform that streamlines the curation, annotation, and evaluation of multimodal data for AI development. It allows AI teams to manage and label various data types, including images, videos, audio, and documents, on a unified platform. This enhances workflows with human-in-the-loop capabilities, enabling the transformation of raw data into high-quality datasets for training and fine-tuning AI models.

The platform features three main components: Index for data management and organization, Annotate for AI-powered data labeling, and Active for monitoring and evaluating data quality. Encord integrates with major cloud and AI infrastructure providers, ensuring seamless workflow integration. Trusted by over 200 AI teams globally, including notable companies like Synthesia and Stanford Medicine, Encord serves multiple industries such as healthcare, logistics, and technology.

With a focus on security and compliance, Encord holds certifications like SOC 2 and HIPAA. Founded by experts in technology and finance, the company aims to address AI alignment challenges by providing essential tools and infrastructure for scalable AI development.', 'Sponsorship can be offered for all roles.', '1', '33', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/1186.png', 'true', 'Medium-sized company', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', 'lever', 'CordTechnologies', null), ('443', 'Intropic', 'Intropic Limited', 'https://www.intropic.io/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/intropic-io/', 'Intropic is a London-based private limited company founded in 2018, dedicated to enhancing the information economy by unlocking the value of data through innovative, decentralized approaches. The company was established by Ravinder Bhadhal and Sam Shannon, who have extensive backgrounds in data analysis, investment funds, and computer science. Intropic believes that progress relies on harnessing information rather than just raw data, focusing on constant innovation and technological development.

The company offers a suite of data processing tools and customizable dashboards that empower users to structure and connect their data independently. This decentralized approach aims to reduce bottlenecks and enable faster decision-making in complex systems. Intropic primarily serves professionals and organizations in sectors like finance and investment, where advanced data analytics and knowledge extraction are essential. With a commitment to transforming complex data into actionable insights, Intropic is positioned as a leader in the evolving landscape of data management.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '3', '11', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/420.png', 'true', 'Medium-sized company', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', 'lever', 'intropic', null), ('445', 'Tokamak Energy', 'Tokamak Energy Ltd', 'https://www.tokamakenergy.co.uk/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/tokamak-energy-ltd/', null, 'The company is able to offer sponsorship to successful candidates.', '1', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/128.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', 'teamtailor', 'tokamakenergy', null), ('448', 'Codility', 'Codility Limited', 'https://www.codility.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/codility/', 'Codility is a technology company founded in 2009, with headquarters in San Francisco and significant operations in Warsaw and London. It specializes in a technical hiring platform that assesses the coding skills and problem-solving abilities of software engineers. This platform enables companies to make evidence-based hiring decisions, focusing on real-life coding challenges rather than traditional resumes or interviews.

The core mission of Codility is to enhance the world’s problem-solving capacity by providing a fair and efficient way to evaluate technical talent. Its services include a code assessment platform, candidate evaluation tools, and scalable testing that supports the evaluation of thousands of candidates across 63 countries. Codility also offers remote hiring support, allowing companies to build diverse engineering teams regardless of location.

With a team of around 150 employees from 11 countries, Codility emphasizes a flexible work culture and diversity. The company has raised approximately $22 million in venture capital and generates estimated revenues of $36.8 million, highlighting its strong position in the HR technology market.', 'The company rarely sponsors individual contributor (IC) roles, but may consider support for the right person, typically in a high-profile or senior role (Director-level and above).', '1', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/329.png', 'true', 'Medium-sized company', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', 'hibob', 'https://codility.careers.hibob.com/api/job-ad', null), ('450', 'Accurx', 'AccuRx Limited', 'https://www.accurx.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/accurx/', 'Accurx is a British software company founded in May 2016, dedicated to improving communication within the healthcare sector, particularly for the NHS in England. Initially focused on tackling antimicrobial resistance, the company shifted its focus in 2018 to address broader communication challenges faced by healthcare professionals and patients.

Accurx develops digital communication tools that enhance interactions between healthcare staff and patients, as well as among healthcare professionals. Its flagship product, Chain SMS, is a secure messaging platform widely used by GP surgeries for patient communication, appointment booking, and referrals. The company also offers Record View, a platform for sharing patient medical records with permission, and a Vaccine Booking System that managed nearly 30 million vaccinations during the COVID-19 pandemic. Additionally, Accurx supports healthcare surveys and remote monitoring, contributing to effective patient care management. With over 98% of GP practices in England using its software, Accurx plays a vital role in modernizing healthcare communication across the UK.', 'Accurx are limiting the number of roles they offer sponsorships for. They can still put cases forward in "exceptional circumstances."', '1', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/218.png', 'true', 'Large company', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', 'ashby', 'https://api.ashbyhq.com/posting-api/job-board/accurx', null), ('452', 'Cardlytics', 'Cardlytics UK Limited', 'https://www.cardlytics.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/cardlytics/', 'Cardlytics, Inc. is a commerce media and advertising technology company based in Atlanta, Georgia, founded in 2008. The company operates a proprietary purchase intelligence platform that utilizes first-party purchase data from financial institutions. This platform provides marketers access to data from over 2,000 financial institutions, covering around 215 million customers and a significant portion of card-based transactions in the U.S. and U.K.

Cardlytics offers two main solutions: Cardlytics Direct, which allows marketers to reach consumers through digital banking channels with personalized cash back offers, and the Bridg Platform, a customer data platform that enables advanced analytics and targeted loyalty marketing. The company''s services help marketers acquire new customers, boost sales, and measure marketing effectiveness, while also providing financial institutions and consumers with customized offers and rewards. With a workforce of over 450 employees, Cardlytics is publicly traded on Nasdaq under the ticker symbol CDLX.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/361.png', 'true', 'Large company', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', 'workday', 'cardlytics/CardlyticsExternalCareerSite', null), ('453', 'Stone Nest', 'Stone Nest', 'https://www.stonenest.org/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/stone-nest/about/', null, 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/990.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', 'greenhouse', 'stone', null), ('454', 'AutogenAI', 'AutogenAI Ltd', 'https://autogenai.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/auctane/', 'AutogenAI is a private limited company founded in February 2022, with offices in New York City, London, and Brisbane. The company specializes in developing AI-powered language engines that enhance bid, proposal, and grant writing processes for businesses and organizations globally. AutogenAI''s mission is to empower clients to produce high-quality content quickly, helping them gain a competitive edge in securing grants and proposals.

The company offers a generative AI platform that supports the entire bid and proposal lifecycle. Key features include content generation, storyboarding, research assistance, document automation, and RFP management. The platform integrates smoothly into existing workflows, allowing users to efficiently retrieve and adapt content. AutogenAI serves a diverse clientele, including Fortune 500 companies, international government agencies, and large enterprises across various sectors. Its technology has been recognized for significantly improving the speed and quality of proposals, contributing to client success and productivity.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '4', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/1125.png', 'true', 'Medium-sized company', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', 'greenhouse', 'autogenai', null), ('455', 'Brandwatch', 'Cision Group Limited', 'https://www.brandwatch.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/brandwatch/', 'Brandwatch is a digital consumer intelligence and social media software company founded in 2007 and headquartered in Brighton, United Kingdom. With 17 locations worldwide, it specializes in helping brands understand online conversations and extract valuable insights for business decisions. The company has evolved by integrating data science and artificial intelligence into its social media analysis platform.

Brandwatch offers a range of services, including a Consumer Intelligence Platform for market research, social media management tools following its merger with Falcon.io, and add-on applications like Reviews and Vizia for customer insights and data visualization. Its Audiences product helps brands identify key audience segments through social media analytics, while the Influence tool focuses on influencer marketing. Brandwatch serves a diverse clientele, including major brands like Delta Airlines and Unilever, and aims to empower companies to make data-driven decisions and engage effectively with their audiences. In 2021, Brandwatch was acquired by Cision, enhancing its capabilities and market presence.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '6', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/427.png', 'true', 'Large company', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', 'greenhouse', 'brandwatch', null), ('457', 'Depop', 'Depop Limited', 'https://www.depop.com/gb/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/depop/', 'Depop is a social e-commerce platform founded in 2011 by Simon Beckerman. Initially linked to a fashion magazine, it has evolved into a peer-to-peer marketplace focused on secondhand, vintage, and repurposed fashion. Headquartered in London, with offices in Milan and New York City, Depop combines the visual appeal of Instagram with the marketplace functionality of eBay, allowing users to buy, sell, and discover unique fashion items.

The platform supports a vibrant community of users, primarily targeting Gen Z and Millennials, with about 90% of active users under 26 years old. Depop enables sellers to act as influencers, curating and reselling thrifted items while also supporting emerging designers in building their brands. With over 35 million registered users and significant sales since its inception, Depop plays a key role in promoting sustainable fashion and reshaping the secondhand shopping experience.', 'Sponsorship can be offered. However, it may be limited to certain roles and skillsets. It is unclear which.', '3', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/45.png', 'true', 'Very large company', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', null, null, null), ('459', 'Count', 'Count Technologies Ltd', 'https://count.co/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/counthq/', 'Count is a UK-based software company that specializes in a canvas-based business intelligence (BI) tool designed to improve data collaboration and analysis within organizations. Founded in 2004, Count has transitioned from providing financial consultancy services to schools to focusing on innovative data solutions. The company is headquartered in London and operates with a small team of fewer than 25 employees.

The flagship product, the Count BI Tool, allows users to create interactive and flexible data visualizations. This platform moves beyond traditional dashboards by enabling users to display relationships between metrics and business processes in a more intuitive way. Count also offers professional services, including tailored training and consulting aimed at enhancing the skills of data teams and business users. These services cover various aspects, from the fundamentals of using Count to bespoke consulting for workflow optimization and team training. Count''s platform is particularly beneficial for data analysts, product teams, and business stakeholders, helping them solve complex business problems and enhance collaboration across teams.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/518.png', 'true', 'Small company', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', null, null, null), ('460', 'Grabyo', 'Grabyo Limited', 'https://about.grabyo.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/grabyo/', 'Grabyo is a global technology company that specializes in cloud-based video production, distribution, and monetization solutions. Founded in 2013, Grabyo aims to simplify and enhance professional video creation through its flexible, cloud-native platform. Users can produce live broadcasts, virtual events, highlight reels, and video clips from anywhere using just a web browser.

The company offers a fully managed video production environment that supports live event broadcasting and multi-camera productions. Grabyo''s platform allows for rapid deployment of production environments, significantly reducing costs. It also features AI-powered tools for automated clipping and highlights, along with video-on-demand editing capabilities. Grabyo supports hybrid and fully virtual event production, enabling high-quality broadcasts with branded graphics and low-latency streaming. With over 20,000 media professionals as clients, Grabyo collaborates with major social media platforms and technology providers to enhance user workflows and revenue opportunities.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/1033.png', 'true', 'Medium-sized company', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', null, null, null), ('461', 'Mirakl', 'Mirakl Ltd', 'https://www.mirakl.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/mirakl/', 'Mirakl is a French-American cloud-based e-commerce software company founded in 2012 by Philippe Corrot and Adrien Nussenbaum. With dual headquarters in Paris and Boston, Mirakl specializes in enterprise marketplace SaaS platforms that help businesses, including retailers and wholesalers, efficiently launch and manage their own online marketplaces.

The company''s core product is a comprehensive platform that supports both B2C and B2B marketplaces, allowing clients to expand their offerings without the need for inventory. Mirakl also offers dropship and B2B marketplace solutions, enhancing control over pricing and customer experience. Additionally, Mirakl Connect is a marketplace ecosystem platform that connects operators with sellers and service providers to boost growth. The company has demonstrated adaptability by creating a COVID-19 response platform to facilitate the distribution of personal protective equipment.

Mirakl serves over 450 clients globally, including major names like Carrefour, H&M Home, and Best Buy Canada. With a strong presence in Europe and North America, Mirakl has been recognized as a French Tech Next40 company and has achieved unicorn status with a valuation of $3.5 billion.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '3', '9', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/893.png', 'true', 'Large company', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', 'greenhouse', 'mirakl', null), ('462', 'Altana AI', 'Altana Technologies UK Ltd', 'https://altana.ai/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/altana-ai/', 'Altana is a New York-based technology company that specializes in artificial intelligence solutions for global supply chain management. Founded in 2018, Altana has quickly established itself as a unicorn valued at $1 billion, reflecting its significant contributions to supply chain transparency and efficiency.

The company offers an AI platform that creates a dynamic digital map of global supply chains, analyzing billions of data points related to products, shipments, and companies. This platform provides high-fidelity data for shipment-level visibility, enabling clients to manage risks, ensure compliance, and maintain continuity. Altana''s services include a value chain management system that utilizes federated machine learning, decision support and automation tools, and collaboration features that enhance stakeholder engagement.

