The company offers two main products: AI Search, which provides a customizable search bar with features like personalization and real-time indexing, and AI Recommendations, a tool that generates personalized content to boost user engagement. Algolia serves a diverse range of customers, including developers, startups, and enterprises across various industries such as e-commerce and media. With a global infrastructure of over 70 data centers, Algolia handles more than 1.75 trillion searches annually, making it a prominent player in the search technology market.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '3', '12', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/282.png', 'true', 'Large company', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', 'greenhouse', 'algolia', null), ('472', 'Nu Quantum', 'Nu Quantum Ltd', 'https://nu-quantum.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/nu-quantum/', 'Nu Quantum is a quantum technology company based in Cambridge, founded in 2018 as a spin-out from the University of Cambridge’s Cavendish Laboratory. The company focuses on developing quantum networking hardware and systems that facilitate the interconnection of Quantum Processing Units (QPUs) through its proprietary Quantum Networking Unit (QNU). This technology aims to create the Entanglement Fabric, a quantum networking infrastructure that allows for scalable, multi-core quantum computers.

The company offers a range of hardware solutions, including the QNU, photonic switching fabric, advanced control systems, and single-photon emitters and detectors. These components are essential for quantum communication and secure random number generation. Nu Quantum''s technology supports applications in quantum computing scale-out, secure communications, and distributed quantum data centers. The company collaborates with various partners, including government agencies, telecommunications firms, and research institutions, to advance quantum networking solutions. With a diverse team of over 60 employees, Nu Quantum is committed to fostering innovation in the quantum technology space.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/1170.png', 'true', 'Medium-sized company', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', null, null, null), ('473', 'Netlify', 'Netlify UK Limited', 'https://www.netlify.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/netlify/', 'Netlify is a software company founded in 2014 and headquartered in San Francisco. It is recognized as a leading platform for building, deploying, and scaling modern web applications. The company serves millions of developers and thousands of enterprises globally, focusing on the JAMstack architecture, which enhances web development by separating frontend and backend processes.

Netlify offers a range of services, including static site hosting, continuous deployment, and serverless functions. Developers can deploy directly from Git repositories, run backend code without server management, and utilize tools for efficient testing and deployment. The platform also supports API composition with GraphQL and provides collaboration tools for teams, enhancing content management and project workflows. Recent acquisitions, such as Gatsby, have further strengthened its offerings in modern web development.

With significant funding and a growing team, Netlify continues to empower developers and organizations to create high-performance web applications that are secure and scalable.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/891.png', 'true', 'Medium-sized company', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', 'greenhouse', 'netlify', null), ('474', 'Bank of Baroda', 'Bank of Baroda (UK) Ltd', 'https://www.bankofbarodauk.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/bankofbaroda/', 'Bank of Baroda UK is the UK branch of Bank of Baroda, one of India''s largest public sector banks, founded in 1908. The bank has a significant international presence, operating in 17 countries and serving over 183 million customers globally. In the UK, it focuses on wholesale banking services, catering primarily to corporate and institutional clients.

