The company’s patented technology enables seamless integration of audio-only ads into games. Features include pausing existing audio during ads and resuming it afterward, as well as volume detection to enhance engagement. Audiomob offers a simple plugin and SDKs for developers, connecting top brands and artists with a global audience of over 3 billion mobile gamers. The company has received significant funding from investors like Google and LightSpeed Ventures and has notable clients such as Sony Music and Warner Music Group. Audiomob has been recognized for its innovation, winning the StartUp of the Year award in 2022.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '3', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/1288.png', 'true', 'Small company', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', 'greenhouse', 'audiomob', null), ('484', 'bp', 'BP plc', 'https://www.bp.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/bp/', 'BP plc is a British multinational oil and gas company based in London, England. Founded in 1909 as the Anglo-Persian Oil Company, BP has grown to become one of the world''s largest oil companies, known as a "supermajor." The company operates across the entire oil and gas value chain, engaging in exploration, extraction, refining, distribution, and marketing of fuels and lubricants. BP also focuses on power generation and energy trading.

