Palta''s portfolio includes successful apps like Flo, a leading period-tracking app; Simple, a mindful nutrition app; Zing Coach, an AI-powered fitness coach; and Prisma Labs, known for the popular Lensa photo editing app. The company also utilizes its proprietary data platform, Palta Brain, to enhance product development and marketing strategies across its offerings.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/306.png', 'true', 'Small company', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', null, null, null), ('491', 'Tab', 'Tab Labs Ltd', 'https://theguide.tab.travel/explore/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/tab-/?originalSubdomain=uk', 'Tab powers payments and bookings for travel and tourism businesses across 40 countries in Latin America, Africa, and Asia. Our platform helps tourism businesses accept card payments from their guests — whether online, in advance, or in person — making it easier to get paid in any currency.

We reduce payment costs, simplify operations, and give businesses more flexibility — so they spend less time on admin and more time with their guests.

We work with a wide range of partners, from boutique hotels to budget stays, activity retreats to tour operators, wellness stays to day tour guides - anyone who works directly with tourists! Our focus is on emerging destinations where payments and bookings can be a real challenge — and we''re trusted by thousands of tourism businesses worldwide. Together, we''ve helped millions of travellers pay easily in over 100 currencies.

We integrate with popular booking management systems such as Cloudbeds and Bookinglayer, and we''re backed by Y Combinator (the investors behind Airbnb, Dropbox and Stripe).', 'The company does not tend to offer sponsorship.', '2', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/457.png', 'true', 'Medium-sized company', '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', null, null, null), ('493', 'Jungheinrich UK', 'Jungheinrich UK Limited', 'https://www.jungheinrich.co.uk/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/jungheinrich-uk-ltd/', 'Jungheinrich UK Ltd is a prominent provider of materials handling solutions, focusing on the manufacture, rental, and servicing of warehouse trucks and equipment. Established in 1963 and part of the global Jungheinrich Group, the company is headquartered in Milton Keynes and has customer service centers across the UK, including regions like Scotland and the Midlands.

The company offers a wide range of products, including electric and internal combustion engine forklifts, reach trucks, pallet trucks, and automated systems. Jungheinrich UK is known for its innovative contributions to the industry, such as the first reach truck and the world’s first forklift with a rotating cab. In addition to equipment sales, they provide extensive aftersales support, maintenance, and tailored warehouse planning solutions. Their commitment to environmental responsibility is evident in their promotion of lithium-ion powered forklifts and energy-efficient technologies. Jungheinrich UK serves a diverse clientele, from small businesses to large enterprises, aiming to enhance productivity and sustainability in warehouse operations.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '3', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/873.png', 'true', 'Large company', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', 'greenhouse', 'jungheinrich', null), ('494', 'General Assembly', 'General Assembly Space', 'https://generalassemb.ly/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/school/generalassembly/', 'General Assembly is a private education organization founded in 2011, specializing in practical technology skills training. Headquartered in the United States and owned by the Adecco Group since 2018, it offers a variety of learning formats, including short courses, immersive bootcamps, and online classes. The courses cover digital technology fields such as mobile and software engineering, data science, product management, web development, and user experience design.

