As part of Republic, R Europe likely offers services such as equity crowdfunding, Web3-optimized financial services, and cross-border investment infrastructure. The platform supports a diverse range of ventures, including those in technology, real estate, and cryptocurrency. R Europe benefits from Republic''s commitment to regulatory compliance and its global reach, facilitating investment opportunities across multiple jurisdictions.', 'Sponsorship can be offered for some roles.', '1', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/561.png', 'true', 'Medium-sized company', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', 'bamboohr', 'europe', null), ('497', 'BlueOptima', 'BlueOptima Limited', 'https://www.blueoptima.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/blueoptima/', 'BlueOptima is a software analytics company based in the UK, founded in 2009 and headquartered in London. The company emerged from research at Cambridge University and focuses on providing metrics and analytics to enhance software development resources. Their services aim to improve productivity through automation, standardization, and objective measurement.

The platform offers data-driven insights that help organizations optimize their software engineering performance. BlueOptima delivers objective metrics to measure and manage software development productivity, enabling enterprises to make informed decisions regarding their software resources and processes. The company serves a notable customer base, including major global organizations such as four of the ten largest banks and twelve of the Fortune 50 companies.

With a global presence, BlueOptima has offices in locations like London, Phoenix, Guadalajara, Gurgaon, Bangalore, and Yokohama. The company employs over 400 people and emphasizes values such as transparency, integrity, and a data-driven approach, fostering innovation and growth within its diverse team.', 'Sponsorship can be offered for some roles.', '3', '12', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/913.png', 'true', 'Medium-sized company', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', 'smartrecruiters', 'v1', null), ('498', 'Field', 'Virmati Energy Ltd', 'https://www.field.energy/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/field-energy/', 'Field Energy is a UK-based private limited company focused on developing, constructing, and operating advanced battery energy storage systems. Founded in 2012 and headquartered in London, the company aims to accelerate the transition to a net-zero carbon future by building critical renewable energy infrastructure. Their battery storage solutions capture energy from renewable sources like wind and solar, releasing it during peak demand to enhance grid stability and reduce reliance on fossil fuels.

