Resi offers a range of services, including tailored architectural drawings, planning permission support from experienced professionals, and access to a marketplace of vetted builders. Their platform also features integrated financing options and a single online dashboard to manage every aspect of the project. With a strong emphasis on accessibility and customer satisfaction, Resi has built a solid reputation, earning numerous 5-star reviews and becoming the top-rated architectural service on Trustpilot in the UK.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '3', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/461.png', 'true', 'Medium-sized company', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', 'teamtailor', 'resi', null), ('500', 'Auctane', 'Auctane, Limited', 'https://auctane.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/auctane/', 'Auctane is a leading provider of shipping and fulfillment software solutions, headquartered in Austin, Texas. With over 25 years of experience, the company serves more than 3 million customers globally and processes over 3 billion orders each year. Auctane specializes in innovative shipping and logistics software that helps ecommerce merchants and businesses of all sizes streamline their order fulfillment and delivery processes.

The company offers a diverse range of products, including ShipStation for shipping management, Stamps.com for mailing solutions, and Packlink for connecting to top carriers. Other offerings include Metapack for enterprise delivery management, ShippingEasy for growing ecommerce businesses, and Return Rabbit for enhancing customer return experiences. Auctane''s solutions address complex shipping challenges, enabling businesses to efficiently manage their operations and focus on customer engagement. With partnerships with over 600 industry leaders, Auctane is committed to improving shipping experiences by making them faster, more cost-effective, and transparent.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '3', '2', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/340.png', 'true', 'Very large company', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', 'greenhouse', 'auctane', null), ('501', 'Threads Styling', 'Threads Styling Limited', 'https://www.threadsstyling.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/threadsstyling/', 'Threads Styling is a luxury personal shopping and concierge company founded in 2009 by Sophie Hill. Based in London, it specializes in sourcing rare designer fashion items, including Hermès Birkin bags, Chanel jackets, and Christian Louboutin shoes. The company serves an international clientele across the UK, US, Middle East, Hong Kong, China, and is expanding into South America and Russia.

In addition to fashion sourcing, Threads Styling offers a wide range of luxury services such as wardrobe management, couture orders, bespoke gifting, and event styling for parties and weddings. They provide personalized experiences, including VIP travel arrangements and itinerary planning, with each client assigned a dedicated personal shopper to ensure seamless service. The company also features bilingual stylists to cater to non-English-speaking clients. With partnerships that include Claridges Hotel and Paramount Pictures, Threads Styling is recognized for its expertise in the luxury service sector.', 'Sponsorship can be offered for some roles.', '3', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/84.png', 'true', 'Medium-sized company', '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', null, null, null), ('502', 'XYZ Reality', 'XYZ Reality Ltd', 'https://www.xyzreality.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/xyz-reality/', 'XYZ Reality is a UK-based construction technology company that specializes in engineering-grade augmented reality (AR) solutions. Founded in 2017 by architect David Mitchell, the company focuses on enhancing the planning, building, and delivery of mission-critical construction projects. Their core product, the XYZ Atom™, is the first engineering-grade AR headset that overlays 3D design models onto construction sites with up to 5mm accuracy. This technology allows teams to visualize Building Information Models (BIM) in real time, facilitating immediate decision-making and quality assurance.

In addition to the XYZ Atom™, XYZ Reality offers a construction delivery platform that integrates project data and optimizes workflows. Their solutions are used globally on projects valued at over $12 billion, helping to reduce risks, lower costs, and improve sustainability. The company also provides HoloSite®, a mixed reality solution that combines AR goggles with position-tracking sensors to ensure builds meet exact tolerances. XYZ Reality serves complex build environments, including data centers and pharmaceutical manufacturing facilities, and collaborates with leading developers and contractors to enhance construction workflows.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/1024.png', 'true', 'Medium-sized company', '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', 'bamboohr', 'xyz', null), ('503', 'Hokodo', 'Hokodo Services Ltd', 'https://www.hokodo.co/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/hokodo/', 'Hokodo is a pan-European fintech company founded in 2018, focused on modernizing B2B commerce. It simplifies and secures trade between businesses by providing digital trade credit solutions. Merchants can offer flexible payment terms, such as Buy Now, Pay Later, to their business customers instantly, even on first purchases. This approach helps increase sales and improve cash flow by making trade credit accessible through technology.

Hokodo''s core offerings include Trade Credit as a Service, which provides instant credit assessments and automated credit limit management via APIs. The company also offers credit management solutions, including credit information services and insurance against late payments. Its credit insurance is underwritten by major insurers like AIG and Lloyd’s of London. Hokodo leverages machine learning and various data sources to manage risk effectively, catering primarily to B2B merchants, especially SMEs, who seek better payment terms for their customers. The company is headquartered in London and operates under relevant financial services and insurance regulations in Europe.', 'The company is not currently offering visa sponsorship.', '2', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/1256.png', 'true', 'Medium-sized company', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', 'bamboohr', 'hokodo', null), ('504', 'Playfair', 'Playfair Capital LLP', 'https://playfair.vc/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/playfair-vc/', 'Playfair Capital is a London-based venture capital firm that specializes in pre-seed investments. Founded in 2013 by Federico Pirzio-Biroli, the firm partners with visionary founders who are driven to create transformative futures. Playfair Capital emphasizes a collaborative approach, providing not just financial support but also day-one expert guidance to help startups thrive.

The firm is dedicated to promoting diversity in venture capital, particularly by supporting female founders. Their female founder network has collectively raised over £600 million, showcasing their commitment to fostering inclusive access to funding. Playfair Capital serves early-stage startups across various sectors, offering strategic mentorship and access to a broad network of investors. With a team of 11 members, the firm combines extensive experience in startups and angel investing to empower its portfolio companies.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/1109.png', 'true', 'Small company', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', null, null, null), ('505', 'TravelPerk', 'TravelPerk UK IRL Limited', 'https://www.perk.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/perk/', 'Perk Company, Inc. is a Cleveland, Ohio-based construction firm with over 30 years of experience. Established in 1992, the company specializes in concrete paving, bridge work, underground utilities rehabilitation, and site work. It has expanded its services to include general contracting, new construction, and complete roadway rehabilitation, addressing a wide range of infrastructure needs.

The company is known for delivering cost-efficient construction solutions and has built a strong reputation for quality workmanship. Perk Company, Inc. serves both public and private sectors, working extensively with government agencies and municipalities, including the Ohio Department of Transportation and the City of Cleveland. Its services encompass concrete paving, sitework, bridges and structures, water, sewer, and drainage systems, as well as design-build projects.', 'The company doees not offer sponsorship for most of its roles.', '1', '2', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/229.png', 'true', 'Very large company', '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', null, null, null), ('506', 'Drift', 'Drift.com Europe Ltd', 'https://www.drift.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/drift/', 'Drift is a prominent buyer experience and Conversational AI company based in Massachusetts. Founded in 2015, Drift focuses on enhancing the B2B buying process through its innovative Conversational Marketing approach. The company aims to create engaging customer experiences by facilitating personalized conversations that reduce friction in the buying journey.

Drift develops AI-powered platforms that help businesses analyze conversational data and buyer behavior. This enables companies to build deeper relationships and increase revenue by delivering tailored experiences at every interaction. Drift''s solutions integrate seamlessly with Salesloft''s revenue orchestration platform, allowing businesses to create effective sales workflows and convert high-intent web visitors into leads.

