The company offers various services, including the Current Account Switch Service, Confirmation of Payee, and Request to Pay, all designed to enhance the payment experience and reduce fraud. Pay.UK is committed to innovation, adopting global messaging standards and improving risk management processes to ensure its systems remain safe and efficient. Its vision is to be the smartest way to move money, collaborating with government and industry stakeholders to drive advancements in the payment landscape.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '3', '3', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/271.png', 'true', 'Large company', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', 'greenhouse', 'payuk', null), ('508', 'Bloomreach', 'BloomReach UK Ltd', 'https://www.bloomreach.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/bloomreach/', 'Bloomreach is a cloud-based e-commerce experience platform founded in 2009 and headquartered in Mountain View, California. The company focuses on marketing automation, product discovery, and content management systems to enhance online customer experiences for businesses in various sectors, including retail, travel, and finance.

