The organization is known for its significant contributions to AI, including the development of advanced models like GPT-3, Codex, and DALL-E. In late 2022, it launched ChatGPT, a conversational AI application that quickly gained over 100 million users, followed by the introduction of GPT-4, which can understand text, images, and voice. OpenAI provides API access to its language models, subscription services like ChatGPT Plus, and developer tools for integrating AI into applications. The company emphasizes safety, transparency, and collaboration in its research and product offerings.', 'Sponsorship can be offered for all roles. They also provide immigration support, depending on circumstances.', '1', '21', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/244.png', 'true', 'Very large company', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', 'ashby', 'https://api.ashbyhq.com/posting-api/job-board/openai', null), ('511', 'InfoSum', 'InfoSum Limited', 'https://www.infosum.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/infosumhq/', 'InfoSum is a technology company founded in 2015, specializing in privacy-first data collaboration through its patented decentralized platform. The company aims to connect data securely, allowing organizations to analyze and activate data without moving or exposing it. With offices in London, New York, and Hamburg, InfoSum serves various industries, including financial services, retail, healthcare, and entertainment.

The company''s decentralized data collaboration platform, often referred to as a Data Clean Room, enables businesses to collaborate on first-party data while maintaining privacy. It helps unlock customer insights, activate data across technology stacks, and overcome data fragmentation. InfoSum''s self-service platform is designed for marketers, facilitating effective data collaboration that enhances marketing performance while safeguarding customer privacy.

InfoSum holds multiple patents for its innovative technology, which is crucial in today''s landscape of increasing privacy regulations. The company is committed to empowering collective innovation and is focused on expanding its client base and developing robust data collaboration solutions.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '3', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/115.png', 'true', 'Medium-sized company', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', 'workable', 'infosum', null), ('513', 'W1TTY', 'W1TTY Global Ltd', 'https://www.w1tty.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/w1tty/', 'W1TTY is a digital financial services provider based in the UK and Lithuania, licensed and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority and the Central Bank of Lithuania. Since its establishment in August 2020, W1TTY has aimed to empower individuals, particularly targeting Generation Z, with a range of financial services designed to meet their needs.

The company offers customizable finance plans, money transfer services, and multiple account management options. Customers can access video call customer service and financial education through videos and podcasts. W1TTY also provides tailored card plans, allowing users to pay only for what they use. With a user base of over 150,000 across Europe, W1TTY is focused on innovation and plans to expand into Poland and other European Economic Area countries.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/1099.png', 'true', 'Small company', '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', null, null, null), ('514', 'Stability AI', 'Stability AI Ltd', 'https://stability.ai/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/stability-ai/', 'Stability AI is a UK-based artificial intelligence company founded in 2019, with its headquarters in London. The company is recognized for developing Stable Diffusion, an open-source text-to-image generative AI model that gained popularity after its release in August 2022. Stability AI aims to advance open generative AI models and democratize access to AI-powered creativity, focusing on innovation and responsible development.

The company offers a range of products and services, including Stable Diffusion, which allows users to create high-quality images from text descriptions. Stability AI also provides enterprise AI solutions with scalable tools and APIs tailored for business applications. The company has raised significant funding, totaling approximately $173.8 million, and has a diverse customer base that includes individual creators, developers, and enterprises. With a commitment to open models and customization, Stability AI positions itself as a leader in the generative AI space.', 'Sponsorship can be offered for all roles.', '1', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/342.png', 'true', 'Medium-sized company', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', 'greenhouse', 'stabilityai', null), ('515', 'StackOne', 'StackOne Technologies Ltd', 'https://www.stackone.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/stackonehq/?originalSubdomain=uk', 'StackOne is an integration platform tailored for B2B SaaS companies, enabling fast and secure enterprise-grade integrations through a unified API. It connects SaaS products with various third-party enterprise software, such as HRIS, ATS, CRM, and marketing automation tools, facilitating seamless workflows and real-time data exchange while prioritizing data privacy.

Founded by experts from major tech companies, StackOne operates as a white-label embedded integration layer. It allows customers to manage integrations directly within their vendor’s systems without storing sensitive customer data. The platform features a pre-mapped unified API, AI-driven automation capabilities, and tools for integration management, authentication handling, and real-time webhooks. With over 200 integrations and a commitment to security and compliance, StackOne supports enterprises in automating workflows and enhancing data privacy.

StackOne''s mission is to empower SaaS companies to innovate confidently by providing a flexible and secure integration solution. The company aims to expand its AI capabilities and integration coverage, evolving into essential infrastructure for AI agents across enterprise software.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '3', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/1010.png', 'true', 'Medium-sized company', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', 'breezy', 'stackone', null), ('516', 'Dojo', 'Paymentsense Limited', 'https://dojo.tech/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/dojo-tech/', null, 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '3', '30', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/436.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', null, null, null), ('517', 'Soldo', 'Soldo Software & Services Ltd', 'https://www.soldo.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/soldo/', 'Soldo is a fintech company that specializes in spend management solutions for businesses. Founded by Carlo Gualandri and a team with experience from companies like Box, Xero, and Visa, Soldo focuses on helping organizations gain control over decentralized spending through automation and user-friendly technology.

The company offers a comprehensive spend management platform that includes a centralized system for managing expenses, prepaid business cards for authorized spending, and a mobile app for tracking and approving expenses. Soldo''s automation tools streamline financial workflows, while its multi-currency support facilitates spending across different countries. With a customer base of over 25,000 organizations in 31 countries, Soldo serves a diverse range of businesses, from startups to established enterprises, including notable names like Facebook, Spotify, and Deliveroo. 

Soldo has experienced significant growth, bolstered by substantial funding rounds, which have allowed it to enhance product development and expand into new markets. The company is committed to providing innovative solutions that improve financial agility and empower employees to manage spending responsibly.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/799.png', 'true', 'Large company', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', null, null, null), ('518', 'YuLife', 'Yu Life Ltd', 'https://www.yulife.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/yulife/', 'YuLife is a tech-driven life insurance and wellbeing company founded in 2016. It aims to inspire healthier, more fulfilling lives by integrating technology with insurance and holistic wellbeing. YuLife is recognized as the world’s first life insurance company that rewards healthy behavior, focusing on mental and physical wellness through digital engagement.

The company offers a B2B life insurance product that includes wellbeing tools and support services via a mobile app. This app motivates users to adopt healthy habits by rewarding them for positive behaviors. YuLife''s offerings include life insurance, private medical insurance, and workplace benefits, all designed to enhance employee health and wellness. Their innovative approach has led to significant growth, with a notable revenue increase and recognition in the Deloitte UK Technology Fast 50 list.

