The core technology, the Prove Identity Network (PIN), supports over 1,000 global companies across various industries, including banking, insurance, telecommunications, and e-commerce. Prove''s services include Prove Pre-Fill®, which simplifies consumer onboarding; Prove Identity®, which verifies identities using just a phone number; and Prove Auth®, a passwordless authentication solution. The company also provides tools like Trust Score® and SIM Swap Detection to help clients manage identity risks.

