Overall, Unmind aims to help organizations implement effective wellbeing strategies, improve employee mental health, and drive positive business outcomes.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '3', '2', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/153.png', 'true', 'Medium-sized company', '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', 'ashby', 'https://api.ashbyhq.com/posting-api/job-board/unmind', null), ('569', 'Simpplr', 'Simpplr Limited', 'https://www.simpplr.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/simpplr/', 'Simpplr is an AI-powered employee experience platform founded in 2014 and based in Silicon Valley, California. It focuses on unifying the digital workplace by streamlining internal communications, automating workflows, and enhancing the overall employee experience. The platform serves as a centralized hub that integrates company news, events, collaboration tools, and engagement features, making it especially useful for hybrid and remote work environments.

