Intercom offers a suite of tools that help businesses engage with customers at every stage of their journey. Its core product includes messaging and support applications that allow companies to send targeted messages, provide live chat and automated support, and manage customer relationships with personalized communication tools. The platform also features AI-powered capabilities, including an AI agent named Fin, to enhance customer service efficiency. Intercom serves a diverse customer base, from startups to large enterprises, and combines marketing, sales, and support functionalities in one system.', 'Sponsorship can be offered for certain roles.', '3', '50', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/223.png', 'true', 'Very large company', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', 'greenhouse', 'intercom', null), ('609', 'Pleo', 'Pleo Technologies Ltd', 'https://www.pleo.io/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/pleo-company/', 'Pleo is a European fintech company founded in 2015 in Copenhagen by Jeppe Rindom and Niccolo Perra. It specializes in smart spend management solutions for businesses, offering a platform centered around smart company cards. This allows employees to make purchases while finance teams maintain control over expenses, reimbursements, invoices, and mileage tracking.

