The company''s core offering is a marketplace protocol that links developers with providers of compute power, ensuring transparency and security through blockchain technology. Gensyn supports a wide range of hardware, including CPUs, GPUs, and Apple M1 and M2 chips, enabling a scalable compute network. Additionally, the platform allows for confidential AI queries, ensuring data privacy and compliance for businesses.

Gensyn aims to democratize access to AI infrastructure, making it as accessible as oxygen. By providing affordable and decentralized compute power, the company empowers startups, researchers, and the broader AI community to build and deploy AI systems without relying on large centralized data centers.', 'Sponsorship can be offered for all roles.', '1', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/21.png', 'true', 'Small company', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', 'greenhouse', 'gensyn', null), ('621', 'Headout', 'Headout UK Ltd', 'https://www.headout.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/headout-com/', 'Headout is a New York-based mobile marketplace that helps travelers and locals discover and book curated tours, activities, and events around the world. Founded in 2014, the company focuses on making travel spontaneous and affordable by offering last-minute deals that are typically 15% cheaper than competitors. With a user-friendly mobile platform, Headout allows bookings within a 24 to 48-hour window, catering to those who prefer to plan their adventures on the go.

