The company offers a suite of AI agents designed to streamline recruitment tasks. The AI Notetaker automatically records and transcribes interviews, saving recruiters time on manual note-taking. The AI Job Posts feature generates compliant job descriptions quickly, while AI Answers provides instant insights about candidates and roles. Additionally, the AI Reports tool transforms interview data into actionable insights, helping teams optimize their hiring processes. Metaview emphasizes ethical AI use, data security, and compliance with standards like SOC 2 Type 2 and GDPR, ensuring a responsible approach to recruitment technology.', 'Sponsorship can be offered for some roles.', '4', '9', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/34.png', 'true', 'Medium-sized company', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', 'ashby', 'https://api.ashbyhq.com/posting-api/job-board/metaview', null), ('632', 'MEDDICC', 'MEDDICC Ltd', 'https://meddicc.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/meddicc/', 'MEDDICC is a private limited company based in Wisbech, Cambridgeshire, United Kingdom, founded in 2020. The company specializes in educational support services, focusing on enhancing sales team competencies through the MEDDIC sales qualification methodology. This framework, developed in the 1990s, is designed to help B2B sales teams qualify leads more effectively and improve their overall sales performance.

