The company serves a diverse clientele, from technology startups to established international firms, helping them navigate complex technology challenges and develop new products. Cambridge Consultants is known for generating valuable intellectual property and has a history of spinning out successful ventures. It positions itself as a leader in combining engineering excellence and design innovation to drive progress across multiple industries.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '3', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/273.png', 'true', 'Large company', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', 'greenhouse', 'cambridgeconsultantslimited', null), ('634', 'Gymshark', 'Gymshark Ltd', 'http://gymshark.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/gymshark/', 'Gymshark is a British athletic apparel retailer founded in 2012 by Ben Francis and Lewis Morgan. Starting from a garage in Birmingham, the company has grown into a billion-dollar brand with over 900 employees and customers in more than 230 countries. Initially focused on drop shipping bodybuilding supplements, Gymshark quickly shifted to designing and manufacturing its own performance-driven fitness clothing.

