The company has raised approximately $7.49 million in funding from investors such as Tiferes Ventures, Hoxton Ventures, and Triple Point. Fluent''s customer base primarily consists of marketing agencies and client service teams seeking efficient and reliable reporting tools to enhance client communication and operational efficiency.', 'Sponsorship can be offered for all roles.', '1', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/1267.png', 'true', 'Small company', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', null, null, null), ('637', 'Tandem Bank', 'Tandem Bank Limited', 'https://www.tandem.co.uk/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/tandem-bank/', 'Tandem Bank is a UK-based digital challenger bank established in 2015, focusing on customer-centric financial services through its mobile app. Operating without physical branches, it offers a full range of regulated banking products under a license acquired from Harrods Bank Limited in 2017. Tandem Bank is authorized by the Prudential Regulation Authority and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority, ensuring a secure banking experience for its customers.

