The company offers a range of privacy-enhancing products and services, including confidential payments, private decentralized finance (DeFi) interactions, and zk-rollups technology. Aztec''s zk-rollup solution bundles multiple transactions into a single proof, which reduces gas costs and increases transaction throughput while maintaining user privacy. The company aims to build a fully private, programmable, and decentralized Layer 2 network on Ethereum, addressing the growing demand for privacy in Web3 applications. Co-founded by Zac Williamson and Joe Andrews, Aztec Network is positioned as a leading provider of privacy solutions in the blockchain space.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '3', '1', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/332.png', 'true', 'Medium-sized company', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', 'greenhouse', 'aztec', null), ('643', 'Gaia', 'Gaia Fertility Limited', 'https://gaiafamily.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/gaiafamily/', 'Gaia is dedicated to making fertility treatments, particularly IVF (in vitro fertilization), more accessible and affordable. Founded by Nader AlSalim, the company addresses the challenges and high costs associated with fertility treatment. Gaia''s innovative approach combines personalized insurance products with flexible payment plans, helping to reduce financial uncertainty for individuals and couples seeking fertility assistance.

