Signal AI serves over 650 customers globally, including notable corporations like Bank of America Securities, Google, and Exxon Mobil. The company has raised over $100 million in funding, with a focus on expanding its predictive analytics capabilities and advancing AI research and development. The company culture promotes innovation, diversity, and a people-centric approach.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/117.png', 'true', 'Medium-sized company', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', 'ashby', 'https://api.ashbyhq.com/posting-api/job-board/signal-ai', null), ('725', 'Clari', 'Clari U.K. Limited', 'https://www.clari.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/clari/', 'Clari is an AI-powered Revenue Orchestration Platform founded in 2013. It helps enterprises optimize their revenue processes by unifying data, workflows, and sales activities into a single system. The platform supports revenue operations by connecting sales, marketing, and customer success teams, allowing them to manage revenue as an enterprise-wide process.

Clari offers a suite of modular products that cover the full revenue lifecycle. Key features include automated data entry, opportunity and account management tools, pipeline management, sales engagement, and forecasting insights. The platform also includes AI Revenue Agents that automate workflows, enabling revenue teams to focus on selling. Clari serves a diverse range of companies, including notable clients like Adobe, Okta, and Zoom, helping them improve forecasting, reduce churn, and drive predictable revenue growth.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/390.png', 'true', 'Large company', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', 'lever', 'clari', null), ('726', 'Volt', 'Volt Technologies Holdings Ltd', 'https://www.volt.io/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/voltio/', 'Volt.io is a fintech company based in London, UK, founded in 2019. It specializes in real-time account-to-account payment solutions using open banking technology. The company has created a "network of networks" that allows merchants globally to send and receive instant payments directly between bank accounts, avoiding traditional card and wallet systems.

The core offering is a single API that connects to over 1,900 banks across 33 countries, facilitating a standardized checkout experience. Merchants can enable customers to pay directly through their banking apps, ensuring secure and instant fund transfers. Volt.io''s product suite includes tools for transaction management, cash handling, fraud prevention, and customer identity verification. The company is authorized as an Electronic Money Institution in the UK and a Payment Institution in Poland, ensuring compliance and secure fund management. With over $83 million raised in funding, Volt.io serves high-volume industries like ticketing, retail, gaming, and financial services, providing a reliable alternative to card payments.', 'The company is only open to sponsoring very senior roles (SVP & above).', '1', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/1110.png', 'true', 'Medium-sized company', '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', 'smartrecruiters', 'volt', null), ('727', 'Ophelos', 'Ophelos Ltd', 'https://ophelos.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/opheloshq/', 'Ophelos, now part of Intrum, is an AI-native debt resolution company based in the UK. It specializes in transforming how businesses engage with customers facing financial difficulties through digital and automated solutions. The company uses advanced machine learning and AI technology to automate the debt collection process, providing a more empathetic and efficient approach to debt repayment.

As an AI-powered digital engagement platform, Ophelos aims to support individuals in financial difficulty by streamlining credit management processes. Its services include a digital-first debt resolution platform that automates debt collection, personalized repayment plans tailored to individual circumstances, and a self-service interface for customers to manage repayments flexibly. Ophelos also employs advanced AI models to detect customer vulnerability, ensuring sensitive handling of debt cases. The company serves businesses across major European markets, enhancing recovery rates and fostering positive customer relationships.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '4', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/1229.png', 'true', 'Medium-sized company', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', 'greenhouse', 'ophelos', null), ('728', 'BrainStation', 'Brainstation Learning Limited', 'https://brainstation.io/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/school/brainstation/', 'BrainStation is a global leader in digital skills training and workforce transformation, established in 2012. The company focuses on providing hands-on, project-based learning experiences to empower professionals and organizations in the digital economy. With physical campuses in major cities like New York, London, Toronto, and Vancouver, BrainStation has trained over 100,000 professionals worldwide.

The company offers a variety of digital skills training programs, including courses and bootcamps in data science, design, web development, product management, and marketing. These programs are available both online and in-person. BrainStation also provides corporate training solutions to help organizations upskill their teams and navigate digital transformation. Their proprietary online platform supports live, instructor-led classes, allowing for real-time feedback and collaboration among learners. With a strong emphasis on practical projects, over 90% of graduates find employment within 180 days of completing their training.', 'The company is not currently offering visa sponsorship.', '2', '7', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/260.png', 'true', 'Large company', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', 'greenhouse', 'brainstation', null), ('730', 'Inspired Thinking Group (ITG)', 'Inspired Thinking Group (ITG) Limited', 'https://teamitg.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/teamitg/', null, 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/1028.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', 'workable', 'itg', null), ('731', 'Lendable', 'Lendable Operations Ltd', 'https://www.lendable.co.uk/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/lendable/', 'Lendable is a UK-based financial technology company founded in 2014, specializing in consumer lending through a fully digital platform. The company offers personal loans ranging from £1,000 to £25,000, with repayment terms of 1 to 5 years and interest rates varying based on the borrower''s profile. Lendable emphasizes transparency, allowing customers to view their loan rates before applying, and features a no-paperwork application process that is entirely online. Loan decisions are made quickly, often within seconds, and funds can be disbursed in as little as two hours.

The company utilizes advanced data science and machine learning to enhance its credit decision-making process. By leveraging multiple data sources, Lendable can approve loans for customers who may be declined by traditional lenders. Customer service is available seven days a week through various channels, and borrowers can manage their loans online, reflecting Lendable''s commitment to a user-friendly experience. Headquartered in London, Lendable operates as a private limited company and is authorized by the Financial Conduct Authority.', 'Sponsorship can be offered for some roles.', '1', '45', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/213.png', 'true', 'Medium-sized company', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', 'bamboohr', 'lendable', null), ('734', 'Rightship', 'Rightship UK Ltd', 'https://rightship.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/rightship-pty-ltd/?originalSubdomain=au', 'RightShip is an Australian company founded in 2001 that focuses on improving safety, environmental sustainability, and social responsibility in the global maritime industry. The company aims to be a trusted partner in innovation, helping the maritime sector achieve high standards in safety, sustainability, and crew welfare through practical business solutions.

RightShip offers a maritime risk management system that evaluates vessel safety by analyzing factors like casualty history and vessel age. Its flagship platform, RightShip Qi, utilizes big data and advanced analytics to identify patterns and predict risks, providing actionable insights for risk mitigation. The company provides tools for maritime risk management, data analytics, and sustainability support, assisting customers in meeting emission reduction targets and improving operational safety. RightShip collaborates with maritime businesses, associations, and governments to promote industry-wide change.

