The company is evolving into an end-to-end marketplace, allowing customers to not only find but also book and pay for care services online. Lottie has introduced Seniorcare by Lottie, a support service for employees caring for elderly relatives, and offers a free concierge service to assist care seekers. With a strong commitment to social responsibility, Lottie has pledged 1,000 free overnight stays for carers during the cost of living crisis. The company has raised $31 million in funding to enhance its technology and expand its team, positioning itself as a leader in the eldercare sector in the UK.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '3', '7', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/174.png', 'true', 'Medium-sized company', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', 'ashby', 'https://api.ashbyhq.com/posting-api/job-board/lottie', null), ('747', 'SharkNinja', 'SharkNinja Europe Ltd', 'https://sharkninja.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/sharkninja/', 'SharkNinja is a global product design and technology company that specializes in small household appliances and cleaning solutions. Founded in 1994 in Montreal, Canada, the company moved its headquarters to Needham, Massachusetts, and rebranded from Euro-Pro Operating LLC to SharkNinja in 2015. The company is known for its two flagship brands, Shark and Ninja.

The Shark brand features advanced vacuum cleaners with "No-Loss-of-Suction" technology, steam cleaners, and other cleaning devices. The Ninja brand offers kitchen appliances such as blenders, air fryers, coffee systems, juicers, and cookware. SharkNinja products are distributed worldwide through major retailers like Walmart, Target, and Macy’s, as well as through direct-to-consumer channels. The company has gained recognition for its innovative technology and user-friendly designs, appealing to busy households looking for reliable and affordable solutions. SharkNinja became an independent public company in 2023 and has been recognized by TIME magazine as one of the 100 Most Influential Companies in 2025.', 'The company only tends to sponsor highly technical electrical, design, and hardware engineering roles.', '1', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/1265.png', 'true', 'Very large company', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', null, null, null), ('749', 'Chattermill', 'Chattermill Analytics Limited', 'https://chattermill.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/chattermill/', 'Chattermill is a London-based technology company founded in 2015 by Mikhail Dubov and Dmitry Isupov. The company specializes in Customer Experience Intelligence using advanced AI and deep learning. Its platform enables customer experience, support, product, and insights teams to analyze unstructured customer feedback from various channels, such as surveys, online reviews, and social media, to extract actionable insights that enhance customer retention and satisfaction.

The core offering is a Customer Feedback Analytics and Voice of Customer (VOC) platform that unifies and analyzes feedback at scale. This allows businesses to understand their customer reality in real time. Chattermill’s AI models interpret meaningful concepts in the data, helping teams identify pain points and opportunities for improvement. The platform serves various users within organizations, including customer experience, product, support, and insights teams, facilitating a comprehensive approach to customer feedback analysis.

Chattermill has a global clientele, including brands like Uber, HelloFresh, Wise, and Amazon. The company has raised significant funding, including a $26 million Series B round in 2022, and employs around 83 people, generating estimated revenues of approximately $17.1 million.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '3', '1', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/266.png', 'true', 'Medium-sized company', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', 'ashby', 'https://api.ashbyhq.com/posting-api/job-board/chattermill', null), ('751', 'Tunic Pay', 'Tunic & Co UK Limited', 'https://www.tunicpay.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/tunic-pay/?originalSubdomain=uk', 'Tunic Pay is a fintech company based in London, UK, dedicated to developing payment intelligence technology that protects banks and their customers from scams and fraud in real time. Founded by Nicky Golimis and Nico Barawid, the company aims to rebuild trust in the payments ecosystem by creating a trust infrastructure that safeguards real-time payments.

Their technology enables financial institutions to flag scams early, clear genuine payments instantly, and prevent fraud before it impacts customers. Tunic Pay utilizes artificial intelligence and real-time risk assessment to enhance decision-making at scale, allowing banks to secure transactions without delaying the payment process. Their services include real-time scam detection tools and payment intelligence platforms that analyze transactions to distinguish between legitimate payments and potential fraud. Tunic Pay focuses on providing reliable and scalable solutions for major banks, emphasizing transparency, ethical conduct, and innovation in their approach to fighting fraud.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/935.png', 'true', 'Small company', '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', null, null, null), ('752', 'Dishpatch', 'Dishpatch Ltd', 'https://dishpatch.co.uk/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/dishpatch/', 'Dishpatch is a London-based food and beverage company founded in 2020. It specializes in delivering high-quality restaurant meal kits across the UK. By partnering with top chefs and restaurants, Dishpatch creates exclusive, chef-prepared menus that customers can cook at home using pre-portioned ingredients and detailed instructions. This "finish at home" model allows individuals and households to enjoy gourmet dining experiences without leaving their homes.

Since its inception, Dishpatch has shown significant growth, expanding from 25 restaurants in 2021 to 69 as of June 2023, and delivering 120,000 meals. The company has built a strong customer base with 80,000 email subscribers and maintains a high satisfaction rating of 4.8 out of 5 stars on TrustPilot. Dishpatch has raised €11.6 million in funding from notable investors, supporting its ongoing expansion efforts. The leadership team includes experienced professionals from consulting, startups, and investment backgrounds.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/136.png', 'true', 'Small company', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', null, null, null), ('753', 'Citadel', 'Citadel Enterprise Europe Limited', 'https://www.citadel.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/citadel-llc/', 'Citadel is a prominent American multinational financial services company, primarily recognized as a hedge fund manager. Founded in 1990 by Kenneth C. Griffin and headquartered in Miami, Florida, Citadel manages over $65 billion in assets and employs more than 2,900 professionals across 24 global offices. The firm has generated approximately $74 billion in net gains since its inception, focusing on delivering long-term investment returns through expertise in various asset classes and strategies.

Citadel''s core business revolves around hedge fund management, offering a range of investment funds and strategies, including the Wellington Fund, Citadel Global Equities, Tactical Trading, and Fixed Income and Macro. The company also provides financial analytics, market-making, private capital management, and risk management services, utilizing a quantitative and technology-driven approach to investment management. Citadel serves a diverse clientele, including institutional investors, pension funds, sovereign wealth funds, endowments, foundations, and high-net-worth individuals, benefiting from its deep market expertise and global reach.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '1', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/767.png', 'true', 'Very large company', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', null, null, null), ('755', 'Trade Ledger', 'Trade Ledger Limited', 'https://www.tradeledger.io/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/tradeledger/', 'Trade Ledger™ is a fintech company founded in 2016, offering an end-to-end digital business credit management platform. This innovative platform supports a wide range of working capital lending products, including invoice funding and supply chain financing. It enables lenders to manage everything from one-off loans to complex credit facilities within a single system.

The core service is a composable, API-driven platform that integrates all aspects of business credit origination and servicing. This integration reduces operational costs and improves data quality, allowing lenders to make informed decisions while minimizing risk. Trade Ledger’s flexible architecture allows users to digitize entire credit products or specific phases of the lending lifecycle, enhancing efficiency and speeding up time to cash for businesses.

Headquartered in London, with additional offices in the US, Australia, and Poland, Trade Ledger is privately owned and backed by notable investors, including Barclays. The platform primarily serves financial institutions and lenders, helping them leverage real-time digital data to lend faster and more sustainably.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/1027.png', 'true', 'Small company', '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', null, null, null), ('756', 'Goji', 'Euroclear SA/NV', 'https://www.goji.investments/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/goji/', 'Goji, a London-based company and part of the Euroclear Group since 2022, specializes in digitizing the servicing and distribution of private funds globally. It operates a fully digitized investment platform that simplifies private market fund investments, facilitating seamless investor onboarding, subscriptions, capital calls, distributions, and centralized reporting.

