The platform supports multimedia content, allowing fans to explore characters, lore, and stories in an immersive way. Fandom hosts and supports wikis across various topics, providing tools for collaborative content creation and sharing. The company also offers advertising opportunities for entertainment brands to connect with passionate fan bases. Fandom serves fans, content creators, and entertainment companies, creating a vibrant community dedicated to celebrating fictional worlds.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '3', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/268.png', 'true', 'Large company', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', 'greenhouse', 'fandom', null), ('768', 'Helsing', 'Helsing Limited', 'https://helsing.ai', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/helsing/', 'Helsing is a German defense technology company founded in 2021 and based in Munich. The company specializes in artificial intelligence (AI) software and autonomous systems aimed at enhancing the military capabilities of democratic societies. Helsing was established by Torsten Reil, Gundbert Scherf, and Niklas Köhler, with a mission to improve the effectiveness of defense forces while maintaining a strong ethical commitment.

Helsing develops AI platforms that process large volumes of sensor and weapons system data in real time, providing critical battlefield insights. Their offerings include the HX-2 autonomous strike drone, the Altra decision-making software, and AI-enhanced weapons systems. The company operates subsidiaries in Estonia, France, and the United Kingdom and collaborates with major defense firms like Rheinmetall and Saab. Helsing exclusively serves democratic governments, including NATO countries, and is recognized as a leader in Europe’s defense AI sector.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '3', '22', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/318.png', 'true', 'Large company', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', null, null, null), ('770', 'Ankorstore', 'Ankorstore Ltd', 'https://www.ankorstore.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/ankorstore/', 'Ankorstore is a European B2B wholesale marketplace founded in November 2019 by four French entrepreneurs. The company connects independent brands with retailers, aiming to simplify the wholesale market for small businesses. Its platform allows brands to showcase and sell their products to retailers across Europe, handling essential processes like invoicing, payments, shipping, and taxes.

With over 15,000 brands and more than one million unique products available, Ankorstore offers a diverse range of items, including fashion, homeware, beauty, and lifestyle goods. The platform caters primarily to independent shops and boutiques, providing them with access to high-quality, curated products. Ankorstore operates in 23 European countries and has offices in major cities such as Paris, London, Berlin, Amsterdam, and Stockholm. The company has achieved rapid growth, reaching unicorn status within two years and is committed to empowering small businesses in the retail sector.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '3', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/820.png', 'true', 'Medium-sized company', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', null, null, null), ('771', 'The Drum', 'Carnyx Group Limited', 'https://www.thedrum.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/thedrum/', 'The Drum covers modern marketing, agency business, creativity & the future of media. Our content helps global marketers make better decisions.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '3', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/86.png', 'true', 'Medium-sized company', '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', null, null, null), ('772', 'Flawless AI', 'Flawless Holdings Limited', 'https://www.flawlessai.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/flawlessai/', 'Flawless is a London-based technology company that specializes in artificial intelligence solutions for the film and television industry. Founded in 2019 by industry veterans, including director Scott Mann and CEO Nick Lynes, Flawless focuses on enhancing global storytelling through innovative visual and performance editing tools. The company aims to empower creators by overcoming traditional barriers such as language and budget constraints, making filmmaking more affordable and accessible.

Flawless offers several advanced products, including TrueSync, which visually translates foreign language films by synchronizing lip movements and facial expressions with dubbed audio. Their DeepEditor tool assists filmmakers in refining performances and visual elements without costly reshoots. Additionally, Flawless provides AI-assisted performance editing and generative AI tools for automated dialogue replacement and CGI generation. The company primarily serves filmmakers, content owners, and entertainment companies looking to expand their global reach while maintaining quality and authenticity.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '3', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/1135.png', 'true', 'Large company', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', 'ashby', 'https://api.ashbyhq.com/posting-api/job-board/flawless', null), ('774', 'SuperAwesome', 'SuperAwesome Trading Limited', 'https://www.superawesome.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/superawesome/', 'SuperAwesome is a UK-based technology company founded in 2013 that focuses on the "kidtech" market. It provides digital media infrastructure designed to ensure safe and privacy-compliant digital engagement for children under 13. The company aims to empower the kids’ digital media ecosystem, allowing brands and content owners to connect with nearly half a billion kids and teens globally each month.

