Key offerings include Zego Pay, which automates rent and dues collection with 100% digital payment options, and Zego Utility, which manages utility operations from billing to expense recovery. The Zego Mobile Doorman app enhances the resident experience by automating tasks like rent payments and work order management. Zego serves various sectors, including property managers, homeowner associations, manufactured housing, property owners, student housing, and build-to-rent communities, focusing on improving communication, cash flow, and operational efficiency. The company prioritizes user experience and security, ensuring personalized support and data protection for its clients.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '8', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/166.png', 'true', 'Large company', '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', null, null, null), ('777', 'B2C2', 'B2C2 Ltd', 'https://www.b2c2.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/b2c2-ltd-/', 'B2C2 is a global crypto-native liquidity provider and digital asset trading firm, established in 2015 and acquired by SBI Group in 2020. Headquartered in the UK, with offices in the US and Japan, B2C2 specializes in delivering reliable liquidity and advanced trading solutions to institutional clients across major cryptocurrency and fiat currency pairs, operating 24/7.

The company offers a comprehensive suite of over-the-counter (OTC) trading products, including spot trading, derivatives like Contracts for Difference (CFDs) and options, and innovative funding solutions. B2C2''s services are designed to meet the needs of over 450 institutional clients, including banks, cryptocurrency exchanges, and hedge funds. The firm is regulated by the UK''s Financial Conduct Authority (FCA) and is known for its pioneering products, such as the first electronic OTC options trading and the first bitcoin/gold derivative. B2C2 focuses on bridging traditional financial practices with the crypto ecosystem, ensuring compliance and trust for its clients.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '3', '10', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/829.png', 'true', 'Medium-sized company', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', 'greenhouse', 'b2c2', null), ('779', 'JUMO', 'JUMO Europe Limited', 'https://jumo.world/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/jumo-world/', 'JUMO is a technology company founded in 2015, specializing in digital financial services for emerging markets, particularly in Africa. The company operates a mobile financial services platform that allows mobile network operators and banks to provide credit and savings products to unbanked individuals and small businesses through mobile devices, including feature phones. JUMO utilizes alternative data, such as GSM records and mobile wallet transactions, to make automated credit decisions without the need for prior financial history or collateral.

The company focuses on financial inclusion, serving unbanked merchants and individuals in countries like Kenya, Tanzania, Zambia, Rwanda, and Uganda. JUMO partners with major mobile operators, including Airtel, MTN, and Tigo, to expand access to financial services. Its innovative approach has garnered recognition in the fintech space, and it has received funding from investors like LeapFrog Investments and Anthemis Group.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/870.png', 'true', 'Large company', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', 'greenhouse', 'jumo', null), ('780', 'Artefact', 'Artefact Marketing Engineers UK Limited', 'https://www.artefact.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/artefact-global/', 'Artefact is a global services company that specializes in consulting, data science, artificial intelligence (AI), and marketing. With a workforce of over 1,700 employees, Artefact focuses on helping organizations adopt data and AI technologies to enhance their operations and create positive impacts. The company aims to transform businesses into consumer-centric leaders by integrating digital, data, and AI capabilities.

