Anthemis operates as an investment platform, providing capital and strategic support to startups and growth-stage companies in fintech and related sectors. It manages approximately $230 million in total funding and invests in various stages, from pre-seed to Series B+, with investment sizes ranging from $1 million to $10 million. The firm emphasizes principle-driven investing, including opportunities in emerging areas like climate fintech, and targets entrepreneurs and businesses looking to scale their innovations in financial services and technology-driven markets.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '3', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/1255.png', 'true', 'Medium-sized company', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', null, null, null), ('791', 'Osborne Clarke', 'Osborne Clarke Services', 'https://www.osborneclarke.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/osborne-clarke/', 'Osborne Clarke is an international legal practice with a history that dates back to 1748, when it was founded in Bristol, UK. Headquartered in London, the firm has grown into a global law firm with a presence in over 25 locations, including major cities like New York, Singapore, Paris, and Shanghai. With more than 1,600 lawyers and around 340 partners, Osborne Clarke offers a wide range of legal services, focusing on strategic advice and innovative solutions for clients.

The firm serves a diverse clientele, including established market leaders and high-growth start-ups. Its culture emphasizes approachability and straightforwardness, setting it apart from traditional law firms. Osborne Clarke has expanded internationally since the early 2000s, opening offices in the US and Germany, and continues to grow its global network. The firm''s commitment to innovation and forward-thinking practices has established it as a significant player in the legal services market.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '1', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/582.png', 'true', 'Very large company', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', 'bamboohr', 'osborne', null), ('792', 'Attio', 'Attio Limited', 'https://attio.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/attio/', 'Attio is an AI-native Customer Relationship Management (CRM) platform based in California, USA. It focuses on empowering businesses, particularly those with go-to-market strategies, by providing a highly customizable and data-driven solution. The platform is designed to adapt to unique business workflows, offering features like quick setup, real-time collaboration, and AI integration to streamline customer relationship management.

