Attio has raised $25 million in Series A funding, reflecting strong investor confidence in its innovative approach to CRM, positioning it as a flexible and user-friendly alternative to traditional CRM solutions.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '15', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/545.png', 'true', 'Medium-sized company', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', 'ashby', 'https://api.ashbyhq.com/posting-api/job-board/attio', null), ('793', 'JOB TODAY', 'JobToday UK Limited', 'https://jobtoday.com/gb', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/jobtoday/', 'Job Today is a mobile-first employment platform founded in 2015 in Barcelona, Spain, and now based in Luxembourg. It connects job seekers with employers in the hospitality, retail, and service sectors across the U.S., U.K., Spain, and Luxembourg. The platform has facilitated over 100 million job applications and more than 10,000 hires since its inception.

The mobile hiring app allows job seekers to apply with a single tap and chat directly with employers, aiming for matches within 24 hours. Job Today also offers recruitment tools for businesses to post jobs, manage applications, and communicate with candidates. The platform serves over 1 million global employers and has 10 million active job seekers, processing over 100 million applications annually. The company is led by CEO Eugene Mizin and has a team of over 50 staff members.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/537.png', 'true', 'Very small company', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', 'smartrecruiters', 'job', null), ('794', 'Relay', 'Relay Technologies Limited', 'https://relaytech.co/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/relay-tech/', null, 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '3', '28', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/1153.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', 'lever', 'relay', null), ('795', 'Vortexa', 'Vortexa', 'https://www.vortexa.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/vortexa/', 'Vortexa is an energy and shipping analytics company that specializes in real-time data and advanced analytics for global waterborne energy, freight, and commodity markets. Founded in 2016 by CEO Fabio Kuhn, Vortexa utilizes technologies like artificial intelligence, machine learning, and satellite data to provide insights into crude oil, refined products, LNG, and LPG flows.

The company offers a platform that tracks over $3.4 trillion in global energy flows annually with high accuracy. Clients can access data through various methods, including a web-based application, RESTful API, and Microsoft Excel. Vortexa serves a diverse client base, including energy traders, analysts, charterers, and shipping companies, helping them optimize trading and logistics strategies. With headquarters in London and regional offices in key global locations, Vortexa is committed to enhancing transparency and efficiency in the energy markets.', 'Sponsorship can be offered for some roles. Senior engineering opportunities have been sponsored in the past.', '1', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/145.png', 'true', 'Medium-sized company', '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', null, null, null), ('796', 'Digital Marmalade', 'Digital Marmalade Limited', 'https://www.digitalmarmalade.co.uk/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/digital-marmalade/', 'Digital Marmalade is a full-service digital design and development agency founded in 1997, with offices in London and Cyprus. The company specializes in web and mobile app development, UX/UI design, and software engineering. They focus on understanding client goals and user needs to create intuitive digital products that enhance customer experience and drive business growth.

