The company offers an embedded payments API that allows small and medium-sized enterprises (SMEs) to send and receive fast, secure payments directly between bank accounts. This solution reduces transaction fees and enhances cash flow by processing payments in real time. Crezco supports integration with all major UK and EU banks and partners with popular accounting software to automate invoicing and payment reconciliation. Key features include low transaction fees, instant payments, enhanced security, and multi-currency support for cross-border transactions. With a focus on innovation, Crezco is dedicated to providing efficient payment solutions for SMEs, particularly those involved in international trade.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/921.png', 'true', 'Small company', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', null, null, null), ('848', 'Squire Technologies', 'Squire Technologies Ltd', 'https://www.squire-technologies.co.uk/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/squire-technologies/', 'Squire Technologies is a UK-based telecommunications company founded in 2002 and headquartered in Wareham, England. The company specializes in advanced signaling solutions and core network optimization for the telecom industry, delivering carrier-grade products and services globally. 

Squire Technologies develops critical network infrastructure components that help telecom operators manage and evolve their core networks. Their unified signaling platform, Sigla, integrates multiple core network functions, offering features such as flexible routing, centralized mediation, security and fraud prevention tools, and a management information system for data analysis. The company serves a diverse range of customers, including Mobile Network Operators, Mobile Virtual Network Operators, and Application Service Providers, focusing on optimizing network performance and enabling new revenue streams. 

With over 20 years of expertise, Squire Technologies provides scalable and adaptable solutions that support innovation in dynamic telecom environments, backed by global deployment and support capabilities.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/988.png', 'true', 'Small company', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', 'smartrecruiters', 'squire', null), ('849', 'Dare', 'Dare International Ltd', 'https://www.dare.global/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/wearedare/', 'Dare is an energy tech company founded in 2016, specializing in energy trading and liquidity provision in global commodities markets. It has established itself as the leading liquidity provider in key energy markets and is expanding into new regions and connected commodities. The company focuses on enhancing market efficiency and supporting the transition to renewable energy sources.

Dare leverages proprietary technology and data science to optimize trading strategies and risk management. Its advanced technology program, Drama, accelerates the development of low-carbon infrastructure. The company also emphasizes talent development through structured programs for aspiring trading professionals. With a commitment to innovation and employee recognition, Dare fosters a dynamic workplace culture that encourages initiative and open communication.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '3', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/1117.png', 'true', 'Medium-sized company', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', null, null, null), ('850', 'Paradigm', 'Paradigm Communication Systems Limited', 'https://www.paracomm.co.uk/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/paradigm-comms/', 'Paradigm Communication Systems Ltd is a UK-based provider of satellite communications solutions with over 25 years of experience. The company specializes in designing, integrating, manufacturing, and delivering advanced satellite terminals and earth stations. Their mission is to simplify satellite communications, making them versatile, portable, and rugged for military, government, non-governmental organizations, and commercial customers worldwide.

Paradigm offers a range of ruggedized satellite communication terminals, including the MANTA, HORNET, and SWARM models. These products feature advanced modem technology and are designed for quick deployment in extreme environments. The Paradigm Interface Module (PIM®) enhances performance and integration, while their satellite solutions are known for their lightweight and compact design, allowing for rapid setup and operation in the field. The company serves a diverse customer base, focusing on secure communications for defense, humanitarian efforts, and business continuity in challenging conditions.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/958.png', 'true', 'Small company', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', 'greenhouse', 'paradigm', null), ('851', 'Showpad', 'Showpad Ltd', 'https://www.showpad.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/showpad/', 'Showpad is a technology company based in Ghent, Belgium, that specializes in mobile sales enablement applications. The company develops software that helps businesses create and manage customized sales and presentation applications. These applications allow sales teams to efficiently distribute content to tablets and other mobile devices, enhancing customer engagement during sales interactions.

