Scopely specializes in free-to-play games across various genres, including casual, midcore, and strategy. Its portfolio features original titles and games based on popular intellectual properties, such as *Star Trek™ Fleet Command*, *MARVEL Strike Force*, *MONOPOLY GO!*, and *Stumble Guys*. The company is known for its strong live operations and analytics, supported by its proprietary technology platform, Playgami. Scopely has achieved significant growth through strategic acquisitions and has surpassed $1 billion in lifetime revenues, making it the second-largest mobile video game developer globally by revenue as of 2024. In 2023, Scopely was acquired by Savvy Games Group, further enhancing its position in the gaming industry.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '17', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/1262.png', 'true', 'Very large company', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', 'greenhouse', 'scopely', null), ('860', 'JustPark', 'JustPark Parking Limited', 'https://www.justpark.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/justpark/', 'JustPark is a technology company founded in 2006 by Anthony Eskinazi, specializing in smart parking solutions. The company operates an app and platform that allows drivers to find, reserve, and pay for parking spaces easily. JustPark connects users with over 45,000 parking locations across the UK, including car parks, supermarkets, and municipal parking. With more than 14 million users and over 2 million bookings annually, JustPark maintains a high customer satisfaction rating.

The company offers advanced cashless payment technology and digital pay-on-foot machines, partnering with local authorities and providing solutions to over 300 hotels and property management companies. Following its merger with ParkHub in 2024, JustPark expanded its services to North America, supporting large venues and event operators. JustPark serves a diverse range of customers, including individual drivers, space owners, local authorities, and businesses, making it a comprehensive platform for parking reservations and management.', 'Sponsorship can be offered for some roles.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/102.png', 'true', 'Medium-sized company', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', 'workable', 'justpark', null), ('861', '32Co', 'BBLHD Ltd', 'https://www.32co.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/32co/', '32Co is a healthcare technology company based in London, England, founded in 2021. The company focuses on enhancing access to specialist-grade orthodontic care by connecting general dentists with orthodontic specialists through a collaborative digital platform. This innovative approach allows everyday dentists to deliver specialist orthodontic treatments locally, minimizing the need for patient referrals and reducing wait times and costs.

The platform facilitates real-time collaboration between general dentists and top orthodontists in the UK, addressing the shortage of orthodontic specialists and the high prevalence of misaligned teeth. 32Co offers a digital system for case planning and treatment oversight, along with an intensive orthodontist-led training program for dentists. This training equips them with the skills to manage clear aligner cases effectively. Additionally, 32Co is recognized for its clear aligner dentistry network, providing resources and expertise to improve the predictability and efficiency of orthodontic care.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '3', '1', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/480.png', 'true', 'Medium-sized company', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', 'lever', '32Co', null), ('862', 'SingleStore', 'SingleStore UK Limited', 'https://www.singlestore.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/singlestore/', 'SingleStore is a distributed relational SQL database management system designed for high-speed data ingestion, transaction processing, and query execution. Founded in 2011, the company rebranded from MemSQL to SingleStore in 2020 to emphasize its focus on unifying operational and analytical workloads. 

The SingleStore platform supports various data types, including relational, JSON, geospatial, key-value vector, and time-series data. It efficiently handles both Online Transaction Processing (OLTP) and Online Analytical Processing (OLAP) workloads, enabling real-time analytics. Key offerings include SingleStoreDB Self-Managed, which allows customers to deploy and manage the database themselves, and SingleStore Helios, a fully managed cloud-native service that combines transactional and analytical capabilities.

Headquartered in San Francisco, SingleStore has seen significant growth, achieving $100 million in Annual Recurring Revenue by the end of 2023. The company serves a diverse range of global enterprises, including notable users like Uber and John L. Scott, and has established partnerships with major cloud providers to enhance deployment options.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/983.png', 'true', 'Large company', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', 'greenhouse', 'singlestore', null), ('863', 'Influencer', 'Influencer Ltd', 'https://www.influencer.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/influencer/', 'Influencer is a global influencer marketing company founded in 2017 by Ben Jeffries and Caspar Lee. The company specializes in providing end-to-end influencer marketing solutions, combining technology and human expertise to help brands execute impactful campaigns on social media platforms. With a network of over 120 social experts across five key locations, Influencer emphasizes a data-driven approach, focusing on deep analytics and insights to enhance campaign effectiveness.

The company maintains strategic partnerships with major social media platforms like TikTok, Meta, and YouTube, which helps expand the reach of their campaigns. Influencer serves a high-profile client base, including 95% of top-tier global brands featured in Ad Age, and collaborates with leading media agencies. Their diverse team of creatives, marketers, strategists, and data experts drives innovation and execution in the influencer marketing space, empowering both creators and brands to achieve their goals.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '3', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/206.png', 'true', 'Medium-sized company', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', 'teamtailor', 'influencer', null), ('864', 'Permutive', 'Permutive Limited', 'https://permutive.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/permutive/', 'Permutive is a technology company focused on privacy-first data management and audience activation solutions for publishers, advertisers, agencies, and retail media leaders. Its platform allows clients to utilize first-party data to create real-time audience segments, optimize advertising campaigns, and enhance outcomes while ensuring user privacy and consent.

The core offering, the Permutive Audience Platform, employs patented on-device technology to capture various data types without exposing personally identifiable information (PII). This enables publishers to analyze and model data for improved advertising performance and revenue. For advertisers, Permutive connects them with over 150 trusted publishers, providing access to high-quality, privacy-safe audiences and insights into audience behavior across the open web.

Key features include a Data Management Platform for enriching first-party data, a secure Data Clean Room for compliant data collaboration, and AI-enriched Curated Audiences for precise targeting. Permutive''s platform supports seamless audience activation and has been recognized with multiple industry awards, reflecting its commitment to maximizing audience reach and advertising effectiveness in a privacy-compliant manner.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '3', '6', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/265.png', 'true', 'Medium-sized company', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', 'ashby', 'https://api.ashbyhq.com/posting-api/job-board/permutive', null), ('865', 'IMPOSSIBREW', 'IMPOSSIBREW Limited', 'https://impossibrew.co.uk/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/impossibrewbeer/', 'IMPOSSIBREW® is a UK-based functional beer startup founded in 2021. The company specializes in innovative non-alcoholic beers that serve as relaxing alternatives to traditional alcoholic beverages. Their mission is to create the world’s most relaxing alcohol alternatives by combining traditional brewing techniques with active nootropic ingredients.

