Equifax UK provides a range of services, including detailed credit reporting and scoring, risk management analytics, and data solutions. It aggregates data from over 100 sources into its Equifax Cloud™ platform, ensuring compliance and advanced data governance. The company also supports consumers in managing their credit history and offers educational resources to simplify complex data. With a diverse client base across various industries, Equifax UK plays a vital role in helping organizations make informed credit and identity decisions.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/1067.png', 'true', 'Large company', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', null, null, null), ('900', 'Financial Times', 'The Financial Times Ltd', 'https://ft.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/financial-times/', 'The Financial Times (FT) is a British daily newspaper that focuses on business, financial, and economic news and analysis. Founded in 1888 and based in London, it is known for its distinctive salmon pink pages. The FT is owned by Nikkei Inc. since 2015 and has a global editorial presence with offices in Britain, the US, and continental Europe.

The FT publishes a daily print edition and has a strong digital platform, catering to a global audience. It offers a weekend edition that includes expanded coverage of international news and lifestyle sections. The newspaper also produces over 100 special reports annually on various topics relevant to business professionals. Group subscription packages are available for organizations, providing comprehensive access to its content.

