Cognitive Credit aims to innovate within a market that has been slow to adopt automation. The company values diverse talent and seeks to expand its offerings and client base, aspiring to become a leading data and analytics service in the global credit markets.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/1213.png', 'true', 'Small company', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', null, null, null), ('904', 'Watershed', 'Watershed Technology Limited', 'https://watershed.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/watershedclimate/', 'Watershed is an enterprise sustainability platform founded in 2019, focused on helping companies decarbonize and advance the climate economy. The company aims to assist its customers in reducing or removing 500 megatonnes of CO2 equivalent by 2030, which represents about 1% of annual global emissions. With nearly 400 employees, Watershed operates globally from offices in San Francisco, New York, London, and Sydney.

