The company offers a range of credit and liquidity products tailored for payment companies. These include Merchant Advance, which provides upfront funding by allowing businesses to sell a portion of their future payment receivables; Instant Payout, which gives clients immediate access to funds; Settlement Pre-funding, which ensures smooth operations by bridging settlement cycles; and Custom Payment Liquidity, designed to optimize cash flow for unique business models. SAPI''s mission is to drive growth in the payment ecosystem by enabling faster money movements and real-time liquidity solutions for millions of businesses worldwide.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '3', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/1210.png', 'true', 'Medium-sized company', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', 'bamboohr', 'sapi', null), ('910', 'Simprints', 'Simprints Technology Ltd', 'https://www.simprints.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/simprints-technology-ltd/', 'Simprints is a non-profit technology company founded in 2015 at the University of Cambridge. It focuses on improving global development outcomes through biometric identification solutions designed for low-resource environments. The company aims to enhance the delivery of essential services like healthcare and aid distribution, ensuring that resources reach the intended beneficiaries.

