Ascend serves a global clientele of gene and cell therapy developers, including biotech and pharmaceutical companies. The company collaborates closely with clients to guide products from clinical trials to commercialization, balancing yield and quality in the development of life-saving therapies.', 'The company rarely offers sponsorship but has done so in the past.', '3', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/1172.png', 'true', 'Medium-sized company', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', 'workable', 'ascend-advanced-therapies', null), ('918', 'Proportunity', 'Proportunity Ltd', 'https://www.proportunity.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/proportunity/', 'Proportunity is a London-based fintech and proptech company founded in 2016 by Vadim Toader and Stefan Boronea. The company aims to make home ownership accessible, particularly for millennials facing challenges in affording homes through traditional financing. Proportunity''s mission is to help 1 million people become homeowners by 2030 by offering innovative home financing solutions that address the affordability gap in the housing market.

