The company specializes in creating hardware-agnostic quantum software, collaborating with major quantum hardware providers like Google, IBM, and Rigetti. Phasecraft''s algorithms can enhance computational efficiency significantly, addressing complex challenges in materials discovery, chemical simulations, and optimization tasks. With a team of around 30 researchers and offices in London, Bristol, and Washington DC, Phasecraft is well-positioned to drive innovation in quantum technologies.

