ZOE (Health Science & Nutrition) focuses on personalized nutrition using digital technologies and machine learning. It offers a program based on at-home tests and expert advice, along with supplements and nutrition coaching, primarily targeting consumers in the U.S. and UK interested in optimizing their metabolic health.', 'The company will only sponsor visas for certain roles. These will be assessed on a case-by-case basis. Applicants should ask at the time of application.', '3', '5', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/365.png', 'true', 'Large company', '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', 'ashby', 'https://api.ashbyhq.com/posting-api/job-board/zoe', null), ('948', 'Opensignal', 'OpenSignal Limited', 'https://www.opensignal.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/opensignal/', 'Opensignal is a global leader in mobile network analytics, founded in 2010 and headquartered in London, UK. The company specializes in measuring the real-world mobile network experience through crowdsourced data from billions of on-device measurements. This approach provides an accurate view of network performance, focusing on metrics such as 4G/5G availability, download speeds, and video streaming quality.

Opensignal''s mission is to enhance the telecommunications industry by offering customer-centric insights that help telecom operators, regulators, and analysts make informed decisions. The company provides various services, including the Global Network Excellence Index, market performance insights, and cloud-based analytics solutions. Opensignal serves a diverse clientele, including major telecom operators and industry analysts in over 60 countries, and is recognized for its independent reports on mobile network performance.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/937.png', 'true', 'Large company', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', null, null, null), ('949', 'Funding Circle', 'Funding Circle Ltd', 'https://www.fundingcircle.com/uk/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/funding-circle/', 'Funding Circle UK is a financial technology company founded in 2010 that specializes in lending services for small and medium-sized enterprises (SMEs). Established by Samir Desai, James Meekings, and Andrew Mullinger, the company aims to improve access to finance for small businesses by connecting them directly with investors. Initially a peer-to-peer lending platform, Funding Circle has shifted its focus to institutional lending since 2022, facilitating loans that support business growth.

The company operates an online marketplace where SMEs can apply for loans, and investors can fund these loans. This model allows businesses to access capital more efficiently than traditional bank lending. Funding Circle offers business loans with transparent pricing and flexible terms, as well as tools for investors to manage their portfolios. With operations in the UK, US, Germany, Spain, and the Netherlands, Funding Circle has facilitated billions in loans, helping thousands of businesses thrive. The company is headquartered in London and is listed on the London Stock Exchange under the ticker FCH.', 'The only roles being sponsored are "extremely senior" and "technical" roles.', '1', '27', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/455.png', 'true', 'Large company', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', 'ashby', 'https://api.ashbyhq.com/posting-api/job-board/fundingcircle', null), ('950', 'LOGOS Legal Services', 'Logos Legal Services Ltd', 'https://www.logos.is/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/logos-legal-services/', 'LOGOS Legal Services is a fully integrated international law firm with office in Reykjavik.  LOGOS Legal Services is the exclusive member firm for Iceland of Lex Mundi, the world´s leading network of independent law firms.	

