DICE operates internationally, selling tickets in various markets, including the UK, US, and Australia. The company has raised over $120 million in Series-C funding and has been appointed the primary ticketing partner for the iconic London venue Alexandra Palace.', 'Sponsorship can be offered for certain roles and locations. It isn''t clear which roles these are.', '3', '8', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/221.png', 'true', 'Large company', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', 'greenhouse', 'dicefm-careers', null), ('956', 'Klaviyo', 'Klaviyo Ltd', 'https://www.klaviyo.com/uk/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/klaviyo/', 'Klaviyo is a technology company based in Boston, Massachusetts, founded in 2012. It specializes in marketing automation, focusing on email and SMS marketing solutions tailored for e-commerce businesses. Klaviyo''s platform helps brands build direct and personalized relationships with their customers through a robust customer relationship management (CRM) system.

