Headquartered in Cardiff, Wales, with an office in Amsterdam, Sonovate provides embedded finance and payment solutions, swift credit decisions, same-day funding, credit insurance, and debt collection services. Its platform also features timesheet and workflow automation, credit control, and client credit checks, helping recruitment agencies manage cash flow and reduce administrative burdens. Sonovate empowers recruitment and consultancy businesses with tailored financial solutions that combine technology and expert service, enabling them to scale confidently while efficiently managing payment deadlines and operational workflows.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '3', '1', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/85.png', 'true', 'Medium-sized company', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', 'teamtailor', 'sonovate', null), ('960', 'Pixability', 'Pixability Ltd', 'https://www.pixability.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/pixability/', 'Pixability is a video advertising technology company that focuses on optimizing large advertising campaigns primarily on YouTube and Connected TV platforms. Founded in 2008 by MIT graduate Bettina Hein, the company has become a leader in YouTube advertising by utilizing advanced data science and proprietary technology to help brands maximize the value of their video content.

