Pixability serves a diverse client base, including well-known brands and advertising agencies, and has been recognized on the Inc. 500 list of America’s fastest-growing private companies. Its innovative approach and commitment to data-driven results position it as a significant player in the digital video advertising market.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/962.png', 'true', 'Medium-sized company', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', 'greenhouse', 'pixability', null), ('961', 'Amplience', 'Amplience (UK) Limited', 'https://amplience.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/amplience/', 'Amplience is a technology company founded in 2008, specializing in digital experience management. The company helps brands create personalized and engaging shopping experiences across various digital channels using AI-driven content solutions. 

