Headquartered in London, UK, Amplience operates as a private limited company and continues to evolve its offerings to meet the needs of the digital commerce landscape. The company values speed, responsibility, trust, and collaboration in its approach to innovation and customer success.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '3', '2', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/1219.png', 'true', 'Medium-sized company', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', 'pinpoint', 'amplience', null), ('962', 'Isla', 'Islacare Ltd', 'https://isla.health/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/islahealth/', 'Isla Health is a London-based healthcare technology company founded in 2019 by Pete Hansell and James Jurkiewicz. The company specializes in a digital pathway platform that supports healthcare providers in delivering remote and connected patient care. This platform offers real-time insights into patients'' conditions, enabling clinicians to monitor and intervene proactively, which enhances decision-making and improves patient outcomes.

Isla''s platform supports over 40 medical specialties and provides end-to-end digital pathway management, facilitating effective remote patient monitoring. The technology is widely adopted across more than 30 NHS trusts in the UK, helping healthcare providers manage increasing patient demand and transition to remote care models. As a Certified B Corporation, Isla is committed to high standards of social and environmental performance, aiming to create a fairer and more sustainable healthcare system. The company values transparency, sustainability, and social impact, focusing on improving healthcare for providers, patients, and the wider community.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '3', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/80.png', 'true', 'Small company', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', 'teamtailor', 'isla', null), ('964', 'Quantum Dice', 'Quantum Dice Limited', 'https://www.quantum-dice.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/quantum-dice/', 'Quantum Dice is a photonics technology company based in Oxford, UK, founded in 2020 as a spin-out from the University of Oxford. The company specializes in developing device-independent, self-certifying quantum random number generators (QRNGs) using their patented DISC™ protocol. This technology generates verifiably true, unbiased random numbers by leveraging the fundamental properties of light, which is vital for enhancing security in encryption and various computational applications.

The core offering of Quantum Dice includes QRNG devices that provide secure random numbers for encryption and key generation, crucial for robust information security. Their technology is also applicable in sectors such as simulation and artificial intelligence, where high-quality randomness is essential. Quantum Dice collaborates with industry partners like Thales to integrate their QRNG technology into hardware security modules, enhancing security features through quantum entropy as a service. The company focuses on manufacturing electronic components and conducting research and development in natural sciences and engineering.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/1291.png', 'true', 'Small company', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', 'greenhouse', 'dicefm-careers', null), ('965', 'nPlan', 'nPlan Limited', 'https://nplan.io/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/nplan/', 'nPlan is a technology company founded in 2017, specializing in artificial intelligence and machine learning for construction and infrastructure project management. Headquartered in London, with offices in Austin and Sydney, nPlan serves clients globally across North America, Europe, Asia, and Australia.

The company offers a suite of AI-powered solutions that enhance project management at various stages. Their tools include Plan, which generates and edits project schedules; Assure, providing detailed forecasts of uncertainty; De-risk, identifying potential risks early; and Deliver, offering dashboards for tracking project progress and risks. These solutions cater to project owners and contractors in sectors such as energy, transportation, and public infrastructure, enabling them to make informed decisions and improve project outcomes.

nPlan''s innovative platform is built on a vast dataset of historical project schedules, allowing for precise risk analysis and forecasting. The company promotes a collaborative work culture focused on leveraging data and AI to address complex challenges in the industry.', 'The company offers sponsorship alongside many of its roles. We have excluded any that definitely cannot be.', '1', '7', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/433.png', 'true', 'Small company', '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', 'breezy', 'nplan', null), ('966', 'Prosek Partners', 'Prosek UK Limited', 'https://www.prosek.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/prosek-partners/', 'Prosek Partners is an independent public relations, communications, and marketing firm that specializes in the financial and professional services sectors. The company provides a comprehensive range of integrated communications solutions aimed at building, amplifying, protecting, and engaging client brands worldwide. With offices in the U.S., London, and the Middle East, Prosek Partners operates on a global scale and is recognized for its creativity and marketing expertise.

