The agency focuses on designing brands that create emotional and cultural impact. Their services include brand strategy, brand design systems, brand engagement, and brand effectiveness. They also have specialized teams dedicated to sectors like Gaming & Entertainment, Sustainability, and Industrial Design. Design Bridge and Partners serves a diverse range of prestigious clients, including NASA Artemis, Unilever, Coca-Cola, and Mastercard. The company is recognized for its strong workplace culture, emphasizing growth, inclusivity, and collaboration, and is celebrated for its creative excellence in the industry.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/994.png', 'true', 'Very large company', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', 'greenhouse', 'designbridge', null), ('968', 'Cognizant', 'Cognizant Worldwide Limited', 'https://www.cognizant.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/cognizant/', 'Cognizant Technology Solutions Corporation is a prominent multinational IT consulting and outsourcing company, founded in 1994 in Chennai, India. Originally part of Dun & Bradstreet, it became independent in 1996 and is now headquartered in Teaneck, New Jersey. Cognizant is publicly traded on NASDAQ under the ticker CTSH and is included in major indices like the NASDAQ-100 and Fortune 500.

Cognizant provides a wide range of services, including IT consulting, digital transformation, application development, and business process outsourcing. The company specializes in industry-specific solutions for sectors such as financial services, healthcare, manufacturing, and retail. Its offerings also encompass cloud services, data analytics, automation, and cybersecurity. With a focus on long-term partnerships, Cognizant aims to help large enterprises modernize their IT infrastructure and optimize business processes through innovative technology solutions.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/1085.png', 'true', 'Very large company', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', 'smartrecruiters', 'cognizant', null), ('969', 'Elliptic', 'Elliptic Enterprises Limited', 'https://www.elliptic.co/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/ellipticco/', 'Elliptic is a British blockchain analytics company founded in 2013, with headquarters in London and additional offices in New York and Singapore. The company specializes in cryptoasset compliance, financial crime risk management, and forensic investigation software. Elliptic was the first to develop anti-money laundering (AML) and sanctions compliance tools specifically for cryptoassets, helping financial institutions, crypto businesses, and government agencies detect and prevent financial crime in the digital asset ecosystem.

Elliptic offers a comprehensive suite of solutions, including tools for AML compliance, sanctions screening, and transaction monitoring across over 50 blockchains. Their blockchain investigation tools assist in tracing illicit activity, while real-time token screening and wallet monitoring help detect suspicious behavior. The company also provides data and intelligence feeds integrated into client workflows and offers tailored training resources for compliance teams and law enforcement. Recognized as a Technology Pioneer by the World Economic Forum, Elliptic is committed to protecting crypto customers and enabling the safe growth of the crypto economy.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '28', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/559.png', 'true', 'Medium-sized company', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', 'ashby', 'https://api.ashbyhq.com/posting-api/job-board/elliptic', null), ('970', 'Objective', 'Objective Corporation UK Ltd', 'https://www.objective.co.uk/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/objective-corporation/', 'We create software to make a difference. To help government shift to being completely digital. Where our customers can work from anywhere; with access to information, governance guaranteed and security assured.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '3', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/949.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', 'lever', 'objective', null), ('971', 'Peckwater Brands', 'Peckwater Investments Ltd', 'https://www.peckwaterbrands.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/peckwater-brands/', 'Peckwater Brands is Europe''s largest virtual food brand operator, founded in 2019 and based in London, UK. The company specializes in creating delivery-only, data-driven virtual food brands that partner with existing hospitality businesses. This model allows restaurants, bars, and cafés to optimize their kitchen capacity and increase revenue by running multiple virtual brands alongside their existing menus.

Peckwater Brands develops fully-serviced food concepts that can be added to current operations without requiring additional kitchen space or significant upfront investments. Utilizing data analytics, the company quickly designs and launches new brands, often bringing them to market in under a month. With over 600 virtual food brands across Europe, the USA, and the Middle East, Peckwater offers a diverse range of cuisines, including burgers, Korean fried chicken, and tacos. The company aims to empower hospitality operators and meet the growing demand for food delivery services through its innovative franchise model.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '3', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/377.png', 'true', 'Medium-sized company', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', null, null, null), ('972', 'Emitwise', 'Emitwise Limited', 'https://emitwise.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/emitwise/', 'Emitwise is a carbon management platform tailored for manufacturing businesses and complex supply chains. Based in the London Borough of Southwark, United Kingdom, Emitwise has been a certified B Corporation since February 2022. The platform leverages extensive carbon accounting expertise and advanced machine learning technology to help companies accurately measure, track, and reduce their carbon footprint, with a particular emphasis on Scope 3 emissions.

The services offered by Emitwise include carbon footprint management, which provides detailed insights into emissions across the supply chain, and Procurewise, which focuses on managing supply chain emissions. Procurewise features tools like a database of primary emission factors, supplier engagement management, and carbon calculators, assisting suppliers in setting Science-Based Targets and creating actionable decarbonization pathways. Emitwise''s machine learning technology automates emissions data calculations, ensuring accuracy and efficiency in processing large datasets. 

Emitwise supports businesses in achieving significant reductions in their carbon emissions, with many customers setting net-zero targets and taking the Climate Pledge. The platform is recognized for its innovative approach and commitment to climate action.', 'Sponsorship can be offered for some roles.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/413.png', 'true', 'Small company', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', 'lever', 'emitwise', null), ('973', 'Altium', 'Altium UK Limited', 'https://www.altium.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/altium/', 'Altium is a global provider of software solutions for designing and realizing printed circuit boards (PCBs) and electronic systems. Founded in 1985, the company has evolved from its early days with the DOS-based Protel PCB tool to a comprehensive platform that supports the entire electronics creation process.

Altium''s flagship product, Altium Designer, offers a robust platform for PCB design, including schematic capture, PCB layout, and 3D visualization. The company also provides Altium 365, a cloud-based platform that enhances collaboration and productivity in the electronics design ecosystem. Additionally, Altium has acquired Octopart, an electronic parts search engine, and Ciiva, a cloud-based parts management solution, to further streamline the design and manufacturing process.

Altium serves a diverse range of industries, including aerospace, automotive, consumer electronics, and industrial automation. Its mission is to empower innovation by connecting PCB designers, part suppliers, and manufacturers, facilitating efficient design processes and accelerating the development of electronic products.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '3', '10', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/819.png', 'true', 'Very large company', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', 'greenhouse', 'altium', null), ('974', 'Learnerbly', 'Enternships Limited', 'https://www.learnerbly.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/learnerbly/', 'Learnerbly is a London-based Learning & Development (L&D) marketplace founded in 2016 by Rajeeb Dey MBE. The platform provides employees with access to a curated selection of learning resources from over 200 top content providers, including books, courses, coaching, and e-learning subscriptions. Learnerbly empowers employees to take charge of their personal development by offering personal learning budgets and guiding them to resources tailored to their preferences and roles.

The platform focuses on facilitating self-directed learning within organizations, connecting employees to expertly curated content from leading providers like Blinkist, Masterclass, and Pluralsight. This model allows companies to pay only for the content consumed, leading to higher engagement rates and better return on investment. Learnerbly also reduces administrative burdens for HR teams with a fully managed service that integrates with existing HR systems, supporting a wide range of professional development needs across various roles.

