Logically serves a diverse clientele, including governments, NGOs, and businesses, helping them navigate complex online discourse and manage reputational risks effectively.', 'The company has no more Certificates of Sponsorship available for this year (2024).', '2', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/387.png', 'true', 'Medium-sized company', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', 'bamboohr', 'logically', null), ('983', 'Ezra', 'Adecco UK Limited', 'https://helloezra.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/ezracoaching/', 'EZRA Coaching is a global coaching company that offers virtual coaching solutions for organizations aiming to enhance their workforce. Operating under LHH and part of the Adecco Group, EZRA connects employees with International Coaching Federation (ICF) accredited coaches through an app-based platform. This platform focuses on building leadership skills, improving performance, and increasing employee retention.

The core offering includes unlimited 1:1 coaching for professional development, focused development interventions lasting 8 to 10 weeks, and tailored executive coaching programs. The platform supports global accessibility with virtual sessions available in multiple languages and time zones, and in-person sessions in select locations. EZRA uses a data-driven approach with its proprietary EZRA Measure™ tool to track progress and measure the impact of coaching on performance and retention.

EZRA also provides project management expertise, strategy workshops, HRIS integrations, and a dedicated client marketing team to enhance coaching engagement. The company recruits a global network of qualified coaches, ensuring a personalized coaching experience tailored to each organization''s needs.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '3', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/909.png', 'true', 'Very large company', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', 'greenhouse', 'ezra', null), ('984', 'Brave', 'Brave Software Europe Ltd', 'https://brave.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/brave-software/', 'Brave is a technology company based in San Francisco, founded in 2015 by Brendan Eich and Brian Bondy. The company focuses on developing privacy-oriented internet tools, including the Brave Browser and Brave Search, aimed at enhancing user privacy and browsing speed.

The Brave Browser is an open-source web browser that blocks third-party ads and trackers by default, resulting in faster page loads. It features privacy protections like anti-fingerprinting and a private browsing mode integrated with the Tor network. Brave Search is a privacy-respecting search engine that does not collect user data and operates independently. Additionally, Brave offers a cryptocurrency-based rewards system using Basic Attention Token (BAT), allowing users to earn tokens by viewing privacy-respecting ads.

Brave''s products cater to privacy-conscious users, content creators, and advertisers looking for alternatives to traditional ad models. The company aims to reshape the online experience by prioritizing user control and transparency.', 'The company is globally remote and rarely offers sponsorship.', '3', '1', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/832.png', 'true', 'Medium-sized company', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', 'greenhouse', 'brave', null), ('985', 'LaunchDarkly', 'Launchdarkly Ltd', 'https://launchdarkly.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/launchdarkly/mycompany/', 'LaunchDarkly is a feature management platform founded in 2014, based in Oakland, California. The company provides an end-to-end feature flagging platform that enables software development teams to launch, control, and measure digital products with agility and stability. This platform allows developers to manage software releases by toggling features on or off without the need for redeploying code.

The core capabilities of LaunchDarkly include gradual rollouts, dark launches, and targeted feature releases. These features help teams reduce risk and enhance the stability of software deployments. The platform supports A/B testing and user segmentation, allowing companies to test new features with specific user groups and quickly roll back any problematic changes. LaunchDarkly serves a diverse range of customers, from small businesses to large enterprises, and emphasizes speed and reliability in software development. With over 4,000 customers, the company has grown significantly, reflecting its commitment to improving software release stability and developer agility.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '3', '5', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/879.png', 'true', 'Large company', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', 'greenhouse', 'launchdarkly', null), ('986', 'intent.ly', 'intent.ly Global Ltd', 'https://intent.ly/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/intent-ly/', 'intent.ly is a data-driven shopper journey optimization platform founded in 2014 and headquartered in London, UK. The company focuses on helping online retailers enhance conversion rates from their existing website traffic. With a team of over 50 conversion rate optimization experts, intent.ly operates globally across various regions, including the US, EMEA, and APAC.

The company offers personalized engagement tools and intelligent overlays designed to convert non-buying visitors into customers. Their key services include onsite overlay technology to engage users showing exit intent, a universal site messaging tool for promotions, email remarketing, and deep insights into shopper journeys. intent.ly operates on a performance-based cost per acquisition model, allowing clients to pay only for successful conversions without additional fees. They partner with over 150 affiliate networks and agencies, serving more than 1,000 retailers, from large enterprises to small businesses, to improve onsite conversions and increase average order values.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/919.png', 'true', 'Small company', '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', 'bamboohr', 'intently', null), ('987', 'Moloco', 'Moloco UK Limited', 'https://www.moloco.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/moloco/', 'Moloco is a global machine learning company founded in 2013 by engineers from Google and Oracle. Headquartered in Silicon Valley, it operates eight offices worldwide. The company focuses on making advanced machine learning accessible to businesses of all sizes, helping them unlock the value of their first-party data for digital growth.

Moloco specializes in mobile adtech and performance advertising. Its flagship platform, Moloco Cloud, optimizes mobile app monetization, user acquisition, and in-app purchases using big data and machine learning. The company also offers a Demand Side Platform (DSP) that processes ad requests at scale, a Retail Media Platform launched in 2022, and an ad fraud detection service called DoubleCheck. Moloco serves a diverse range of clients, including mobile app developers, retailers, and video streaming services, reaching over 10 billion devices globally. The leadership team emphasizes innovation and data privacy, fostering a culture recognized for its inclusivity and commitment to social responsibility.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '3', '7', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/894.png', 'true', 'Large company', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', 'greenhouse', 'moloco', null), ('989', 'Ziff Davis', 'Ziff Davis International Ltd', 'https://www.ziffdavis.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/ziff-davis-inc/', 'Ziff Davis, Inc. is a digital media and internet company founded in 1927. Initially a publisher of aviation magazines, it has evolved into a leading authority in technology media, focusing on technology, gaming, and health-oriented content. The company operates a diverse portfolio of websites and digital brands that provide news, reviews, and information for technology consumers and professionals.

Ziff Davis offers digital media and publishing services through numerous technology-focused websites that deliver editorial content, product reviews, and buying guides. It also engages in online shopping and lead generation, connecting advertisers with targeted audiences in the tech and health sectors. The company has expanded into gaming media and cybersecurity services, enhancing its digital presence. With reported revenues of approximately $1.40 billion in 2024, Ziff Davis continues to adapt and thrive in the digital landscape, serving a global audience of tech enthusiasts and professionals.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/939.png', 'true', 'Very large company', '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', null, null, null), ('990', 'Sona', 'Sona Technologies Ltd', 'https://www.getsona.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/getsona/', 'Sona is a London-based startup focused on workforce management for deskless workers, who make up about 80% of the global workforce. Founded by Ben Dixon, Steffen Wulff Petersen, and Oli Johnson, Sona offers an AI-driven platform that integrates scheduling, HR, payroll, and employee engagement specifically for frontline industries like hospitality. The platform serves over 100,000 users and aims to replace outdated systems with user-friendly technology to enhance efficiency and revenue growth.

Sona''s platform includes several specialized components: the Operations Cloud for smart scheduling and time tracking, the HR Cloud for managing employee data, the Engagement Cloud for monitoring team morale, the Finance Cloud for payroll processing, and the AI Cloud for forecasting and auto-scheduling. Additionally, the Employee App provides tools for shift management and communication tailored for frontline staff. Sona emphasizes collaboration and rapid execution, positioning itself as a leader in modern workforce management solutions.', 'The company is open to sponsoring the right candidate.', '1', '8', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/38.png', 'false', 'Medium-sized company', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', 'ashby', 'https://api.ashbyhq.com/posting-api/job-board/sona', null), ('991', 'BVNK', 'BVNK Services Limited', 'https://www.bvnk.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/bvnk/', 'BVNK is a global B2B financial technology company founded in 2021. It specializes in enterprise-grade stablecoin payment infrastructure and a digital financial services platform tailored for businesses. BVNK connects traditional banking systems with blockchain technology through a unified API, facilitating the integration of fiat currencies and stablecoins for payments, conversions, and wallet management.

Operating in over 61 countries, BVNK employs more than 200 people across the UK, Europe, and Africa. The company offers multi-currency virtual accounts, enabling businesses to manage funds in various fiat currencies and stablecoins. Its payments infrastructure supports real-time cross-border transactions by integrating traditional payment networks with blockchain technology. BVNK also provides secure wallets, compliance solutions, crypto trading, and treasury management services. The platform is designed for enterprise financial institutions, fintech companies, and other businesses with significant payment processing needs. BVNK is committed to security and regulatory compliance, holding multiple licenses across different jurisdictions.', 'The company only offers sponsorship under exceptional circumstances and offers no guidance on what these circumstances are.', '2', '4', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/299.png', 'true', 'Large company', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', 'greenhouse', 'bvnk', null), ('992', 'Proxymity', 'Proxymity Limited', 'https://www.proxymity.io/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/proxymityic/?originalSubdomain=uk', 'Proxymity is a digital investor communications platform that connects issuers, intermediaries, and investors in real time. Founded by Dean Little and Jonathan Smalley, the company emerged from Citigroup’s innovation program and became independent in 2020. Proxymity is supported by major global financial institutions managing over $200 trillion in assets, including BNY Mellon, Citi, and JP Morgan.

The platform offers a range of digital solutions focused on investor communications and proxy voting. Its digital proxy voting platform allows for real-time transmission of meeting agendas and voting instructions, providing true vote confirmation to investors. The shareholder disclosure platform automates identification requests in compliance with regulations, enhancing efficiency and transparency. Proxymity operates globally, with services in the UK, Australia, New Zealand, and EU markets, and is recognized for its innovative approach in the financial sector, receiving multiple industry awards for its contributions to digital proxy voting and asset servicing technology.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/107.png', 'true', 'Medium-sized company', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', 'bamboohr', 'proxymity', null), ('993', 'Maze', 'Maze.Design Limited', 'https://maze.co/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/mazedesign/', 'Maze is a user research and continuous product discovery platform that helps product teams create user-centric products more efficiently. It allows designers, product managers, and researchers to quickly collect, analyze, and act on user feedback throughout the product development cycle. With over 60,000 teams using the platform, Maze supports rapid feedback collection, enabling insights in hours rather than weeks.

The platform offers usability testing, prototype testing, and customizable surveys for both quantitative and qualitative data collection. It features advanced analytics tools, including heatmaps and performance metrics, to provide a deep understanding of user behavior. Maze also includes collaboration tools for team involvement and integrates with third-party applications for enhanced functionality. Its AI-powered features, such as automated interviews, allow for global research without time zone limitations. Maze is accessible via subscription, making it suitable for organizations at various stages of research maturity.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '3', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/36.png', 'true', 'Medium-sized company', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', 'ashby', 'https://api.ashbyhq.com/posting-api/job-board/mazedesign', null), ('994', 'AiSolve', 'Aisolve Limited', 'https://aisolve.com/', null, 'AiSolve Limited is a technology company based in Brighton, East Sussex, UK, that specializes in artificial intelligence (AI), virtual reality (VR), and mixed reality (MR) solutions. Founded in 2007, AiSolve focuses on creating immersive technologies and innovative applications primarily for the education, training, and out-of-home entertainment sectors. The company has developed proprietary AI-driven platforms and patented VR hardware to enhance learning and training experiences.

AiSolve offers AI-powered educational and training solutions that provide personalized learning experiences tailored to individual needs. Their VR applications create engaging environments that simplify complex subjects and improve knowledge retention. Additionally, AiSolve develops VR and MR products for entertainment, utilizing their AI capabilities to boost user engagement. The company employs standard game engines like Unity and Unreal, while also building custom software to deliver unique solutions.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '3', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/1216.png', 'true', 'Small company', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', null, null, null), ('995', 'Skyral', 'Skyral Group Limited', 'https://skyral.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/skyral/', 'Skyral is a British software company based in London, specializing in advanced modeling and simulation technology for the enterprise, defense, and national security sectors. Founded in June, Skyral develops AI-powered digital twins and synthetic engineering solutions to address complex challenges faced by governments and businesses.

The company offers sophisticated simulation platforms that create detailed digital representations of real-world systems. These tools assist customers in analyzing scenarios, predicting outcomes, and optimizing strategies in uncertain environments. Skyral''s core services include AI-powered digital twins for real-time simulation, advanced synthetic engineering for modeling complex systems, and decision-making simulations that enhance strategic planning through predictive analytics.

