ThoughtSpot offers a suite of products, including ThoughtSpot Analytics, which enables users to query and visualize data using natural language search. Other offerings include ThoughtSpot Embedded for integrating analytics into applications, and Analyst Studio for data analysts to manage complex workflows. The platform supports various data sources and integrates with major cloud data platforms like Snowflake and Google BigQuery. ThoughtSpot aims to empower decision-makers at all levels by providing direct access to data, fostering a more fact-driven world.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '3', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/259.png', 'true', 'Large company', '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', null, null, null), ('1000', 'Porotech', 'Poro Technologies Ltd', 'https://www.porotech.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/porotech/', 'Porotech is a Cambridge University spin-out founded in 2018, specializing in the development and commercialization of a unique porous gallium nitride (GaN) semiconductor material platform called PoroGaN®. This innovation supports advanced microLED display technologies, particularly in the microLED industry, with applications in augmented reality (AR) and wearables.

The company''s core technology, Dynamic Pixel Tuning®, allows for the production of color-tunable microLEDs from a single material and toolchain. This includes the world''s first commercial native red indium gallium nitride (InGaN) LED epiwafer for microLED applications. Porotech provides porous GaN epiwafers for microLED manufacturing and offers technology consultancy and collaboration in microLED display development. The company has formed strategic partnerships with industry leaders, including Foxconn, to enhance its microLED technology and manufacturing capabilities. 

