Zoom provides a range of communication solutions, including Zoom Meetings for video conferencing, Zoom Phone for cloud-based telephony, and Zoom Team Chat for team collaboration. The Zoom App Marketplace enhances productivity by offering integrations with third-party applications. The platform is known for its reliability and scalability, making it suitable for various sectors, including education, healthcare, and business. Zoom serves a diverse customer base, including educational institutions, enterprises, and individual users, and has become a key player in remote work and virtual communication.', null, '3', '9', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/501.png', 'true', 'Very large company', '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', null, null, null), ('1005', 'Thirdfort', 'Thirdfort Limited', 'https://www.thirdfort.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/thirdfort/', 'Thirdfort is a UK-based software company that specializes in client due diligence solutions aimed at protecting regulated professionals and their clients from fraud and money laundering. Founded by Olly Thornton-Berry and Jack Bidgood, the company serves over 1,500 regulated businesses, primarily in the legal and property sectors. Thirdfort''s platform helps these businesses comply with evolving regulations while safeguarding transactions.

