The company offers a range of services designed to help enterprises adapt to technological changes and enhance productivity. Their expertise includes custom software development, capability building, and strategic guidance on digital transformation. NearForm partners with clients throughout the software development lifecycle, focusing on delivering tailored solutions that support organizations in achieving digital maturity. Their client base includes ambitious enterprises and global organizations across various sectors, with a presence in Ireland, the UK, and the US.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '4', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/856.png', 'true', 'Large company', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', 'greenhouse', 'nearform', null), ('1013', 'Edited', 'Stylescape Limited', 'https://edited.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/edited/', 'EDITED is a London-based retail intelligence company founded in 2009 by Geoff Watts and Julia Fowler. The company specializes in AI-powered retail analytics software that enhances decision-making throughout the retail product lifecycle. Its platform combines internal enterprise data with external market signals to improve processes such as product sorting, pricing, inventory replenishment, and targeted marketing campaigns.

