EDITED serves over 200 leading brands and retailers across 40 countries, focusing primarily on major fashion brands. The company has received multiple industry accolades and emphasizes continuous innovation and global expansion, with offices in London, New York, and Texas.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '1', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/27.png', 'true', 'Medium-sized company', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', 'ashby', 'https://api.ashbyhq.com/posting-api/job-board/edited', null), ('1014', 'Fnatic', 'Fnatic Ltd', 'https://fnatic.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/fnatic/', 'Fnatic is a prominent European esports organization founded in 2004 by Sam and Anne Mathews. Headquartered in London, it has established itself as one of the most successful brands in esports, known for its competitive gaming teams and achievements in various game titles, including Counter-Strike, League of Legends, and Dota.

