Refeyn''s core technology allows for direct measurement of molecular mass at the single-molecule level without labels or complex sample preparation. Their product lineup includes the TwoMP Auto, an automated mass photometer; the OneMP, their first commercial device; the SamuxMP Auto, designed for GMP-compliant biotherapeutic manufacturing; and the MassFluidix HC system for advanced studies. Refeyn also provides lifecycle support and maintenance services for its instruments, ensuring customers receive comprehensive assistance. The company is dedicated to fostering innovation and collaboration in the scientific community.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/971.png', 'true', 'Medium-sized company', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', 'greenhouse', 'refeyn', null), ('1016', 'Thrive Networks', 'Thrive Operations Limited', 'https://thrivenextgen.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/thrivenextgen/', 'Thrive is a managed IT service provider based in Concord, Massachusetts, founded in 2000. The company specializes in global cybersecurity, cloud services, and digital transformation for mid-market and sophisticated small to medium-sized businesses. Thrive focuses on delivering high returns on technology investments through standardized and scalable solutions, supported by a client-centric approach.

