The company offers a visual intelligence platform that allows users to create and manage complex business diagrams, timelines, and organizational charts much faster than traditional tools. This platform emphasizes speed and aesthetics, enabling firms to produce on-brand visuals in seconds. It integrates seamlessly with popular office tools such as PowerPoint, Visio, Word, and Excel, making it easy to visualize data and collaborate effectively. Jigsaw serves over 200 organizations globally, including top law firms and leading asset managers, and is supported by experienced professionals in the industry.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/795.png', 'true', 'Medium-sized company', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', 'ashby', 'https://api.ashbyhq.com/posting-api/job-board/jigsaw', null), ('1024', 'Purlos', 'My Digital College Ltd', 'https://www.purlos.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/purlos/?originalSubdomain=uk', 'Purlos is an EdTech software company based in London, UK, founded in 2018. The company aims to empower education providers to connect with students and enhance their learning experiences. Purlos is committed to supporting 10 million students in achieving positive educational or career outcomes by 2030, with a focus on helping learners from disadvantaged backgrounds.

