With a small team of fewer than 25 employees, Purlos focuses on improving student engagement and outcomes through innovative software solutions.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '3', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/184.png', 'true', 'Small company', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', null, null, null), ('1026', 'Cassini', 'Cassini Systems Limited', 'https://cassini.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/cassini-margin-collateral-analytics/', null, 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/1224.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', 'bamboohr', 'cassini', null), ('1030', 'Board', 'Board MIT Ltd', 'https://www.board.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/board/', 'Board is an enterprise software company that specializes in a web-based Enterprise Planning Platform. Founded in 1994, it operates globally with 25 offices and serves over 2,000 organizations, including major companies like H&M, BASF, and Coca-Cola. The platform unifies financial and operational planning, providing tools for forecasting, financial consolidation, reporting, and advanced analytics.

The Enterprise Planning Platform supports various use cases, including financial planning and analysis, supply chain planning, and integrated business planning. It features AI-driven insights and predictive analytics, allowing users to monitor performance and optimize decisions. Board also offers custom application development, enabling users to create tailored solutions that integrate financial and operational data. Customers can choose between cloud deployment on Microsoft Azure or on-premises installations, ensuring flexibility to meet their needs. Board is recognized for its innovation and performance in the enterprise planning software market.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '1', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/563.png', 'true', 'Large company', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', 'bamboohr', 'board', null), ('1031', 'International WELL Building Institute', 'IWBI (UK) Limited', 'https://www.wellcertified.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/iwbi/', 'The International WELL Building Institute (IWBI) is a public benefit corporation dedicated to enhancing health and well-being in buildings, organizations, and communities. It administers the WELL Building Standard, a certification system that emphasizes human health through evidence-based design and operational strategies. Established in 2013, IWBI has certified over 5 billion square feet of space across 130 countries, impacting around 25 million occupants in nearly 74,000 projects.

