In addition to QDID, Crypto Quantique offers QuarkLink, a software platform that enables secure provisioning, connectivity, and lifecycle management for IoT devices across various cloud service providers. The company also provides QRoot Lite, a lightweight root-of-trust IP block designed for resource-constrained IoT devices. Crypto Quantique''s solutions cater to IoT device manufacturers and enterprises, helping them manage device identities and comply with security regulations while ensuring scalable and secure IoT ecosystems.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '1', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/534.png', 'true', 'Small company', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', 'smartrecruiters', 'cryptoquantique', null), ('1045', 'Wise', 'Wise Payments Limited ', 'https://wise.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/wiseaccount/', 'Wise, formerly known as TransferWise, is a British financial technology company based in London. Founded in January 2011 by Kristo Käärmann and Taavet Hinrikus, Wise specializes in international money transfers and cross-border financial services. The company aims to make sending, receiving, and managing money across currencies cheaper, faster, and more transparent.

