Croud offers a wide range of digital marketing services, including pay-per-click (PPC), search engine optimization (SEO), content marketing, programmatic advertising, and analytics. Their expertise also covers brand planning, integrated media, social media, and data-driven marketing. The agency utilizes advanced technologies and automation tools to enhance marketing efficiency and engagement. Croud serves a diverse portfolio of global brands, leveraging its local market knowledge and technology-driven approach to drive measurable growth and return on investment.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '3', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/211.png', 'true', 'Large company', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', null, null, null), ('1072', 'Outreach', 'Outreach Corporation UK Limited', 'https://www.outreach.io/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/outreach-saas/', 'Outreach is a Seattle-based company founded in 2014 that provides an artificial intelligence-powered sales execution platform. This platform is designed to enhance sales engagement, deal management, and pipeline management for teams in various industries, including IT services, financial services, telecommunications, manufacturing, and retail. The company has experienced significant growth, supported by $489 million in funding and a valuation of $4.4 billion after its Series G financing.

The Outreach platform centralizes sales tools and workflows, offering features such as AI-driven forecasting, conversation intelligence, and deal insights. It supports over 90 integrations with popular tools like HubSpot and LinkedIn Sales Navigator, facilitating seamless workflow automation. Outreach also provides tailored professional services, including implementation, platform optimization, and user training, to help customers maximize their use of the platform. The company is led by CEO Abhijit Mitra and a team of executives dedicated to enhancing sales and customer engagement processes.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '7', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/1053.png', 'true', 'Large company', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', 'lever', 'outreach', null), ('1073', 'Carta', 'Vauban Technologies Limited', 'https://carta.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/carta--/', 'Carta, Inc. is a technology company based in San Francisco that specializes in equity management and capitalization table software for private companies, investors, and employees. Founded in 2012, Carta automates the management of company ownership, equity plans, valuations, and compliance, making these processes more efficient and less prone to errors.

The company offers a range of services, including cap table management, equity plan administration, valuations, and fund administration. Its cloud-based platform allows companies to maintain capitalization tables, manage stock options, and generate audit-ready reports. Carta also facilitates secure financial transactions and provides accounting and financial reporting services. With a mission to enhance transparency and accessibility in private markets, Carta serves thousands of venture-backed startups and tracks over $2.5 trillion in equity. The company is committed to diversity and inclusion, aiming to create opportunities for underrepresented groups in the tech industry.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '3', '9', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/335.png', 'true', 'Very large company', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', 'greenhouse', 'carta', null), ('1074', 'GuestReady', 'GuestReady Limited', 'https://www.guestready.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/guestready/', 'GuestReady is a global short-term rental management company founded in 2016 and headquartered in London, UK. It operates in over 70 cities across Europe, the Middle East, and Asia, including the UK, France, Portugal, Spain, Switzerland, UAE, and Malaysia. The company specializes in helping property owners and hosts maximize their rental income through comprehensive property management services tailored for platforms like Airbnb, Booking.com, and Vrbo.

The core services offered by GuestReady include listing creation and optimization, guest communication with 24/7 check-in, professional cleaning, property maintenance, and concierge services. They utilize proprietary technology for online property management, allowing hosts to efficiently monitor and manage their rentals. With a portfolio of over 3,000 homes and a focus on high-quality, professionally managed accommodations, GuestReady serves more than 1.5 million guests. The company also provides a mobile dashboard for hosts to manage pricing and performance easily.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/861.png', 'true', 'Large company', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', 'teamtailor', 'app', null), ('1075', 'Intradiem', 'Intradiem UK Limited', 'https://intradiem.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/intradiem/', 'Intradiem is a software company based in Alpharetta, Georgia, founded in 1995. It specializes in AI-powered workforce management and automation solutions tailored for customer service call centers. Originally established as an e-learning tool, Intradiem has evolved to provide a platform that enables real-time responses to operational events, enhancing how contact centers manage their workforce and customer interactions.

The company offers advanced automation technology that optimizes call center operations. Its core product automates scheduling, real-time adherence, and intraday management of call center agents. Additionally, Intradiem''s solutions streamline routine tasks and workflows, allowing for quicker and more accurate responses to customer needs. The software also enables managers to dynamically respond to changing call volumes and agent availability throughout the day, improving operational agility.

Intradiem serves medium to large enterprises across various industries, focusing on customer service automation and workforce management. The company employs between 100 and 500 people and has raised over $30 million in funding, reflecting its commitment to technology innovation.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '1', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/867.png', 'true', 'Medium-sized company', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', 'greenhouse', 'intradiem', null), ('1077', 'AXON', 'Axon Communications Inc.', 'https://axon-com.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/axon-communications', 'Axon is a global technology company based in Scottsdale, Arizona, focused on personal and public safety solutions. Founded in 1993 by brothers Rick and Tom Smith, Axon aims to "Protect Life" by creating technologies that enhance safety and reduce violence. The company started with the TASER conducted energy weapon, a non-lethal device designed to provide safer alternatives to firearms for law enforcement.

Over the years, Axon has developed a wide range of products and services, including TASER energy weapons, body-worn cameras, in-car cameras, and a cloud-based digital evidence management platform. They also offer software solutions for dispatch, incident reporting, and workflow management, along with training tools like VR-based de-escalation simulators. Axon serves law enforcement agencies, military, private security, and civilian markets, providing innovative technology to improve safety and operational efficiency. With over 4,100 employees, Axon maintains a strong position in the public safety technology market.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '3', '2', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/828.png', 'true', 'Medium-sized company', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-07 12:17:45.62+00', 'greenhouse', 'axonag', null), ('1078', 'Bloom & Wild', 'Bloom and Wild Limited', 'https://www.bloomandwild.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/bloom-&-wild/', 'Bloom & Wild is a prominent online flower and gift delivery company based in the UK, founded in 2013 by Aron Gelbard and Ben Stanway. The company is known for its innovative "letterbox flowers," which are fresh flowers packaged in slim boxes that fit through most letterboxes, allowing for convenient delivery. By sourcing flowers directly from producers in Kenya and Europe, Bloom & Wild ensures high-quality blooms that arrive in bud form, designed to last longer.

The company operates exclusively online and has expanded its offerings to include cakes, candles, and cocktails, aiming to be Europe''s top direct-to-consumer gifting destination. Bloom & Wild utilizes proprietary AI tools for demand forecasting and merchandising, enhancing customer choice while promoting sustainability. With a strong focus on customer experience, the company boasts a high Net Promoter Score (NPS) of over 85% in the UK, reflecting its commitment to customer satisfaction. Bloom & Wild continues to grow internationally, with offices in the Netherlands and France, and employs over 350 people.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '3', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/393.png', 'true', 'Large company', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', 'greenhouse', 'bloom', null), ('1080', 'Ruggable', 'Ruggable UK Ltd', 'https://ruggable.co.uk/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/ruggable/', null, 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '2', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/977.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', 'greenhouse', 'ruggable', null), ('1082', 'V7', 'V7 Ltd', 'https://www.v7labs.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/v7labs/', 'V7 Labs is a London-based AI company that specializes in visual data annotation and document intelligence automation. Founded by Alberto Rizzoli and Simon Edwardsson, the company integrates human knowledge into AI systems to enhance decision-making in fields such as medicine, engineering, and manufacturing. V7 Labs offers a powerful AI training data platform that allows users to annotate images, videos, and volumetric data with features like automatic labeling and model training, significantly reducing data annotation time.

In addition to its core platform, V7 Labs provides V7 Go, an automation tool designed for complex, document-intensive workflows. This platform is tailored for industries such as finance, legal, insurance, and real estate, enabling teams to build intelligent agents that analyze contracts and process claims. V7 Labs operates on Amazon Web Services, ensuring data protection and security while supporting innovation across various sectors. The company aims to improve efficiency and outcomes by bringing human visual knowledge into AI systems.', 'Sponsorship can be offered for most roles, and we have excluded any that definitely cannot be.', '1', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/16.png', 'true', 'Medium-sized company', '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', null, null, null), ('1083', 'Taptap Send', 'Taptap Send UK Limited', 'https://www.taptapsend.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/taptapsend/', 'Taptap Send is a private financial technology company based in London, England, founded in 2015. It offers a mobile money transfer service that simplifies and reduces the cost of sending money internationally, focusing on developing countries in Africa, Asia, and the Caribbean. The company aims to make international remittances cheaper, faster, and more convenient than traditional methods.

By leveraging advanced technology and a network of local banks and mobile money providers, Taptap Send enables secure and rapid mobile-to-mobile money transfers. Its transparent revenue model features small transfer fees that vary by destination, avoiding hidden charges. This approach has helped the company build a loyal user base among individuals sending remittances to underserved markets. Taptap Send is committed to reducing remittance costs to 3%, aligning with the United Nations Sustainable Development Goals, and enhancing financial inclusion globally.', 'The company has limited sponsorship slots.', '4', '13', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/405.png', 'true', 'Large company', '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', 'bamboohr', 'taptap', null), ('1084', 'Pact Coffee', 'Your Grind Ltd', 'https://www.pactcoffee.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/pactcoffee/', 'Pact Coffee is a British speciality coffee company founded in 2012 by Stephen Rapoport. It specializes in sourcing and selling speciality-grade coffee directly from farmers in Central and South America and East Africa. By using a direct-trade model, Pact ensures that farmers receive fair prices, averaging 60% above the Fairtrade base price. The company operates primarily through online subscriptions and also supplies offices, hospitality venues, and supermarkets like Waitrose and Whole Foods Market.

Pact Coffee emphasizes ethical sourcing and sustainability, building long-term relationships with coffee farmers to improve their livelihoods. All coffee is freshly roasted in its Surrey roastery, which became carbon-neutral in 2022. The company offers subscription coffee delivery, B2B supply for businesses, and retail presence in supermarkets. In 2022, Pact Coffee achieved B Corporation certification, reflecting its commitment to social and environmental performance. Overall, Pact Coffee serves ethically conscious consumers and businesses with a focus on quality and traceability.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '3', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/119.png', 'true', 'Medium-sized company', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', 'teamtailor', 'pactcoffee', null), ('1085', 'Greenpeace UK', 'Greenpeace Limited', 'https://www.greenpeace.org.uk/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/greenpeace/', 'Greenpeace UK is the British branch of Greenpeace International, an independent global environmental organization founded in 1971. It is dedicated to environmental protection through non-violent direct action, scientific research, lobbying, and public education. Greenpeace UK addresses urgent environmental issues such as climate change, deforestation, ocean protection, pollution, and sustainable agriculture.

The organization leads campaigns to raise awareness and influence policymakers on environmental matters. It is known for its peaceful protests and advocacy efforts. Greenpeace UK also conducts scientific research to document environmental harm and supports its campaigns with credible evidence. Additionally, it engages in legal actions to uphold environmental laws and educates the public through various events and publications to promote sustainable behavior. Its primary audience includes environmentally conscious individuals, policymakers, corporations, and the general public.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '4', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/860.png', 'true', 'Medium-sized company', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', 'greenhouse', 'greenpeace', null), ('1086', 'Zuora', 'Zuora UK Limited', 'https://www.zuora.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/zuora/', 'Zuora, Inc. is an enterprise software company founded in 2007 and headquartered in Redwood City, California. It specializes in cloud-based subscription management and monetization solutions that help businesses launch, manage, and scale subscription-based services. Zuora''s flagship product, Zuora Billing, automates subscription billing and revenue management, allowing companies to streamline their operations without building their own systems.

The company offers a range of products, including Zuora Revenue for financial reporting, Zuora Collect for managing collections and payments, and Zuora CPQ to enhance sales processes for subscription products. In 2021, Zuora introduced the Central Platform, which integrates all aspects of subscription business management. Zuora serves various industries, including SaaS, media, and automotive, with notable clients like Bloomberg, Zoom, and General Motors. 

Recognized as a pioneer in the subscription economy, Zuora launched the Subscription Economy Index and hosts events to support the subscription business community. The company went public in 2018, raising $154 million and achieving a valuation exceeding $2 billion shortly after.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '5', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/1168.png', 'true', 'Very large company', '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', 'greenhouse', 'zuora', null), ('1087', 'Mytos', 'Mytos Bio Ltd', 'https://www.mytos.bio/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/mytosbio/?originalSubdomain=uk', 'Mytos is a biotech company based in London, founded in 2016. It specializes in developing fully automated machines for growing human cells, primarily catering to large pharmaceutical and biotechnology firms involved in drug development and cell therapies. The company aims to modernize the manual process of cell culture, which is essential for early-stage drug discovery and testing.

The Mytos Platform is their core product, an automated system that combines robotics, advanced sensors, and cloud connectivity. This platform allows users to remotely manage cell culture operations, reducing human error and contamination risks. Mytos also offers the iDEM™, a closed manufacturing system for pluripotent stem cells, which are vital for regenerative medicine. Their technology supports the automated production of various human cell types, enhancing the efficiency and consistency of drug development.

Mytos serves top global pharmaceutical companies and generates revenue through sales and support services for its platforms. The company is backed by prominent venture capital investors and has a skilled team with expertise in robotics, cell biology, and biotech product development.', 'The company does not offer sponsorship for any of its junior roles. They are open to offering visa support for other roles.', '3', '8', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/813.png', 'true', 'Small company', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', 'lever', 'mytos', null), ('1088', 'Talogy', 'Talogy Limited', 'https://www.talogy.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/talogy/', 'Talogy is a global talent management company with over 75 years of experience, specializing in talent assessment, development, and consulting solutions. Founded in 1946 by pioneers in psychology, Talogy has grown into a leading provider of people-focused talent solutions, helping organizations effectively identify, build, and grow their workforce.

The company offers a range of services, including scientifically validated talent assessments like the Caliper Profile, which measures personality traits and motivations. Talogy also provides leadership development programs and consulting services to design scalable talent strategies that enhance workforce well-being and performance. Their technology platform integrates assessment and development tools, enabling organizations to streamline talent management processes and make informed decisions.

Headquartered in Atherton, California, Talogy employs approximately 600 people and generates an estimated revenue of $251.2 million. The company serves a diverse array of industries, focusing on creating environments where employees thrive and organizations succeed.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/908.png', 'true', 'Very large company', '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', 'smartrecruiters', 'talogy', null), ('1089', 'Fortune', 'Fortune Media Group (UK) Limited', 'https://fortune.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/fortune/', 'Fortune Media Corporation is a multinational media company based in New York City. It publishes *Fortune* magazine and operates Fortune.com, along with various business-related media products and events. The company became independent in December 2018 after being sold by Meredith Corporation.

*Fortune* magazine, founded in 1930, is known for its in-depth business journalism, corporate profiles, and economic analysis. It has gained a reputation for its literary style and artistic covers, as well as its annual rankings like the Fortune 500. The company also organizes conferences and forums, such as the Global Forum and the Most Powerful Women Summit, which connect business leaders and influencers for networking and thought leadership.

