In the defense sector, Raft focuses on autonomous data fusion and agentic AI to support the U.S. Department of Defense and national security organizations. They develop modular, scalable data platforms and AI capabilities that enhance legacy systems. Their flagship product, the [R] AI Mission System, provides autonomous, edge-capable AI for real-time battle management and mission support. Raft''s solutions are trusted by over 25 federal agencies, emphasizing human-centered AI and data governance to improve decision-making in critical missions.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '3', '17', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/66.png', 'true', 'Medium-sized company', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', 'greenhouse', 'raft', null), ('1095', 'Yapily', 'Yapily Ltd', 'https://www.yapily.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/yapily/', 'Yapily is a European open banking infrastructure platform founded in 2017 by Stefano Vaccino. The company provides a secure API that allows enterprises, including financial service providers and fintechs, to connect to thousands of banks across 19 European countries. This connection enables access to financial data and payment initiation, helping clients integrate open banking capabilities into their offerings.

