Urb-it has formed partnerships with several major e-commerce companies, including Cainiao, AliExpress, The Hut Group, Zara, MetaPack, and Shein. These collaborations enhance Fin''s access to a diverse client base and support its growth strategy in the logistics sector. With a focus on AI-powered route optimization and logistics management, the combined company aims to improve efficiency and customer satisfaction in delivery services.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/f18caf03-577b-4d67-9346-5437d84615ac.png', 'true', 'Medium-sized company', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', null, null, null), ('1136', 'Strolll', 'Strolll Limited', 'https://strolll.co/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/strolll/', 'Strolll is a private limited company based in Stafford, UK, founded in 2019. It specializes in digital therapeutic software for neurorehabilitation, utilizing augmented reality (AR) technology. The Strolll® platform is the first clinically validated digital therapeutic solution designed for commercially available AR glasses, enabling immersive therapy that connects patients with their physical environment.

