The platform features a robust mortgage sourcing engine, real-time lender affordability checks, and a variety of product types, including second charge and retirement options. Acre also provides tools for client record management, compliance automation, and workflow streamlining, enhancing operational efficiency. Its unique pricing model charges intermediaries only for successfully completed mortgage cases, eliminating per-user fees and hidden costs. Acre serves a diverse clientele, including mortgage brokers, banks, and financial institutions, and is partnered with leading mortgage clubs in the UK to support their advisors.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '3', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/3e4a3f07-4bbd-4dc0-8045-5112204d3531.png', 'true', 'Medium-sized company', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', 'breezy', 'acre', null), ('1139', 'Contentsquare', 'Content Square Ltd', 'https://contentsquare.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/contentsquare/', 'Contentsquare is a global digital experience analytics company founded in 2012 in Paris by Jonathan Cherki. It offers an all-in-one Software-as-a-Service (SaaS) platform that tracks and visualizes user behaviors across websites and mobile apps. The platform provides intelligent recommendations to help businesses enhance their digital experiences, increase revenue, and foster customer loyalty.

