Nory targets restaurant brands and hospitality businesses looking to improve operational control and profitability. The platform provides seamless integrations with existing POS, payroll, and accounting systems, creating a connected ecosystem for users. Founded by a restaurant owner, Nory emphasizes innovation and collaboration, backed by significant funding and a dedicated team.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '14', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/12a3fee8-f037-4817-ae71-810b736c2c4a.png', 'true', 'Medium-sized company', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', 'ashby', 'https://api.ashbyhq.com/posting-api/job-board/nory', null), ('1144', 'Hello Klean', 'Helloklean Ltd', 'https://helloklean.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/hello-klean/', 'Hello Klean is a London-based beauty brand founded in 2019 by Karlee and Omer Ozener. The company focuses on addressing the negative effects of hard water on hair and skin, stemming from Karlee''s personal experiences with dryness and irritation caused by poor water quality. Hello Klean specializes in "showercare" solutions that improve hair and skin health by reducing exposure to harmful water contaminants.

