The company''s platform, Stord One, simplifies supply chain operations by offering end-to-end visibility and control. It includes features such as omnichannel warehousing, transportation services, and an order management system that automates order routing. Stord also focuses on last-mile optimization and provides analytics tools for data-driven decision-making. Their fulfillment network supports scalable inventory distribution and order processing, making it easier for brands to manage complex supply chains effectively.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/c655d88b-42f1-4bdd-8104-bfba419e3ce7.png', 'true', 'Small company', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', null, null, null), ('1147', 'mvpr', 'MV Public Relations Limited', 'https://mvpr.io/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/mvpublicrelations/', 'MVPR is a public relations agency designed for the AI era, utilizing proprietary software and a unique dataset of journalist insights. This innovative approach enables efficient media engagement and helps transform technical milestones into compelling narratives for journalists and target audiences.

The agency focuses on a tech-first strategy in public relations, emphasizing collaboration and strategic communications. MVPR assists clients in building thought leadership and executing strategic announcements, all while maintaining lower costs compared to traditional agencies. The company is recognized for its effective media engagement, exemplified by its role in announcing significant financial milestones, such as a $100 million debt round, which garnered substantial media coverage.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/b7960b91-898b-40ea-b861-9623b50b4a40.png', 'true', 'Small company', '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', null, null, null), ('1149', 'EasyA', 'EasyA Ltd', 'https://www.easya.io/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/easya/', 'EasyA is a technology company founded in 2019 by Phil and Dom Kwok, specializing in blockchain education and Web3 technology. The company has developed the EasyA app, which is recognized as the leading Web3 learning platform with over one million users. EasyA aims to educate and onboard a billion people into blockchain and Web3 technologies, providing accessible and personalized tutoring without the need for prior booking.

In addition to its educational platform, EasyA Labs focuses on creating products that simplify access to cryptocurrency and blockchain for everyday users. The company also offers AI software development services through Easy Authoring, catering to various industries such as e-commerce, healthcare, and finance. These services include AI-assisted recommendations, speech recognition, and personalized learning solutions, all delivered through secure and scalable infrastructure. EasyA is committed to fostering innovation and mass education in the blockchain space.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/137176b3-b719-4cce-84f5-c9d435d62c0d.png', 'true', 'Small company', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', null, null, null), ('1151', 'Sensat', 'Sensat Digital Limited', 'https://www.sensat.co/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/sensat/', 'Sensat is a UK-based technology company that specializes in digital visualization and mapping solutions for large-scale civil infrastructure projects. Founded in 2017 by James Dean and Harry Atkinson, Sensat focuses on creating 3D digital maps to help infrastructure teams visualize complex project data in real-world contexts, enhancing decision-making and promoting environmental sustainability.

The company''s main product is Mapp®, a cloud-based digital twin platform that utilizes autonomous mapping drones to generate highly accurate 3D replicas of physical sites. This platform allows users to visualize project constraints, evaluate planning options, and communicate findings effectively from a desktop interface. Key features include reality-based site maps, measurement tools for verifying plans, and collaboration capabilities that keep all stakeholders aligned.

Sensat supports over $200 billion worth of civil infrastructure projects across Europe and is trusted by major clients such as Severn Trent and National Grid. The company has received multiple awards for its innovation and is recognized for its unique capability to operate autonomous drones Beyond Visual Line of Sight over major motorways. Sensat is committed to addressing environmental challenges in the infrastructure sector by simplifying complex information and reducing waste.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '2', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/87907b6b-cee4-4029-9022-6355c5947108.png', 'true', 'Small company', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', 'ashby', 'https://api.ashbyhq.com/posting-api/job-board/sensat', null), ('1152', 'Hack the Box', 'Hack the Box Ltd', 'https://www.hackthebox.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/hackthebox/', 'Hack The Box is a cybersecurity company founded in 2017 by Haris Pylarinos, James Hooker, and Aris Zikopoulos, with a presence in the UK and Greece. It has grown into one of the largest hacking communities globally, with over 1.7 million users. The company aims to address the shortage of skilled cybersecurity professionals through an innovative, gamified platform that offers hands-on penetration testing and training.

