With significant funding and a growing team of over 100 employees, Hack The Box is committed to building a community of skilled ethical hackers and supporting organizations in strengthening their cyber defenses.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/1e2e7958-c428-4a73-85b6-f250a460e49f.png', 'true', 'Very large company', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', 'workable', 'hack-the-box-ltd', null), ('1153', 'The Modern Milkman', 'Modern Milkman Ltd', 'https://themodernmilkman.co.uk/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/the-modern-milkman', 'The Modern Milkman is a sustainable grocery delivery service based in the UK, founded in 2018 and headquartered in Manchester. The company aims to reduce plastic waste by using a return-and-reuse model, delivering fresh groceries in eco-friendly packaging. It operates as a private limited company and focuses on ethical sourcing by partnering directly with independent farmers and suppliers.

