In 2023, Pasta Evangelists opened the largest fresh pasta factory in the UK, allowing them to maintain artisanal quality through traditional Italian methods and premium ingredients. They serve customers throughout the British Isles, ensuring freshness with insulated packaging and chilled ice packs. The company also provides pasta-making masterclasses and has expanded its reach to cities like Birmingham and Manchester. With plans for international growth, including a store opening in Paris in 2025, Pasta Evangelists has established itself as the UK’s leading pasta brand by revenue, serving approximately 2 million consumers.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '17', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/b0271cc1-afb4-49ae-bd87-5cc17b1de583.png', 'true', 'Large company', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', 'teamtailor', 'pastaevangelists', null), ('1157', 'RevLifter', 'RevLifter Ltd', 'https://www.revlifter.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/revlifter/', 'RevLifter is a technology company founded in 2017, based in London, that focuses on intelligent eCommerce offers. The company uses machine learning and smart targeting to create personalized promotions that drive growth and profitability for retailers. RevLifter''s platform enables brands to deliver real-time hyper-personalized offers to online customers, enhancing conversion rates and incentivizing purchases.

