The platform, known as Translation as a Service (TaaS), integrates seamlessly with customer relationship management (CRM) and support tools like Zendesk. It supports 28 languages and offers real-time translation of customer emails, chat messages, and support tickets. Unbabel''s hybrid model leverages machine learning for initial translations and human expertise for refinement, making it faster and more accurate than traditional methods. The company serves a diverse range of industries, including e-commerce, travel, gaming, and technology, helping businesses enhance their global communication capabilities.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/afc8ad53-d69c-4d0c-ad4f-21a0be476ebb.png', 'true', 'Large company', '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', null, null, null), ('1261', 'Flock', 'Flock Limited', 'https://flockcover.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/flockmotor/', 'Flock is a UK-based insurance technology company that specializes in exposure-based insurance for commercial vehicle fleets, including drones, cars, vans, and trucks. Founded in 2015 and headquartered in London, Flock offers a fully digital insurance platform aimed at making commercial fleets safer and more cost-effective to insure.

The company provides tailored fleet insurance products for various types of commercial fleets, such as courier services, rental fleets, and taxi services. Flock''s insurance model is usage-sensitive, linking pricing directly to the actual risk exposure of the fleet. Their Connected Insurance platform utilizes telematics and data analytics to monitor driving behavior, allowing for premium rebates of up to 10% based on performance. Flock serves commercial fleet operators with a minimum of 10 vehicles and distributes its insurance through a network of brokers, ensuring accessibility for a wide range of customers.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '3', '5', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/803f81f8-fd78-4243-8321-abe473cc9d93.png', 'true', 'Medium-sized company', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', null, null, null), ('1262', 'Cledara', 'Cledara Limited', 'https://www.cledara.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/cledara/', 'Cledara is a SaaS management platform founded in 2018 by Cristina Vila. It helps businesses efficiently discover, buy, manage, and cancel cloud software subscriptions. With over 1,000 customers in 32 countries and management of more than 5,600 software vendors, Cledara is recognized as a leading solution for finance teams.

