Currencycloud serves a diverse customer base, including fintech startups and established banks. Notably, it has supported Revolut, the UK''s leading fintech, since 2015, facilitating global spending and bank transfers in multiple currencies. The company is backed by teams of experts in product management, compliance, and technology, ensuring its platform remains secure and aligned with client needs.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/6e4ffd32-64e4-4408-ab05-f25a4b2d8024.png', 'true', 'Large company', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', 'smartrecruiters', 'v1', null), ('1264', 'Visa', 'Visa Europe Limited', 'https://www.visa.co.uk/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/visa/', null, 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '22', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/778859e4-d495-4bd8-87dc-16c21bc3282b.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', 'smartrecruiters', 'visa', null), ('1265', 'Hurdle', 'Chronomics Limited', 'https://hurdle.bio/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/hurdlebio/', 'Hurdle is a biotechnology company focused on developing innovative diagnostic solutions. Founded by scientists from Cambridge and Oxford, the company specializes in biomarker research and Diagnostics-as-a-Service (DaaS). Hurdle aims to enhance preventative healthcare by utilizing multi-omics datasets and machine learning, particularly in epigenetics.

