AISI''s mission is to minimize risks posed by AI, particularly in areas such as cyberattacks, fraud, and biological weapon development. The institute conducts risk assessments of AI systems, engages in research and development to investigate AI misuse, and provides policy guidance to shape AI governance strategies. It has developed the Inspect framework, an open-source tool for testing AI systems, to foster collaboration in research. AISI primarily serves UK policymakers and international partners, working with organizations like Anthropic to balance economic growth with security measures.', 'The organisation will only sponsor "super senior" roles.', '1', '7', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/0545acb9-4007-4ff3-885e-415ddd7989e7.png', 'true', 'Medium-sized company', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', 'greenhouse', 'aisi', null), ('1275', 'TrueLayer', 'TrueLayer Limited', 'https://truelayer.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/truelayer/', 'TrueLayer is a prominent open banking platform based in the UK, dedicated to enhancing online payments through real-time bank integrations. The company serves over 10 million users across 21 European countries, processing more than $50 billion in payments annually. TrueLayer focuses on creating a future-ready payments network, fostering a culture of creativity and accountability among its employees.

