IMAA offers a range of executive education and certification programs that cover the entire M&A lifecycle. These programs are designed for M&A professionals, corporate executives, consultants, and organizations looking to enhance their M&A capabilities. Key certifications include the International Mergers & Acquisitions Expert and the Certified Post Merger Integration Expert. The institute also serves as a non-profit think tank, providing expert insights and commentary on M&A topics to major media outlets. With a focus on networking and collaboration, IMAA supports professionals in building connections and improving their dealmaking skills.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '3', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/a792c76f-357d-4416-a340-d01d9a46d010.png', 'true', 'Large company', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', 'greenhouse', 'clearscoretechnologylimited', null), ('1324', 'Kriya', 'KRIYA FINANCE LIMITED', 'https://www.kriya.co/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/kriyafinance/', 'Kriya Software Solutions Inc is an IT consulting and technology services company based in Houston, TX, with a delivery center in Hyderabad, India. The company specializes in computer consulting, IT solutions, and outsourced IT services, focusing on mission-critical systems. Their offerings include full lifecycle application development and mobile app solutions tailored for enterprises.

