The company specializes in personalized investment management through its digital platform. It creates tailored investment profiles for customers based on their financial goals and risk tolerance, utilizing proprietary algorithms to assign them to one of 12 diversified portfolios. Moneyfarm also offers a digital Self-Invested Personal Pension (SIPP) product, enhancing its retirement planning services. With over 160,000 investors and assets exceeding £1.6 billion, Moneyfarm aims to make investing accessible and transparent for retail investors across Europe.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '3', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/4580025e-eb99-4848-b67c-618daeb7bbbd.png', 'true', 'Medium-sized company', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', null, null, null), ('1328', 'Accelex', 'Accelex Technology Limited', 'https://www.accelextech.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/accelextech/', 'Accelex, founded in 2018 and based in London, specializes in AI-driven data solutions for private markets. The company serves institutional investors, asset servicers, and fund administrators worldwide, with additional offices in Paris, Luxembourg, New York, and Toronto. Accelex has raised a total of $25.05 million in funding, including a $15 million Series A round led by FactSet in October 2023.

