That''s why we founded Distributed.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/fb32f874_2f12_469d_b624_d9ad001aff01.png', 'true', 'Medium-sized company', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', null, null, null), ('1427', 'Hypervsn', 'Kino-mo Limited', 'https://hypervsn.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/hypervsn/', 'HYPERVSN is a London-based technology company founded in 2011 by Kiryl Chykeyuk and Art Stavenka. The company specializes in 3D holographic display systems that create immersive visuals without the need for wearable equipment. Their proprietary hardware and software platform delivers high-quality holographic content managed via a cloud platform, providing a unique visual experience for audiences.

HYPERVSN aims to revolutionize the audiovisual industry with innovative digital display solutions. Their product offerings include connected hardware and software for 3D holographic displays, suitable for various sectors such as digital signage, retail, events, education, and public safety. The technology allows businesses to showcase holographic visuals that appear to float in mid-air, enhancing advertising and promotional efforts.

The company serves a prestigious customer base, including global brands like Nike, Disney, and BMW, and has established over 120 official partners in more than 80 countries. Supported by high-profile investors like Sir Richard Branson and Mark Cuban, HYPERVSN has received multiple international awards for its excellence in holographic technology.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/ad1de37c_4710_4e88_908b_40483a4308f6.png', 'true', 'Medium-sized company', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', null, null, null), ('1428', 'Seat Unique', 'RMS Events Limited ', 'https://www.seatunique.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/seat-unique/', 'Seat Unique is a London-based online marketplace that specializes in premium ticketing and hospitality packages for live entertainment and sporting events. Founded in 2018 by Robin Sherry and Phillipa Hicks, the company aims to make official VIP tickets and hospitality experiences more accessible and secure for fans. 

