The company''s core product, the Automated Control Testing Platform, allows institutions to maintain compliance efficiently by automating control testing tailored to their specific risk appetite and regulatory needs. Additionally, Cable offers a Transaction Assurance product that automates the effectiveness testing of financial transaction systems, monitoring for regulatory breaches and enhancing compliance with rules like the “Travel Rule.” Cable''s solutions provide real-time risk assessment alerts, detailed compliance reporting, and facilitate transparency for regulatory oversight.

Cable targets banks, fintechs, and payment platforms, helping them streamline operations and improve compliance processes. The company emphasizes reducing manual oversight, allowing compliance experts to focus on strategic initiatives while ensuring institutions are audit-ready daily.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/54c4e593_ae37_410f_9477_d8b66030f8c8.png', 'true', 'Large company', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', null, null, null), ('1443', 'Tropic', 'Tropic Biosciences UK Limited', 'https://tropic.bio/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/tropic-bio/', 'Tropic Biosciences UK Ltd is a biotechnology company based in Norwich, United Kingdom. Founded in 2016, it specializes in developing high-performing tropical crop varieties using advanced genetic breeding technologies, including CRISPR gene editing. The company focuses on staple crops such as coffee, bananas, and rice, which are vital for global agriculture and nutrition.

