The Waymap app is available for free on both the Apple App Store and Google Play. It utilizes smartphone sensors to deliver accurate location and orientation without needing physical infrastructure like Bluetooth beacons. This technology allows for precise navigation even in areas with weak GPS signals. Waymap also offers mapping services to venues, transit authorities, and other organizations, helping them enhance accessibility for their users. The company collaborates with various partners to test and deploy its technology, focusing on improving the travel experience for individuals with disabilities.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/3182e6cb_5362_4037_8838_cc883c3d7f3b.png', 'true', 'Small company', '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', null, null, null), ('1453', 'Splyt', 'Splyt Technologies Limited', 'https://splyt.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/splyttech/', 'Splyt is a global technology company based in London, specializing in integrating various on-demand lifestyle services into superapps and travel platforms. It operates a comprehensive lifestyle services network that connects ridehailing, airport transfers, bikesharing, scooters, public transport, food delivery, and experiences into a single interface. This integration allows superapps and travel platforms to offer a wide range of services, enhancing customer loyalty and increasing revenue.

The company provides two main solutions: API Integration and SDK Integration. The API Integration connects superapps to Splyt’s network of over 65 partners, enabling access to multiple on-demand services. The SDK Integration offers a user interface software development kit that can be embedded directly into a superapp, allowing for rapid deployment of services. Splyt targets global superapps, travel platforms, and digital wallets, helping them expand their service offerings and improve user engagement. With a presence in over 2,000 cities across 150 countries, Splyt is positioned as a key enabler in the lifestyle and travel services industry.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/715e28b0_f1cb_4d5f_b2bf_ca0ddab27a6f.png', 'true', 'Small company', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', 'bamboohr', 'splyt', null), ('1454', 'TotallyMoney', 'TotallyMoney Limited', 'https://www.totallymoney.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/totallymoney/', 'TotallyMoney is a UK-based fintech company and independent credit broker located in London. Founded in 2007, it provides free credit reports and eligibility checking services through its software platform. The company employs around 80 people and generates approximately $16.8 million in revenue.

The core service of TotallyMoney is to give consumers access to their credit reports and scores at no cost, helping them understand their creditworthiness. It features an eligibility hub that allows users to check which financial products they may qualify for without impacting their credit score. The company partners with various lenders and financial institutions, ensuring impartiality in product rankings on its platform.

