The firm is known for its work on large-scale litigation against multinational corporations, particularly in cases involving environmental disasters and consumer rights violations. A notable achievement includes securing a landmark judgment for over 620,000 victims of the 2015 Mariana dam disaster in Brazil, allowing them to seek redress against BHP in the courts of England and Wales. Pogust Goodhead also leads significant consumer protection cases, such as the Volkswagen diesel emissions fraud litigation and the British Airways data breach claim.

With offices in London and Edinburgh, and a strong presence in the United States, Pogust Goodhead is committed to advocating for victims of corporate wrongdoing and human rights abuses. The firm emphasizes environmental, social, and governance principles in its legal practice.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/7427f9d3_4daf_48d5_a306_33a75e466a37.png', 'true', 'Medium-sized company', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', null, null, null), ('1456', 'Pai Skincare', 'Pai Skincare Limited', 'https://www.paiskincare.com/pages/try-pai-kit', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/pai-skincare/?originalSubdomain=uk', 'Pai Skincare is an organic skincare company based in London, founded in 2007 by Sarah Brown. The brand was created to address sensitive and reactive skin issues, particularly chronic urticaria. Pai Skincare is dedicated to producing natural, ethical, and sustainable products specifically formulated for sensitive and eczema-prone skin, emphasizing transparency and quality.

The product range includes moisturizers, cleansers, and oils, with popular items like the Camellia & Rose Gentle Hydrating Cleanser and Rosehip Oil. Recently, they launched a new line called Concentrates, which features active ingredient boosters developed by their in-house R&D team. All products are formulated and manufactured at their London headquarters, ensuring high standards for ingredient quality and product integrity. Pai Skincare uses certified organic ingredients and conducts independent patch testing to ensure suitability for sensitive skin.

