Heathrow Airport Limited operates the airport, providing extensive passenger services such as check-in, security, lounges, retail, dining, and transportation connections, including a link to the London Underground. The airport also has dedicated cargo terminals that support freight and logistics operations. With its comprehensive infrastructure, including multiple runways and modern terminal buildings, Heathrow efficiently handles high passenger volumes and serves a diverse customer base, including airlines, business travelers, and tourists.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/562f35f6-a919-4e10-b29e-ff9b3335c76f.png', 'true', 'Very large company', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', null, null, null), ('1736', 'WTW', 'Willis Limited', 'https://www.wtwco.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/wtwcorporate', 'WTW (Willis Towers Watson) is a multinational company based in the UK and the US, specializing in insurance brokerage, risk management, employee benefits, and actuarial consulting services. Operating in over 140 countries, WTW serves a diverse clientele, including a significant majority of FTSE 100, Fortune 1000, and Fortune Global 500 companies.

