Separately, Pion (We Are Pion) is a marketing and consumer insights company founded in 2005. It focuses on helping brands grow by leveraging insights and targeted advertising, particularly aimed at strategic consumer groups like students and Gen Z. Pion provides actionable insights, advertising campaigns, and verification services to engage and build loyalty with these demographics. The company serves over 3,500 brands across more than 100 countries, positioning itself as a partner for brands seeking to enhance their marketing strategies.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '2', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/8a9ba933-0ffa-4b49-bd29-0e68fd34dc43.png', 'true', 'Medium-sized company', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', null, null, null), ('1742', 'SmartestEnergy', 'SmartestEnergy Limited', 'https://www.smartestenergy.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/smartestenergy', 'SmartestEnergy is a global B2B renewable energy company founded in 2000, dedicated to helping commercial, industrial, and SME customers, as well as independent renewable energy generators, achieve net zero emissions. Headquartered in the UK, with offices in the US and Australia, the company operates without owning fossil fuel or generation assets, focusing instead on renewable energy supply and market services.

The company supplies 100% certified renewable electricity and plays a key role as an aggregator of independent renewable generation projects. SmartestEnergy offers flexible energy solutions and has a strong track record of innovation, including launching the UK’s first certified 100% renewable supply product in 2015. Backed by Marubeni Corporation, a Fortune Global 500 company, SmartestEnergy is positioned as a reliable partner for businesses looking to transition to sustainable energy solutions.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/3cc14120-eed7-4be6-8814-50e66abf8772.png', 'true', 'Large company', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', 'teamtailor', 'smartestenergy', null), ('1743', 'EquiLend', 'EquiLend Europe Limited', 'https://equilend.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/equilend', 'EquiLend is a global financial technology company founded in 2001 by a consortium of prominent financial institutions, including Barclays Global Investors and Goldman Sachs. The company specializes in securities finance, offering a comprehensive suite of technology solutions that span the entire transaction lifecycle, from pre-trade to post-trade processing, data analytics, and regulatory compliance.

EquiLend''s core offerings include automated trading platforms, post-trade services, regulatory technology tools, and data analytics through its DataLend service. The Spire platform allows clients to manage their securities finance operations efficiently, while EquiLend 1Source utilizes blockchain technology to enhance operational efficiency. With nearly 200 clients worldwide, including asset owners and hedge funds, EquiLend executes over $2.4 trillion in transactions monthly. The company is recognized for its innovation and leadership in the industry, receiving multiple awards and certifications for its services and workplace culture.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '2', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/49282733-60fa-4b51-9006-75f9ad40bd8f.png', 'true', 'Large company', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', 'greenhouse', 'equilend', null), ('1744', 'Hexaware', 'HEXAWARE TECHNOLOGIES UK LTD', 'https://hexaware.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/hexaware-technologies', 'Hexaware Technologies is a global technology and business process services company based in Navi Mumbai, India. Founded in 1990, it has grown to employ over 32,000 professionals across more than 60 offices in 28 countries. The company specializes in digital transformation solutions, helping enterprises address business challenges and create value through technology.

