WSD partners with leading financial data providers like Morningstar, SIX Financial Information, and Refinitiv to offer comprehensive market data. Its primary customers include banks, private equity firms, and corporates, all of whom benefit from WSD''s technology and managed services tailored to their specific needs.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/34b76224-9c33-4966-ba50-7baffbf2a179.png', 'true', 'Large company', '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', 'bamboohr', 'wsd', null), ('1746', 'Reach', 'Reach plc', 'https://www.reachplc.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/reach-plc', 'Reach plc is the largest commercial news publisher in the UK and Ireland, with a diverse portfolio of over 120 brands. This includes well-known national newspapers like the Daily Mirror, Daily Express, and Daily Star, as well as regional titles such as the Manchester Evening News and Liverpool Echo. The company has a rich history, evolving from the Liverpool Daily Post and the Daily Mirror through various mergers and acquisitions since the 19th century.

Headquartered in London, Reach plc focuses on publishing trusted news and information across print, digital platforms, and social media. It reaches about 70% of the UK online population monthly and has a significant presence in the US. The company is committed to high journalistic standards and provides timely news, opinion, and entertainment content tailored to its communities. As a publicly traded entity, Reach plc generates revenue through advertising and digital content monetization, serving a broad audience of news readers and advertisers.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/23889e93-3cf9-44f6-a398-47a78deace09.png', 'true', 'Very large company', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', 'greenhouse', 'reach', null), ('1747', 'Thomson Reuters', 'Reuters News & Media Ltd', 'https://www.thomsonreuters.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/thomson-reuters', 'Thomson Reuters is a Canadian multinational technology conglomerate based in Toronto, Ontario. Formed in 2008 through the acquisition of Reuters Group by the Thomson Corporation, the company specializes in providing professionals with trusted content, AI-powered technology, and workflow automation solutions. With over 150 years of expertise, Thomson Reuters aims to clarify complex information landscapes, enabling users to act confidently and efficiently.

