Adobe''s products cater to a diverse audience, including creative professionals, marketing agencies, enterprises, educational institutions, and publishers. The company is recognized as an industry standard in creative software and digital marketing solutions, empowering millions of users worldwide to create and manage digital content effectively.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/13f1dde4-783a-4ea5-8a0e-a7f53656fee0.png', 'true', 'Very large company', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', 'workday', 'external_experienced', null), ('1749', 'Ansys', 'ANSYS UK Ltd', 'https://ansys.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/ansys-inc', 'Ansys, Inc. is a leading provider of engineering simulation software, established in 1970 by Dr. John A. Swanson. The company specializes in advanced simulation solutions that model complex product behaviors across various physics domains, including structural mechanics, thermal analysis, fluid dynamics, electromagnetics, optics, and semiconductors. Ansys software helps engineers and researchers accelerate product development, optimize performance, and minimize the need for physical prototypes through virtual testing environments.

Headquartered in Canonsburg, Pennsylvania, Ansys serves a diverse range of industries such as aerospace, automotive, energy, electronics, life sciences, and industrial equipment. The company offers a comprehensive portfolio of simulation products, including tools for structural analysis, computational fluid dynamics, electromagnetics, optics, and semiconductor design. Ansys also provides cloud and AI-enhanced simulation platforms, along with consulting, training, and support services to maximize customer value. With approximately 6,000 employees and a revenue of $2.4 billion in 2023, Ansys continues to innovate and expand its capabilities in the engineering simulation market.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/21ac9d2e-bc8c-465f-aa99-558a2f332a12.png', 'true', 'Very large company', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', null, null, null), ('1750', 'Experian', 'Experian Limited', 'https://www.experian.co.uk', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/experian', 'Experian plc is a global data analytics and consumer credit reporting company based in Dublin, Ireland. Founded in 1980 in Nottingham, England, it operates across North America, Latin America, Europe, the Middle East, and Africa. The company specializes in credit reporting, data analytics, fraud prevention, and marketing services. It offers consumer credit reports and scores, business credit reports, identity verification, and fraud detection solutions, including services for underserved consumers.Experian serves a diverse customer base, including financial institutions, retailers, healthcare providers, and government agencies. The company focuses on enabling data-driven decision-making, with a significant portion of its revenue generated from North American operations. Experian''s mission is to leverage data to create a better tomorrow for consumers and businesses, emphasizing financial inclusion and innovation.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '20', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/aab06361-9f83-4c21-9390-ea9352d7277f.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', 'smartrecruiters', 'v1', null), ('1751', 'Intuit', 'Intuit Limited', 'https://www.intuit.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/intuit', 'Intuit is a prominent financial software company founded in 1983 in Palo Alto, California, by Scott Cook and Tom Proulx. The company specializes in software and online services that simplify personal finance management, small business accounting, and tax preparation. Its flagship products include QuickBooks for small business accounting, TurboTax for tax preparation, and Mint for personal financial management.

With approximately 50 million customers worldwide and a workforce of over 8,000 employees, Intuit has established itself as a key player in the financial software industry. The company has evolved from its origins with Quicken, a personal finance tool, to offer a range of services including payroll processing, mortgage lending, and insurance products. Intuit is known for its commitment to innovation and customer-centric product development, continuously adapting to technology trends with cloud-based and mobile solutions.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/cd712519-0fe8-4346-8983-5f812fd5138e.png', 'true', 'Very large company', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', 'oracle_cloud', 'intuit', null), ('1752', '2i', '2i Limited', 'https://2itesting.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/2i-testing', '2i is a UK-based software quality assurance and testing company founded in 2005, with its headquarters in Edinburgh and additional offices in Glasgow, Newcastle, and London. The company specializes in providing comprehensive software testing services to a diverse range of clients, including small and medium enterprises, public sector organizations, and large financial institutions, particularly in investment banking and asset management.

The services offered by 2i include software quality assurance and testing, test automation, test data generation, non-functional testing, and AI testing services. Their methodologies focus on ensuring software quality, security, reliability, and regulatory compliance. With a strong emphasis on data security and system availability, 2i has established itself as a trusted partner in highly regulated industries. The company has a proven track record of delivering zero critical incidents post-launch for public sector services and supports core banking platforms and payment systems for notable clients like Virgin Money.

With nearly 100 staff and an estimated revenue of $36.5 million, 2i combines deep domain expertise and innovative automation to help organizations reduce risk and accelerate time to market for complex software projects.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/6cbf2e7b-2cd8-4f41-84be-e636ccb47aa8.png', 'true', 'Medium-sized company', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', null, null, null), ('1753', '360insights', '360insights (Europe) Ltd', 'https://www.360insights.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/360insights', '360insights is a global leader in Channel Incentives Management (CIM), founded in 2008 by Jason Atkins. The company is headquartered in the USA and has operations in the UK. It serves over 100 top brands across various sectors, including appliances, electronics, technology, automotive, and telecommunications.

The core offering of 360insights is the Channel Success Platform, a fully integrated software-as-a-service (SaaS) solution. This platform helps brands optimize their partner marketing and consumer incentive spending by enabling the calculation, tracking, and awarding of business rebates. It supports the management of marketing programs at local, regional, or global levels, providing transparency and motivation for sellers.

In addition to its software, 360insights offers services such as channel strategy consulting and marketing services. Their no-code portal solution enhances consumer experiences for claiming incentives and facilitates efficient partner engagement. Overall, 360insights combines technology and expert services to help brands improve channel incentives and drive business growth.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/92439fce-dde1-4d34-8e99-6d1b71d15a5d.png', 'true', 'Large company', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', null, null, null), ('1754', 'Digital Catapult', 'Digital Catapult', 'https://www.digicatapult.org.uk/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/digital-catapult', 'Digital Catapult is the UK’s leading innovation agency focused on advanced digital technology. Established in partnership with Innovate UK, its mission is to accelerate the adoption of emerging deep technologies to foster economic growth and societal benefits across the UK. The organization connects startups, scaleups, established businesses, investors, academia, and the public sector, facilitating the transition from research to real-world application of technologies like artificial intelligence, machine learning, 5G, immersive technologies, quantum computing, and the Internet of Things.

