With over 10,000 corporate customers worldwide, Mimecast has established a strong presence across various industries, including healthcare, financial services, legal, and government sectors. Recent developments include strategic acquisitions to enhance its capabilities and the launch of new products aimed at improving email security and management.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '4', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/07a708ac-0fd3-4113-bf02-059a8e5f701c.png', 'true', 'Very large company', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', 'workday', 'mimecast/Mimecast-Careers', null), ('1756', 'NVIDIA', 'NVIDIA Ltd', 'https://www.nvidia.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/nvidia', 'NVIDIA is a leading global technology company founded in 1993 and headquartered in Santa Clara, California. Known for inventing the GPU in 1999, NVIDIA has grown from a graphics chip manufacturer to a full-stack computing infrastructure provider. The company focuses on accelerated computing technologies that support various industries, including gaming, artificial intelligence, automotive, healthcare, robotics, and industrial digitalization.

