d in August 2010 by Stu Sjouwerman, KnowBe4 has rapidly grown to become the largest provider in its field, serving over 35,000 organizations worldwide. The company focuses on educating employees to recognize and respond to cyber threats, such as ransomware and phishing, through engaging training content and realistic simulations.

The core offerings of KnowBe4 include interactive security awareness training modules, a simulated phishing platform for testing employee vigilance, vulnerability scanning services, and an email exposure check tool. The company also provides additional training on topics like secure handling of sensitive information and mobile device security. Notably, KnowBe4 introduced a Crypto-Ransom Guarantee to offer assurance against ransomware attacks. With a diverse customer base that includes enterprises, government agencies, and educational institutions, KnowBe4 is recognized for its innovation and impact in the cybersecurity industry.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '8', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/0276712a-885b-4e90-8d52-b645fae41689.png', 'true', 'Very large company', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', 'greenhouse', 'knowbe4', null), ('1766', 'Epicor', 'Epicor Software (UK) Limited', 'https://www.epicor.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/epicor', 'Epicor Software Corporation is a global business software company based in Austin, Texas, with a history that dates back to 1972. Originally founded as Platinum Software Corporation in 1984, Epicor specializes in industry-focused enterprise software solutions for manufacturing, distribution, retail, and service sectors. The company has grown significantly through acquisitions and innovations, becoming a leading provider of enterprise resource planning (ERP) software and related applications.

Epicor offers a comprehensive suite of software products designed to enhance core business processes. Its flagship product, Epicor ERP, integrates management of manufacturing, supply chain, financials, and operations, available in both cloud-based and on-premises models. The company also provides customer relationship management (CRM) solutions, supply chain management (SCM) tools, human capital management (HCM) software, and configure, price, quote (CPQ) solutions. Epicor serves tens of thousands of small to mid-sized enterprises across approximately 150 countries, focusing on improving operational efficiency and customer engagement.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '9', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/27d4e932-eb1b-4e56-bab7-3c0c499bbb87.png', 'true', 'Very large company', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', 'workday', 'epicorsoftware/epicorjobs', null), ('1767', 'Expedia Group', 'Expedia.com Ltd', 'https://www.expediagroup.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/expedia', 'Expedia Group is a prominent global online travel company based in Seattle, Washington. Established in 1996 as part of Microsoft, it became a pioneer in online travel services. The company went public in 1999 and became an independent entity in 2005. Today, it operates a diverse portfolio of travel brands, connecting travelers with suppliers in the travel industry.Expedia Group offers a range of travel booking platforms, including Expedia.com, Hotels.com, and Vrbo, allowing users to book flights, hotels, vacation rentals, and more. It also provides corporate travel management through Egencia and Expedia Cruises. The company supports its partners with advertising services via Expedia Group Media Solutions and operates trivago, a hotel price comparison tool. With a focus on both individual and business travelers, Expedia Group utilizes mobile apps, websites, and call centers to facilitate bookings and offers private-label solutions for travel suppliers.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '31', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/7de07d0e-fd27-4c98-9d90-be9eebedeb75.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', 'smartrecruiters', 'expediagroup', null), ('1768', 'Hitachi Solutions', 'Hitachi Solutions Europe Ltd', 'https://www.hitachi-solutions.co.uk/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/hitachi-solutions-europe', 'Hitachi Solutions UK is a digital, data, and technology consultancy that specializes in Microsoft technologies, including Dynamics 365 Business Applications, Power Platform, and Azure. As a Microsoft Solutions and Cloud Services partner, the company focuses on providing end-to-end digital transformation services for both private and public sector clients. Their offerings include digital transformation consulting, application modernization, and tailored industry-specific solutions.

The company operates under the broader Hitachi group, leveraging global expertise to deliver local market knowledge and customized services. Hitachi Solutions UK is dedicated to helping organizations enhance efficiency and drive growth through innovative technology solutions. They are recognized for their positive workplace culture, with a strong commitment to employee well-being and inclusivity. Headquartered in London, the company serves a diverse range of clients, ensuring effective navigation through complex digital transformations.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '16', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/1e36a99c-0126-4f32-a45a-fa33a40446f3.png', 'true', 'Large company', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', 'smartrecruiters', 'HitachiSolutions', null), ('1769', 'Liberty IT', 'Liberty Information Technology Limited', 'https://www.liberty-it.co.uk/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/libertyit', 'Liberty IT, officially known as Liberty Information Technology Limited, is a private limited company based in Belfast, Northern Ireland. Established in 1996, it serves as the technology and digital solutions arm of Liberty Mutual Insurance, a leading global insurance company. With a workforce of 500 to 1,000 employees, Liberty IT generates approximately $39.2 million in revenue.

