l, '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', null, null, null), ('1809', 'Evestia Clinical', 'Evestia Clinical Limited', 'https://evestiaclinical.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/evestiaclinical', 'Evestia Clinical is a global Contract Research Organization (CRO) that specializes in clinical trials, focusing on oncology, rare diseases, neurology, immunology, and inflammation. Established in 1998, the company has become a leading clinical service partner for biotech firms, dedicated to accelerating the development of innovative therapies through personalized and expert-driven research solutions.

