isney, and Virgin. Their commitment to sustainability is evident in initiatives like planting over 120,000 trees through their projects. The agency continues to expand its capabilities, enhancing its offerings through strategic partnerships and acquisitions.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/79d54d5c-8cad-4a24-92c4-0fa417367d81.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', 'greenhouse', 'make', null), ('1859', 'Mann Williams', 'Mann Williams Ltd', 'https://www.mannwilliams.co.uk', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/mann-williams-consulting-civil-and-structural-engineers', 'Mann Williams Consulting Civil and Structural Engineers is a UK-based engineering consultancy founded in 1986, with offices in Bath, Cardiff, and Belfast. The firm specializes in both new build and conservation projects across the UK and Europe, serving various sectors within the built environment.Their services include structural and civil engineering, emphasizing creativity, technical skill, and collaboration. Mann Williams is known for its expertise in restoring historic buildings and ancient monuments, having worked on significant projects such as cathedrals in Winchester and Exeter, as well as stately homes like Chatsworth House and Longleat House. The company is an early adopter of Building Information Modeling (BIM) and integrates sustainable design principles into its projects.Mann Williams serves a diverse clientele, including heritage organizations like the National Trust and Historic Royal Palaces, as well as commercial clients such as AB Dynamics. Their portfolio also includes educational and cultural buildings, showcasing their commitment to innovative engineering solutions and heritage conservation.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/85ee25ce-35f3-43a9-870