oothwall Ltd', 'https://smoothwall.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/smoothwall-ltd', 'Smoothwall, part of the Qoria family, is a UK-based leader in digital safety technology focused on the education sector. With nearly 25 years of experience, Smoothwall specializes in safeguarding solutions that protect children in their digital lives. Their offerings address the challenges of online safety in schools, colleges, and multi-academy trusts (MATs).The company provides advanced digital safeguarding solutions, including filtering, monitoring, and reporting tools that help educational institutions comply with statutory safeguarding requirements. Their award-winning Monitor solution enables real-time monitoring of online activity to identify risks such as cyberbullying and self-harm, allowing for timely intervention by school safeguarding teams. Smoothwall''s team comprises experts from various fields, including digital safety engineers and child psychologists, ensuring comprehensive support for their customers.Smoothwall serves a wide range of educational institutions in the UK and has a global reach through Qoria, supporting over 24,000 schools and 12 million student licenses. Their mission is to enhance child digital safety and wellbeing, bridging the safety gaps between home and school environments.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/c15d4bec-4a6b-40b0-ad4f-d006973f7004.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', null, null, null), ('1867', 'La Caisse', 'CDPQ London LLP', 'https://www.lacaisse.com/en', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/lacaisse', 'La Caisse (Caisse de dépôt et placement du Québec, CDPQ) is a prominent institutional investor based in Quebec, Canada. Established in 1965, it manages funds primarily for public and parapublic pension plans and insurance programs in Québec. With total assets around CAD 473 billion, La Caisse is one of the largest institutional investors in the world, serving 48 depositors that represent over 6 million Quebec residents.The organization has a diversified investment portfolio that includes equities, fixed income, real assets, private equity, and customized financial instruments. La Caisse emphasizes optimal financial performance, supports Québec’s economic development, and focuses on sustainable investing. It operates globally with offices in various countries, including the US, UK, and Australia, and employs approximately 1,644 people. The governance structure includes a board of directors appointed by the Quebec government, ensuring strategic oversight and compliance.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/19ca54c4-e920-4056-95e8-e96c1caa14c1.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', 'workday', 'cdpq/CDPQ', null), ('1868', 'Silvercat', 'Silverstripe Credit and Technologies Limited', 'https://silvercat.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/silverstripecreditandtechnologies', 'Silvercat is reshaping the lending landscape. Our platform allows lenders to reach a broader audience, gain valuable insights into their customers, and provide them with unparalleled service.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/3048de94-33ed-40bf-bc1d-7b48bfb5fcbb.png', 'true', 'Small company', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', null, null, null), ('1869', 'Yoko Property', 'Yoko Property Ltd', 'https://www.yokoproperty.co.uk', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/yoko-property', 'Yoko Property is a real estate company based out of 54 The Oval, Oldbrook, Milton Keynes, United Kingdom.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/23bc4d0c-e