Unboxed develops bespoke software solutions tailored to client needs, with notable projects such as the Back Office Planning System and the Repairs Hub. They serve a diverse range of clients, including UK government departments, local authorities, and charities, reflecting their commitment to impactful digital services.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/64e5799d-7d45-4ecf-b077-65c4f6616b13.png', 'true', 'Medium-sized company', '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', null, null, null), ('1877', 'atVenu', 'atVenu UK LTD', 'https://www.atvenu.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/atvenu', 'atVenu is a live event commerce platform founded in 2012, focused on managing merchandise, food, and beverage sales at concerts, festivals, and other live events. Based in San Clemente, California, the company has established itself as an industry standard, serving over 125,000 events annually and supporting around 16,000 artists, 375 venues, and 250 festivals.

The platform offers a comprehensive point-of-sale (POS) system tailored for the unique challenges of live events. It includes features such as inventory management, sales tracking, cashless payment solutions, and reporting tools designed specifically for the food and beverage industry. atVenu''s solutions are built by live event professionals, ensuring reliability and efficiency in high-pressure environments. The company emphasizes strong partnerships and support, helping clients maximize revenue and streamline operations during their events.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/f3cf6714-9240-4e83-a110-66f6a6ed34eb.png', 'true', 'Medium-sized company', '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', null, null, null), ('1878', 'Lovable', 'Lovable Labs UK Limited', 'https://lovable.dev', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/lovable-dev', 'Lovable is an AI-powered full-stack development platform that allows users to create web applications using natural language prompts, eliminating the need for coding. It integrates coding, deployment, and collaboration into a single interface, enabling the development of everything from simple websites to complex applications with features like authentication, databases, and API integrations. The platform utilizes modern technologies such as React, Vite, Supabase, and Stripe, and supports continuous deployment through its integration with GitHub.

The company has introduced a unique approach called "vibe coding," where users describe the desired functionality and feel of their product, while the AI manages the implementation. This method makes app development accessible to a wide range of users, including non-coders and designers. Lovable offers various solutions and templates for different use cases, such as landing pages, portfolios, and membership platforms. With features like real-time visual editing and backend integration, Lovable has facilitated the creation of over 10 million projects and achieved significant growth in its annual recurring revenue.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/3a0cd64c-0586-4050-9332-4f02266430f8.png', 'true', 'Large company', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', 'ashby', 'https://api.ashbyhq.com/posting-api/job-board/lovable', null), ('1879', 'Proteus Marine Renewables', 'Proteus Tidal (Scotland) Limited', 'https://proteusmr.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/proteus-marine-resources', 'Proteus Marine Renewables is a leading marine renewable energy company that specializes in tidal energy systems. With over 20 years of experience, the company provides a complete end-to-end solution that includes consultancy, design, testing, production, installation, operations, and maintenance of tidal energy technologies. It operates in the UK, Europe, and Japan, showcasing its global reach and commitment to advancing marine renewable energy.

The company’s core product is its tidal energy generation units, which operate quietly underwater to produce clean and reliable electricity without visual pollution or negative impacts on marine life. Proteus has successfully deployed tidal turbines in significant projects, including the MeyGen project in Scotland and Japan’s first 1.1 MW tidal turbine in the Naru Strait. Their services encompass specialized design, development of tidal turbines, and ongoing operations and maintenance, all aimed at ensuring system reliability and supporting the viability of marine renewable projects. Proteus collaborates with industry partners to enhance tidal energy solutions and is dedicated to providing affordable renewable energy for the future.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/1f903ed7-93e5-41c9-8d0a-dc66b96a7a9d.png', 'true', 'Small company', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', 'bamboohr', 'proteus', null), ('1880', 'Talan', 'Talan UK & Ireland Limited', 'https://www.talan.com/uk/en', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/talan', 'Talan is a global technology and consulting group that specializes in accelerating client transformation through innovation, technology, and data. With over 20 years of experience, Talan supports enterprises and public institutions in implementing transformation projects across France and internationally. The company operates in 21 countries on five continents, employing over 7,000 professionals and projecting significant revenue growth.

Talan positions itself as a data-driven partner, combining business expertise with technological mastery. It offers a wide range of services, including artificial intelligence, blockchain, Internet of Things, digital strategy consulting, and IT solutions optimization. In the Americas, Talan also focuses on IBM Maximo services, helping medium and large companies enhance their operations. The company is committed to sustainable and human-centric innovation, ensuring that technology serves to enhance human potential.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '6', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/3a82aa8c-9dbd-4f13-87a6-b7e7bd1f6ea9.png', 'true', 'Very large company', '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', 'smartrecruiters', 'talan', null), ('1881', 'AmaranthLabs', 'Amaranthlabs Ltd', 'https://amaranthlabs.co.uk', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/amaranthlabs', 'AmaranthLabs is a B2B food ingredients company dedicated to unlocking the full potential of amaranth – one of the most nutrient-dense and sustainable crops on the planet. Our mission is to develop the most functional and scalable plant-based ingredients, enabling the future of food, nutrition, and beyond.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/c6ec64e5-4899-49e8-93bb-df17dbac1ab7.png', 'true', 'Very small company', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', null, null, null), ('1882', 'Audio Venue', 'AUDIO VENUE LIMITED', 'https://www.audiovenue.uk', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/audiovenue', 'Audio Venue, specialists in bespoke home cinema and home audio systems. Years of expertise in designing the very best home cinema, multiroom and audio systems available.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/e92bd973-13c1-4bd2-b7ea-ef16b403f408.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', null, null, null), ('1883', 'Ballintaggart', 'Ballintaggart Hotel', 'https://ballintaggart.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/ballintaggart', 'Surrounded by the rolling hills of the Tay Valley, at the heart of Scotland''s natural larder, two charming venues offering the chance to escape, indulge and immerse yourself in the beauty and flavours of this ancient and wild place.  

Make yourself comfortable in one of our twelve individually designed bedrooms, and enjoy eating or learning to cook fabulous food centred on the finest Scottish ingredients. 

Expect a personal welcome, relaxing and charming surroundings and outstanding Scottish food as standard.

OUR LOCATIONS

Ballintaggart Farm, where our story began, enjoys an elevated position with spectacular views over the valley. With two individually designed rooms, kitchen, The Cook School by Ballintaggart, Kitchen Garden, orchard and happy hens, the farm is a luxury, home from home experience. Nearby, East End Cottage has two delightful rooms offering alternative accommodation.

An extraordinary restaurant with rooms, outstanding yet informal dining featuring the best the seasons and Scottish larder have to offer and Seasonal Feasts all help make Ballintaggart Farm unique.  The Cook School by Ballintaggart, a venue with a library, barn, Kitchen Garden and orchard are all part of what makes Ballintaggart farm such a special destination. 

A short, five minute drive along the route once favoured by Queen Victoria, leads to The Grandtully Hotel, built in 1866. Positioned by the river, the hotel has eight charming bedrooms, a restaurant, bar, private dining room and outside terrace.

Taking its lead from Ballintaggart Farm, The Grandtully Hotel by Ballintaggart is focused on an exceptional Scottish food and drink experience. 

The former grandeur of the space has been restored with passion and an eye for contemporary design. Antiques sit comfortably next to today''s foraged bounty, cocktails together with tempting bar snacks. A sophisticated yet welcoming experience at any time of day or night.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/6c16bfe2-9f2e-4d29-a1c9-b3cae919ed31.png', 'true', 'Small company', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', null, null, null), ('1884', 'Xinix', 'Calldesk Limited t/a XINIX', 'https://xinix.co.uk', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/xinixuk', 'Xinix is a UK-based global telecommunications service provider that specializes in delivering quality and affordable telecom solutions to small and medium-sized enterprises (SMEs) and corporate businesses. Established in 2006, Xinix focuses on modernizing communication, collaboration, and connectivity through cloud-based environments to support the evolving digital workplace.The company offers a wide range of services, including high-quality VoIP solutions for reliable business communication, various network services like Ethernet and high-speed broadband, secure data transmission solutions, hosted PBX and cloud telephony systems, and mobile communication services. Xinix is known for its super-fast broadband and SIP trunk services, all backed by strong customer support. With a presence in the UK, Europe, the US, and Canada, Xinix is recognized for providing scalable and cost-effective telecommunications solutions tailored to meet the needs of its clients.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/a7859da5-f76f-4435-9000-b1d13f29ba2e.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', null, null, null), ('1885', 'Firmament', 'Firmament Capital Advisors UK LLP', 'https://firmament.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/the-firmament-group', 'Firmament is a private equity and investment management firm that specializes in providing tailored equity and debt capital solutions to small- and medium-sized enterprises (SMEs) in the lower-middle market. The firm focuses on control equity, minority equity, and growth debt capital for businesses with annual recurring revenues typically between $5 million and $25 million. Firmament aims to be a value-added partner to entrepreneurs and management teams, helping them scale and grow their businesses.

The company concentrates its investments in three main sectors: technology, healthcare, and environmental services. In technology, it invests in software and supply chain management systems, while in healthcare, it targets service and software companies with significant growth potential. In the environmental sector, Firmament focuses on specialty manufacturing and service companies dedicated to environmental solutions. Additionally, the firm offers customized debt financing solutions, including senior and junior debt, tailored to meet the needs of middle-market businesses. 

Firmament operates in the United States and the United Kingdom, emphasizing trust, vision, and stewardship in its partnerships.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/21035856-c0b0-420c-bf8a-a09ca46899b8.png', 'true', 'Medium-sized company', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', null, null, null), ('1886', 'Stowe Family Law', 'Stowe Family Law LLP', 'https://www.stowefamilylaw.co.uk', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/stowe-family-law', 'Stowe Family Law LLP is the UK''s largest specialist family law firm, established in 1982 and based in Leeds. With around 90 offices across major cities and market towns, the firm employs over 170 family lawyers who collectively bring more than 800 years of experience. Their team includes forensic accountants, adoption specialists, surrogacy law experts, and trained mediators.

