e company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/c4226e6d-e52c-4459-8140-25ab4cc55908.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', null, null, null), ('1894', 'Beavertown', 'Beavertown Brewery Limited', 'https://beavertownbrewery.co.uk', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/beavertown-brewery-ltd', 'Beavertown Brewery is a British craft beer company founded in 2011 by Logan Plant in De Beauvoir Town, London. It began as a small operation brewing with a 50-litre rice pan and has since grown into one of the UK’s largest independent craft brewers, now located in Tottenham, North London. The brewery has a production capacity of 500,000 hectolitres per year following a major expansion in 2020.The company is known for its innovative and flavorful beers, particularly India Pale Ales (IPAs) and seasonal brews. Beavertown''s vibrant branding, created in collaboration with Creative Director Nick Dwyer, draws inspiration from pop culture and Victorian illustrations, enhancing the consumer experience. Beavertown offers a broad portfolio of craft beers, an online shop for beer and merchandise, and a taproom experience, including a presence at Tottenham Hotspur Stadium as the official craft beer partner. The brand appeals to craft beer enthusiasts, supermarket shoppers, and sports fans alike, solidifying its position in the UK craft beer scene.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/2c4f5b50-502f-4b9c-bb57-1862afa76c8d.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', null, null, null), ('1895', 'Lewmar', 'Lewmar Ltd', 'https://www.lewmar.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/lewmar', 'Lewmar is a prominent global manufacturer of leisure marine equipment, focusing on products for yachts, sailboats, and powerboats. Established in 1946 by Len Lewrey, the company has evolved into a respected brand known for its high-quality marine products. Under the leadership of John Burton, who acquired the company in 1967, Lewmar became a pioneer in high-technology marine solutions, including the first winch package for the America''s Cup.

