For job seekers, Jack offers services such as personalized job matching, CV feedback, interview preparation simulations, and career coaching. He continuously searches for new job postings to find relevant opportunities. For employers, Jill streamlines recruitment workflows through automated candidate sourcing and screening, ensuring efficient matching of candidates to roles. Companies only pay a fee if a hire is made through the platform.

Jack and Jill aims to humanize the recruitment experience by providing empathetic interactions that help candidates articulate their aspirations and assist companies in identifying the best talent. The platform is designed to be a smarter alternative to traditional recruitment methods, focusing on quality, personalization, and an engaging user experience.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/58e125b8-d930-4e16-83a0-199f3f6b19ea.png', 'true', 'Small company', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', 'breezy', 'jack', null), ('1932', 'GVI', 'GVI Travel Limited', 'https://www.gvi.co.uk', 'https://www.linkedin.com/school/gvitravel/', 'Join GVI''s volunteer and internship programs! Make a sustainable impact while boosting your personal and professional growth. Your journey starts here.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '2', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/8ef051b0-3a9b-42c4-bd28-faee9d5b7d6b.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', 'bamboohr', 'gvi', null), ('1933', 'Kadmos', 'KDMS Payments Limited', 'https://www.kadmos.io', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/kadmos-io', 'Kadmos is a fintech company founded in 2021, with headquarters in Berlin and London. It specializes in end-to-end digital salary payment solutions for international employees, focusing on seafarers and migrant workers. The company aims to enhance the salary payment experience by digitizing crew payroll and automating payment processes, which helps reduce administrative costs.

Kadmos offers a comprehensive platform that includes an employer web app for automating salary payments and an employee mobile app for instant salary access. The platform also features a global debit card for convenient spending and cash withdrawals worldwide. With competitive foreign exchange rates and low transaction fees, Kadmos ensures secure and cost-effective transactions. The platform supports multiple payment methods and currencies, integrating seamlessly with accounting and CRM systems.

Kadmos primarily serves shipowners, ship-management companies, and their global workforce, as well as other industries employing international migrant workers. In 2025, Kadmos was acquired by Nippon Yusen Kabushiki Kaisha (NYK) to expand its digital salary payment services and enhance financial inclusion for maritime workers worldwide.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '4', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/bf01c50f-e8a1-4dc3-b3dc-e3c009b9381e.png', 'true', 'Small company', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', 'greenhouse', 'kadmos3', null), ('1934', 'Priory', 'Priory Group', 'https://www.priorygroup.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/priory', 'Priory Group is a prominent UK provider of mental health care and addiction rehabilitation services, established in 1980. With over 500 sites across the country, it offers more than 7,000 beds for patients. The group provides a wide range of services, including inpatient and outpatient care, secure and non-secure facilities, and rehabilitation clinics. Additionally, Priory is involved in specialist education and care for children and young adults, particularly those with autism spectrum disorders.

The company serves individuals seeking treatment for mental health conditions and addiction, as well as local authorities and NHS Clinical Commissioning Groups. Priory has expanded its offerings through acquisitions, enhancing its healthcare and education services. It operates under private equity ownership and maintains a significant presence in both the healthcare and education sectors, positioning itself as a key player in the UK market.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/7a25ad6d-a483-4148-82a1-c8bd5cebcfa4.png', 'true', 'Very large company', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', null, null, null), ('1935', 'Tillo', 'Reward Cloud Ltd t/a Tillo', 'https://www.tillo.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/tillo', 'Tillo is an embedded rewards and incentives platform that helps businesses drive growth by connecting them with rewards from over 2,000 global brands. It specializes in digital e-gift cards and offers innovative solutions for customer engagement and retention throughout the customer lifecycle. Tillo’s platform provides seamless access to a wide range of gift cards and incentives.

The core service is a plug-and-play API that integrates easily with business systems, allowing for effortless management and delivery of rewards. Tillo operates in 37 markets and supports 16 currencies, having processed over $2 billion in gift cards. Its offerings include real-time digital e-gift cards, the Tillo StoreFront for branded gift card catalogs, and support for various innovative use cases like embedded rewards and cashback alternatives. Tillo is designed for businesses looking to enhance customer loyalty and improve their rewards processes through a diverse selection of gift cards.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '4', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/bf83e8e3-dca6-4e44-b5d0-53f7ba78e5ec.png', 'true', 'Medium-sized company', '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', null, null, null), ('1936', 'V-Count', 'V-Count UK LTD', 'https://v-count.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/v-count', 'V-Count is a global technology company that specializes in AI-powered people counting and visitor analytics solutions. With over 18 years of experience in computer vision and pattern recognition, V-Count has developed patented technologies that ensure privacy-assured tracking and analytics. The company offers a range of products, including the Nano Series of eco-friendly sensors and the BoostBI analytics platform, which provide accurate visitor counts and actionable insights for businesses.

V-Count serves a diverse array of industries, such as retail, airports, shopping malls, and public spaces, helping clients enhance operational efficiency and improve customer experiences. The company has a strong global presence, with over 600 customers, including more than 11 Fortune 500 companies, across 128 countries. V-Count is recognized as a market leader in its field, known for its innovative technology and significant market share.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/586d5aa0-059c-43fb-9c40-ee7fe3d7d3fb.png', 'true', 'Medium-sized company', '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', null, null, null), ('1937', 'Hedyn', 'Tai Hedyn Limited', 'https://hedyn.wales', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/hedyn-wales', 'Hedyn is a social housing landlord organization formed on April 1, 2025, through the merger of Melin Homes and Newport City Homes. It operates in five local authority areas in south-east Wales, managing over 15,000 properties. The organization is dedicated to supporting residents and communities, focusing on not just housing but also community development.

Hedyn''s vision is to create connected communities where everyone can thrive. The name "Hedyn," meaning "seed" in Welsh, reflects its mission of growth and positive change. The company provides social housing and related landlord services, emphasizing resources and support to enhance residents'' quality of life. With a commitment to transparency and accountability, Hedyn engages actively with its residents and stakeholders to understand community needs.

Led by Chief Executive Paula Kennedy, Hedyn''s governance includes a diverse board of 12 members, ensuring strong oversight and strategic direction. The organization is guided by core values that emphasize integrity, action, and making a difference in the communities it serves.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/47cf3edc-7bdb-432e-86b2-6e327680ec0c.png', 'true', 'Medium-sized company', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', null, null, null), ('1938', 'Datox', 'Datox Ltd', 'https://datox.ai', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/datox-ai', 'Datox is on a mission to transform financial regulatory reporting. Our mission is to revolutionize how financial services companies handle regulatory requirements through our AI-powered automation platform, ensuring accuracy, efficiency, and compliance across various jurisdictions.

Our Vision:

Navigating complex financial regulations from entities like the FCA and SEC can be challenging. Our vision is to bridge the gap between financial institutions and regulatory bodies, providing an intelligent, automated solution that adapts to the evolving regulatory landscape.

Datox focuses on automating the preparation and submission of a wide range of financial regulatory reports, including:

AIFMD (Annex IV)
MiFID II Transaction
EMIR Trade
Solvency II
PRIIPs KID
SEC Filings (Form 10-K, 10-Q, 8-K, etc.)
Basel III Compliance
FATCA and CRS

Our platform handles data from various sources, performs complex calculations, and ensures compliance with the latest regulations.

Innovations We''re Bringing:

AI-Powered Automation: Our platform uses AI and machine learning to automate data extraction, processing, and reporting, reducing manual work and errors.
Regulatory Compliance: Continuously updated to meet the latest FCA, SEC, and global regulations, minimizing non-compliance risks.
Seamless Integration: Integrates with your existing systems and data sources, handling all formats.
User-Friendly Interface: An intuitive interface that simplifies reporting and provides actionable insights.
Comprehensive Support: Our experts offer training, consultation, and ongoing assistance.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/233352c7-a853-463b-83e7-087e92436573.png', 'true', 'Small company', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', null, null, null), ('1939', 'Digital Manufacturing Centre (DMC)', 'Digital Manufacturing Centre Ltd', 'https://www.digitalmanufacturingcentre.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/digital-manufacturing-centre', 'The Digital Manufacturing Centre (DMC) is a UK-based advanced production facility and innovation hub located at Silverstone Park. Established in 2019, DMC specializes in additive manufacturing (AM) and offers a range of services that include the production of metal and polymer components. The facility utilizes state-of-the-art technologies to enhance material properties and reduce component weight and assembly steps.

DMC provides engineering solutions aimed at improving production efficiency across various sectors, including aerospace, defence, motorsport, automotive, and medical industries. The company is known for its agile manufacturing techniques, enabling rapid production and adaptation to market demands. With a dedicated team and significant technical capabilities, DMC supports high-performance engineering projects and championship-winning motorsport teams. The company is part-funded by SEMLEP’s Local Growth Fund and collaborates with industry leaders to drive innovation in manufacturing.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/facf4254-74c9-495b-af9f-1e28c4f101ce.png', 'true', 'Small company', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', null, null, null), ('1940', 'INDUSTRY of Us', 'INDUSTRY of Us Limited', 'https://www.industryofus.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/industry-of-us', 'INDUSTRY of Us is a UK-based insight and innovation agency that focuses on a people-centered approach to help businesses tackle contemporary and future innovation challenges. Established in January 2019, the company specializes in management consultancy activities and offers a range of services designed to foster innovation.

Their offerings include global consumer research to inspire teams, ideation workshops that enhance creativity, and design-led training courses aimed at empowering teams. They also assist organizations in defining future scenarios to build resilience and confidence in their strategic directions. By combining consumer insights, creative ideation, and iterative experimentation, INDUSTRY of Us supports business innovators in enhancing their innovation capabilities and developing effective strategies.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/e211e45e-b11a-48e3-b9a5-aa566c57844a.png', 'true', 'Small company', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', null, null, null), ('1941', 'Stiff + Trevillion', 'STIFF AND TREVILLION ARCHITECTS LIMITED', 'https://www.stiffandtrevillion.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/stiff---trevillion-architects', 'Stiff + Trevillion Architects is a London-based architectural practice founded in 1981 by Michael Stiff and Andrew Trevillion. The firm employs 30 to 40 staff, including architects, interior designers, and graphic designers, and operates from a spacious open-plan studio near Notting Hill. They focus on creating stylish and timeless buildings and interiors that are tailored to their clients'' aspirations and the surrounding environment.The company offers a wide range of architectural and interior design services, including new buildings, refurbishments, and masterplanning. Their work spans commercial buildings, high-end residential projects, and hospitality venues, with notable projects including the first Wagamama and Giraffe restaurants, as well as various Italian restaurants for celebrity chef Jamie Oliver. Stiff + Trevillion has completed over 2,000 projects, primarily in London and the UK, and is recognized for its collaborative approach with clients throughout the design process. The firm has received multiple awards for its work, highlighting its commitment to quality and innovation in design.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/c8f994ae-6f71-47a4-be60-a978ccdd0cb2.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', null, null, null), ('1942', 'Cimple', 'Cimple Limited', 'https://cimple.uk', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/cimple-limited', 'As specialists in the field, we know how confusing, intimidating and complex the procurement process can be. We''re working to demystify procurement and make it more accessible and intuitive for everyone.

We''re nurturing a platform that promotes transparency, fairness and trust, providing both public and private sector buyers and suppliers with the guidance and tools they need to forge valuable partnerships and make profitable decisions.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/5a48dfd4-ccd3-4da0-8e16-f8b606b72c46.png', 'true', 'Very small company', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', null, null, null), ('1943', 'MATA Architects', 'MATA Architects Limited', 'https://www.mata-architects.co.uk', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/mataarchitects', 'MATA Architects is an RIBA chartered architecture practice based in Westminster, Central London. The practice was founded in 2015 by Dan Marks as a collaborative studio to develop projects at a range of scales; from bespoke furniture to new build and open space/public realm. 

We believe in the value of thoughtful and considered architecture that puts people and communities first. And in the power and capability of inventive and original design to act as a catalyst for positive change. 

Whether residential, commercial, public or cultural, the spaces we make have the ability to profoundly affect everyday lives. We want to make places that change people''s lives for the better - places that inspire and enrich, not only the lives of all who experience them, but also of those involved in the collaborative process of making them.

We believe that architecture should be of it''s place, responding to local context; landscape, culture, history and economy, whilst also bold enough to be original. It is this tension between the old and the new that ultimately produces architecture that is both thought provoking and durable.

Our work is guided by the fundamentals – manipulation of light and shadow, honest use of materials put together with the aim of creating spaces that are beautiful but at the same time functional and pragmatic.

We enjoy working closely with our clients to create an open and collaborative relationship that results in crafted and bespoke solutions.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/6d5476be-b82d-4c81-940a-8e94bb6ca1a3.png', 'true', 'Very small company', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', null, null, null), ('1944', 'ISO', 'Studio ISO Limited', 'https://studio-iso.io', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/studio-iso-io', 'Studio ISO was founded to close a critical implementation gap: companies build smarter tech, but struggle to create technology that makes sense to people. This challenge is compounded by impractical designs that prioritise technical sophistication over human understanding. We help technology companies bridge the divide between what their breakthrough technology can do and what people actually need.What sets us apart:Strategic Thinking Transformation - We reshape how companies approach technology and markets, shifting mindsets beyond tactical solutions.Hardware Specialisation - Unique expertise in turning intangible technology into compelling physical products people actually want.Business Impact Focus - We solve business issues through design, not create showcase pieces that look impressive but don''t perform.We specialise in: Companies at the intersection of hardware and intelligence - whether you''re integrating tech into physical products, scaling IoT ecosystems, or designing the next generation of autonomous systems.Recent impact: → Guided autonomous robotics company to $150M investment with clear 2030 vision → Transformed smart home platform into #1 market leader with 5M connected homes → Unified AI assistant startup strategy, expanding portfolio from 10 to 100 SKUs with 50M+ active users.For technology companies facing:-Complex technical challenges requiring strategic design input-Pressure to integrate technology capabilities thoughtfully-Need to balance innovation with usability-Software-to-hardware transitionsKey sectors: IoT Manufacturing | Smart Home Tech | Robotics | Industrial Automation | Consumer Electronics | Clean Tech HardwareReady to turn your breakthrough technology into human-centred success? Let''s connect.mail@studio-iso.io', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/873c744a-c3ba-48d5-9751-a2ab17099fbe.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', null, null, null), ('1945', 'Hybrid Air Vehicles', 'Hybrid Air Vehicles Limited', 'https://www.hybridairvehicles.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/hybrid-air-vehicles-ltd', 'Hybrid Air Vehicles (HAV) is a UK-based aerospace company established in 2007. The company specializes in the design, development, and manufacture of hybrid aircraft that utilize lighter-than-air technology combined with aerodynamic lift and vectored thrust. HAV is headquartered in Bedford, England, and operates as a private limited company.

The flagship product of HAV is the Airlander 10, a hybrid airship that can take off and land on nearly any flat surface. It boasts long endurance capabilities of up to five days in the air and a low carbon footprint compared to traditional aircraft. The Airlander 10 can accommodate up to 100 passengers or a 10-tonne freight payload, making it versatile for various applications such as surveillance, search and rescue, cargo transport, and eco-tourism. HAV aims to lead in zero-emissions aviation, with significant investments and a strong market presence, targeting a global market valued at over $1 trillion.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/0bd2d03b-d86f-4784-9b9e-5ddc816b5978.png', 'true', 'Medium-sized company', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', 'teamtailor', 'hybridairvehicleslimited', null), ('1946', 'Nano Fibre UK', 'Nano Fibre UK LImited', 'https://nanofibre.co.uk', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/nano-fibre-uk-limited', 'Nano Fibre UK Limited is a private limited company based in Gilmorton, England, established on May 11, 2016. The company specializes in FTTP (Fibre to the Premises) installations, providing ultrafast fibre broadband directly to homes across the UK. Its mission is to enhance digital connectivity in residential areas by delivering efficient and precise fibre installation services.In addition to FTTP installations, Nano Fibre UK offers engineering and technical consulting services to support its core operations. The company serves residential customers, focusing on last-mile fibre broadband connections and continuously expanding its service coverage. With a commitment to customer satisfaction and operational excellence, Nano Fibre UK aims to connect communities to reliable, high-speed internet.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/59e03850-8243-4149-9641-98f59db11357.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', 'breezy', 'nano-fibre-uk', null), ('1947', 'Renaissance Strategic Advisors', 'Renaissance Strategic Advisors Ltd', 'https://rsadvisors.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/renaissance-strategic-advisors', 'Renaissance Strategic Advisors is a global advisory firm focused on the aerospace, defense, space, intelligence, and government services sectors. With offices in Arlington, VA; London, UK; Paris, France; and Melbourne, Australia, the firm provides expert strategy consulting and M&A advisory services to corporate clients and financial investors.

The company’s mission is to deliver confidence and clarity to clients through deep sector expertise and rigorous analysis. Their team of approximately 75 specialists brings diverse backgrounds in government, military, investment banking, and management consulting, allowing for a comprehensive approach to strategy development and implementation. Renaissance Strategic Advisors handles over 50 M&A assignments annually, offering support throughout the entire M&A lifecycle, from value creation strategy to post-close growth strategy formulation. They also produce industry-leading insights and reports on key markets, providing stakeholders with valuable market assessments and forecasts.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/121ee85b-ac2a-4748-bd07-a4207bec4818.png', 'true', 'Medium-sized company', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', 'bamboohr', 'rsadvisors', null), ('1948', 'Wrisk', 'WRISK LIMITED', 'https://www.wrisk.co', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/wrisk', 'Wrisk is a London-based technology-enabled insurance company founded in 2015, specializing in digital, customer-centric insurance products for the automotive sector. Operating as a Managing General Agent (MGA), Wrisk focuses on innovative, data-driven insurance solutions offered on a subscription basis. The company has transitioned from a direct-to-consumer model to a B2B2C approach, partnering with major brands to enhance the consumer insurance experience.

Wrisk''s flagship offerings include flexible car insurance products that allow customers to pay based on actual usage, such as miles driven. Their product portfolio features subscription-based automotive insurance with no long-term commitments, usage-based insurance that adjusts charges according to driving behavior, and embedded insurance solutions integrated into partner platforms. Additionally, Wrisk launched a real-time analytics suite in 2024 to provide partners with valuable data insights. The company aims to disrupt the traditional insurance market by delivering personalized, transparent, and flexible coverage options tailored to modern mobility and lifestyle trends.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/5cdc940c-72af-49bc-8c63-e1935f20eca7.png', 'true', 'Medium-sized company', '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', null, null, null), ('1949', '2X Global', '2X GLOBAL LIMITED', 'https://www.2xglobal.org', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/2x-global', '2X Global is a global membership organization focused on advancing gender-smart investing in both developed and emerging markets. Formed from the merger of GenderSmart and 2X Collaborative, it has been catalyzing billions in gender-smart investments since 2018. The organization operates with a fully remote team dedicated to transforming financial systems through inclusive and equitable capital deployment.

2X Global engages a diverse network of investors, capital providers, and intermediaries through various activities. These include Communities of Practice for knowledge sharing, educational forums for stakeholder alignment, and the development of shared resources like toolkits. Its flagship product, the 2X Criteria, sets a global standard for assessing investments that empower women, influencing many capital providers and businesses worldwide. The organization also facilitates connections among members through deal-sharing platforms.

With a community of over 50 institutional members and thousands of investment professionals, 2X Global actively participates in initiatives like the 2X Challenge, which has mobilized significant investments to support women''s economic empowerment. Its vision is to unlock gender-smart capital at scale, promoting positive societal and business outcomes.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/74e8dc88-aba2-42c9-8c32-75015c450dd4.png', 'true', 'Small company', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', null, null, null), ('1950', 'Autonomy Capital', 'Autonomy Capital Research LLP', 'https://autonomycapital.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/autonomy-capital', 'Autonomy Capital is a global investment firm based in New York City, with an additional office in London. Founded by Robert Gibbins, the firm specializes in hedge fund management and investment strategies that focus on emerging markets and global macroeconomic trends. With a team of approximately 35 employees, Autonomy Capital aims to deliver superior returns by embracing unconventional investment approaches.

The firm serves a diverse clientele, including institutional investors and high-net-worth individuals, who are interested in innovative investment solutions. Autonomy Capital emphasizes a culture of challenging the status quo within the financial sector, positioning itself as a forward-thinking player in investment management. Its strategies are designed to capitalize on unique market opportunities and disrupt traditional financial practices.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/ead8f9e8-db96-43f6-8b59-03521fdf6d10.png', 'true', 'Small company', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', 'bamboohr', 'autonomycapital', null), ('1951', 'Blue Whale Growth Fund', 'Blue Whale Capital LLP', 'https://bluewhale.co.uk', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/blue-whale-capital', 'Blue Whale Growth Fund is an investment fund that focuses on capital growth through global large-cap equities. It aims to achieve capital appreciation over a five-year period by investing at least 80% of its assets in a concentrated portfolio of 25 to 35 stocks worldwide, including emerging markets. 

The fund is designed for investors seeking growth through equity investments and can be held in various investment wrappers such as ISAs, SIPPs, and general investment accounts. It offers a managed equity portfolio that emphasizes growth stocks and provides diversification across sectors and geographies. The fund is actively managed to select companies with strong growth prospects and is available in different share classes, including accumulation and income options, to cater to various investor preferences.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/bd9ab8c2-033c-4897-a42a-66f3b221a42f.png', 'true', 'Small company', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', 'lever', 'blue', null), ('1952', 'Brindisa', 'Brindisa Ltd', 'https://brindisa.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/brindisa-ltd', 'Brindisa is a London-based company founded in 1988 by Monika Linton, dedicated to introducing and celebrating authentic Spanish gastronomy in the UK. The name Brindisa comes from the Spanish word *brindis*, which means to raise a glass in a toast, reflecting the company''s cultural ethos. Initially starting as a small importer of Spanish cheeses, Brindisa has grown into a multifaceted business with a focus on artisan and family-produced Spanish foods.

