tes approximately $7.1 million in revenue. The company has built a strong reputation for trust and excellence in the precision engineering sector.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/b20f2580-08c8-4ce9-8b8f-268d361d3b64.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', 'teamtailor', 'pentaprecision', null), ('1968', 'aosphere', 'aosphere Limited', 'https://www.aosphere.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/aosphere', 'aosphere is a UK-based legal services company founded in 2002 and headquartered in London. It specializes in comprehensive online legal risk management products that help businesses operate efficiently while minimizing legal and regulatory risks worldwide. With a team of over 40 senior lawyers and legal experts, the company serves more than 1,300 clients and 18,000 individual users.

