The company is heavily invested in artificial intelligence, utilizing a robust infrastructure to enhance its products. With 2,000 GPUs dedicated to photo enhancement, Bending Spoons processes millions of photos and makes billions of AI predictions daily. Its growth strategy involves acquiring promising software companies, improving them, and reinvesting profits for further acquisitions. Bending Spoons employs over 400 people from 39 countries, promoting a diverse and collaborative work environment. The company is also committed to social responsibility, engaging in initiatives to support STEM education and environmental sustainability.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/7236ebc1-ec16-4d1f-89b5-61f17792bb40.png', 'true', 'Large company', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', null, null, null), ('1976', 'Thaleron', 'Thaleron Limited', 'https://www.thaleron.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/thaleron', 'Thaleron Limited is a UK-based private company that specializes in developing innovative mechanical energy storage solutions. Founded on January 31, 2022, and headquartered in Maidenhead and Woking, the company focuses on providing cost-effective, large-scale energy storage systems to support the energy transition and enhance renewable energy integration.

Thaleron''s core offering is a new mechanical energy storage technology designed to be more affordable and scalable than existing solutions. The company emphasizes rapid prototyping and practical engineering, utilizing a small, skilled team to address complex challenges in the energy sector. Their services include the development of mechanical energy storage systems aimed at utilities, renewable energy developers, and grid operators seeking to improve energy reliability and sustainability. 

With a commitment to advancing energy storage technology, Thaleron is positioned to play a significant role in the climate technology and engineering sectors.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '2', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/bbc7cbb0-bc91-4576-9bc0-6c7c8cdba4cf.png', 'true', 'Small company', '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', null, null, null), ('1977', 'Cora Health', 'CORA HEALTH LIMITED', 'https://www.corahealth.co.uk', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/corahealth1', 'Cora Health (FKA Connect Health) is a UK-based community healthcare provider that specializes in musculoskeletal (MSK), mental health, and pain management services. Established in 1989 and headquartered in Newcastle Upon Tyne, the company has a strong presence in the healthcare sector. In December 2024, Connect Health merged with Healthshare to form Cora Health, creating a multi-disciplinary healthcare services provider.Connect Health offers a range of services, including assessment, treatment, and rehabilitation for MSK conditions, community-based mental health support, and pain management programs. The merger with Healthshare has expanded its offerings to include surgical and diagnostic services, enhancing its ability to provide integrated care. The primary customers are NHS Integrated Care Boards (ICBs) and other NHS bodies in England, benefiting from the comprehensive healthcare services provided by Connect Health and Cora Health.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/1de91443-35b3-49dc-8033-5e1a23a2a42c.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', null, null, null), ('1978', 'Patek Philippe', 'PATEK PHILIPPE UK LIMITED', 'https://www.patek.com/en', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/patek-philippe', 'Patek Philippe is a prestigious Swiss luxury watch manufacturer founded in 1839 in Geneva. Initially named Patek, Czapek & Cie, the company was renamed Patek Philippe & Co. in 1851 after Jean Adrien Philippe joined Antoni Norbert de Patek. Renowned for its tradition of innovation, Patek Philippe introduced the keyless winding and hand-setting mechanism, which transformed watchmaking.

The company specializes in the design, manufacture, and sale of luxury mechanical watches, including pocket watches and wristwatches. Its iconic collections, such as the Nautilus and Calatrava, are celebrated for their design, precision, and complexity. Patek Philippe is known for meticulous craftsmanship, producing watches with intricate complications and innovative features. The brand is recognized as the last independent, family-owned Genevan watch manufacturer, maintaining a strong legacy of tradition and exclusivity. Its timepieces are often considered heirlooms and status symbols, appealing to collectors and connoisseurs worldwide.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/fb0c2d6c-d43f-470f-8cba-926a196b9cb1.png', 'true', 'Very large company', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', null, null, null), ('1979', 'XBP Europe', 'XBP EUROPE LIMITED', 'https://xbpeurope.com/en-uk/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/xbp-europe', 'XBP Europe is a pan-European integrator that specializes in bills, payments, and digital solutions aimed at facilitating the digital transformation of its clients. Founded in 1998, the company has grown into a global entity with operations in Europe, North America, and Asia. It is part of XBP Global, serving over 2,500 clients, including many Fortune 100 companies, with a workforce of approximately 11,000 employees.

The company offers a range of services, including AI-powered digital transformation solutions, omni-channel bills and payments integration, and the OmniDirect platform for multi-location marketing and procurement. XBP Europe combines proprietary technology and hardware to streamline workflows and enhance transaction efficiency. Its solutions cater to various industries, such as banking, healthcare, and utilities, supporting organizations of all sizes in their digital initiatives. XBP Europe emphasizes partnership, innovation, and expertise, aiming to deliver measurable impacts while fostering a collaborative work environment.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/2b7b1a09-349b-4db0-998d-c0208e55e98e.png', 'true', 'Very large company', '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', 'workday', 'bp/BP_careers_home', null), ('1980', 'Cala Hotels', 'Cala Hotels Group Ltd', 'https://www.calahotels.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/cala-hotels-limited', 'Experience Hebridean Hospitality at Cala Hotels in Stornoway on the Isle of Lewis. Book direct for guaranteed lowest price.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/05db4321-4c98-46f3-8e45-89fa6aeeb70d.png', 'true', 'Very small company', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', null, null, null), ('1981', 'IMG', 'INTERNATIONAL MANAGEMENT GROUP (UK) LIMITED', 'https://www.img.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/img', 'IMG (International Management Group) is a global company based in New York City, specializing in sports, fashion, events, and media. Founded in 1960 by Mark McCormack, IMG has played a pivotal role in shaping the sports management industry. The company operates across six continents, in 35 countries, and over 100 cities, emphasizing a fan-first approach to marketing and content distribution.IMG offers a range of services, including athlete and celebrity management, event ownership and operation, and media production and distribution. The company also provides consulting services in media rights, fan engagement, and commercial strategy. IMG Academy serves as a premier training and education institution for athletes, offering programs in various sports. With a focus on integrating athlete representation, event management, and media production, IMG is a significant player in the global sports and entertainment landscape.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '25', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/7f0d8d9d-577f-4e62-80b9-0dc66f7fdc52.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', 'workday', 'wwecorp/IMG', null), ('1982', 'London North Eastern Railway', 'London North Eastern Railway', 'https://www.lner.co.uk', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/london-north-eastern-railway', 'The London North Eastern Railway (LNER) is a historic British railway company established in 1923. It was formed from the merger of several railway companies and became the second largest of the "Big Four" railway companies in the UK. LNER primarily managed the East Coast Main Line, connecting London with major cities in the north and east of England and Scotland, including Edinburgh, York, and Newcastle upon Tyne.

LNER was known for its high-speed rail services and operated iconic trains such as The Flying Scotsman and The Silver Jubilee, which set new standards for speed and comfort. The company also managed significant freight operations, including coal transport, and expanded into road transport by acquiring shares in bus companies. LNER served a diverse customer base, including long-distance travelers, commuters, and freight customers, while maintaining a strong commitment to customer service and innovation in rail travel. Its legacy includes a significant role in the development of high-speed rail in the UK.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/37027376-3bc7-4d1e-8566-671b6f573beb.png', 'true', 'Very large company', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', 'greenhouse', 'london', null), ('1984', 'ManvsMachine', 'Man vs Machine Limited', 'https://mvsm.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/manvsmachine', 'ManvsMachine is an independent creative company based in London and Los Angeles, specializing in design, film, motion graphics, and visual arts. Founded in 2007, it has built a strong reputation for excellence in design and innovative motion graphics. The company fosters a collaborative environment that encourages artistic exploration and emphasizes creativity and meticulous craftsmanship.

The studio offers a wide range of services, including brand identity, motion graphics, animation, film production, visual effects, and digital experiences. ManvsMachine collaborates with global brands and advertising agencies to create striking visual content, such as animated commercials, title sequences, and interactive media projects. Their work is recognized for its high quality and artistic sophistication, earning numerous industry awards.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/9a039903-7e87-438f-938f-be1caa7f8ece.png', 'true', 'Medium-sized company', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', 'greenhouse', 'manvsmachine', null), ('1985', 'Mitsui & Co.', 'Mitsui & Co. Europe Ltd', 'https://www.mitsui.com/eu/en/index.html', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/mitsui-co-ltd-', 'Mitsui & Co., Ltd. is one of Japan''s largest general trading companies, established in 1876 and reformed in 1947. With a global network of 124 offices across 62 countries, the company employs over 56,000 people. Mitsui''s diverse business activities include product sales, logistics, financing, and the development of major international infrastructure projects.The company operates in various sectors such as mineral and metal resources, energy, infrastructure, mobility, chemicals, food and retail management, wellness, and IT. Mitsui facilitates global trade, organizes joint ventures, and manages finance and transport, acting as a vital link in international supply chains. In the fiscal year ending March 2023, Mitsui reported consolidated revenues of approximately ¥5.3 trillion and a net income of ¥320 billion. Headquartered in Tokyo, Japan, Mitsui is publicly traded on the Tokyo Stock Exchange.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/c0f75996-bb37-4743-88e7-415a88b4d86a.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', null, null, null), ('1986', 'ResQ', 'ResQ Limited', 'https://resqcs.co.uk', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/resq-contact-services-limited', 'ResQ is a UK-based contact center solutions and Business Process Outsourcing (BPO) provider, headquartered in East Yorkshire. Founded in 2006, the company has grown significantly, employing around 1800 to 2000 staff across three locations and generating revenues exceeding £51 million in 2021. ResQ specializes in customized customer care and sales services, offering inbound and outbound customer service, tele-sales, and tailored customer support solutions.

The company is known for its strong emphasis on employee growth and satisfaction, boasting a low attrition rate of 5.6% and high employee satisfaction ratings. ResQ serves a diverse range of sectors, including utilities, retail, and media, and has built a reputation as a trusted partner for large, blue-chip clients. Its commitment to investing in technology and skilled personnel enables it to deliver exceptional service experiences, setting it apart in the competitive outsourcing industry.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/6d458fba-de26-4253-a872-f5e4da4a9bff.png', 'true', 'Very large company', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', null, null, null), ('1987', 'Snap Inc.', 'SNAP GROUP LIMITED', 'https://www.snap.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/snap-inc-co', 'Snap Inc. is an American technology company founded in 2011 and based in Santa Monica, California. It is primarily known as the parent company of Snapchat, a multimedia messaging app that allows users to send time-limited photos, videos, and text messages, focusing on ephemeral communication.

The company has expanded its offerings beyond the Snapchat app, which features visual communication tools, AR filters, and creative options. Snap Inc. also produces Spectacles, smart glasses that enable hands-free content capture, and Bitmoji, personalized avatars for users. Additionally, Snap Inc. provides a range of advertising services, including Snap Ads and AR Ads, helping businesses connect with a diverse audience.

With over 850 million users globally, Snap Inc. has established itself as a significant player in the tech landscape, particularly in Venice Beach, California. The company reported revenues of $5.36 billion in 2024, reflecting its commitment to innovation and growth in augmented reality and content engagement.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/613cfd9e-7809-4020-b2b2-c9434384e925.png', 'true', 'Very large company', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', 'smartrecruiters', 'snapinc', null), ('1988', 'Paramount Commerce', 'Paramount Commerce Services Limited', 'https://www.paramountcommerce.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/paramount-commerce', 'Paramount Commerce is a Canadian fintech company founded in 2003, based in Toronto, Ontario. The company specializes in real-time, bank account-based payment solutions that simplify online transactions by allowing consumers to pay directly from their bank accounts. Paramount Commerce has established itself as a leading provider in the pay-by-bank space, processing over $100 billion in payments and serving well-known brands in high-growth digital sectors such as online gaming and remittance.

The company offers a suite of customizable pay-by-bank solutions that enable businesses to accept, send, and verify bank payments with high security and efficiency. Key features include direct bank payments that lower costs, real-time payment processing for instant access to funds, and AI-driven risk management to prevent fraud. Paramount Commerce also provides technical support and development services to enhance payment platforms and user experiences. With a strong focus on regulatory compliance and data security, the company is committed to delivering innovative solutions that meet the needs of Canadian consumers.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/70c74b76-ff81-400a-b326-11aafa1099fd.png', 'true', 'Medium-sized company', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', 'bamboohr', 'paramountcommerce', null), ('1989', 'Space NK', 'Space NK Limited', 'https://www.spacenk.com/uk/home', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/spacenk', 'Space NK is a British luxury beauty retailer founded in 1991 by Nicky Kinnaird. The first store opened in Covent Garden, London, in 1993. Initially offering fresh smoothies and independent fashion labels, Space NK has since focused exclusively on beauty products, becoming a destination for niche and innovative brands known for their quality and luxury.

The company operates an omnichannel retail model with 67 stores across the UK and Ireland and 29 stores in the US, including flagship locations in New York City. Space NK launched its online store in 2004, expanding its reach to beauty enthusiasts. The retailer offers a curated selection of skincare, cosmetics, and beauty gadgets, along with a loyalty program called N.dulge to enhance customer engagement. Known for exclusive brand partnerships and unique customer experiences, Space NK also provides a satisfaction guarantee and a straightforward returns policy for unopened products.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/7f589ad3-d2b4-4f7d-822e-855d213fefc2.png', 'true', 'Large company', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', 'breezy', 'space-nk', null), ('1990', 'Thrive', 'THRIVE TECHNOLOGY LTD', 'https://www.thrivetech.co', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/thrivetechnology', 'Thrive Technologies specializes in AI-driven supply chain planning and inventory optimization solutions for wholesale distributors. Founded over 20 years ago, the company focuses on enhancing profitability for multi-location distributors by improving inventory management without the need for large software implementations. Thrive was an early adopter of the SaaS model, establishing itself as a technology innovator in the field.

The company offers two main products: Thermostock® and Tiltmeter®. These AI-powered tools help clients manage unpredictable demand and identify inventory issues, such as stockouts and dead stock. Thrive''s solutions enhance purchasing systems by quickly responding to changes in demand and supply, leading to improved inventory turns and fill rates. With a commitment to research and development, Thrive invests over 20% of its annual revenue to continuously enhance its offerings and provide value to clients.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/51fbf170-e3ec-4474-93a0-650e13d62c8b.png', 'true', 'Small company', '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', 'greenhouse', 'thrive', null), ('1991', 'Data Innovations', 'PGP (UK) Ltd t/as Data Innovations', 'https://www.datainnovations.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/data-innovations-inc-', 'Data Innovations LLC is a global software company based in Colchester, Vermont, specializing in lab enablement software and solutions. With over 35 years of experience, the company focuses on optimizing clinical laboratory performance to enhance patient care. It serves more than 6,000 hospitals and laboratories across over 85 countries, establishing itself as a leader in laboratory enterprise management.

The company offers a comprehensive suite of software solutions that include lab connectivity tools, productivity enhancements, quality and performance management, advanced analytics, and instrument validation services. These solutions promote interoperability and support an open ecosystem, allowing laboratories of all sizes to improve efficiency and gain valuable insights. Data Innovations is committed to fostering a mission-driven culture that values innovation, inclusion, and employee well-being.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/f7ef87e4-1323-4f19-b838-93802188bfc5.png', 'true', 'Large company', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', null, null, null), ('1992', 'Mooncup', '&SISTERS LTD', 'https://wearemooncup.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/mooncup-ltd', 'Mooncup Ltd is a UK-based company that specializes in the manufacture and retail of menstrual care products. Incorporated on July 31, 2023, the company is located in London and focuses on providing innovative solutions for menstrual hygiene. 

Best known for creating the world''s first medical-grade silicone menstrual cup in 2002, Mooncup Ltd offers a reusable and hypoallergenic alternative to traditional disposable products. Their menstrual cups are designed without petroleum plastics or hidden ingredients, emphasizing safety and sustainability. The company targets menstruating individuals who value health, environmental impact, and cost-effectiveness in their menstrual care choices. Products are available through specialized retail channels and online platforms, ensuring accessibility and convenience for customers.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/b4653f69-d18a-4f98-9b3f-58b597900005.png', 'true', 'Small company', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', null, null, null), ('1993', 'Crockett & Jones', 'Crockett and Jones Ltd', 'https://www.crockettandjones.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/crockett-and-jones-limited', 'Crockett & Jones Limited is a distinguished British shoe manufacturer established in 1879 in Northampton, England. The company specializes in high-quality, Goodyear-welted footwear, a traditional construction method known for its durability and repairability. It remains family-owned, currently managed by the great-grandson of co-founder Charles Jones, and operates from its historic factory on Magee Street.

The company offers a range of men''s footwear, including the Hand Grade Collection, Main Collection, and Shell Cordovan Collection, each reflecting meticulous craftsmanship and timeless style. For women, Crockett & Jones produces a limited selection of boots and low-heeled shoes, maintaining the same high standards. The brand is recognized globally, exporting about 70% of its production to various markets, including the USA, Australia, and South Africa. With over 250 employees and a strong financial standing, Crockett & Jones continues to thrive in the luxury footwear market, appealing to customers who appreciate traditional craftsmanship and quality materials.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/b380810f-e265-4db9-8061-b396746d3dee.png', 'true', 'Large company', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', null, null, null), ('1994', 'Dishoom', 'Dishoom Ltd TA Dishoom', 'https://www.dishoom.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/dishoom', 'Dishoom is a UK-based restaurant group founded in 2010 by cousins Shamil and Kavi Thakrar. Inspired by the Irani cafés of Bombay, the company aims to provide an authentic dining experience that reflects the culture and cuisine of the city. With a distinctive mid-20th century Bombay café aesthetic, Dishoom combines quality Indian food with a warm and inviting atmosphere.

Operating multiple locations across the UK, including eight in England and one in Edinburgh, Dishoom serves over 40,000 diners weekly and employs around 900 people. The brand is known for popularizing Indian breakfasts and redefining perceptions of Indian cuisine in the UK. Dishoom prioritizes quality and hospitality, focusing on creating memorable guest experiences and fostering a strong brand culture.

In addition to its culinary offerings, Dishoom engages in cultural projects such as an album, a play, and a cookbook, all celebrating the heritage of Bombay’s Irani cafés. The restaurants are well-regarded and often attract long queues, showcasing their popularity and significant presence in the UK dining scene.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '1', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/c6cf0f59-3a27-4a84-a9ef-18bedb2be661.png', 'true', 'Very large company', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', null, null, null), ('1995', 'Knorr-Bremse', 'Knorr-Bremse Rail Systems (UK) Limited', 'https://rail.knorr-bremse.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/knorr-bremse', 'Knorr-Bremse AG is a German multinational company founded in 1905, specializing in braking systems and safety-critical components for rail and commercial road vehicles. As a global market leader in braking technology, the company emphasizes safety, efficiency, and innovation in its products.

The company designs and manufactures advanced braking systems for passenger and freight trains, including pneumatic and electronic solutions. It also supplies air brake systems for trucks, buses, and other commercial vehicles. With a strong focus on adapting to evolving traffic demands and regulatory standards, Knorr-Bremse holds around 12,000 patents, reflecting its commitment to continuous innovation. In fiscal 2023, the company generated revenues of approximately EUR 7.9 billion.

Knorr-Bremse serves a diverse customer base, including railway operators and commercial vehicle manufacturers worldwide. Its products are integral to rail networks and commercial fleets across various regions, supported by long-standing partnerships that contribute to its market leadership.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/497d8178-fd2e-4529-8ccb-b970fb0f3029.png', 'true', 'Very large company', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', null, null, null), ('1996', 'FLS', 'FLSmidth UK Limited', 'https://fls.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/163852/', 'FLS is a leading, full flowsheet minerals processing supplier to the global mining industry. We deliver proven technologies and services across the lifecycle of operations, and have set targets of providing solutions for zero-emissions mining by 2030 with our MissionZero programme.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/ca938ddb-eaa7-4775-b203-9e859fcd82f3.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', 'bamboohr', 'fls', null), ('1997', 'Vitrue Health', 'Vitrue Ltd', 'https://www.vitruehealth.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/vitruehealth', 'Vitrue Health is a digital health startup based in the UK, founded in 2018. The company focuses on the assessment, diagnosis, and treatment of musculoskeletal (MSK) issues, including back, neck, and shoulder pain, as well as injuries like ACL tears and hip replacements. Vitrue Health utilizes computer vision technology and biomechanics to provide objective data by tracking patients during standard movements, which helps create personalized intervention and recovery plans.

Their main product, Vitrue VIDA, is an AI-powered SaaS platform aimed at workplace health. It automates digital assessments and compliance reporting related to musculoskeletal health, assisting employers in meeting regulatory requirements while enhancing employee wellbeing and productivity. VIDA offers personalized pain prevention programs, engaging reports for patients, and seamless integration into existing health pathways. Vitrue Health collaborates with surgeons and professional athletes to ensure the effectiveness of its technology. The company has secured significant venture capital funding to support its growth and expansion into new markets.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/3c97322a-310b-46d6-be0a-648f812a8613.png', 'true', 'Small company', '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', 'teamtailor', 'vitruehealth', null), ('1998', 'Ab-Anbar Gallery', 'Ab-Anbar Limited', 'https://ab-anbar.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/ab-anbar-gallery', 'Ab-Anbar is a contemporary art gallery that engages with the non-linear intersections of histories of Art and History. Often diasporic, Ab-Anbar represents artists from multiple latitudes and identities, who traverse the aesthetic and political, as well as social and psychological borders.
 
Ab-Anbar initially opened in 2014 in Tehran, Iran. The gallery is a conceptual representation of its name which means a water reservoir in Farsi. The word is made of two parts: ''ab'' meaning water and ''anbar'' meaning a reservoir. Thus, Ab-Anbar as a gallery is the architectural expression of a physical space that shapes malleable content, nurturing life and growth. The space, through its solidity and form, brings to sight the fluidity of art.
 
Since its inception, the gallery has presented exhibitions as well as hosted and collaborated with a variety of cultural tenants, not-for-profits, independent publishers, musicians, and performers, fashioning a year-long programme of wide-reaching cultural engagement. 
 
2020 marked the beginning of Ab-Anbar''s program in London, UK. With its new permanent and sole space, open in September 2023 in London''s historical Fitzrovia, the gallery intends to expand the dialogue between artists, collectors, museums and curators towards an inclusion and understanding of marginalised realities.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/0871fedf-4306-470b-b041-76b26211922a.png', 'true', 'Very small company', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', null, null, null), ('1999', 'Egg London', 'Chapter One Creations ltd', 'https://egglondon.co.uk', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/egg-london', 'Egg London is an iconic veteran of London''s nightlife scene – a colossal warehouse club, famous for pumping out great party vibes late into the night. Not content with just being a great night out, the multifaceted events space also turns its hand to a variety of private and corporate events too, from product launches and award ceremonies to themed parties and networking events.
Egg''s size and versatility means that it provides many different event spaces, each of which can easily be adapted to fit the needs of a wide range of events. Egg boasts some of the best sound and light tech anywhere in London, so it naturally specialises in creative events - many of the spaces within the venue feature programmable lighting systems, and all of them have built-in DJ booths for live performance, complete with top-of-the-range professional kits.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/f65d1c43-5eb9-4773-86c6-7685bd44aea7.png', 'true', 'Small company', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', null, null, null), ('2000', 'CJCH Solicitors', 'CJCH Legal Ltd', 'https://cjchsolicitors.co.uk', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/cjchsolicitors', 'CJCH Solicitors is a prominent legal firm with over 35 years of experience, formed from the merger of Colin Jones Solicitors and Clarke & Hartland Solicitors in 2013. With a team of more than 130 solicitors, consultants, and paralegals, the firm operates from four offices in South Wales and one in Bristol, providing both local and international legal services.

The firm offers a wide range of legal services categorized into Private Law, Business Law, and Legal Aid. Its Business and Commercial Law practice includes Dispute Resolution, Employment Law, and Corporate Law, while the Private Client & Family Law practice covers areas such as Mental Health, Family Law, and Wills and Probate. CJCH Solicitors is regulated by the Solicitors Regulation Authority (SRA), ensuring compliance with strict regulatory standards and a commitment to client satisfaction.

Registered as CJCH SOLICITORS LIMITED, the firm has also expanded through acquisitions, including Wales'' oldest law firm, Gaskell & Walker, highlighting its dedication to heritage and expertise in the Welsh legal market.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/b6e04ce8-1f2a-430f-a639-ba28933c833b.png', 'true', 'Medium-sized company', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', null, null, null), ('2001', 'Electric Twin', 'Electric Twin Ltd', 'https://www.electrictwin.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/electric-twin', 'Electric Twin is a London-based private limited company, established in September 2023, that specializes in advanced software development and data-driven solutions. The company focuses on simulating human behavior through large language models (LLMs) to create science-based synthetic populations. These simulations allow users to explore customer segments, attitudes, and needs in innovative ways.

The core offering includes a suite of investigative tools for qualitative polling, quantitative analysis, simulated focus groups, and one-on-one discussions with synthetic personas. This technology enables organizations to gather insights rapidly, with surveys and focus groups that traditionally take weeks being completed in seconds. Electric Twin''s approach ensures privacy and confidentiality, as the data does not involve real individuals. The company is led by a multidisciplinary team with expertise in data science, AI, and product design, including co-founders with notable backgrounds in government and technology.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/6aef0936-4495-41b5-bb16-b1eb0978e165.png', 'true', 'Small company', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', null, null, null), ('2002', 'Fabergé', 'Faberge (UK) Limited', 'https://www.faberge.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/faberge-sa', 'Fabergé is a prestigious jewellery firm founded in 1842 in Saint Petersburg, Russia, by Gustav Fabergé. The company gained fame under his son, Peter Carl Fabergé, who established it as a luxury brand known for exquisite craftsmanship and innovative design. Fabergé is particularly celebrated for its elaborate, jewel-encrusted Imperial Easter Eggs, which are iconic symbols of the brand''s artistic excellence.

The company offers high-end jewellery, objets d''art, and decorative luxury items, showcasing mastery in enamelling and vibrant colored gemstones. Fabergé has a rich history of bespoke jewellery design, often creating unique pieces for royalty and aristocracy. With a global presence, the brand has catered to a distinguished clientele, including European nobility and the Russian Imperial family. Today, Fabergé Limited continues the legacy of fine craftsmanship and luxury, focusing exclusively on jewellery and gemstones.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/5e36149b-b0cb-4fe7-abd8-98f11b666cf1.png', 'true', 'Medium-sized company', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', null, null, null), ('2003', 'Haefele Software', 'Haefele Software Limited', 'https://www.haefelesoftware.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/haefele-software', 'Haefele Software is a specialist software development consultancy founded in the UK in 2006, with additional offices in South Africa, Australia, and the United States. The company focuses on the Microsoft .Net and Azure ecosystems, providing a nearshore alternative to traditional offshore development hubs. With around 50 specialists, Haefele Software emphasizes a pragmatic and collaborative approach to software development, fostering stable teams to enhance project delivery.

