The core offerings include licensed scaled replicas of legendary cars from prestigious brands like Bugatti, Ferrari, Aston Martin, and Bentley. These models are designed to be fully operational, zero-emission electric vehicles that capture the essence and heritage of the originals. Hedley Studios emphasizes precision craftsmanship, sustainability, and authenticity through collaborations with iconic automotive brands, ensuring that each creation reflects the spirit of the past while appealing to modern collectors.

Headquartered at Bicester Heritage, a historic automotive hub, Hedley Studios serves a global clientele of collectors and automotive enthusiasts who appreciate the fusion of art and engineering. The company fosters an exclusive community, providing bespoke customer service and privileges to its discerning clients.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/2abc0eec-bd3c-4323-b9f9-631bb9186942.png', 'true', 'Medium-sized company', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', null, null, null), ('2005', 'RVT Architects', 'RVT Architects', 'https://rvtarchitects.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/rvt-architects-ltd', 'RVT Architects Limited is a UK based architectural practice dedicated to excellence in architecture, master planning, design and fundamentally successful project implementation.

