k based in London, established in 2010 through the merger of Abbey National plc and the savings business of Bradford & Bingley plc. As a wholly owned subsidiary of Banco Santander, it operates independently with its own management team. The bank serves around 14 million active customers across the UK, supported by approximately 18,000 employees and a network of 64 corporate business centers and numerous branches.

