ors dedicated to sustainable finance. In 2024, AFII was recognized as the NGO/Charity/Non-profit of the Year by Environmental Finance for its significant contributions to the sustainable fixed income market.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/8fdcf1cc-121a-4374-be90-ed6307dffe7d.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', null, null, null), ('2047', 'The New York Times Company', 'New York Times Limited', 'https://www.nytco.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/the-new-york-times-company', 'The New York Times Company is a prominent media corporation founded in 1851, recognized for publishing *The New York Times* and the *International New York Times*. Headquartered in Midtown Manhattan, the company has a strong reputation for high-quality journalism and investigative reporting. It has adapted to the digital age with the launch of its website, NYTimes.com, in 1996 and a successful digital subscription model introduced in 2011.

