dently minded travelers seeking authentic experiences and boutique hotel owners looking to enhance their visibility in the luxury market.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/d0934046-8f5c-4bda-b84f-8bc323de378a.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', 'bamboohr', 'slh', null), ('2081', 'Stacklok', 'Stacklok UK Ltd', 'https://stacklok.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/stacklok', 'Stacklok is a Seattle-based company specializing in cybersecurity and supply chain solutions, particularly focused on open source technologies. Led by Craig McLuckie, co-creator of Kubernetes, Stacklok develops secure and developer-friendly tools that help enterprises connect AI agents and models to their data and systems. This approach aims to unlock business value while maintaining high security standards.

