nciples. Qlar is also advancing digital transformation through integrated IT solutions, enhancing efficiency and scalability in its operations. The company positions itself as a leader in green transformation within the bulk materials processing industry, focusing on innovation and environmental responsibility.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '2', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/84ad9026-d3ea-48ad-b456-a8f4104a4f41.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', 'workday', 'qlar/Qlar_Careers', null), ('2096', 'Smedley Group', 'Smedley Motorsport Group Limited', 'https://www.smedleygroup.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/smedley-group', 'Smedley Group is a consultancy that utilizes Formula 1 methodologies and data-driven strategies to address challenges in the motorsport industry. Founded by Rob Smedley, a former F1 engineer with experience at Ferrari and Williams, the company focuses on optimizing performance, engaging fans, and identifying talent through advanced data analysis, simulation, and visualization technologies.

