GT Wings also offers feasibility studies and integration support for shipowners looking to adopt this technology. Their first operational installation is on the M/V Vectis Progress, demonstrating the real-world impact of the AirWing™. With significant government funding backing their efforts, GT Wings is positioned as a key player in the sustainable shipping sector.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/e5ba45e5-c132-434b-9517-99af9eddd863.png', 'true', 'Small company', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', null, null, null), ('2104', 'itsu', 'Itsu Limited', 'https://www.itsu.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/itsu-cp', 'itsu is a British private company founded in 1997 by Julian Metcalfe, known for its fast casual restaurant chain that specializes in East Asian-inspired meals. Headquartered in London, itsu aims to provide a healthier alternative to traditional fast food, focusing on fresh, nutritious, and visually appealing dishes. The name "itsu," meaning "when" in Japanese, reflects the company''s inspiration from Japanese food culture.

The restaurant menu features a variety of options, including sushi, salads, hot noodle dishes, gyoza, and bao buns, all made fresh daily. Itsu also offers a grocery line launched in 2012, which includes Asian-inspired products like frozen gyoza and noodle cups, available in supermarkets. The company targets health-conscious consumers looking for quick and convenient meal solutions in urban settings, emphasizing quality and customer satisfaction in its operations. With a growing presence in cities across the UK and some international locations, itsu continues to expand its reach while maintaining its commitment to fresh and healthy dining.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/7e400870-2ab7-4b11-83cb-ecb5174b4909.png', 'true', 'Very large company', '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', null, null, null), ('2105', 'Micro Nav', 'Micro Nav Limited', 'https://www.micronav.co.uk', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/micro-nav-ltd', 'Micro Nav Limited is a UK-based company that specializes in developing and supplying advanced air traffic control (ATC) and air defense simulators and training systems. Founded in 1988 by former air traffic controllers, the company focuses on creating practical training solutions for both civil and military environments. 

Their flagship product suite, BEST (Beginning to End for Simulation and Training), is a customizable and scalable platform that supports various training purposes. It includes BEST Tower for tower environments, BEST Radar for approach and area control training, and BEST Link for operational equipment stimulation. Additionally, Micro Nav offers the BEST 3D Fast Airport Builder, which allows users to create and modify 3D airport models efficiently.

