mance optimization for marketers, especially in the direct-to-consumer (D2C) sector. The company offers a hybrid ad measurement platform that utilizes various privacy-enhancing technologies, including Google’s Privacy Sandbox APIs and probabilistic tracking, to analyze ad performance without third-party cookies.

