The services provided by Project London include full project management, design consultation, contractor management, quality control, and budget and timeline management. They cater primarily to private homeowners seeking luxury renovations or new builds, as well as property professionals who recommend their services. With a focus on high standards and client satisfaction, Project London has established a solid customer base in the luxury residential market.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/ba247abe-8197-42e6-8bbe-e788234825b2.png', 'true', 'Small company', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', 'bamboohr', 'project', null), ('2111', 'Battle Systems', 'Battle Systems Ltd', 'https://battlesystems.co.uk', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/battle-systems-ltd', 'Battle Systems is a friendly little company from the UK, and is principally Colin Young, the creator/founder. He has all the crazy ideas, designs the beautiful products and is an all round clever clogs.

