With a network of over fifty shops in the UK and one in Taiwan, Whittard also provides online and mail-order services. The company enhances the customer experience through its tea rooms and tea bars, including a flagship location in Covent Garden. Whittard caters to tea and coffee enthusiasts, luxury gift buyers, and those seeking high-quality beverages, all while maintaining a strong heritage and reputation as a premium British retailer.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/805d4e15-6a79-4034-9445-76d45373c489.png', 'true', 'Large company', '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', null, null, null), ('2133', 'Fidelity International', 'FIL Investment Management Limited', 'https://www.fidelityinternational.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/fidelity-international', 'Fidelity International is a private investment management company that has been operating since 1969. Originally the international arm of Fidelity Investments, it became independent in 1980. The company is primarily owned by its management and founding family members. Fidelity International provides a wide range of investment solutions and retirement expertise to various clients, including institutions, individual investors, financial advisers, and pension funds.

