re projects, ensuring efficiency and reliability in its operations. Atlantica is recognized for its commitment to delivering clean energy solutions and supporting the transition to low-carbon energy systems globally.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/a926c3dc-596c-4378-bca6-9ce183055fc3.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', 'smartrecruiters', 'atlantica', null), ('2135', 'City & Guilds', 'City & Guilds Limited', 'https://www.cityandguilds.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/city-and-guilds', 'City & Guilds is a prominent educational organization established in 1878, focused on enhancing technical education in the UK. Operating under a Royal Charter since 1900, it has a long-standing commitment to vocational training and skills development. The organization is a registered charity and serves as the awarding body for City & Guilds and ILM qualifications, providing a wide range of accredited vocational qualifications aligned with the Regulated Qualifications Framework.

