Led by second-generation MD James Dowds, the company emphasizes a strong family ethos and a positive workplace culture. Dowds Group is known for its commitment to employee well-being, safety, and inclusivity, which contributes to high employee retention and satisfaction. The company serves diverse sectors, including healthcare, education, leisure, commercial, and residential, and has built a reputation for exceeding customer expectations through repeat business and innovative project solutions.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/c8c7acdc-dea2-4784-8914-9ad73419b557.png', 'true', 'Medium-sized company', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', null, null, null), ('2137', 'Mockingbird Raw Press', 'Mockingbird Raw Press Limited', 'https://mockingbirdrawpress.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/mockingbird-raw-press', 'Mockingbird Raw Press is a London-based company that specializes in the manufacture of cold-pressed fruit and vegetable juices and smoothies. Established in October 2013, the company operates with a small team and focuses on producing raw, nutrient-dense beverages. They utilize cold hydraulic press and High-Pressure Processing (HPP) technology to preserve the natural nutrients of handpicked ingredients, ensuring freshness and health benefits.

Their product range features a variety of smoothies and juices made from ingredients like mango, carrot, spinach, and ginger, among others. These blends are fortified with essential vitamins, catering to health-conscious consumers looking for convenient and nutritious options. Mockingbird Raw Press emphasizes natural ingredients, sustainability, and innovation, appealing to those who prefer clean-label, minimally processed foods. The brand positions its products as wholesome alternatives for busy individuals and families, suitable for breakfast or as healthy snacks.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/4dd8247f-ed0c-4e49-9ac8-d5e976cdf1f7.png', 'true', 'Small company', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', 'bamboohr', 'mockingbird', null), ('2138', 'NewStore', 'NewStore Ltd', 'https://www.newstore.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/newstore-inc', 'NewStore, Inc. is a technology company founded in 2015 by Stephan Schambach, known for his work in e-commerce software. Based in Boston, Massachusetts, with offices in Berlin and Utrecht, NewStore specializes in Omnichannel-as-a-Service solutions for enterprise retail brands around the world.

The company offers a mobile-first, modular cloud platform that enhances the retail experience across various channels. Its platform includes a mobile-optimized Point of Sale (POS) system, an Order Management System (OMS), real-time inventory management, and tools for store fulfillment and clienteling. NewStore''s solutions are designed to help retailers deliver a consistent shopping experience both online and in physical stores, ultimately boosting conversion rates and customer engagement.

NewStore primarily serves large retail brands, including luxury fashion retailers, aiming to modernize their operations. The company has raised significant funding to support its growth and product development, enhancing its global presence in the retail technology market.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/f1ce69ab-eda5-4bff-a275-b70935c8c7e6.png', 'true', 'Medium-sized company', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', 'bamboohr', 'newstore', null), ('2139', 'Cordiant Digital Infrastructure', 'Cordiant Digital Infrastructure Management LLP', 'https://www.cordiantdigitaltrust.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/cordiant-digital', 'Cordiant Digital Infrastructure Limited is a UK-listed investment company based in Guernsey, specializing in digital infrastructure assets in the UK, the European Economic Area, and North America. The company focuses on essential components of internet infrastructure, including data centres, telecommunications towers, and fibre-optic networks, which facilitate the efficient processing and storage of data.

