The company primarily serves telecommunications operators, corporations, cloud computing firms, and governments, providing them with the necessary infrastructure to support growing data demands. With the digital infrastructure market rapidly expanding, Cordiant is well-positioned to capitalize on the increasing need for robust connectivity and data management solutions.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/4785239d-da11-4c4d-9738-30105a6db356.png', 'true', 'Large company', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', null, null, null), ('2140', 'Elation Pictures', 'Elation Pictures Limited', 'https://www.elationpictures.co.uk', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/elation-pictures-limited', 'ELATION PICTURES LIMITED is a London-based Film Production Company.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/e7d6a857-c8ed-4b37-9b2f-ff544608f0eb.png', 'true', 'Very small company', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', null, null, null), ('2141', 'Handshake', 'Handshake International UK Limited', 'https://joinhandshake.co.uk', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/team-handshake', 'Handshake is a career network platform that connects students and early talent with employers, making job discovery and recruitment easier. It allows companies to create a unified profile to showcase their brand, post job opportunities, and engage with prospective candidates, particularly college students and recent graduates.The platform features customizable brand pages where employers can share their company story, culture, and values. These pages include sections for employee testimonials, job listings, and community posts, helping job seekers understand the organization better. Handshake maintains a single profile per brand to ensure clarity for career service offices and students, with options to merge duplicate profiles while keeping branding consistent.With over 4 million active users and significant job views, Handshake is the largest student career network. It serves as a valuable tool for employers to attract and engage emerging talent, streamlining the recruitment process and enhancing connections between employers and students.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '35', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/5098cb83-6ede-4bd1-8f5f-859101e10d48.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', 'greenhouse', 'handshake', null), ('2142', 'Harvey', 'Harvey AI UK Ltd', 'https://www.harvey.ai', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/harvey-ai', 'Harvey is a generative artificial intelligence company founded in 2022 and based in San Francisco. It focuses on providing AI solutions specifically for the legal industry. Co-founded by Winston Weinberg and Gabriel Pereyra, Harvey aims to connect advanced AI technology with practical legal workflows through tools developed by legal practitioners.

The company offers a legal AI platform that includes a suite of tools for tasks such as contract analysis, legal research, and litigation support. Harvey''s AI is built on large language models trained with extensive legal data, allowing it to function as a knowledgeable legal assistant. The platform also supports custom model training, enabling law firms to enhance the AI''s accuracy with their own documents. Additionally, it automates routine workflows and integrates with enterprise tools like Microsoft Azure, providing legal professionals with efficient and context-aware solutions.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '90', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/8731b598-9e4d-4fc0-9f05-29d427b554aa.png', 'true', 'Large company', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', 'ashby', 'harvey', null), ('2143', 'Congenica', 'Congenica LTD', 'https://www.congenica.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/congenica', 'Congenica is a digital health company focused on genomic medicine, offering a clinical decision support platform for genomic data interpretation. Founded in 2014, the company is based at the Wellcome Genome Campus in Cambridge, UK, and serves international laboratories, academic medical centers, hospitals, and biopharmaceutical companies.

The flagship product, the Sapientia™ platform, is a clinical genomic analytics tool that integrates DNA sequencing data with clinical phenotyping. It enables healthcare professionals to analyze human genomes, interpret complex genomic data, and produce actionable reports. This platform supports the diagnosis of rare genetic diseases and cancers, enhancing diagnostic efficiency and confidence. Congenica also provides automated genomic data analysis, integration of genomic data into clinical care, and insights for biopharmaceutical companies.

Congenica is the exclusive clinical decision support partner for the NHS Genomic Medicine Service and has received the CE Mark for its platform, ensuring regulatory compliance and reliability. The company is dedicated to delivering actionable genomic results that improve patient care and reduce healthcare costs.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/b6790166-2868-4e25-aae5-a0a7e1cd9784.png', 'true', 'Small company', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', null, null, null), ('2144', 'Hoptroff', 'Hoptroff London Ltd', 'https://www.hoptroff.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/hoptroff-london', 'Hoptroff is a London-based company that specializes in distributed timing services and precision time synchronization solutions. Founded in 2010 by physicist Richard Hoptroff, the company initially focused on high-accuracy mechanical and atomic watches, including the world’s first commercial atomic wristwatch launched in 2013. Hoptroff has since transitioned to developing a global network of timing hubs featuring Grand Master atomic clocks in major cities like London, New York, and Tokyo.

The company offers a Traceable Time as a Service (TTaaS) platform, providing highly accurate, synchronized timestamps essential for industries such as financial services, technology, and telecommunications. Hoptroff''s modular and managed timing solutions are tailored to meet the specific needs of clients, ensuring operational accuracy and security. With a commitment to integrity, trust, and collaboration, Hoptroff aims to deliver reliable and traceable time synchronization solutions that support the demands of an interconnected world.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/df469673-aae4-4fa5-a411-2c4b6000bc21.png', 'true', 'Small company', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', null, null, null), ('2145', 'Runna', 'The Run Buddy Limited', 'https://www.runna.com/en-gb', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/runna', 'Runna is a London-based digital running coaching company founded in 2022. It offers personalized, AI-powered training plans for runners of all levels, helping them achieve specific goals, from completing a first 5K to setting personal bests in marathons and ultramarathons. Runna is recognized as the world’s #1 rated running coaching app, combining expert coaching with advanced technology to provide tailored advice based on individual fitness levels and goals.

The platform features adaptive training plans that adjust dynamically based on user performance and feedback. It also includes customizable strength training programs, integrates with popular smartwatches, and fosters a global community of runners. Runna operates on a subscription model, providing an affordable alternative to traditional coaching while emphasizing AI-driven personalization and community support. Recently acquired by Strava, Runna is positioned for further growth within the fitness ecosystem.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '15', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/d643f945-ae20-4683-8589-675d5fd4cf69.png', 'true', 'Medium-sized company', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', 'ashby', 'https://api.ashbyhq.com/posting-api/job-board/runna', null), ('2146', 'Constructive Thinking', 'CONSTRUCTIVE THINKING STUDIO LIMITED', 'https://www.constructivethinking.co.uk', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/constructive-thinking-studio-limited', 'Constructive Thinking is an RIBA Chartered Architectural Practice based in the North West of England. Formed in 2002, we have grown year on year and have a fully established reputation in the fields of Sustainable Architecture, Housing, Retrofit, Hotels and Leisure, Building Information Modelling (BIM), & Interior Design.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/6d4cf1f6-0369-4576-bed9-d19d401f67c8.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', null, null, null), ('2147', 'nVent', 'ELDON ELECTRIC LIMITED', 'https://www.nvent.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/nvent', 'nVent Electric plc is a global leader in electrical connection and protection solutions, established on May 1, 2018, after spinning off from Pentair plc. Headquartered in St. Louis Park, Minnesota, with incorporation and tax headquarters in Ireland and London, UK, nVent reported net sales of $873 million in Q1 2024 and anticipates full-year sales between $3.48 billion and $3.54 billion.The company offers a wide range of products and services under well-known brands. nVent Hoffman specializes in industrial enclosures, while nVent CADDY provides fixing and fastening products for various applications. nVent ERIFLEX focuses on low voltage power distribution solutions, including flexible busbar systems. Recent strategic moves include the acquisition of Avail Infrastructure Solutions'' businesses and a partnership with NVIDIA for large-scale liquid cooling solutions. nVent serves electrical contractors, engineers, architects, and industrial customers across multiple sectors, ensuring a strong global distribution network.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '6', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/9b41fdc1-eaf9-415b-a680-f7cb243dcc1a.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', 'workday', 'nVent', null), ('2148', 'FKP Scorpio Entertainment', 'FKP Scorpio Uk Ltd', 'https://fkpscorpioentertainment.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/fkp-scorpio-entertainment-ltd', 'FKP Scorpio Entertainment Ltd is a division of FKP Scorpio GmbH, focusing on exhibitions, family entertainment, comedy, and spoken word events. Established in 2022 and headquartered in London, the company operates across Europe with additional offices in Germany and the Nordic countries. It specializes in large-scale immersive exhibitions, including popular titles like *Jurassic World: The Exhibition* and *Disney100: The Exhibition*, hosted in major venues such as London’s ExCeL Centre and the OBEX venue in Oberhausen, Germany.

The company aims to engage a wide audience through family-friendly events and immersive experiences. It also promotes comedy shows and spoken word events, showcasing a diverse entertainment portfolio. FKP Scorpio Entertainment Ltd emphasizes exceptional visitor experiences and sustainability, maintaining strong partnerships with major IP owners and venues to support its growth in the European market.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/c8eaf163-c430-4475-8d75-36b4612547a8.png', 'true', 'Small company', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', null, null, null), ('2149', 'GreenCap Partners', 'GreenCap Partners', 'https://www.greencap-partners.co.uk', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/greencap-partners', 'GreenCap focuses on providing sellside and buyside advisory services for renewable energy developers. We also participate in asset-based transactions of onshore wind, offshore wind and solar PV projects across Europe.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/5af244b8-6b66-4e04-997b-60781408f359.png', 'true', 'Very small company', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', null, null, null), ('2150', 'Hughes Fowler Carruthers', 'HFC Law LLP', 'https://hfclaw.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/hughes-fowler-carruthers-limited', 'Hughes Fowler Carruthers is a prominent law firm based in London, specializing in divorce and family law. With over 20 years of experience, the firm focuses on ultra-high net worth and high-profile cases, particularly those with international elements. Located at Academy Court on Chancery Lane, it is recognized as one of the leading family law practices in the UK.

The firm provides a wide range of family law services, including complex financial disputes, international jurisdiction issues, and high-value pre-nuptial and post-nuptial agreements. They also handle intricate children''s matters, such as child abduction cases. Known for its expert litigation and alternative dispute resolution methods, Hughes Fowler Carruthers emphasizes a client-focused approach, ensuring discretion and confidentiality for clients in the public eye.

The team consists of eight partners and thirteen solicitors, many of whom are multilingual and internationally acclaimed. The firm is connected to global legal networks, allowing it to offer seamless international legal services. Hughes Fowler Carruthers serves a diverse clientele, including individuals from various industries, and is highly rated in legal directories for its expertise and professionalism.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/7f3f0ad1-53a2-44af-8178-84bdfbc67947.png', 'true', 'Small company', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', 'smartrecruiters', 'hughes', null), ('2151', 'JetBrains', 'JETBRAINS UK LIMITED', 'https://www.jetbrains.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/jetbrains', 'JetBrains is a global software company founded in 2000 and based in Prague, Czech Republic. With over 1,800 employees and 12 offices worldwide, it specializes in creating tools that enhance productivity for software developers and teams. JetBrains serves more than 15 million users, including 90 of the Fortune Global Top 100 companies.

The company offers a comprehensive range of products that support all stages of the software development lifecycle. Its flagship products include integrated development environments (IDEs) like IntelliJ IDEA, ReSharper, and PyCharm, as well as developer tools such as TeamCity and YouTrack. JetBrains also provides collaboration platforms like Space and educational resources through JetBrains Academy. Additionally, it is known for the Kotlin programming language and various modern technologies that support remote development and cloud integration.

JetBrains fosters a culture of innovation and quality, aiming to make software development enjoyable and productive. Its strong partnerships with over 140 resellers and technology partners, including a strategic collaboration with Google Cloud, further enhance its offerings in the development community.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '34', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/4028f59a-660b-4c8d-b01e-e6cfb2135db1.png', 'true', 'Very large company', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', 'greenhouse', 'jetbrains', null), ('2152', 'Jumpstart', 'Jumpstart Careers Ltd', 'https://www.jumpstart-uk.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/jumpstartprogramme', 'Jumpstart is a UK-based start-up graduate program that connects talented graduates with innovative start-ups. The program selects and trains top graduates monthly, providing them with mentorship and support to secure roles in start-ups. Jumpstart also serves as an outsourced HR function, streamlining hiring processes for start-ups and helping them access diverse, trained talent.

Founded during the COVID-19 lockdown, Jumpstart aims to offer an alternative to traditional corporate graduate schemes. It focuses on giving graduates early responsibility and unique learning experiences. The program has successfully placed over 270 individuals in junior roles across various functions, including operations, sales, and marketing. Jumpstart''s structured program combines recruitment, training, and placement services tailored specifically for the start-up ecosystem.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/6a6d6d04-2748-4b42-82ff-3bb2bf4ca9cf.png', 'true', 'Medium-sized company', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', 'breezy', 'jumpstart', null), ('2153', 'Lightcast', 'Economic Modelling UK Ltd T/A Lightcast', 'https://lightcast.io/uk', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/lightcastdata', 'Lightcast is a global leader in talent intelligence, labor market data, and skills insights. The company provides comprehensive solutions that help organizations make informed decisions regarding talent and workforce planning. Formed from the merger of Emsi and BurningGlass, Lightcast is recognized as the largest integrated data provider of jobs, skills, roles, and occupational data worldwide.

The company offers a suite of services, including a Talent Intelligence Platform that combines real-time labor market data with internal organizational data. This platform helps organizations forecast skill needs and assess competitive recruiting activity. Lightcast also provides detailed skills insights, scalable labor market data access, and advisory services to guide clients in leveraging labor market data effectively. Their product portfolio includes Lightcast Data Shares, which deliver extensive datasets on job postings and workforce profiles, and Talent Transform, a solution integrated with platforms like Workday. Lightcast serves a diverse range of clients, including enterprises and government agencies, helping them optimize workforce planning and stay competitive in a changing labor market.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/b91833e0-d841-4b48-8a05-e734093e6c75.png', 'true', 'Large company', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', null, null, null), ('2154', 'EFL', 'EFL Global UK (PVT) LTD', 'https://efl.global', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/efl-global', 'EFL is a global leader in freight forwarding and supply chain solutions, based in Colombo, Sri Lanka. With around 3,000 employees and a reported revenue of approximately $979.7 million, EFL specializes in innovative logistics services tailored for various industries, including agriculture, apparel, pharmaceuticals, technology, and automotive.

The company provides a wide range of services, including air freight, ocean freight, ground transportation, customs brokerage, warehousing, and supply chain management. EFL operates a vast network with over 70 offices in 39 countries, allowing it to deliver comprehensive end-to-end supply chain solutions worldwide. EFL is committed to sustainability and corporate responsibility, focusing on environmental stewardship and social impact through its initiatives.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/b55b2000-2924-4714-8bd4-5724673a265c.png', 'true', 'Very large company', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', null, null, null), ('2155', 'Emperia', 'Emperia Ltd', 'https://emperiavr.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/emperialondon', 'Emperia is a technology company focused on creating immersive virtual worlds for retail and brand experiences. With offices in London and New York, the company aims to bridge traditional e-commerce with personalized in-store shopping. Emperia empowers creators and enterprises to build high-quality virtual environments that enhance user engagement and data analytics.

