ompany is committed to continuous learning and employee development, providing opportunities for skill enhancement and career growth.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/d213e869-1e06-4b87-9177-c9ba69b18695.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', null, null, null), ('2211', 'Digital Autopsy UK', 'Advanced Visualisation Technologies Ltd T/A Digital Autopsy UK', 'https://www.digitalautopsy.co.uk', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/digital-autopsy-uk', 'Digital Autopsy UK is the premier company in the United Kingdom dedicated to providing a comprehensive and professional digital autopsy service to the Office of His Majesty''s Coroner and bereaved families. We pride ourselves on our effectiveness, efficiency, respectfulness, appropriateness, timeliness, and professionalism.

