tiple sectors. But we''ve kept our core values of dependability, exceptional service and excellent workmanship; because they''re as important now as they were when we founded the business more than 25 years ago. From the very beginning, exceptional quality and outstanding service have been paramount to our success.With the backing of our ISO 9001 registered system you can be sure of our consistency and performance. Our aim is to offer our customers a friendly, reliable service and support them in meeting the demands of their clients and markets, in what are challenging economic times.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/98c6e7bd-7760-4629-babf-857989a4fa39.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', null, null, null), ('2218', 'Multiplier', 'MULTIPLIER TECHNOLOGIES UK LTD', 'https://www.usemultiplier.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/usemultiplier', 'Multiplier is a global technology company that provides a comprehensive platform for hiring, onboarding, managing, and paying employees and contractors worldwide. Founded in 2020 by Sagar Khatri, Amritpal Singh, and Vamsi Krishna, the company aims to eliminate geographic barriers in talent acquisition and workforce management. With a team of over 500 employees, Multiplier supports businesses in over 150 countries, allowing them to build and manage global teams without the need for local legal entities.

