pany is dedicated to ensuring the safe reuse of surgical instruments, which helps protect patients and uphold the reputation of healthcare institutions. Their mission focuses on providing healthcare providers with access to the safest and most effective sterile medical equipment.The company offers a wide range of tailored decontamination and sterilization services, including flexible endoscope sterilization, low temperature sterilization, robotics, consultancy, and managed services. IHSS operates four purpose-built decontamination facilities that are available 24/7, ensuring reliable service delivery. With a senior management team boasting over 60 years of combined experience, IHSS employs over 500 staff members across five sites, consistently exceeding key performance indicators in their operations.IHSS serves a diverse array of healthcare customers, including Acute Trusts, Primary Care Trusts, and private clinics. The company is also committed to sustainability, focusing on enhancing the environmental, economic, and social well-being of the communities they serve.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/bb3c02cf-f505-4720-9e50-c94244886a6d.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', 'smartrecruiters', 'ihss', null), ('2250', 'Jamworks', 'Jamworks Platform Limited', 'https://jamworks.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/jamworksapp', 'Jamworks is an AI-driven educational technology company based in Farnham, England, founded in 2020. The company specializes in enhancing learning solutions that improve student engagement, accessibility, and inclusivity. Its core product, the Jamworks AI Note Taking App, records and transcribes lectures with high accuracy, including complex STEM equations, and supports 26 languages. The app integrates seamlessly with popular virtual learning environments like Canvas, Moodle, Blackboard, and Brightspace.

