mpany is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/8b390436-c2db-4c79-9792-8ae4fe9d3fcb.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', 'smartrecruiters', 'v1', null), ('2260', 'Freemavens', 'Freemavens', 'https://freemavens.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/freemavens', 'Freemavens is a strategy and innovation consultancy based in London, founded in 2012. The company specializes in using big data and advanced analytics to help brands understand their customers and drive growth. By combining human and artificial intelligence, Freemavens analyzes real-time consumer behavior data to uncover actionable insights and identify market opportunities.

