uinly love our patients and would love to do the best for them. Their happiness is our wish. It is only then we know we have succeded with our job. The main practitioner, Mr. Louie, is working as a Implantologist for larger dental companies and placing implants in many practices in south of the country.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/23e978f3-33ea-4286-b41c-301cc5c6aef0.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', 'smartrecruiters', 'premier', null), ('2299', 'Proteus Façades', 'Proteus Facades Limited', 'https://proteusfacades.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/proteusfacades', 'Proteus Façades is a designer and manufacturer of high-performance building envelope solutions, based in Skelmersdale, Lancashire. With over 20 years of experience, the company specializes in bespoke façade systems and rainscreen cladding, offering a range of innovative products that meet the needs of architects and contractors.

