ent industry. Investment managers and their counterparties use the platform to efficiently comply with their legal and regulatory obligations.  ume has won several industry awards and accolades, including:  2017 Luxembourg Startup of the year 2018 Luxembourg Regtech of the year 2019 Top100 most innovative Regtech in the world', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/6a5a4ec9-9128-4c50-8499-541e13a129fa.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', null, null, null), ('2328', 'A&B Smart Materials', 'A and B Smart materials', 'https://www.absmartmaterials.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/a-b-smart-materials', 'A&B Smart Materials is a UK-based startup founded in December 2022 by Amaury van Trappen de Buggenoms and Dr. Benjamin White. The company specializes in developing biobased superabsorbent hydrogels and passive cooling technologies. Headquartered at the Centre for Innovation & Enterprise in Begbroke Science Park, Oxfordshire, A&B Smart Materials focuses on engineering plant-based hydrogels that absorb moisture at night and release it during the day, providing passive cooling without the need for external energy.Their technology combines elements of thermal engineering, nanotechnology, and smart materials, emphasizing advanced material science and sustainable solutions. A&B Smart Materials aims to address applications in various sectors, including renewable energy, agriculture, and construction, aligning with trends in sustainability and eco-friendly materials. The company is dedicated to pioneering innovative solutions that enhance energy efficiency and environmental management.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/7275b928-5304-4ce7-8b66-c6692d2d82d9.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', null, null, null), ('2329', 'Accent Catering', 'Accent Catering Services Limited', 'https://accentcatering.co.uk', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/accent-catering-services-ltd', 'Accent Catering Services Ltd, founded in 2001 and based in Staines-upon-Thames, Surrey, specializes in bespoke contract catering services. The company focuses on delivering fresh, healthy, and high-quality food tailored to the specific needs of its clients, including business staff restaurants and educational institutions. Accent Catering is recognized for its commitment to quality and sustainability, using locally sourced ingredients.The company serves a diverse clientele across London and the South East, providing nutritious meals for schools, event catering for corporate clients, and fine dining for various occasions. With around 610 employees and generating approximately $43.1 million in revenue, Accent Catering combines the personalized service of a small organization with the resources of a larger company. It has earned accolades for being one of the best employers in the food service industry and was included in the "1000 Companies to Inspire Britain 2019" by the London Stock Exchange.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/e756c619-9e78-474c-b379-71d9c547bd24.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', 'smartrecruiters', 'accent', null), ('2330', 'Compound Real Estate', 'Compound RE Strategies Limited', 'https://www.compound-re.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/compound-real-estate', 'Founded in 2022, we are an investor and developer of UK real estate. We combine a depth of experience in operational real estate with a focus on design, user experience and environmental and social impact to create property, portfolios and places that genuinely serve the local communities in which they exist. Through this approach we maximise the creation of value for our users, their neighbours and our investors.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/29355ff8-0124-4291-82ea-e39ea8dfb30a.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', null, null, null), ('2331', 'Focus SB', 'Focus SB Ltd', 'https://www.focus-sb.co.uk/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/focus-sb-ltd', 'Focus SB Ltd is a British manufacturer of premium electrical wiring accessories, based in St. Leonards on Sea, East Sussex. With over 40 years of industry experience, the company was established in 2001 through a merger and has since become a multi-award-winning brand, recognized with the King’s Award for Enterprise for International Trade in 2023.The company specializes in designing and manufacturing high-quality luxury electrical accessories, including faceplates, light switches, and sockets. Their products feature a combination of traditional craftsmanship and modern technology, such as matching rocker and toggle switches, durable electrophoretic lacquering, and electronic low-voltage keypad switches. Focus SB maintains full control over its manufacturing process, ensuring high standards and quality through in-house capabilities, including metal plate design and assembly.Focus SB serves a diverse range of markets, including commercial, hospitality, residential, and heritage sectors, with a strong international presence. They also provide bespoke design and consultancy services, catering to prestigious projects worldwide. The company is uniquely positioned as the first UK and European electrical accessories manufacturer licensed to sell directly to mainland China.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/b75e16bb-6b67-4eb3-a6c3-f23943396967.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', null, null, null), ('2332', 'Medical Connections', 'Medical Connections Ltd', 'https://www.medicalconnections.co.uk', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/medical-connections-ltd', 'Medical Connections Ltd is a small, innovative medical imaging software and consultancy business, created with the aim of making medical image integration simpler, reliable and cheaper. Medical Connections was founded by the late Dr David Harvey and now jointly owned and run by Rapten Bhutia, Qian Wang and Philippa Webb.Our toolkit assists development of DICOM conformant applications for medical imaging. They are available for COM/ActiveX environment and .NET framework. Medical Connections also provides consultancy services in the field of medical image integration, and has advised suppliers, integrators, purchasers and government agencies on how best to achieve their goals in this area. This can include advice on choice of communication methods, conformance testing and even dispute resolution. In addition, we can provide customised software solutions for specific DICOM needs, such as routing, tag morphing, etc.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/09edab2a-eb65-4e2d-b670-7e47f166ed13.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', 'smartrecruiters', 'medical', null), ('2333', 'Melin', 'Melin Energy Consultants Limited', 'https://www.melinconsultants.co.uk', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/melin-consultants', 'We are a dynamic and experienced practice delivering sustainable building compliance services to the built environment.  We take immense pride in being a valued part of delivering buildings fit for a healthier and more sustainable future. We are able to provide a range of solutions at all stages of development.  We believe strongly in good old fashioned customer service. We make it a priority to understand our client needs – delivering a first class service, in an efficient manner.  From a client base that includes leading international architectural practices, national contractors and local authorities, our reputation is second to none in delivering a solution.Our Clients demand a cost effective service without compromising on quality.  Our dynamic team, drawing on many years experience, are able to provide the solution you want when you need it.All work undertaken by our in house team that are fully accredited and licensed individuals and CIBSE qualified Low Carbon Consultants which is recognised as the leading governing body of professional energy consultants.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/19431bef-1dd0-4d23-a21a-928d9d028bdd.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', null, null, null), ('2334', 'Qargo', 'Qargo Tech Limited', 'https://www.qargo.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/qargo-tms', 'Qargo TMS is a cloud-based transport management platform designed to enhance the efficiency and profitability of transport and logistics businesses. Founded by industry veterans, Qargo replaces outdated TMS systems with an AI-driven solution that simplifies logistics workflows and automates administrative tasks.The platform features Qargo Intelligence (Qi), which automates processes such as order data extraction, error flagging, and invoicing. It provides a comprehensive view of operations, accessible to all stakeholders, and eliminates the need for spreadsheets. With real-time dashboards and intelligent alerts, Qargo enables faster decision-making and operational improvements. The software is tailored for road transport firms and midsize companies, facilitating quicker implementation and reduced training requirements.Qargo serves a diverse customer base, including hauliers and freight forwarders across Europe, helping them optimize routes, enhance customer experience, and improve financial performance. The company is committed to promoting sustainability through optimized logistics and reduced inefficiencies.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/08415736-bc84-4cf0-944c-f1270cff11fb.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', 'teamtailor', 'www', null), ('2335', 'Realtime Civil Engineering', 'REALTIME CIVIL ENGINEERING LIMITED', 'https://www.realtimecivil.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/realtime-civil-engineering', 'Realtime Civil Engineering is a private limited company based in Potters Bar, Hertfordshire, UK, established in 1987. With over three decades of experience, it has become a leading groundworks contractor in London and the Home Counties.The company specializes in groundworks, substructure, and superstructure construction across various sectors, including commercial, residential, educational, and healthcare. Its core services include enabling works such as demolition, sub-structure construction, and superstructure concrete frame construction. Realtime Civil Engineering manages complex projects valued between £250,000 and £16 million, showcasing its technical expertise and resource capability.With a focus on thorough planning and strong client collaboration, the company aims to deliver high-quality projects that meet industry standards. Its client-centered approach has fostered lasting relationships with top contractors and prestigious clients, resulting in repeat business.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/8eea2452-ef33-4c91-9f47-89fe2cd10717.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', null, null, null), ('2336', 'Roam', 'Roam Foods Ltd', 'https://roamfood.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/roam-foods', 'Roam is a natural nutrition brand born out of a need for an alternative to all of the fake "health foods" that we currently see filling the high protein segment of the market. Our launch line of savoury grass-fed beef bars are made using just a handful of real ingredients, are completely free from artificial preservatives and are a source of fibre. Real food that you can take with you anywhere and consume anytime.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/f8aee340-d925-4531-96ee-c8b28813cb59.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', 'bamboohr', 'roam', null), ('2337', 'Batt', 'Batt Cables Limited', 'https://battcables.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/batt-cables-worldwide', 'Batt Cables Worldwide is a prominent UK-based cable supplier and distributor, established in 1952. With over 70 years of experience, the company is recognized for its commitment to quality and dependable service. Headquartered in London, Batt Cables serves a diverse range of customers, including electrical wholesalers and contractors, particularly in the construction industry.The company offers a wide selection of over 3,200 products, including armoured and unarmoured cables, flexible power cables, fire-resistant cables, and electric vehicle charging cables. Batt Cables specializes in low and medium voltage power cables made from copper and aluminium, as well as marine and offshore cables for sectors like renewable energy and oil & gas. With a focus on supporting critical infrastructure projects, Batt Cables plays a vital role in electrification efforts across various industries worldwide.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/3289fc67-9216-4da9-8baf-d0fae5bd32a6.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', 'teamtailor_html', 'https://breathebatterytechnologies.teamtailor.com/jobs', null), ('2338', 'Empower Translate', 'Empower Translate (Global) Limited', 'https://www.empowertranslate.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/empowertranslate', 'Empower Translate, based in Chepstow, Wales, is a specialist language service provider with over 25 years of experience. Founded in 1997, the company focuses on delivering expert translation and localization services tailored for the global market research and insight industry. With a team of around 35 staff members, Empower Translate emphasizes innovation and customer service, utilizing advanced translation technology to support its clients.The company offers a range of language services, including the translation and localization of research materials, coding and theming of qualitative data, verbatim transcription, proofreading, online link-checking, and audiovisual translation. These services are designed to facilitate multilingual research projects, allowing researchers to concentrate on their core activities while ensuring accurate and actionable insights.Empower Translate primarily serves global market researchers and insight agencies that require multilingual support for international research projects. The company is committed to providing high-quality translations and localization services, backed by a passionate team of linguists with expertise in market research.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/08b4e3c2-d1c9-41d9-8d36-67c13dee1a14.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', 'smartrecruiters', 'empower', null), ('2339', 'Hellios', 'HELLIOS INFORMATION LIMITED', 'https://hellios.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/hellios-information', 'Hellios Information is a UK-based private limited company founded in 2012 and headquartered in Oxford. The company specializes in supplier compliance and qualification services, focusing on collaborative, industry-based communities. Hellios aims to simplify the collection and management of supplier data for buying organizations across various sectors.The company offers a Supplier Information Management (SIM) platform that helps organizations efficiently collect, validate, and monitor critical supplier information. Hellios operates in key industries such as Financial Services and Defence, Aerospace & Security, facilitating collaboration among buyers to manage supply chain compliance and reduce risks. Their services include supplier data collection and management, compliance and risk management, and community collaboration, all designed to enhance procurement efficiency and ensure adherence to ethical and regulatory standards.Hellios generates revenue through subscription fees from buyers and suppliers participating in its communities. The platform is endorsed by major organizations, showcasing its effectiveness in delivering supplier compliance visibility and streamlined onboarding processes. The leadership team brings extensive experience in technology, software development, and financial services.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/0bf0eea1-665d-4e23-bc75-e24db6a80476.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', null, null, null), ('2340', 'Neighbourhood', 'Neighbourhood Agency Ltd', 'https://neighbourhood.net', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/heyneighbourhood', 'Welcome to the Neighbourhood. We''re a digital performance agency working with good brands to build online audiences and optimise digital spaces.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/aaec824d-57fd-4066-9e13-9ce75d4d95e8.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', null, null, null), ('2341', 'The Culture Club', 'The Culture Club', 'https://wearethecultureclub.co.uk', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/theculture-club', 'The Culture Club is a company culture agency founded in 2018 and based in Surrey, UK. It focuses on enhancing organizational culture through improved employee experience and communication. The company aims to inspire and engage organizations by building better workplace cultures, emphasizing a practical approach to culture transformation. Founder Nikki Burslam leads the team with expertise in culture mapping and strategic narrative development.The Culture Club offers a range of services, including culture discovery and strategy, employee engagement initiatives, internal communications, leadership development, and collaboration facilitation. They also manage a membership community called *The Clubhouse*, which supports ongoing culture development. The company partners with various organizations to clarify their culture and values, enhance employee experience, and manage change effectively.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/2d9c7e00-7c99-4f90-b5dc-6facf21c989d.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', null, null, null), ('2342', 'Town Legal LLP', 'Town Legal LLP', 'https://www.townlegal.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/town-legal-llp', 'Town Legal LLP is a boutique legal firm based in London, specializing in planning law across England and Wales. As a limited liability partnership, it is authorized and regulated by the Solicitors Regulation Authority. The firm has rapidly expanded from six to around 50 employees in five years, including 12 partners, and has received accolades such as Boutique Law Firm of the Year from *The Lawyer* and recognition from *Planning Magazine* as the top planning law team in the UK.The firm provides a wide range of legal services related to planning law, including advice for residential and commercial developments, highways agreements, compulsory purchase matters, and planning inquiries. Town Legal''s team consists of lawyers, former local government planners, and heritage consultants, offering a multidisciplinary approach to complex development challenges. The firm also utilizes advanced technology solutions to enhance service delivery and operational efficiency, ensuring effective collaboration and communication within its team.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/24232871-691c-4971-af86-38e1e8470182.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', null, null, null), ('2343', 'Amaia', 'Amaia Clothing Limited', 'https://amaialondon.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/amaia-clothing-limited', 'AMAIA CLOTHING LIMITED is a kidswear company based in London, with a flagship store in Chelsea and a website shipping worlwide.Designed in London, made in Spain in our traditional family owned ateliers, trusted by Families all around the world since 2004.Discover our world of chic, refined, yet easy to wear clothes made with love and care for lively happy children.  Amaia''s unique style is all about timeless and joyful effortless elegance, matching looks for siblings, subtle colours'' harmony and attention to details.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/bde4de4b-b4b7-493b-bb1a-f56b922c089b.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', null, null, null), ('2344', 'possible', 'Be Possible Limited', 'https://bepossible.co.uk', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/bepossibleuk', 'possible is a strategic healthcare consulting firm that provides advisory and transformation services to organizations within the healthcare ecosystem. The company focuses on navigating the complexities of the healthcare industry through strategic insights, planning, activation, and performance development. BEPOSSIBLE positions itself as a full-ecosystem partner, tailoring solutions to meet the unique needs of each client.The firm operates across three primary service areas: Insights & Strategic Planning, Strategic Activation, and Learning & Performance. In Insights & Strategic Planning, BEPOSSIBLE develops brand strategies and conducts market analysis to help organizations achieve sustainable growth. Their Strategic Activation services include creating omni-channel strategies and organizational transformations. Additionally, the Learning & Performance area offers capability development programs to enhance individual skills and support teams in achieving strategic objectives.BEPOSSIBLE has earned recognition for its innovative approaches and has worked with a diverse range of clients, from biotech companies to blue-chip organizations, delivering customized solutions that address specific challenges and drive measurable business impact.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/6246ba81-3b69-477a-a718-3cde718c7012.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', null, null, null), ('2345', 'BBS', 'Border Business Systems Limited', 'https://www.bbsltd.co.uk', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/borderbusinesssystemsltd', 'BBS are the UK''s leading address data experts. Over 40 years, BBS has built pioneering address management solutions and used its expertise in advanced data optimisation to deliver bespoke direct marketing campaigns. We are proud to have worked with many of our clients over decades - from the largest mailing houses to small independent retailers - to help them grow.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/2f152856-bfe2-43b3-b329-48e021ff2525.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', null, null, null), ('2346', 'BSA', 'BSA Company Limited', 'https://www.bsacompany.co.uk', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/bsacompany', 'BSA Company Limited is a UK-based motorcycle manufacturer and service provider, incorporated in 1980. The company specializes in the sale, maintenance, and repair of motorcycles, along with related parts and accessories. BSA has a rich history, having acquired the rights to the BSA name after the liquidation of Norton Villiers Triumph in 1978. It has produced military motorcycles and models for developing countries, focusing on high ground clearance designs.In 2016, BSA was acquired by the Indian conglomerate Mahindra Group, which aims to revive the BSA brand globally. The company has launched new models, including the BSA Gold Star in 2021. BSA Company Limited serves various markets, including military clients, developing countries, and motorcycle enthusiasts, while also providing aftermarket parts and services for BSA and Norton motorcycles. The management team reflects its international ownership, with active operations in both the UK and India.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/be1fcaab-9ebd-48d1-90c8-8b11f7d63d47.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', 'smartrecruiters', 'bsa', null), ('2347', 'Burlingtons', 'Burlingtons Group Limited', 'https://burlingtons.group', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/burlingtons-group-ltd', 'Burlingtons is a full service international law firm headquartered in London’s West End.  We help you to structure and achieve your objectives whether you own, manage or advise a business, as well as in your personal capacity. Our clients range from start-ups, owner-managed businesses and medium enterprises through to international and public listed companies across a variety of market sectors.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/a26cd665-14e7-4b53-a116-caaac44e7746.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', null, null, null), ('2348', 'Centra', 'Centra Technology UK Limited', 'https://centra.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/centra-commerce', 'Centra is an e-commerce platform designed specifically for global fashion and lifestyle brands. It provides a comprehensive solution to manage and scale digital commerce operations across various sales channels, including direct-to-consumer (DTC), wholesale, marketplaces, and physical retail stores. This unified approach allows brands to create localized shopping experiences without extensive IT projects or third-party dependencies.The platform supports both DTC and wholesale business models, making it suitable for businesses of all sizes, from startups to large enterprises. Centra offers an all-in-one solution that streamlines operations with features like real-time inventory management, advanced analytics, and a fashion-specific Product Information Management (PIM) system. Brands can customize the platform extensively and integrate with various partners to meet their specific needs, enhancing their omnichannel retail strategies and improving overall efficiency.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/6dce54c5-55f5-40d8-865c-3c96da9acd23.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', 'teamtailor', 'centra', null), ('2349', 'Europa Worldwide Group', 'Europa Worldwide Group Limited', 'https://www.europa-worldwide.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/europa-worldwide-logistics', 'Europa Worldwide Group is a prominent privately owned transport and logistics company based in the United Kingdom, with a significant international presence. Established in 1966, the company has expanded rapidly since its acquisition by CEO Andrew Baxter in 2013, growing from 400 to over 1,400 employees across 29 global sites and achieving an annual turnover exceeding £300 million.The company operates through three main divisions: Europa Road, Europa Air & Sea, and Europa Warehouse. Europa Road specializes in European road freight, featuring the UK''s largest European groupage hub and offering daily direct services to 30 continental hubs. Europa Air & Sea provides tailored air and sea freight services with a global agent network and proprietary software for tracking and order management. Europa Warehouse manages extensive fulfillment facilities and offers third-party logistics services, ensuring compliance and quality through various certifications.Additionally, Europa Showfreight delivers specialized logistics for exhibition goods. The company serves a diverse range of sectors, emphasizing innovation, customer service, and sustainability in its operations.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/f1bfff2a-3706-410e-808e-501f44d38386.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', 'bamboohr', 'europa', null), ('2350', 'IRIS', 'IRIS Group Limited', 'https://www.iris.co.uk', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/iris-software-group', 'IRIS Software Group is a UK-based provider of business-critical software solutions and services, with over 45 years of experience. The company serves more than 100,000 customers in 135 countries, focusing on sectors such as accountancy, education, payroll, HR, and finance. Originally centered on accountancy software, IRIS has expanded its offerings to include integrated solutions that automate essential processes like tax return submissions and payroll management.The company emphasizes a client-first approach, providing tailored support and involving customers in product development through user groups and events. With a workforce skilled in accounting, tax, and IT management, IRIS understands client needs and industry practices. The company has also grown through acquisitions, enhancing its automation and integration capabilities, and has expanded into the North American market.IRIS is dedicated to sustainability and social responsibility, promoting environmental awareness and supporting charitable initiatives. Its corporate culture values innovation and high performance, making it a trusted partner for organizations ranging from small enterprises to large firms.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/ef4c28ef-339c-48f2-b0c7-1f93326a76d5.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', 'greenhouse', 'iris', null), ('2351', 'The Magnum Ice Cream Company', 'Magnum ICC UK Limited', 'https://corporate.magnumicecream.com/en/home.html', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/the-magnum-ice-cream-company', 'The Magnum Ice Cream Company is a premium ice cream brand owned by Unilever, known for its luxurious ice cream bars. Launched in 1989, Magnum was developed in Denmark and quickly gained popularity for its signature thick Belgian chocolate coating that cracks when bitten, revealing smooth, creamy ice cream inside. Magnum offers a variety of flavors and chocolate coatings, including classic vanilla, Magnum White, Almond, Chocolate Truffle, and Chocolate Brownie. The brand also features Magnum Mini and Magnum Double, with the latter being noted for its indulgent experience. In addition to ice cream bars, Magnum provides tubs and bites in various markets. Targeting adult consumers, Magnum emphasizes indulgence and sophistication in its marketing, positioning itself as a lifestyle brand that elevates ice cream consumption to a pleasurable experience. The brand continues to innovate with new flavors and formats, maintaining its status as a leader in the premium ice cream segment.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/43bd64d7-cdad-4fd2-a38e-1dbed74ce294.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', null, null, null), ('2352', 'Open Hydro', 'Open Hydro Ltd', 'https://openhydro.net', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/open-hydro', 'OpenHydro was an Irish company established in 2004, specializing in the design, manufacture, installation, and maintenance of tidal stream turbines for renewable energy generation. The company developed an innovative open-centred horizontal-axis tidal turbine, which featured a ducting shroud to enhance water flow and a direct-drive generator that eliminated the need for a gearbox. Headquartered in Dublin, OpenHydro operated a manufacturing facility in Greenore, producing turbines in various sizes.OpenHydro was a pioneer in tidal energy testing, being the first to use the European Marine Energy Centre (EMEC) tidal test site in Scotland. Their 250 kW turbine, installed in 2006, was the first tidal turbine to connect to the grid in Scotland and the UK. The company conducted multiple tests in Scotland, France, and Canada, contributing significantly to tidal energy research and development. In 2013, OpenHydro was acquired by Naval Energies, which later ceased tidal turbine development, leading to the company''s liquidation in 2018.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/382add62-e327-4c0b-af95-6025ebd22816.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', 'smartrecruiters', 'open', null), ('2353', 'Pfizer', 'Pfizer Limited', 'https://www.pfizer.co.uk', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/pfizer/', 'Breakthroughs that change patients'' lives. We strive to provide access to safe and effective and affordable medicines and health care services to the people who need them.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/c8ecd336-bac4-470f-9edc-d7c249fe48b7.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', 'smartrecruiters', 'pfizer', null), ('2354', 'Retalia', 'Retalia Solutions Ltd', 'https://www.retaliasolutions.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/retalia-solutions', 'In today''s fast-evolving retail environment, businesses need to deliver seamless customer experiences across multiple channels. Retalia''s Imagine Retail Suite is a cutting-edge, cloud-based platform designed for modern retailers.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/d215bce2-1a6f-42d1-b3f9-43d8ecaa58bb.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', null, null, null), ('2355', 'Recraft', 'Recraft AI Limited', 'https://www.recraft.ai/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/recraftai', 'Recraft is an AI-driven design technology company founded in 2022 and based in London, UK. It provides professional designers, illustrators, and marketers with advanced AI-powered tools to create and refine original images, vector art, illustrations, icons, and 3D graphics. The company aims to democratize creative expression by giving creators full control over their design processes.The core offering is an AI-native design platform that serves as a comprehensive creative operating system. It includes a suite of tools such as text-to-image generation, professional background removal, AI-powered vectorization, and product mockup generation. Recraft also features a Brand-Orchestration Engine for maintaining consistent visual brand systems and an infinite canvas for real-time collaboration. The platform is supported by Recraft V3, a leading text-to-image diffusion model, and is trusted by over 3 million users globally, including professionals from major companies like Ogilvy, HubSpot, and Netflix.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '3', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/23146373-9f23-455a-ac36-c7f393632ffb.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', 'ashby', 'recraft', null), ('2356', 'Apis Partners', 'Apis Partners (Group) UK Limited', 'https://apis.pe/companies/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/apis-partners', 'Apis Partners is a global private equity firm founded in 2014 by Matteo Stefanel and Udayan Goyal. The firm specializes in growth-stage investments in technology-enabled financial services companies across emerging and global markets. Apis Partners focuses on financial inclusion and wellness, aiming to combine strong financial returns with positive social impact.The firm invests in companies that have established product-market fit and are ready to scale, particularly those that innovate in financial services. Apis Partners emphasizes Environmental, Social, and Governance (ESG) principles and has a presence in six countries across Europe, Asia, and Africa to support its portfolio companies. Their investment strategy includes growth capital for financial services and infrastructure, with a specialization in sectors like payments, insurtech, and fintech.Apis Partners manages several funds, including the Apis Growth Fund and the Apis Insurtech Fund, and has notable investments in companies like Thunes, Memed, and iKhokha. The firm is recognized for its performance and impact, ranking highly in private equity performance and committed to advancing financial inclusion in low- and middle-income communities.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/8154f09d-526c-4c5d-b874-a0eaaba66fbc.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', null, null, null), ('2357', 'Axitan', 'Axitan Research UK Limited', 'https://www.axitan.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/axitan', 'Axitan is a UK biotech company focused on eliminating antibiotics from animal feed and improving productivity. It is developing a library of endolysins, and associated products, capable of targeting those pathogens that impact livestock farming historically managed through antibiotic supplements in animal feed and, in so doing, improve productivityyields. Its focus forms part of wider WHO One Health initiative to combat the threat posed by antimicrobial resistance caused by the overuse of antibiotics, animals accounting for two thirds of the antibiotics consumed globally each year. In October 2022, Axitan achieved US FDA GRAS ("Generally Recognised As Safe") status for the algal biomass ingredient used in its first product, FORC3®, which promotes healthy growth in poultry by targeting the pathogen Clostridium perfringens that causes $6b of economic loss each year to the poultry industry. Axitan has operations in the UK and US.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/79852b73-0c3e-40b2-b7d8-cde535761192.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', null, null, null), ('2358', 'Coherence Neuro', 'Coherence Neuro LTD', 'https://www.coherenceneuro.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/coherenceneuro', 'Coherence Neuro is a neurotechnology company based in Cambridge, founded in 2022 by Dr. Ben Woodington and Dr. Elise Jenkins. The company focuses on developing therapeutic neurotechnology to treat cancer by decoding and modulating the body''s bioelectronic signals. They create implantable brain-computer interfaces (BCIs) that precisely sense and stimulate neural activity to disrupt cancer progression.Their flagship product, SOMA-1, is designed to measure and modulate brain tumors like glioblastoma in real time. This innovative device represents a new class of precision bioelectronic therapies that target cancer through neural interfaces, moving away from traditional treatments like chemotherapy. Coherence Neuro''s technology integrates miniaturized implantable electronics, advanced AI systems for decoding neural signals, and closed-loop feedback to personalize therapy for each patient.Coherence Neuro collaborates with clinical researchers, neurosurgeons, and institutions in neuro-oncology, aiming to make cancer a manageable condition through their work in electro-oncology. Their goal is to improve survival and quality of life for patients with aggressive cancers by leveraging the bioelectronic code of the body as a therapeutic target.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/3816eecf-d162-410a-b8f8-0d12ccb435a5.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', null, null, null), ('2359', 'CSM Architects', 'CSM Architects', 'https://www.csmarchitects.co.uk', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/csm-architects', 'Coulson Swinburne Partners Practice was formed in 1968 by Jim Coulson and Brian Swinburne. In 1996 Will Moses joined as a Partner and the Practice was renamed Coulson Swinburne Moses. In 2007 Coulson Swinburne Moses and JBC, managed by Neil Atkinson (formally Jowett Buckley Curry) merged to form CSM Architects. CSM Architects brought in Chris Gair as Partner along aide Neil Atkinson and Will Moses in 2015.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/bd4b4373-6f15-4d9e-95ce-553b1c6b2761.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', 'smartrecruiters', 'csm', null), ('2360', 'Dot Square Lab', 'Dot Square Lab Limited', 'https://dotsquarelab.com/team', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/dot-square-lab', 'Dot Square Lab is a UK-based AI consultancy that focuses on delivering scalable and maintainable artificial intelligence solutions across various industries, including logistics, agriculture, defense, chemical engineering, and finance. Founded in January 2022 and headquartered in London, the company operates with a small team and emphasizes a personalized approach to meet unique business needs.The company specializes in end-to-end AI solution development, which includes understanding business goals, creating customized AI roadmaps, designing tailored solutions, and deploying production-ready systems. Their services encompass text summarization, chatbots, sentiment analysis, image recognition, video editing, and speech-to-text technologies. Dot Square Lab aims to help businesses effectively integrate AI into their operations, delivering measurable results that address specific industry challenges.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/dbb262ce-1c43-4582-9f80-b303683fcf99.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', null, null, null), ('2361', 'Fender', 'Fender Musical Instruments Europe Ltd', 'https://uk.fender.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/fender-musical-instruments', 'Fender Musical Instruments Corporation is a prominent American manufacturer of electric guitars, bass guitars, amplifiers, and related musical equipment. Founded in 1946 by Leo Fender in Fullerton, California, the company is known for introducing the first mass-produced solid-body electric guitar, the Telecaster, in 1950, followed by the Precision Bass in 1951 and the iconic Stratocaster in 1954.Fender offers a wide range of instruments and amplifiers designed for musicians across various genres, including rock, jazz, country, and funk. Their products feature innovative designs such as bolt-on necks and patented pickups, contributing to their distinctive sound and playability. The company also supports music education through initiatives like Fender Play, an online platform for beginners to learn guitar and bass. Headquartered in Scottsdale, Arizona, Fender maintains manufacturing facilities in California and Mexico, focusing on quality and innovation in the musical instrument market.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/e3ebae9b-620d-4b3c-b87e-94a6a6ed09b4.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', 'greenhouse', 'fender', null), ('2362', 'Flexiform', 'FLEXIFORM BUSINESS FURNITURE LIMITED', 'https://www.flexiform.co.uk', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/flexiform', 'Flexiform is a UK-based designer, manufacturer, and supplier of office furniture with over 50 years of experience. Headquartered in West Yorkshire, the company specializes in high-quality office interiors, furniture, storage solutions, and seating. Flexiform serves a diverse client base, including UK government bodies, law enforcement agencies, and major blue-chip companies, showcasing its reputation for reliability and quality.The company operates a manufacturing plant in Yorkshire and has showrooms in London and Scotland. Flexiform emphasizes quality and service through its own transport fleet and installation teams, ensuring professional delivery and setup. Committed to environmental responsibility, Flexiform holds several certifications, including ISO 14001, ISO 18001, and ISO 9001, reflecting its dedication to sustainable and safe manufacturing practices. With a turnover of around $20.9 million and a workforce of approximately 72 people, Flexiform is recognized as a reputable leader in the UK office furniture industry.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/6b09f083-bb93-4a7d-af48-aa4509052da3.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', 'bamboohr', 'flexiform', null), ('2363', 'Hawksmoor Construction', 'Hawksmoor Construction Ltd', 'https://www.hawksmoorltd.co.uk', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/hawksmoorconstructionltd', 'We are a multi-award winning, Chartered Building Company, specialising in Prime Residential Construction.Here at Hawksmoor Construction, we are not your typical Building Contractor. We have an unique approach that results in the demolition of stereotypes surrounding the industry and redefining the construction norms!We elevate, innovate & collaborate, prioritising your desires & dreams for your new home.Our client focus & customer service drive our honesty and transparency in every aspect of our business.Its our core focus that we are dedicated to Building Excellence As Standard in all of our projects!Have a question? We are only a phone call or an email away!', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/c466df78-60f6-4b75-8537-0351bea57d2d.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', null, null, null), ('2364', 'Haymarket', 'Haymarket Media Group Limited', 'https://haymarket.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/haymarket-media-group', 'Haymarket Media Group is a private media, data, and information company based in London, UK, with a global presence that includes offices in the US, Canada, Hong Kong, Singapore, India, Germany, and the Netherlands. Established in 1957, the company has a strong history of producing trusted content across various sectors, including consumer, business, and specialist markets. The company operates in multiple media formats such as print, digital, live events, education, data services, video, and audio. Its portfolio features over 80 well-known brands, including Campaign, PrintWeek India, and What Car?, catering to specialist audiences worldwide. Haymarket provides a range of services, including publishing journals and periodicals, organizing exhibitions, and offering customer publishing and data-driven marketing services. The company is privately owned by the Heseltine family, with Michael Heseltine and his son Rupert playing significant roles in its management.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/9e2121e3-eb6c-483b-a2ec-964ca02147af.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', null, null, null), ('2365', 'iXtract', 'Ixtract Limited', 'https://www.ixtract.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/ixtract-ltd', 'Designed, built and tested right here in the UK. The future of Dust and Fume Extraction Solutions.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/c3b2c023-419d-4f79-8c81-e8e04c41b05d.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', null, null, null), ('2366', 'Neptune North', 'Neptune North Limited', 'https://www.neptunenorth.co.uk', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/neptune-north', 'Neptune North Limited is a private limited company based in Morpeth, Northumberland, England, established on June 19, 2024. As a micro-sized company with fewer than 10 employees, it specializes in software development and consulting services for businesses in the Financial Services and Alternative Investment markets. The company offers expertise in software development, data engineering, DevOps, and AI engineering, positioning itself as a technology partner for firms seeking advanced IT solutions.Neptune North is a joint venture between Oliver Wyman, a leader in management consulting, and Rokos Capital Management, a global alternative investment fund manager. This partnership enhances its ability to deliver specialized technology and consulting services. The company operates from a modern office in Newcastle, designed to promote collaboration and creativity, featuring flexible workspaces and wellbeing rooms to support employee productivity and mental health.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/4d763649-3c5c-4345-9ce9-be36991c3aeb.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', null, null, null), ('2367', 'New Gradient', 'New Gradient Ltd', 'https://www.newgradient.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/new-gradient-ai', 'We are a start-up aiming to bring the AI revolution to industries.  We build bespoke AI solutions for companies, helping them to level up their business. We either help automate and improve the efficiency of existing industry practices or create new business opportunities by creating AI solutions and products with our clients.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/04b4597b-5aa6-4323-9385-29c49506d889.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', 'greenhouse', 'new', null), ('2368', 'Premier Marinas', 'Premier Marinas Limited', 'https://www.premiermarinas.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/premier-marinas', 'Premier Marinas Limited, established in 1994 and based in Hampshire, England, is a prominent company in the UK focused on the ownership, management, and development of coastal marina sites. Owned by the Wellcome Trust, Premier Marinas operates eleven marinas and boatyards along the south coast, including locations in Falmouth, Dartmouth, and Brighton. The company offers over 5,000 wet and dry berths for leisure yachts and motorboats, making it one of the largest marina operators in the UK.The core services provided by Premier Marinas include secure wet and dry berthing, maintenance and repair services through its boatyard facilities, and ongoing marina management and development. The company is committed to enhancing customer experience and environmental stewardship by investing in sustainable technologies. Premier Marinas also hosts events like the Southampton International Boat Show and collaborates with the Royal Yachting Association to offer training workshops for boaters. With a focus on customer service and environmental responsibility, Premier Marinas serves leisure boat owners and marine service users seeking quality marina facilities.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/86c683bc-03c9-4258-85fd-bef8721287b5.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', 'smartrecruiters', 'premier', null), ('2369', 'St. George’s Crypt', 'St George''s Crypt', 'https://www.stgeorgescrypt.org.uk', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/stgeorgescrypt', 'St. George’s Crypt is a Christian-based charity and private limited company founded in 1930, located in Leeds, UK. The organization is dedicated to providing practical care, shelter, and support to homeless and vulnerable individuals, including those facing addiction issues. It operates hostels, offers food and accommodation, and provides emotional support to those in need.In addition to immediate assistance, St. George’s Crypt promotes training and resettlement programs to help individuals achieve independent living. The charity also runs three shops to support fundraising and community engagement. With a total income of approximately £4.8 million for the year ending March 2024, it is funded through government contracts, donations, and trading activities. The organization focuses on delivering individualized care, reflecting its Christian ethos and commitment to serving the community.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/8ccadc48-c5ee-4794-9c8d-008b5be18234.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', 'teamtailor', 'st', null), ('2370', '4C LABS', '4C LABS LTD', 'https://4clabs.co', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/4clabs', '4C LABS is a rapidly scaling healthcare, technology and pharmaceutical start-up focused on virtual prescribing, pharmaceutical distribution and clinical development in cannabis based medicinal products for human health. The empirical evidence for the efficacy of CBPM''s as a therapeutic agent in the treatment of cancer related pain, anxiety, childhood epilepsy, spasticity and sleep disorders is now overwhelming. We are committed to advancing scientific research, as well as enabling the regulation, distribution and prescribing of CBPM''s in the UK and Channel Islands. Our work with leading scientists, specialist physicians and pharmacists is underpinned with disruptive technologies that are driving an approach to treatment that prioritizes patients and evidence over stigma. We work closely with Drug Science, the Cannabis Industry Council,  The Home Office, The Medicines and Healthcare and regulatory Authority and the Care Quality Commission to catalyse safe, regulated change in the medical landscape. If you are a technologist, physician, scientist, distributor, LP or a patient and are interested in working with us, get in touch for a conversation: info@4clabs.ca', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/18d191f3-c353-4d70-b965-f60b342b7adb.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', null, null, null), ('2371', 'Acron Aviation', 'Acron Aviation Training Solutions Limited', 'https://acronaviation.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/acronaviation', 'Acron Aviation is a global aviation company that specializes in avionics, pilot training, flight data intelligence, and simulation solutions. Established in 2025 after the acquisition of L3Harris Commercial Aviation Solutions, Acron Aviation aims to be a leading partner in the aviation industry. The name "Acron," derived from the Greek word for "peak," reflects the company''s ambition for excellence.With nearly 100 years of heritage, Acron Aviation operates in the United States, United Kingdom, Thailand, and India. The company offers OEM certified avionics products designed to enhance flight safety, along with a comprehensive range of pilot simulation devices and training technologies. Acron Aviation also runs global training centers that provide specialized pilot and examiner training, supported by advanced technology and expert instruction. Additionally, the company delivers flight data services that improve flight operations through actionable intelligence, monitoring approximately 18,000 flights daily. Acron Aviation serves a diverse clientele, including commercial airlines, business jet operators, and military aviation sectors, reflecting its commitment to innovation and safety in aviation.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/ce27730f-6d34-47cf-9036-a881171e1922.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', null, null, null), ('2372', 'ADEC Innovations', 'ADEC SOLUTIONS LIMITED', 'https://www.adec-innovations.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/adecinnovations', 'ADEC Innovations is a global business solutions organization dedicated to advancing sustainable practices. Founded in Manila and now headquartered in California, the company operates in 26 locations across 14 countries, employing over 4,000 people and generating revenue exceeding $678 million. ADEC Innovations focuses on transforming risk into positive impact through its expertise in Environmental Risk & Compliance, Sustainability & ESG, and Business Process & Impact Sourcing.The company offers a range of services, including environmental risk assessments, regulatory compliance consulting, and sustainability performance improvement. Through its subsidiaries, ADEC Innovations provides tailored outsourcing services, particularly in healthcare, emphasizing sustainable profitability and informed decision-making. The company utilizes proprietary software and technology platforms to support data management and analytics, helping clients meet regulatory requirements and sustainability goals.ADEC Innovations serves a diverse clientele, including governments, corporations, and healthcare organizations, and is committed to creating positive social and environmental impacts. The company actively collaborates with international organizations to promote sustainable development goals.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/d29bfb55-225f-4374-bf81-6455e2bd51e5.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', 'smartrecruiters', 'adecinnovations', null), ('2373', 'ADVANCE AI', 'ADVANCE AI LTD', 'https://advanceai.tech', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/advanceanalytics', 'ADVANCE®AI is a global leader in AI and big data, specializing in digital identity verification, fraud prevention, compliance, risk management, and credit information services. Based in Singapore and part of the Advance Intelligence Group, the company serves over 800 enterprise clients across various sectors, including banking, fintech, retail, and e-commerce, in markets such as Asia, Africa, Latin America, and Greater China.The company offers a range of AI-powered products designed to facilitate digital transformation and automate processes. Their key services include contactless and biometric identity verification with high accuracy, advanced fraud detection technologies, compliance tools for KYC and AML, and credit information services to aid financial decision-making. ADVANCE®AI handles over 4 million API calls daily and is committed to values such as customer-centricity, data innovation, and collaboration.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/c82b4d22-6951-46d3-8cc5-1e49118c2df8.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', 'bamboohr', 'advancedelectricmachines', null), ('2374', 'Contollo', 'CONTOLLO GROUP LIMITED', 'https://www.contollogroup.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/contollo', 'Contollo is a new building consultancy that brings together built environment experts with people who know how to build a group.The demand for energy efficiency, carbon reduction, and sustainability, coincides with increased expectations of what buildings can deliver. However, the building services sector is highly fragmented, with isolated disciplines and limited collaboration. This siloed approach reduces the effectiveness of the consultancy process and prevents developers from realising the full potential of smart buildings.The founders of Contollo are on a journey to form a new mid-sized consultancy that works with commercial developers to offer building consultancy (MEP and Cost Management), with particular expertise in smart buildings. Contollo seeks to bridge the gaps in collaboration, allowing a more integrated and effective approach to building consultancy that unlocks the full potential of smart buildings for developers.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/b4b81cde-62b0-4ef2-ac30-0553d6935d51.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', null, null, null), ('2375', 'De La Rue', 'De La Rue Limited', 'https://www.delarue.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/de-la-rue', 'De La Rue is a prominent global security printing company, established in 1813 by Thomas de la Rue in Guernsey. The company specializes in designing and producing secure printed products, including banknotes, postage stamps, and various security documents. Over the years, De La Rue has evolved from its early days of printing playing cards to becoming the world''s largest independent security printer and papermaker, serving over 150 countries.The company offers a range of services, including the printing of both paper and polymer banknotes for central banks, production of postage stamps, and manufacturing of secure government documents like passports. De La Rue also develops banknote printing technology and produces specialized security paper. Its clients include central banks, governments, and postal authorities, all relying on De La Rue for their currency and secure document needs. The company''s expertise plays a vital role in ensuring the financial stability and security of nations worldwide.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/b1c02b9e-551b-4b87-bc2f-4f12468ceacb.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', null, null, null), ('2376', 'DG Partners', 'DG Partners Services Limited', 'https://www.dgpartners.co.uk', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/dg-partners-llp', 'Building intelligent systems for real-world impact.We are a collective of experienced traders, academics, scientists and technologists.Since the launch of our systematic strategy in 2006, our mission has been to build adaptive trend-following strategies.Our systematic R&D sets us apart. It culminates in a portfolio of diverse momentum trades with potential risk mitigation benefits.We partner with institutional investors who need a liquid but long-term systematic trading solution that ultimately empowers their beneficiaries to make a meaningful impact on the world around them.DG Partners is authorised and regulated by the UK Financial Conduct Authority and only provides services to professional and institutional clients.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/b3b0ce1f-ba14-44a3-a515-894296983854.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', null, null, null), ('2377', 'Energise', 'ENERGISE LTD', 'https://www.energise.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/energise-ltd', 'Energise is a sustainability consultancy based in Cambridgeshire, UK, with operations in Germany and the United States. Founded in 2008, the company is a certified B Corporation and a Great Place to Work-Certified™ organization, recognized for its commitment to environmental and social sustainability. With a team that boasts over 200 years of combined experience, Energise aims to empower organizations to drive meaningful change for people and the planet.Energise provides a wide range of sustainability consultancy and compliance services tailored to large organizations, SMEs, public sector bodies, and charities. Their offerings include developing sustainability strategies, data management, setting Science Based Targets for carbon reduction, and improving resource efficiency. The company also features technology platforms like the Net Zero Club, which centralizes sustainability data to help clients track and achieve their Net Zero goals. Energise has made a significant impact, helping clients avoid over 650,000 tonnes of CO2 equivalent emissions and unlocking substantial financial savings.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/5b06bf1e-3d6b-4b2c-8bd0-b1b0d6aa3f7d.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', null, null, null), ('2378', 'Indefi', 'INDEFI LTD', 'https://indefi.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/indefi', 'INDEFI is an independent strategy consulting firm founded in 2007, focused on serving financial investors like private equity firms, asset managers, and wealth managers. Headquartered in Paris, with additional offices in Lyon and Madrid, the firm employs over 80 consultants and operates with a flat structure that promotes entrepreneurial spirit and client-first values.The company is organized into three main business units: Private Equity, which advises on investment decisions throughout the deal lifecycle; Corporate Strategy, which collaborates with global asset managers on strategic development projects; and Sustainability, which provides ESG and sustainability advisory services. INDEFI''s expertise spans various sectors, including agri-food, healthcare, and energy, offering tailored services such as market research and sustainability impact analysis.INDEFI emphasizes diversity and environmental responsibility, promoting gender parity and reducing its environmental footprint. The firm is dedicated to helping clients improve investment performance and integrate sustainable practices throughout the investment lifecycle.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/7813f673-5fab-42e5-b291-22e67a22f956.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', 'teamtailor', 'indefi', null), ('2379', 'Liberating Research', 'Liberating Research Ltd', 'https://www.liberatingresearch.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/liberating-research', 'Liberating Research is a health research community for patients and practitioners in Europe and the United States. Specialists in healthcare fieldwork, our custom platform allows our community to take part in online, phone or in-person market research relating to their condition, so they can get paid, raise money for charity and help research all at the same time.We believe that the best data and insight comes from respondents who are engaged. So we built a platform that does just that. Our Condition Q&A allows everyone to be a researcher; from posting questions to the community, health polls and wellness recommendations direct from other verified patients, we wanted to use the best in technology to liberate research for all.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/16119f84-8d66-4fd3-8c1d-a7b63c3f9b74.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', null, null, null), ('2380', 'Beettoo', 'Beettoo Ltd', 'https://www.beettoo.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/beettoo', 'We are a different kind of B2B specialist agency, focused on driving better value for B2B marketers through a more expert, agile and accountable agency model, which we call "liquid resource". A model that helps our clients navigate the increasingly complex B2B customer journey and enables better performance through the smarter use of global B2B marketing expertise, all delivered seamlessly through one agency partnerWe believe in the importance of connecting brand to demand and content to media and unlike many B2B agencies, we give equal weight to both.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/981679b7-393f-4ded-97aa-362e5a1149d2.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', null, null, null), ('2381', 'Bourse & Bazaar Foundation', 'BOURSE AND BAZAAR FOUNDATON', 'https://www.bourseandbazaar.org', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/bourse-and-bazaar-foundation', 'The Bourse & Bazaar Foundation is a UK-based non-profit think tank established in October 2020, evolving from its origins as a digital publisher in 2015. It focuses on advancing economic development, economic diplomacy, and economic justice across West Asia, a region that includes countries from Turkey to Afghanistan and Yemen to Kazakhstan.The Foundation aims to promote security, prosperity, sustainability, and cultural flourishing in West Asia through innovative research and analysis. It operates through an initiative model, launching multi-year programs that address specific policy gaps with research, convenings, and advocacy. Notable initiatives include the Integrated Futures Initiative, Rihla Initiative, Sanctions Relief Initiative, and Vision Iran Initiative. The Foundation produces research reports and policy analyses on various economic topics and organizes workshops and dialogues to engage policymakers, business leaders, and civil society stakeholders. Led by founder and CEO Esfandyar Batmanghelidj, the Foundation collaborates with institutions worldwide to foster networks focused on sustainable economic growth in the region. Its work is relevant to policymakers, business leaders, civil society organizations, and academic researchers interested in West Asia''s economic and political development.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/b7a5e5d1-87a8-4542-a4a0-c6e4a22ddd18.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', null, null, null), ('2382', 'Cambustion', 'Cambustion Limited', 'https://www.cambustion.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/cambustion', 'Cambustion is an independent company based in Cambridge, UK, founded in 1987 by a research group from the Cambridge University Engineering Department. The company initially focused on developing a fast response Flame Ionisation Detector (FID) for hydrocarbon measurement and has since broadened its expertise and product offerings.Cambustion operates through two main divisions. The Products Group develops advanced scientific measurement instruments for various applications, including medical device development, fire safety testing, and ambient pollution monitoring. Their product lineup features fast-response gas analyzers such as the HFR500 FID and CLD500 for NOx measurement. The Powertrain Engineering Services Group provides high-specification powertrain development and testing services, utilizing a range of dynamometers and emissions measurement equipment. Their expertise encompasses gasoline, diesel, alternative fuels, and electric powertrains.Cambustion serves a diverse clientele, including researchers, OEMs, and academic institutions, delivering precise measurement and testing solutions that support innovation and compliance across multiple sectors.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/4a8212a3-4fec-4052-b760-f027087a33d5.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', null, null, null), ('2383', 'Chadwicks of Bury', 'Chadwicks of Bury Ltd', 'https://www.chadwickslids.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/chadwicks-of-bury-ltd', 'A world class manufacturer of heat seal, pre-cut lidding. Chadwicks is a UV flexo printer and converter of pre-cut lids in aluminium, polyester, and co-ex materials for dairy, food and drink, household and industrial products. From our head office and manufacturing site in Bury, Greater Manchester, in the UK we use the latest technology and processes to maintain our position at the forefront of the industry. We work with some of the world''s leading brands and our lidding can be found all over the world.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/6134419f-85df-4c66-970e-22fb02f9966d.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', null, null, null), ('2384', 'ComAp Group', 'ComAp Controls Limited', 'https://uk.comap-control.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/comap-group', 'ComAp Group is a global leader in smart energy control solutions, founded in 1991 in Prague, Czech Republic. The company has grown significantly, employing over 400 people and operating 13 subsidiaries with a network of more than 60 distributors worldwide. ComAp is family-owned and focuses on sustainable growth, innovation, and strong customer relationships.The company specializes in advanced control systems for independent and backup power generation. ComAp develops and manufactures a variety of smart controllers and control solutions, including products for power generation and combined heat and power (CHP) applications. Its technology supports efficient, reliable, and sustainable energy operations, helping customers manage their energy needs effectively.ComAp serves a diverse B2B customer base across various industries that require reliable power generation and energy management solutions. With a strong local presence in key markets such as Japan, France, Turkey, and Spain, ComAp tailors its offerings to meet the specific needs of its customers while promoting the transition to sustainable energy sources.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/862213cb-2702-4810-90bf-4b2524dde511.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', null, null, null), ('2385', 'Downforce Technologies', 'Downforce Technologies Limited', 'https://www.downforce.tech', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/downforce-technologies', 'Downforce Technologies is a UK-based company founded in 2020, focused on data-driven land management solutions. Headquartered in Oxford, the company specializes in optimizing soil health, soil organic carbon (SOC) levels, and biodiversity to address soil degradation and enhance climate resilience. With a team of around 25 employees, Downforce operates in the business intelligence software and environmental consulting sectors.The company offers a patented, ISO-certified platform that utilizes remote sensing, airborne and satellite data, and geophysical information to create a high-resolution Digital Twin of land. This platform enables non-intrusive SOC analysis at a 10m x 10m resolution, providing historical data and updates every 10 days. Downforce''s services include SOC analysis, sustainability and net zero reporting, land management insights, and environmental consulting. Their technology supports a diverse range of clients, including farmers, landowners, and sustainability managers, helping them make informed decisions to improve soil health and achieve sustainability goals.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/99488f02-cdfd-470a-a29e-02a1662dbae5.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', null, null, null), ('2386', 'Goods & Services', 'GOODS & SERVICES TECHNOLOGY LIMITED', 'https://www.goodsandservices.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/goodsandservices', 'Goods & Services is a product design and digital engineering firm that collaborates with large enterprises to tackle complex challenges through innovative technology and design solutions. The company specializes in creating and enhancing digital products, platforms, and ecosystems, focusing on delivering comprehensive solutions that integrate design, technology, and engineering.Their services include product experience and design, digital engineering, technology solutions, hardware and IoT development, and AI and intelligent automation. Goods & Services crafts user-centric digital ecosystems and develops IoT devices, smart prototypes, and integrated hardware-software products tailored to client needs. They work with prominent clients across various industries, including JP Morgan Asset Management, ZEISS Microscopy, Becton Dickinson, and Mastercard, among others, to enhance customer engagement and market presence.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/6fe10425-659c-4ac5-92af-9eaed44a3a37.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', 'greenhouse', 'goodsservices', null), ('2387', 'Keyfactor', 'Keyfactor UK Holdings Limited', 'https://www.keyfactor.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/wearekeyfactor', 'Keyfactor is a cybersecurity company that specializes in machine identity management and digital identity solutions. Founded in 2001 in Cleveland, Ohio, the company initially focused on Public Key Infrastructure (PKI) professional services. In 2015, it rebranded to Keyfactor to emphasize its shift towards a product-centric approach, particularly in cryptographic key lifecycle automation.Keyfactor offers a range of products and services, including PKI as-a-Service, certificate lifecycle automation, and a machine and IoT identity platform. The company also provides cryptographic APIs and tools like the Secure Execution Environment and Identity Authority Manager. Following its acquisition of PrimeKey in 2021, Keyfactor expanded its offerings to include advanced PKI and digital signature solutions. With a flexible platform that supports various deployment options, Keyfactor caters to diverse enterprise needs, helping organizations secure their digital infrastructure efficiently.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/651065b2-c76b-4202-b382-ce375dc1866a.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', 'greenhouse', 'keyfactorinc', null), ('2388', 'Panache', 'Panache Lingerie Limited', 'https://www.panache-lingerie.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/panache-lingerie', 'Panache Lingerie Ltd is a private limited company located in Sheffield, South Yorkshire, UK, established on 22 October 1980. The company specializes in the wholesale of lingerie products, offering a diverse range of styles and brands tailored for women of all sizes. Their product line includes bras, panties, and other intimate apparel, focusing on quality and fit.As a medium-sized enterprise, Panache Lingerie Ltd has a reported turnover of approximately £18.9 million to £20.2 million and employs around 98 to 107 people. The company maintains a solid financial position with net assets of about £9 million and a gross margin of nearly 49.4%. With experienced leadership, including directors Mr. John Power and Ms. Siobhan Grantham, Panache Lingerie serves a broad customer base in the UK market, distributing its products primarily through wholesale channels.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/0bc90a61-6ee2-49ca-b915-8c6fdbf16279.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', 'smartrecruiters', 'panache', null), ('2389', 'EUROWAG', 'W.A.G. Payment Solutions Plc', 'https://www.eurowag.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/eurowag', 'Eurowag, founded in 1995 in the Czech Republic by CEO Martin Vohánka, is a prominent integrated payments and mobility platform serving the commercial road transport industry across Europe. Originally established as W. A. G. Group, the company launched its payment services platform in 2000 and has since expanded through strategic acquisitions, enhancing its technology and service offerings.Eurowag provides a variety of services, including payment solutions for fuel and tolls, fleet management through telematics, and support for alternative fuels and eMobility. The company also offers financial services like invoice factoring and tax refund services tailored to the road transport sector. Additionally, Eurowag operates truck parks in several countries, providing essential roadside services for drivers. With a commitment to sustainability and innovation, Eurowag aims to simplify operations for commercial road transport companies and fleet operators across Europe.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/868e36c4-892e-45ce-ae69-5f71bf0e4ca3.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', 'hibob', 'https://eurowaggroup.careers.hibob.com/api/job-ad', null), ('2390', 'Yaspa', 'Yaspa Ltd', 'https://www.yaspa.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/yaspa', 'Yaspa is a fintech company founded in 2017 and based in London, UK, with operations in Europe and a new presence in the United States. Formerly known as Citizen UK Holding Ltd, Yaspa is regulated by the UK’s Financial Conduct Authority. The company specializes in open banking technology, offering instant payment and identity verification services primarily for regulated businesses.Yaspa''s main product is Intelligent Payments, a real-time payments solution that facilitates faster, more secure bank-to-bank transactions compared to traditional card payments. This service also includes integrated customer identity verification, enhancing compliance and reducing fraud. Yaspa focuses on sectors like online gambling, where its account-to-account payment technology improves efficiency and player protection. The company has attracted significant investment to support its expansion, particularly in the US market, and is backed by notable investors in the fintech and technology sectors.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/e6adefd0-2453-4f68-bcd3-9a29363a5954.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', null, null, null), ('2391', '10 Days London', '10 DAYS STUDIO LTD', 'https://www.10days.london', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/10dayslondon', '10 Days London is a creative agency that specializes in rapid advertising and brand campaigns. Founded by brothers Jolyon, George, and Dominic White, the agency leverages their extensive experience in top agencies to deliver high-quality work. With a unique "Music that moves™" approach, they incorporate bespoke compositions and sound design into their creative offerings. The agency has a presence in London, Amsterdam, and New York.The services offered by 10 Days London include brand strategy, concept development, film production, and media planning. They also provide bespoke music composition and sound design, along with AI-driven branding solutions. Their innovative service, "Brief to Blockbuster," condenses a typical campaign process into just ten days, catering to clients who need efficient and effective advertising solutions. The agency''s diverse capabilities allow them to serve a wide range of clients across various media platforms.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/a122aee7-6b7b-498d-a390-88b16bc4d76e.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', null, null, null), ('2392', 'Appian Capital Advisory', 'Appian Capital U.K. Limited', 'https://appiancapitaladvisory.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/appian-capital-advisory', 'Appian Capital Advisory LLP is a private equity investment advisor based in London, specializing in the metals and mining sectors. Founded in 2011, the firm manages around US$3.6 billion in assets and advises several private capital funds, including the Appian Natural Resources Fund series. Appian focuses on investing in mining-related companies and assets, particularly those that are essential for energy transition and green technology.The company aims to be a preferred partner in the metals and mining industry by connecting quality assets with long-term capital and operational expertise. With a team that boasts over 300 years of combined experience in the mining sector, Appian employs a hands-on investment approach to enhance the operational and financial value of its portfolio companies. The firm also emphasizes Environmental, Social, and Governance (ESG) standards, ensuring responsible investment practices throughout its operations. Appian serves institutional investors and stakeholders seeking long-term capital investment and operational partnerships in the mining sector.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/3eb567ec-4df9-4c5e-a419-67dbfe74cbc3.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', 'greenhouse', 'appian', null), ('2393', 'BIOME9', 'Biome9 Limited', 'https://biome9.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/biome9', 'BIOME9 is revolutionising pet care, through personalised, data-led solutions. We use cutting-edge science and AI to decode the complex science of the gut microbiome, eliminating the guesswork around choosing the right diet and nutrition for our dogs. If there was one thing you could do to transform your dog''s health and happiness, wouldn''t you want to know?GutDiscovery® will change that for good. Our groundbreaking, at-home, gut microbiome test gives you a window into your dog''s inner world, and pinpoints their specific nutritional and dietary requirements.Our UK laboratory leads the way for speed and accuracy whilst our proprietary InvisibleHealth™ algorithm, uses the most advanced generative AI to instantly process millions of complex data points and turn them into insights and a care plan, as unique as your dog.A personalised report features a tailored nutritional plan and a precision supplement programme, built specifically around your dog''s complex biological makeup.Why test my dog''s microbiome? Research is proving connections to far more than we once thought:Discover root-cause solutions for digestive issues and IBDEnhance joint, skin, and dental healthBoost immunityDetect early health-risks and complicationsReduce risk of obesity and allergiesWe''re dedicated to transforming pet health through research and tech, providing an innovative science-backed approach to personalised pet nutrition, so you get to enjoy the very best version of your pet - healthy and happy, inside and out.Join the pet care revolution!', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/edcdddbe-1124-4155-80a8-e0ea34f32c7a.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', null, null, null), ('2394', 'Centtrip', 'Centtrip Limited', 'https://www.centtrip.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/centtrip', 'Centtrip Ltd is a UK-based financial technology company that specializes in foreign exchange, international payments, and treasury services for global businesses. Founded in 2013, it operates as an electronic money institution regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority. Centtrip provides multi-currency accounts and prepaid cards, enabling businesses to efficiently manage international spending and currency exchange.The company''s platform offers comprehensive spend management solutions for international teams in dynamic sectors such as music, yacht management, film and television production, private aviation, and merchant marine. Centtrip''s services include foreign exchange, expense management, and international payments integrated with the SWIFT network and MasterCard scheme. With a focus on rapid and flexible financial solutions, Centtrip caters to a niche clientele of internationally mobile organizations.Headquartered in London, Centtrip manages over £1 billion in transactions annually and employs approximately 47 staff members. The company prioritizes customer support and compliance with financial regulations to safeguard customer funds.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/5452c995-0444-4c41-bfd9-4329e7e584ca.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', null, null, null), ('2395', 'CGC', 'CGC LDN Limited', 'https://www.cgc.global', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/c-g-c', 'CGC is an integrated global communications and talent agency that specializes in building brands through storytelling, particularly in the beauty, lifestyle, and retail sectors. The agency focuses on creating impactful partnerships that enhance brand narratives by representing leading talent and storytellers.CGC offers services such as strategic consulting, brand building, and talent representation. They emphasize a personable, in-house approach combined with creative and visionary perspectives. Their work includes curating content, amplifying brand positioning, and developing meaningful partnerships on a global scale. Founded by Clare Goodwin, CGC serves as a collective of influential talent driving brand storytelling worldwide.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/c062269d-eda4-4fee-a13b-bf812592912b.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', 'breezy', 'cgc', null), ('2396', 'Corinthia Global Management', 'Corinthia Global Management Limited', 'https://corinthiagm.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/corinthia-global-management-limited', 'Corinthia Global Management Limited is a private limited company based in London, UK, established in July 2022. The firm operates as a private credit platform, focusing on originating and managing private credit investment opportunities for clients globally, particularly in the UK, Europe, and America.The company specializes in connecting investors with borrowers, facilitating partnerships that promote financial growth. Corinthia offers tailored credit solutions, leveraging local market knowledge and global insights to meet diverse client needs. It emphasizes trust, transparency, and security, ensuring rigorous due diligence for every investment opportunity. Additionally, Corinthia is committed to sustainable and ethical investment practices, aligning its decisions with responsible investing principles. With a small team, Corinthia Global Management serves a wide range of clients, including investors seeking private credit opportunities and borrowers in need of credit financing. The company is authorized and regulated by the UK Financial Conduct Authority.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/33d5f101-fbc6-4c39-8f0d-29ed536d0eb3.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', null, null, null), ('2397', 'Curve Games', 'Curve Digital Publishing Limited', 'https://curvegames.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/curvegames', 'Curve Games Limited is a British video game publisher based in London, founded in 2005 by Jason Perkins. Originally known as Curve Studios, the company shifted its focus from game development to publishing indie games in 2013, rebranding as Curve Digital and later as Curve Games in October 2021. The company specializes in publishing indie video games across various platforms, including Steam, Stadia, Nintendo Switch, Xbox, and PC. Curve Games has published over 21 titles in collaboration with around 25 game studios, with notable games such as *The Swapper*, *Stealth Inc*, *Space Crew*, and *For the King*. The company has built strong relationships with indie developers, providing them with publishing support, marketing expertise, and platform connections, particularly with Sony and Nintendo. In May 2025, Curve Games was acquired by Nazara Technologies, further enhancing its position in the indie game publishing sector.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/a3e7df15-ae1d-4589-bd59-09600cc9a1b0.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', 'teamtailor', 'curvegames', null), ('2398', 'Cyera', 'Cyera UK Ltd', 'https://www.cyera.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/cyera', 'Cyera is a data security company that specializes in AI-powered Data Security Posture Management (DSPM) and data governance solutions tailored for the cloud. The company aims to create an intelligent data security platform that helps businesses safely utilize data to drive innovation and growth. Cyera''s focus is on data security, privacy, compliance, and governance, setting it apart from broader security platforms.The company offers a cloud-native, agentless platform that quickly deploys across cloud and on-premises environments. Key features include automated data discovery and classification, visibility into data risks, data access governance, and real-time detection and response. Cyera also supports compliance with security and privacy regulations. Recently, it launched Omni DLP, an AI-driven Data Loss Prevention solution to enhance data protection. Operating on a Software-as-a-Service (SaaS) model, Cyera serves various industries, including financial services, healthcare, and entertainment, with notable clients like Paramount Pictures and AT&T.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/a352c185-4885-4541-821a-5f3bcbf89c71.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', null, null, null), ('2399', 'Markettiers', 'Eckhart Ltd (Trading as Markettiers)', 'https://markettiers.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/markettiers', 'Markettiers is a global broadcast specialist and consultancy firm based in London, with additional offices in Manchester MediaCityUK and Dubai. Founded in 1994, the company has grown from a radio PR specialist into a comprehensive agency that supports international, national, and regional campaigns for a diverse range of clients, from start-ups to major global brands.The company offers a variety of services, including broadcast consultancy for TV, radio, and live streaming content, media relations, and brand storytelling. Markettiers features in-house production facilities with multiple broadcast studios and a direct link to the BT Tower for live TV interviews. Their multi-lingual media relations teams operate from London, Singapore, and New York, and they have access to a network of production partners in over 30 countries, enhancing their global campaign reach.Markettiers has received numerous industry awards for its work and is recognized for its innovative approaches to audience engagement, including live streaming to social media platforms. The company is also a founding broadcast partner of the Public Relations and Communications Association (PRCA).', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/e77b336f-4773-497a-88f0-5d84c65738b0.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', null, null, null), ('2400', 'EL&N London', 'EL&N Ltd', 'https://elnlondon.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/elnlondon', 'EL&N London is a luxury café and lifestyle brand founded in 2017 in Mayfair, London. Known as the "world''s most Instagrammable café," the brand''s name stands for *Eat, Live & Nourish*, reflecting its mission to enhance everyday dining with innovative menus and stylish interiors. Founded by Alexandra Miller, who has a background in luxury fashion, EL&N has rapidly expanded to over 35 locations worldwide, including cities like Milan, Paris, Dubai, and Kuala Lumpur.The café offers a unique dining experience featuring specialty coffee, an all-day dining menu with popular dishes, handmade patisserie, and grab-and-go options. EL&N London targets a diverse audience, particularly social media-savvy customers who appreciate visually appealing environments. The brand combines high-end fashion aesthetics with accessible luxury, creating a loyal customer base that includes casual coffee drinkers and food enthusiasts alike.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/f75aa8da-d63d-4e4c-913e-db164200ee34.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', null, null, null), ('2401', 'Elliot Scientific', 'ELLIOT SCIENTIFIC LTD', 'https://www.elliotscientific.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/elliot-scientific-ltd', 'Elliot Scientific is a major supplier of Opto-Mechanic, Laser, Cryogenic, Magnetic and other systems and components to Science, Research and Industry. We manufacture our own ranges that are marketed under the Elliot|Martock and Elliot Scientific brands, and also supply world class products sourced from many leading companies. We are uniquely positioned to assist our customers, being able to: - Supply competitive components and systems - Source, integrate and manufacture complex systems - Design and manufacture for Custom or OEM requirementsThe Elliot|Martock and Elliot Scientific own brand products include our award winning optical tweezer systems, the "Lab Essentials"​ optic mounting range, fibre positioning components, waveguide manipulators, automated alignment systems, micropositioners and a broad portfolio of other class-leading products.	All of our customers - from academic institutions and government agencies through to commercial researchers and industry - are provided with the highest levels of service backed up by solid technical support from our team of experienced engineers and scientists.	We pride ourselves in offering Solution Science for Research and Industry. We employ the best-qualified staff to help you sift through the multitude of options available to get the equipment and systems that match your needs. That''s Solution Science.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/a9ad1d5f-d93d-459c-a572-a17e225905aa.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', 'breezy', 'elliot', null), ('2402', 'Enamel Dental', 'Enamel Dental Holdings Limited', 'https://enameldental.co.uk', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/enamel-dental', 'Enamel is a predominantly private, progressive and community focused dental group. We pride ourselves on providing the highest levels of patient care, whilst retaining that local, trustworthy and dependable feel every practice should have. From family dentistry to cosmetic dentistry and everything in between, your healthy smile is our only focus, and we can''t wait to welcome you in to one of our clinics soon.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/a937c2de-02b2-402a-b3d3-dc8a297a382c.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', null, null, null), ('2403', 'Enlight10', 'ENLIGHT10 LIMITED', 'https://enlight10.uk/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/enlight10uk', 'We are Enlight10, pioneering the future of modular construction. Discover our innovative solutions and see how we’re transforming the industry today.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/0012b78d-4796-42bd-a61d-ca1a9ed68208.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', null, null, null), ('2404', 'Workiro', 'GETBUSY UK LIMITED', 'https://www.workiro.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/workirohq', 'Workiro is a cloud-based enterprise content management (ECM) platform that enhances collaboration, document management, and communication for businesses of all sizes. Founded in 1998, the company has over 20 years of experience and serves 70,000 paying users globally. Workiro focuses on regulated sectors and complex businesses, emphasizing security and compliance with standards like ISO27001, CSA STAR, and GDPR.The platform offers a range of features, including document management, task and project management, secure file storage, eSigning, and collaboration tools. It integrates with major third-party applications such as NetSuite, Microsoft 365, and Salesforce, making it suitable for mid-size to large businesses across various departments. Workiro supports industries that require high levels of security and complex document workflows, such as private banking and healthcare. The company is committed to quick deployment and fostering strong customer relationships through continuous product innovation.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/46075ac1-4573-42c2-bc9a-362dbc0def97.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', null, null, null), ('2405', 'Helix', 'Helix Property Advisors Ltd', 'https://helixproperty.co.uk', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/helix-hines', 'Helix, a Hines company, is a commercial property management firm based in London, UK. It provides comprehensive property management services for a portfolio valued at over £3.5 billion, managing more than 200 properties across various asset classes, including office, retail, industrial, and leisure. The firm operates from a single Central London office with a dedicated team of about 60 professionals, ensuring efficient coordination and a client-focused approach.Helix emphasizes building long-lasting relationships with clients and occupiers, aiming to maximize property value and enhance tenant experiences. Its services cover the full spectrum of property management functions, with a strong focus on effective execution and innovation in areas such as environmental, social, and governance (ESG) initiatives and technology integration. As part of Hines, Helix manages high-profile assets and reflects a commitment to sustainable property management practices.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/32e546a7-6a9c-4ff1-b469-276d21d72cdc.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', 'bamboohr', 'helix', null), ('2406', 'HUBNER Group', 'Hubner UK Limited', 'https://www.hubner-group.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/hubner-group', 'The HÜBNER Group is a global technology and system provider based in Kassel, Germany, founded in 1946. With over 3,500 employees and more than 30 locations worldwide, the company has a rich history and a strong focus on innovation, holding around 1,000 patents. HÜBNER serves diverse markets, including mobility, industry, life sciences, and photonics.In the mobility sector, HÜBNER is a leader in gangway systems for rail vehicles, buses, and trams, offering products like folding bellows and chassis technology. The company also specializes in advanced materials, including elastomers and composites, providing tailored solutions for various industrial applications. In photonics, HÜBNER develops high-performance lasers and terahertz technology for use in life sciences, microscopy, and industrial quality control. With a commitment to quality and reliability, HÜBNER maintains long-term partnerships with major clients, including Deutsche Bahn, and plays a vital role in public transportation and advanced scientific applications.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/abd1abb6-41d3-45d6-91a7-403479426acd.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', null, null, null), ('2407', 'INVISIO', 'INVISIO Communications Limited', 'https://invisio.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/invisio-tactical-communication-systems', 'INVISIO is a global leader in advanced communication and hearing protection systems, primarily serving professional users in noisy and mission-critical environments. Founded in 1999 and based in Copenhagen, Denmark, the company shifted its focus exclusively to professional communication solutions in 2008. INVISIO develops sophisticated systems that integrate expertise in hearing, acoustics, electronics, and mechanics, catering to military, law enforcement, and security personnel.The product range includes communication headsets, control units, and hearing protection systems under the INVISIO and Racal Acoustics brands. Notable innovations feature bone conduction technology for enhanced situational awareness, as well as artificial intelligence and digital signal processing for improved sound clarity. INVISIO has secured significant contracts with military forces and law enforcement agencies across various countries, demonstrating strong financial growth and a commitment to research and development. The company emphasizes innovation and quality, fostering a culture of continuous development among its employees.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/9df76794-e412-4f27-b170-ad53c77b2ef0.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', null, null, null), ('2408', 'JEM Property', 'JEM property', 'https://jemproperty.co.uk/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/jem-property-ltd', 'JEM Property is a private limited company established on September 1, 2017, based in Breaston, Derby, England. The company specializes in real estate management, focusing on asset acquisition and disposal services. They operate throughout the United Kingdom, particularly emphasizing the healthcare sector.The company offers a range of services, including identifying acquisition opportunities tailored to client goals, assisting with exit strategies for real estate assets, and fostering strategic partnerships. JEM Property is committed to a client-centered approach, ensuring personalized services that align with clients'' growth objectives. They integrate ethical practices and corporate responsibility into their operations, highlighting their dedication to community values and sustainable development. With a strong emphasis on operational excellence and market knowledge, JEM Property aims to meet client investment objectives effectively. Their experience is demonstrated through case studies of successful acquisitions in various locations, showcasing their expertise in asset management and transactions.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/c09f55bc-aa10-4803-aaa1-f06279b9c96c.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', null, null, null), ('2409', 'Marugame Udon', 'Karali Mu Limited', 'https://marugame.co.uk', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/marugame-udon-europe', 'Marugame Udon Europe is the European branch of the Japanese fast-casual restaurant chain Marugame Udon, known for its authentic Sanuki-style udon noodles and tempura. Founded in 2000 in Japan, the brand has expanded significantly, operating over 1,250 locations worldwide by 2020. In Europe, Marugame Udon Europe Ltd. serves as the master franchisee, with its first UK restaurant opening in London in 2021 and plans for further growth.The restaurant offers freshly made udon noodles prepared in an exhibition-style kitchen, allowing customers to witness the noodle-making process. The menu features a variety of udon dishes, including traditional options and adaptations for local tastes, such as tonkotsu udon and vegan udon. Marugame Udon emphasizes quality, transparency, and sustainability, appealing to fast-casual diners who appreciate authentic Japanese cuisine in a welcoming atmosphere. The company is committed to responsible business practices and cultural exchange, providing training opportunities for staff in Japan.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/980de100-f71a-4736-a479-cad30607e4f6.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', null, null, null), ('2410', 'Crosstown', 'Karali Snacks Ltd', 'https://www.crosstown.co.uk/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/crosstown-doughnuts', 'Crosstown is a London-based artisan bakery known for its handcrafted sourdough doughnuts, ice cream, and specialty coffee. Established in 2014 as a market stall on Leather Lane, the company has expanded to over 30 locations across London, offering walk-in service and online orders with pickup or on-demand delivery. Crosstown emphasizes quality by hand-rolling all dough and making fresh jams, fillings, and toppings daily in their Battersea bakery.The bakery is famous for its signature hybrid sourdough doughnut and has been a pioneer in vegan options since 2017. They frequently introduce limited-edition flavors that challenge traditional doughnut making. Crosstown also provides nationwide delivery across the UK, same-day delivery in London, and caters to weddings and events. Their commitment to sustainability is evident in their use of responsibly sourced packaging. With a focus on quality and customer accessibility, Crosstown has established itself as a leading provider of premium desserts in the UK.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/8c64e406-4a63-4cd3-bd6d-00c315b8f125.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', null, null, null), ('2411', 'Ki Hydrogen', 'Ki Hydrogen Ltd', 'https://www.ki-hydrogen.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/ki-hydrogen', 'Ki Hydrogen is a climate technology company based in London, England, that specializes in producing green hydrogen and green chemicals from waste biomass. Founded in December 2022, the company utilizes an innovative biomass electrolysis process that significantly reduces energy consumption, using about 75% less energy than traditional methods. This technology allows for the co-production of green hydrogen and biogenic carbon, providing a sustainable alternative to fossil fuels.The company targets heavy industry, the chemical sector, and e-fuels producers, offering solutions that contribute to decarbonization and sustainability goals. Ki Hydrogen''s approach aligns with global green hydrogen initiatives, leveraging abundant lignocellulosic biomass to meet the growing demand for clean energy. The founding team brings extensive expertise in biomass electrolysis and hydrogen projects, positioning Ki Hydrogen as a key player in the evolving hydrogen market.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/e55a5ac6-3a1c-48a3-86eb-50c5d1fde5f7.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', null, null, null), ('2412', 'Langage Farm Dairy', 'LANGAGE FARM LIMITED LIABILITY PARTNERSHIP', 'https://www.langagefarm.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/langage-farm-dairy', 'Nestled in the rolling hills of Devon, Langage Farm is a proudly independent, family-run dairy with a passion for producing high-quality, award-winning dairy products. With a heritage that blends traditional farming with cutting-edge sustainability, we are a carbon-neutral dairy farm, committed to protecting the environment while delivering exceptional taste.🌱 Sustainability at Our CoreAt Langage Farm, we don''t just talk about sustainability—we live it. Our Anaerobic Digestion (AD) plant converts waste into renewable electricity, helping to power our operations and reduce our carbon footprint. We plant trees, invest in carbon reduction projects, and embrace regenerative farming to ensure that our land remains fertile and healthy for future generations.🥛 Premium Dairy Products, Made with CareWe take pride in producing a delicious range of dairy products made from the finest milk, sourced from our well-cared-for cows. Our range includes:🥄 Clotted Cream – Rich, indulgent, and traditionally crafted, perfect for scones, desserts, and luxurious cooking.🍦 Luxury Ice Cream – Made with real Devon cream for a smooth, velvety texture in a variety of mouth-watering flavours.🍶 Thick & Creamy Yoghurts – Packed with natural goodness, crafted using live cultures for a rich and satisfying taste.🧀 Soft Cheese & Dairy Delights – A selection of high-quality dairy products made with expertise and care.We believe that great dairy starts with great farming—that''s why our cows live stress-free, natural lives, producing high-quality milk with no unnecessary additives.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/ce5238d9-3a65-49a5-8b68-d6a1b85c0d30.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', null, null, null), ('2413', 'Preply', 'Preply UK Services Limited', 'https://preply.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/preply', 'Preply is an online language learning marketplace founded in 2012 by Ukrainian entrepreneurs Kirill Bigai, Dmytro Voloshyn, and Serge Lukyanov. The platform connects learners with tutors worldwide, offering live, one-on-one classes tailored to individual goals and preferences. Preply utilizes a machine-learning-powered recommendation algorithm to match students with the right tutors.The company provides personalized language tutoring across various languages, along with AI-powered tools that enhance the learning experience. These tools include customized resources such as grammar explanations and conversation starters. Preply also offers a corporate language training program, Preply Business, which helps companies improve employees'' language skills and communication. The platform operates globally, with offices in Barcelona, London, New York, and Kyiv, and a diverse team of over 675 employees from more than 50 nationalities.Preply has raised over $144 million in funding, supporting its growth and innovation. The platform is designed to make language education accessible and flexible for both individual learners and businesses.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '35', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/e53a74dd-2613-4b5a-8a2c-0eb676478b63.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', 'ashby', 'https://api.ashbyhq.com/posting-api/job-board/preply', null), ('2414', 'Luscid', 'Luscid Limited', 'https://luscid.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/luscid-platform', 'The world of sports and entertainment is a thrilling one, offering brands the potential to add valuable equity to their marketing output. But the pathway to finding the right matchup has been clouded for far too long. Luscid is here to change this.  Luscid is the most comprehensive sponsorship data platform that maps out the entire sponsorship ecosystem, delivering new levels of insight, accountability, transparency, and efficiency for the sports and entertainment partnerships space.Email: info@luscid.com', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/333c67cf-e5fb-42e7-b4c2-b0bd38ebdf93.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', null, null, null), ('2415', 'Mirion', 'Mirion Technologies (IST) Limited', 'https://www.mirion.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/mirion', 'Mirion is a global leader in radiation safety, science, and medicine, headquartered in Atlanta, Georgia. The company employs around 2,800 people and operates in 12 countries. Mirion focuses on two main segments: the Mirion Technologies Group, which advances nuclear energy and industrial applications through radiation safety technologies, and the Mirion Medical Group, which enhances cancer care quality with medical solutions for radiation therapy and diagnostic imaging.The company''s product portfolio includes radiation detection instruments, nuclear measurement systems, digital integration solutions, and regulatory compliance tools. Mirion has expanded its capabilities through strategic acquisitions, enhancing its offerings in radiation safety and digital technologies. It serves a diverse range of customers, including nuclear power plants, defense organizations, medical institutions, and industrial companies. Mirion also partners with organizations like RAD-AID International to promote radiology and radiation safety education globally. The company has shown strong financial growth, reporting record revenues of $860.8 million for the full year 2024.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '2', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/e0a851d7-1cab-498d-a4d7-dfbf398faad2.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', 'teamtailor', 'mirion', null), ('2416', 'MollerGroup', 'Mollertech Limited', 'https://www.moellergroup.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/moellergroup', 'MöllerGroup GmbH is a family-owned corporate group based in Bielefeld, Germany, with a history dating back to 1730. The company specializes in manufacturing products from plastic, rubber, and metal, catering to various industries such as automotive, mechanical engineering, agriculture, and railways. The group comprises three independent business units: MöllerTech International GmbH, MöllerWerke GmbH, and MöllerFlex GmbH. This structure allows MöllerGroup to provide tailored solutions to meet specific customer needs, leveraging nearly 300 years of combined experience. With operations in 15 locations across five countries and a workforce of around 1,200 employees in Germany and 800 internationally, MöllerGroup achieved sales of approximately 300 million euros in 2024, with a significant portion coming from the automotive sector.MöllerGroup values strong supplier relationships and fosters a corporate culture that prioritizes employee commitment, which it sees as essential to its success. The company is dedicated to delivering high-quality, customized products and services to its diverse customer base worldwide.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/068b4d73-6c8e-44bc-b177-31cbf2b1871d.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', null, null, null), ('2417', 'Norton Folgate Solicitors LLP', 'Norton Folgate Solicitors', 'https://nfs.law', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/norton-folgate-solicitors-llp', 'Norton Folgate Solicitors LLP is a Law Firm that aims to provide professional and comprehensive legal service. As a service provider our accountability lies with our clients, and we are monitored by the Solicitors Regulations Authority.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/c214f8ca-666a-4c18-9428-157b1118417e.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', null, null, null), ('2418', 'OPRE Solutions', 'OPRE Solutions Ltd', 'https://opresolutions.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/opre-solutions', 'OPRE Solutions is a trusted leader in Purpose-Built Student Accommodation (PBSA) and dedicated rental housing, with over six decades of combined expertise in asset management, development, and investment services. We have successfully managed more than 120,000 units worldwide, delivering outstanding results for clients across diverse real estate sectors.Our tailored solutions are designed to maximize portfolio performance through innovative strategies, data-driven insights, and a long-term, sustainable approach. We specialize in creating value across all phases of the real estate lifecycle, from pre-planning and development to operations and asset management.At OPRE Solutions, we combine industry-leading expertise, a commitment to ESG principles, and a proven track record to deliver superior returns for investors while transforming homes, communities, and lives. Partner with us to unlock the full potential of your real estate investments.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/9bea5a67-40c4-42d2-bcfe-627f3a6274ee.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', null, null, null), ('2421', 'Read Roper & Read Solicitors', 'Read Roper and Read Solicitors L', 'https://www.readroper.co.uk', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/read-roper-and-read', 'Read Roper & Read is a boutique property law firm in the centre of Manchester.We are proud of the strong relationships we build with our clients. Some of our clients have been with the firm for over 25 years. We believe that the key to maintaining that close connection is the emphasis which we place on providing, above all else, a service which meets and often surpasses clients'' expectations.  When you work with Read Roper and Read you can be assured of partner-led assistance with the utmost attention to ensure that we provide you with a high quality service.  Whether your requirements are in relation to commercial property, residential property, property finance, property litigation, landlord and tenant or development we look forward to providing you with our expertise to assist you.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/59fdfbd8-b55d-4872-b4a6-a97894022df9.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', null, null, null), ('2422', 'Reborn', 'REBORN GROUP LIMITED', 'https://wearereborn.co.uk', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/reborn-uk', 'We''re a creative digital agency based in Brighton, UK, just an hour’s train ride from central London. Design, Brand, Infographics & Campaigns.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/44d31d53-0754-459c-9685-f05c44ca55bb.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', null, null, null), ('2423', 'Recycling Lives Services', 'Recycling Lives Compliance Services', 'https://recyclinglives-services.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/recycling-lives-services', 'Recycling Lives Services is a UK-based recycling and waste management company dedicated to social sustainability and environmental innovation. As part of the Recycling Lives group, founded by Steven Jackson OBE, the company is headquartered in Preston, Lancashire. It operates as a certified B Corporation, emphasizing a balance between profit and purpose by prioritizing people and the planet.The company offers a wide range of total waste management solutions, including waste electrical and electronic equipment (WEEE) recycling, battery recycling, packaging compliance services, scrap metal recycling, hazardous waste management, skip and container hire, and waste collection and processing. Recycling Lives Services also provides consultancy services to help clients improve their sustainability practices and meet regulatory obligations. With a workforce of over 200 employees and an annual turnover of approximately £25 million, the company serves a diverse client base, including blue-chip businesses and public sector organizations, while actively contributing to social initiatives that support offender rehabilitation and reduce homelessness.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/21772791-860d-4d34-8ba9-89014c198246.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', null, null, null), ('2424', 'Roundabout', 'Roundabout Ltd', 'https://www.roundabouthomeless.org', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/roundabout', 'Roundabout Ltd is a youth housing charity located in Sheffield, South Yorkshire. Established in 1977, the organization is dedicated to ending youth homelessness by providing shelter, support, and life skills to young people aged 16-25 who are homeless or at risk of homelessness. Currently, Roundabout assists over 380 individuals daily, tailoring its services to meet the diverse needs of each young person.The charity offers a variety of services, including an emergency hostel for immediate shelter, a tenancy support service to help young people secure and maintain their own homes, and transitional housing for young offenders. Additionally, Roundabout provides a dispersed service with semi-supported accommodation and a resettlement scheme for those preparing to leave care or custody. Their approach emphasizes individualized support, recognizing the unique challenges faced by many young people, including experiences of childhood trauma. Roundabout aims to provide a safe living environment and the necessary resources to help these young individuals achieve independence and a brighter future.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/1326a2f1-7d95-477c-9116-5cf644cf95dc.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', 'breezy', 'roundabout', null), ('2425', 'SESSÙN', 'Sessun Ltd', 'https://www.sessun.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/sessun', 'Sessùn is a French fashion company founded in the late 1990s by Emma François-Grasset in Marseille. It specializes in women''s clothing, blending artisanal craftsmanship with contemporary design. The brand is known for its commitment to quality and ethical values, employing over 300 creative professionals who foster a collaborative environment. Sessùn emphasizes precision in garment production, using a "made-to-measure" approach that honors textile traditions.The product range features women''s apparel that showcases attention to detail and unique design elements, often incorporating collaborations with skilled artisans. Sessùn has a strong retail presence with nearly 400 points of sale across France and internationally, including its own boutiques and partnerships with major European department stores. The stores reflect the brand''s vision, creating warm atmospheres that celebrate local cultural heritage.As a certified B Corporation since August 2024, Sessùn is dedicated to social and environmental responsibility, focusing on ethical marketing and customer stewardship. The company aims to make a positive social impact through its business practices, appealing to women who appreciate high-quality, thoughtfully designed clothing.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/372662f8-5f0d-4df3-87d6-20f62ec6f28c.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', null, null, null), ('2426', 'UST HealthProof', 'UST Healthproof Holdings (UK) Private Ltd', 'https://usthealthproof.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/usthealthproof', 'UST HealthProof is a healthcare technology company that specializes in Business Process as a Service (BPaaS) solutions. It aims to enhance operational efficiency and reduce administrative complexity for health plans. As the healthcare technology division of UST, a global digital technology provider, UST HealthProof focuses on empowering health plans, including local and community-based organizations, to compete effectively while prioritizing member well-being.The company offers a comprehensive BPaaS platform that addresses core administration and clinical operations across various lines of business, such as Commercial, Medicare Advantage, and Medicaid. Key service areas include core administration, risk adjustment, and quality management, with notable products like the Quality360™ HEDIS® platform, which is NCQA certified. UST HealthProof''s solutions are designed to streamline health plan operations, providing significant operational cost savings and improving member experiences.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/944ba2b8-51f9-448a-8795-2f8a85f9cbb6.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', 'smartrecruiters', 'ust', null), ('2427', 'Wawa Fertility', 'Wawa Fertility Limited', 'https://www.wawafertility.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/wawafertility', 'Wawa Fertility is a healthcare technology company based in Denmark, founded in 2020, with a mission to enhance the fertility treatment experience for patients and clinics. The company offers a comprehensive digital operating system designed specifically for fertility clinics, integrating patient care, clinic workflows, and administrative processes into a single platform. Their platform includes a personalized patient app that supports medical and mental health needs, along with a clinic platform that streamlines patient bookings, scheduling, and invoicing. Wawa Fertility also focuses on simplifying workflows without requiring clinics to change their existing Electronic Medical Records systems. The company plans to expand its services to include data access and patient recruitment for research institutions and pharmaceutical companies.Wawa Fertility operates on a B2C2B model, connecting patients with clinics and generating revenue through subscriptions and referral fees. With plans for growth across multiple countries, the company aims to support 300,000 patients by 2028, reflecting its commitment to improving fertility treatment outcomes worldwide.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/52eccb25-1287-4454-852d-83fd1e6d4533.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', 'bamboohr', 'wawafertility', null), ('2428', 'Wendover Partners', 'Wendover Studio Limited', 'https://wendoverpartners.com/studio/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/wendoverpartners', 'Wendover Partners represents the intersection of design and development. By bringing these complementary industries together under one roof, we are able to source distinctive sites, allow context to define concepts, and design contemporary sites that pay tribute to their environment and history.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/2e19cbd0-ed05-4bf6-a15c-dcd0045a5878.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', null, null, null), ('2429', 'Aspora', 'Real Transfer Limited', 'https://aspora.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/get-aspora', 'Aspora is a London-based global neobank founded in 2022, focusing on digital banking and financial services for the Indian diaspora and other immigrant communities. The company aims to provide a borderless banking experience, allowing users to manage their money internationally through a single account with live exchange rates. Aspora specializes in remittances, enabling non-resident Indians (NRIs) to send money home at lower costs and with greater convenience than traditional banks.The company has seen rapid growth, increasing its remittance volume from $400 million to $2 billion annually. Aspora offers international payments, credit facilities in multiple countries, and investment opportunities that connect users to their home markets. Its fully digitized banking experience simplifies account management and eliminates the need for cumbersome paperwork. Aspora has raised over $99 million in venture capital, including a $50 million Series B round, to support its mission of providing comprehensive banking solutions for the diaspora and expanding its services globally.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '1', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/7397df3f-6263-42df-935f-6157ff3d42c6.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', 'ashby', 'https://api.ashbyhq.com/posting-api/job-board/Aspora', null), ('2430', 'RBC', 'Royal Bank of Canada', 'https://www.rbc.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/rbc', 'Royal Bank of Canada (RBC) is the largest bank in Canada by market capitalization and a prominent financial services provider in North America. Established in 1864 as the Merchants Bank of Halifax, it became the Royal Bank of Canada in 1901 and has since expanded through various mergers and acquisitions. RBC operates in 29 countries, with a strong presence in the US, Caribbean, Europe, and Latin America.RBC offers a wide range of financial services, including personal and commercial banking, wealth management, insurance, and corporate and investment banking. The bank is known for its retail banking services, consumer mortgages, and investment services through subsidiaries like RBC Dominion Securities. RBC has a history of innovation, being the first Canadian bank to engage in radio advertising and sponsoring the Olympics since 1947. With a balanced business model, RBC focuses on risk diversification and serves a diverse clientele across its global operations.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/c73973ab-222f-499b-aab1-15f43267c75f.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', 'breezy', 'rbc', null), ('2431', 'Fero', 'Ferovinum Limited', 'https://www.ferodrinks.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/ferodrinks', 'Fero is a technology-enabled supply chain financing and logistics platform focused on the drinks industry, particularly beer, wine, and spirits. Founded by industry experts, Fero aims to address challenges like slow cash flows and complex logistics through a modern fintech approach. The company has deployed $570 million in capital and facilitated the trading of 57 million bottles across over 30 global markets.Fero''s platform integrates funding, logistics, and operations into a single system, enhancing efficiency for producers, distributors, and retailers. It offers flexible, inventory-based working capital, manages freight and warehousing, and streamlines workflows for sales orders and invoicing. With a user-friendly interface, Fero supports businesses of all sizes, from small craft producers to large operations, enabling them to scale effectively without disrupting existing commercial relationships. The company is trusted by over 600 partners in the drinks sector, fostering innovation and growth within the industry.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '3', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/50e1e07c-9e29-49e2-b4b1-9e43a812de10.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', 'ashby', 'https://api.ashbyhq.com/posting-api/job-board/Ferovinum', null), ('2432', 'Onetrace', 'Onetrace Ltd', 'https://onetrace.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/onetraceapp', 'Onetrace is a technology-focused software company that provides cloud-based solutions for fire protection management and compliance in the construction industry. Its all-in-one platform allows contractors, subcontractors, and fire safety professionals to capture, monitor, review, and report on fire protection work in real time. This ensures data security, regulatory compliance, and operational efficiency.The platform supports the entire lifecycle of fire protection projects by maintaining a digital "golden thread" of information, which is essential for meeting evolving legislation and government directives. Users can access job-related data anytime and anywhere through mobile devices or laptops, facilitating real-time workflow management and communication. Key features include fire protection traceability software, workflow capture and monitoring, customizable reporting, and a strong emphasis on data security and compliance. Onetrace primarily serves subcontractors, contractors, surveyors, and fire safety professionals, helping them streamline operations and maintain high standards in fire safety management.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/0f831940-1cdf-4ea6-a047-bae4cd9fbbb4.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', null, null, null), ('2433', 'Granola', 'Granola Labs', 'https://www.granola.ai/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/meetgranola', 'Granola is an AI-powered notepad designed to enhance the way users capture and utilize meeting notes. It allows users to take notes while automatically transcribing meeting audio in the background, without the need for intrusive bots. After meetings, Granola enriches and organizes the notes, making them comprehensive, searchable, and shareable.The platform features AI transcription and summarization, a live notepad for manual notes, customizable templates for various meeting types, and a searchable archive of conversations. Granola also includes an AI chat feature for exploring notes and automating post-meeting workflows, such as scheduling follow-ups and generating action items. It integrates seamlessly with tools like Slack and Zapier, making it a valuable resource for professionals and teams who participate in frequent meetings. Granola aims to evolve into a proactive AI assistant that helps users act on meeting outcomes efficiently.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '11', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/9ccc259b-8333-4559-8f9a-25c3f22d8ac1.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', 'ashby', 'https://api.ashbyhq.com/posting-api/job-board/granola', null), ('2434', 'Capi Money', 'Capi Money UK Ltd', 'https://capimoney.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/capimoney', 'Capi Money is a fintech company founded in 2023, based in London, that specializes in facilitating international payments for businesses in emerging markets, particularly in Africa. The company offers a platform that allows SMEs and importers to make fast and affordable payments to overseas suppliers in various foreign currencies, including USD, EUR, GBP, and CNY. Capi Money addresses the challenges of high fees and delays associated with traditional banking by providing competitive rates and 24-hour settlements.The platform enables users to upload invoices, send local currency, and track transactions in real-time. Capi Money emphasizes security by holding funds with licensed financial institutions and offers a multilingual interface. The company is expanding its services to markets in Cameroon and Egypt, and it has raised over $18 million from notable investors. Capi Money aims to support businesses facing foreign exchange challenges in high-fee environments, making international trade more accessible and efficient.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '11', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/790ea2d8-2eaf-4d25-8015-42cb4149b76b.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', 'ashby', 'https://api.ashbyhq.com/posting-api/job-board/capimoney', null), ('2435', 'Glyphic', 'Glyphic AI Limited', 'https://www.glyphic.ai/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/glyphic-ai', 'Glyphic is an AI-powered sales copilot platform that enhances sales processes through automation and conversational intelligence. Founded in 2022 by Devang Agrawal and Adam Liska, the company is based in London, England. Glyphic focuses on helping revenue teams optimize their operations, enabling them to execute tasks faster and improve conversion rates.The primary offering, Glyphic AI Co-Pilot, provides sales teams with valuable insights into prospects and strategic guidance. Key features include automated call analysis, CRM data entry, pre-call preparation, and pipeline management. The platform also supports sales playbooks and coaching, helping representatives develop their skills through video simulations. Glyphic integrates seamlessly with CRM systems, particularly HubSpot, and can be customized to fit the specific needs of different sales teams.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/06e5c408-6e7e-40ea-9680-49af3540c49e.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', 'personio', 'glyphic', null), ('2436', 'Searchland', 'Searchland Ltd', 'https://searchland.co.uk/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/searchlandhq', 'Searchland is a UK-based PropTech company founded in 2020, specializing in a SaaS platform designed for sourcing, assessing, and acquiring off-market development sites. The platform integrates property data, mapping tools, and outreach automation to streamline the land sourcing process. Headquartered in London, Searchland has grown rapidly since its launch in 2021, following participation in the Geovation Accelerator Programme.The core platform features intuitive, map-based tools that aggregate various UK datasets for land identification and analysis. Key functionalities include AI-powered sourcing, site assessment tools, and outreach automation, which help users engage directly with landowners. Searchland serves over 1,500 customers, including property developers, architects, planners, and renewable energy firms, providing them with the resources to navigate competitive markets effectively. The company aims to evolve into a comprehensive CRM-like platform for the property sector.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/46a6387c-d781-493b-a98e-f7aca62b68cb.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', null, null, null), ('2437', 'Aethos', 'Aethos U.K. Limited', 'https://www.aethos.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/originalhospitality', 'Aethos is a rapidly growing lifestyle hospitality brand in Europe, known for its boutique hotels, members'' clubs, and wellness-focused properties. With locations in Milan, Ericeira, Monterosa, and Mallorca, Aethos emphasizes nature, community, creativity, and belonging. The brand creates a network for modern living, offering luxury accommodations that blend social, wellness, and work experiences.Aethos properties feature unique designs in natural settings, equipped with amenities such as spas, gyms, pools, and co-working spaces. Guests can enjoy eclectic rooms with private balconies and Mediterranean-inspired dining options. Key offerings include wellness services like spa treatments and fitness classes, diverse dining experiences, and tiered memberships for the members'' club that promote community engagement. Aethos also provides adaptable event spaces for various occasions, enhancing the overall guest experience.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/b82eb209-83cf-4c88-a82f-0e071ca743c7.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', 'lever', 'aethoshotels', null), ('2438', 'Baker Tilly', 'Baker Tilly International Limited', 'https://www.bakertilly.global', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/baker-tilly-international', 'Baker Tilly International is a global network of independent accounting and advisory firms based in London, UK. It ranks as the 9th largest accounting network worldwide, with a revenue of US$5.6 billion in 2024. The network operates through 698 offices in 143 territories, employing over 43,500 people. Baker Tilly emphasizes personalized client relationships and local expertise, supported by a global scale to facilitate business growth and cross-border operations.The firm offers a range of professional services, including advisory, audit and assurance, tax solutions, and legal services. Its advisory services are tailored to meet specific business needs, covering areas such as growth strategies and digital transformation. Baker Tilly also provides specialized support for international market entry and global supply chain management. The firm is recognized for its leadership in the industry, with notable rankings in various categories, including audit and forensic accounting.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/87bbf301-0272-4133-93a1-65c063ef5143.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', 'bamboohr', 'bakertilly', null), ('2439', 'Freeths', 'Freeths LLP', 'https://www.freeths.co.uk', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/freeths-llp', 'Freeths LLP is a prominent full-service commercial law firm based in the UK, with its headquarters in Nottingham and 13 offices nationwide. Established in 1895, the firm has grown significantly through strategic mergers and expansions, becoming one of the top 50 law firms in the UK by revenue, exceeding £145 million in its latest financial year. Freeths is recognized for its commitment to ethics and community support, earning B Corporation certification and various accolades, including Law Firm of the Year 2024 by Legal Business.The firm offers a wide range of legal services across major practice areas, including corporate and commercial law, employment and HR, property and real estate, and dispute resolution. Freeths serves a diverse clientele, including international corporations, public bodies, charities, and high-net-worth individuals. Notable clients include BMW, RBS, and Oxford University Press. The firm is known for its technical excellence and sector-specific expertise, catering to industries such as retail, technology, and life sciences.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '53', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/0b3b847c-7cfb-46df-9dbc-067ce6aacdfb.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', null, null, null), ('2440', 'Ntropy', 'Ntropy Network, Inc', 'https://www.ntropy.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/ntropy', 'Ntropy is a fintech company founded in 2019, co-founded by CEO Naré Vardanyan and CTO Ilia Zintchenko. The company offers a developer-first API platform focused on financial data standardization, enrichment, and intelligence. Utilizing in-house machine learning and large language models, Ntropy processes transaction data accurately across various sources, formats, and languages. The company is headquartered in San Francisco, California.Ntropy''s main product is a highly accurate financial data standardization and enrichment API. This API analyzes transaction data for context in milliseconds, aiding in credit scoring, loan agreements, and other financial decisions. Additionally, Ntropy AI is a newly launched platform that orchestrates large language models for finance, capable of processing up to 100 million transactions daily with low latency. The platform is designed to be scalable and privacy-compliant, addressing challenges posed by legacy payment systems. Ntropy serves enterprises in financial services and has garnered interest from multiple fintech companies.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/ee6a4110-6321-4daa-8045-73832e7e3172.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', null, null, null), ('2441', 'CloudBees', 'CloudBees UK Limited', 'https://www.cloudbees.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/cloudbees', 'CloudBees is an enterprise software delivery company founded in 2010, specializing in DevOps, CI/CD, and DevSecOps platforms. Headquartered in San Jose, California, with additional offices in several locations including Raleigh, Berlin, and London, CloudBees focuses on enabling secure and scalable software delivery for large organizations. The company has raised over $250 million in funding and serves more than 500,000 developers across major global enterprises.CloudBees offers a comprehensive suite of solutions that optimize the full DevSecOps lifecycle. Key products include CloudBees CI, the leading enterprise Jenkins platform, and the CloudBees Platform, a SaaS DevSecOps solution. Their offerings also encompass Release Orchestration, Feature Management, AI-driven Smart Tests, and Compliance tools. These solutions automate pipelines, integrate AI for efficiency, and support hybrid deployments, allowing developers to concentrate on innovation. CloudBees has established a strong presence in various sectors, including finance, technology, and healthcare, serving notable clients such as Salesforce, Adobe, and the US Internal Revenue Service.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/90b572bf-0889-45ac-b7cf-6df5fc6ada66.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', 'bamboohr', 'cloudbees', null), ('2442', 'ICG', 'ICG PLC', 'https://www.icgam.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/icg-plc', 'ICG plc is a global alternative asset manager established in 1989, with a focus on flexible investment solutions across various sectors, including private equity, debt, secondaries, structured capital, credit, and real assets. As of September 30, 2025, ICG manages total assets of $124 billion and operates from 21 locations worldwide, including major cities like New York, Toronto, and Dubai.The company partners with management teams, business owners, and investors to identify unique opportunities and deliver long-term value. ICG''s investment strategies include structured capital for mid-market companies, private equity secondaries for liquidity solutions, and investments in real estate and infrastructure. The firm emphasizes sustainability and responsible investing, maintaining a strong track record of returns for its stakeholders. With a dedicated workforce of approximately 686 to 812 employees, ICG continues to expand its global presence and client base, serving a diverse range of institutional investors.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '4', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/156bfcc8-fb67-4227-b1a4-b6f6472ee50e.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', 'workday', 'external_careers', null), ('2443', 'NTS Radio', 'NTS LIVE LTD', 'https://www.nts.live', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/nts-live-ltd', 'NTS Radio is a global online radio platform and music discovery service that broadcasts diverse music 24/7 from over 50 cities worldwide. Founded in 2011 by Femi Adeyemi and Sean McAuliffe, NTS aims to provide an alternative to mainstream radio by showcasing underground music, art, and fashion. The platform has evolved from a local community station in London to a global community radio service, featuring over 130 shows and custom-built streaming infrastructure.NTS offers live radio broadcasting with narrative-driven programming that highlights a wide range of genres, including jazz, rap, and j-pop. It also provides a music discovery archive that celebrates global sounds, free from traditional radio constraints. In addition to its online presence, NTS hosts international live events and creates original video content to engage listeners. The platform emphasizes high-quality access and consistency across its offerings, ensuring a unique listening experience.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/20086434-d164-47ce-8878-8838d8a1260a.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', null, null, null), ('2444', 'OrganOx', 'OrganOx Limited', 'https://www.organox.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/organox', 'OrganOx is a medical technology company focused on advanced organ preservation devices. Founded in 2008 as a spin-out from the University of Oxford, it was established by engineering professor Constantin Coussios and transplant surgery professor Peter Friend. In 2025, OrganOx became a wholly owned subsidiary of Terumo Corporation following a significant acquisition.The company is dedicated to improving outcomes for patients with organ failure. Its core mission is to enhance the availability of donor organs, addressing the critical need for transplants. OrganOx specializes in Normothermic Machine Perfusion (NMP) technology, with its flagship product, metra, being a liver NMP device. This device circulates warm, oxygenated fluid through the organ, allowing real-time assessment of organ function. It received FDA approval in 2021 and has been used in over 6,000 liver transplant procedures globally. OrganOx is also developing a kidney NMP device, with plans for commercialization around 2030.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/7ad2f3d0-190e-41f0-a4fd-7d927a1fd3b0.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', 'workable', 'organox', null), ('2445', 'ViroCell Biologics', 'ViroCell Holdings Limited', 'https://www.virocell.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/virocell-biologics', 'ViroCell Biologics is a contract development and manufacturing organization (CDMO) that specializes in the design, optimization, and GMP manufacturing of lentiviral and retroviral vectors for cell and gene therapies. Founded in 2020 in the UK, ViroCell combines a highly experienced team with a focus on collaboration to support early-stage programs from biotechs, universities, and not-for-profits.The company offers a comprehensive service platform that includes innovation research, viral vector design and optimization, process development, and GMP manufacturing. ViroCell is dedicated to delivering GMP-grade vectors tailored for clinical trials, with a streamlined process that typically results in GMP release within six months. Their work emphasizes scientific integrity and scalability, ensuring that therapies can advance efficiently from the lab to clinical settings.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/91d0f0ac-8706-4430-9a1b-432fc1f778bf.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', null, null, null), ('2446', 'Overmind', 'Overmind', 'https://overmindlab.ai', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/over-mind-ai', 'AI is changing the world, we are making sure it changes it for the better.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/5738c4c4-5afb-470c-9449-a61fc9a738e1.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', 'lever', 'overmind', null), ('2447', 'Meticulous', 'Meticulous Ai Limited', 'https://www.meticulous.ai/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/alwaysmeticulous', 'Meticulous is an automated frontend testing platform based in San Francisco, California, with a registered office in London, England. Founded in 2021 and backed by Y Combinator, the company has around 5 employees. Meticulous specializes in generating and maintaining visual end-to-end tests using AI, eliminating the need for developers to write or manage test code manually.The platform operates through a three-step process: record, simulate, and test. It records user sessions from applications and replays them against new code versions, quickly delivering results. Key features include AI-generated test suites that cover all code branches and user flows, an augmented Chromium browser for efficient session replay, and automatic network mocking for side-effect-free tests. Meticulous''s solution integrates seamlessly with CI/CD pipelines, allowing for continuous testing with minimal setup. The company is dedicated to enhancing the software development process for front-end developers by providing tools that support robust and reliable software creation.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '4', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/249b5ba5-b3e0-4215-8670-972292ac7008.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', 'ashby', 'https://api.ashbyhq.com/posting-api/job-board/meticulous', null), ('2448', 'Joy', 'Pungo Ltd', 'https://www.thejoyapp.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/joyuk', 'Joy is a UK-based health technology company that offers a digital social prescribing platform. This platform connects individuals to local non-clinical community services, measures health outcomes, and supports preventative care to improve social health. Joy aims to enhance life expectancy by addressing social determinants of health, such as social connections and barriers to accessing care.The platform features a case management system for social prescribers, an AI-powered directory of services, real-time outcome tracking, and client communication tools. It integrates with various NHS and social care systems, streamlining the referral process and improving attendance rates. Joy is used by over 19.2 million patients and is adopted by 30% of Primary Care Networks in the UK, collaborating with local authorities and community organizations to promote holistic care and reduce health inequalities. The company is committed to safety and privacy, holding ISO/IEC 27001 certification.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/a3940532-8d5c-4cbb-a1d1-41d15bfd96ad.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', 'breezy', 'joy', null), ('2449', 'YLookup', 'Asymptote Labs', 'https://www.ylookup.ai', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/ylookup', 'We''re building YLookup. The first agentic, Excel-native workflow engine for accountants. Today, accountants lose up to three hours a day in spreadsheets instead of serving clients. Excel is powerful but archaic, lacking automation, error detection, and process control. YLookup upgrades Excel into an intelligent workspace that automates the core workflows and eliminates mistakes. Our mission: give accountants their time back to focus on higher-value work.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/c5d00c7d-2254-443f-888d-8e91aadbf333.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', null, null, null), ('2450', 'Cecil', 'Cecil Earth UK Ltd', 'https://cecil.earth', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/cecil-earth', 'Cecil is a nature data platform that focuses on curating, standardizing, and delivering high-quality geospatial datasets. It applies scientific principles to ensure that these datasets are consistent and ready for objective analysis of natural environments. The platform is built on a repeatable and scalable operating model developed in collaboration with the research community.Cecil emphasizes transparency by documenting dataset protocols, methods, and specifications. It also features seamless integration with existing tools and workflows, supporting preferred geospatial libraries for easy connectivity. This makes it easier for users to incorporate high-quality nature data into their analyses.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/402ebfc8-bef5-42de-8ee5-f76fa29d2c33.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', null, null, null), ('2451', 'ClearBank', 'ClearBank Group Holdings Limited', 'https://clear.bank', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/clear-bank', 'ClearBank is the first new full-service clearing bank in the UK in over 250 years, launched in 2017. Founded by Nick Ogden in 2015, it operates as a cloud-native, technology-driven bank that integrates directly with the UK''s banking and payment infrastructure. ClearBank aims to modernize the clearing banking sector by providing a suite of embedded banking and payment infrastructure services through its fully regulated, API-based platform.The bank offers real-time payments, FSCS-protected accounts for institutional clients, and embedded banking services that allow partners to provide banking products. ClearBank serves over 250 institutional clients, including fintechs, banks, and regulated financial institutions. Its cloud-native technology ensures instantaneous payment processing and scalability for global expansion. Recognized as one of the UK''s fastest-growing technology firms, ClearBank is committed to delivering innovative banking services while maintaining strong compliance standards.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '16', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/3eccee75-74f6-4d8f-a9f0-6d7d0aaa33b1.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', 'ashby', 'clearbank', null), ('2452', 'Flagship Pioneering', 'Flagship Pioneering UK Limited', 'https://www.flagshippioneering.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/flagship-pioneering', 'Flagship Pioneering is a venture capital firm and company incubator based in Cambridge, Massachusetts, founded in 2000 by Noubar Afeyan. The firm focuses on inventing, building, and funding first-in-category bioplatform companies in biotechnology, life sciences, health, and sustainability. With a mission to drive innovation through scientific creativity, Flagship has launched over 140 companies and manages substantial capital, including a recent $3.4 billion fund.The firm operates through a unique model that combines pioneering ideas with systematic entrepreneurship. It emphasizes hypothesis-driven innovation and builds enduring value through patentable platforms. Flagship invests in various sectors, including therapeutics, health technologies, and clean tech, often collaborating on initiatives like Pioneering Medicines with Pfizer. Notable successes include companies like Moderna and Sana Biotechnology, which have made significant impacts in their fields. Flagship Pioneering is committed to harnessing technology for a healthier and more sustainable future.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/a48a7e71-9ab9-4c7d-87c5-42106d8f18fc.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', 'bamboohr', 'flagship', null), ('2453', 'Forsters LLP', 'Forsters LLP', 'https://www.forsters.co.uk', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/forsters', 'Forsters LLP is a prominent law firm based in London, specializing in private client and real estate services. Founded in 2003, the firm has grown to employ between 501 and 1000 professionals. Forsters is dedicated to building long-term relationships with clients, offering tailored legal advice through collaborative, partner-led teams. The firm focuses on understanding clients'' needs to deliver effective solutions in wealth management, asset protection, business development, and dispute resolution.The firm provides a wide range of legal services, including estate planning and high-net-worth matters in its private client department, as well as commercial and residential property transactions in real estate. Forsters also supports corporate clients in business transactions and handles complex disputes. With a commitment to client satisfaction and community impact, Forsters has received several accolades, including Solicitors Firm of the Year and recognition in the Chambers High Net Worth Guide.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/aeae8e44-3e22-4a10-ac41-5804d70c4889.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', null, null, null), ('2454', 'Haiilo', 'Haiilo Limited', 'https://www.haiilo.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/haiilo', 'Haiilo is an employee experience platform that connects employees with their organizations through content, community, and communication. Founded in 2022 from the merger of COYO, Smarp, and Jubiwee, the company is headquartered in Hamburg, Germany, and operates five global offices with a diverse team.The platform features four main products: Haiilo Home, Haiilo Stories, Haiilo Share, and Haiilo Insights. These tools support multichannel communication, modern intranet functionality, employee advocacy, and engagement surveys. Key offerings include an AI-powered Content Studio for content management, a central hub for knowledge sharing, and mobile apps for easy access. Haiilo serves various industries, including healthcare, automotive, and education, and has over 1,000 customers with a strong focus on user engagement and retention.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/386a0738-4be2-46e6-ae3a-24075ca7c2e5.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', null, null, null), ('2455', 'PAYSTRAX', 'Paystrax Ltd', 'https://paystrax.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/paystrax', 'PAYSTRAX is a Financial Technology company that provides electronic transaction solutions for merchants in Europe and the UK. Established in 2018, it began offering acquiring services in 2021 and has quickly become a competitive player in the payments industry. The company operates from four international offices in Vilnius, Klaipėda, Reykjavik, and Brighton, employing over 100 specialists and serving more than 500 merchants across the EEA and UK.PAYSTRAX is a licensed payment institution in Lithuania and the UK, regulated by the Bank of Lithuania and the FCA. It is a Principal Member of Mastercard and VISA, which enhances its role in the payments ecosystem. The company offers a range of services, including multi-channel payment acceptance, multi-currency settlement, fraud management, and a payment orchestration platform. PAYSTRAX focuses on delivering a strong customer experience through strategic partnerships and a commitment to adapting to client needs.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/2f2448f0-c678-4eda-9a3a-f0388aced523.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', null, null, null), ('2456', 'Sabe Fluid Dynamics', 'Sabe Technology Limited', 'https://sabe.tech', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/sabe-fluiddynamics', 'Sabe Fluid Dynamics, operating as Sabe Technology Ltd, is a UK-based consultancy founded in July 2019 by Gerson Garsed-Brand. The company specializes in thermal and fluid dynamics, with a strong focus on computational fluid dynamics (CFD), aerodynamics, and hydrodynamics. Headquartered in Silverstone Park, Northamptonshire, Sabe provides turn-key aerodynamic support, enhancing clients'' engineering teams from initial analysis through development to final sign-off.Sabe offers a range of services, including aerodynamics and CFD analysis for race car development, thermal and fluid dynamics simulations, and technology development across various sectors such as aerospace, automotive, and energy. The company emphasizes sustainability and collaborative partnerships, working closely with clients to improve processes and efficiency. With a team that includes experts with extensive experience in motorsport and engineering, Sabe is committed to delivering high-quality consultancy services tailored to meet specific client needs.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/a8a41580-16a9-4017-8df7-54d099e6ca4c.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', null, null, null), ('2457', 'Searchable', 'Searchable Ltd', 'https://www.searchable.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/trysearchable', 'Searchable Limited, founded in 2025, specializes in helping marketing teams optimize for the "agentic web" through its expertise in SEO and Answer Engine Optimization (AEO). The company is co-founded by Chris Donnelly, a seasoned entrepreneur known for scaling successful businesses. Searchable focuses on capital-efficient operations and growth through established playbooks.The company offers a platform featuring a comprehensive scoring system that evaluates site optimization across various metrics, including Technical Score, Content Score, and AEO Score. It also provides guides for getting products listed in ChatGPT Shopping, detailing steps for optimizing product feeds and enhancing visibility in AI-driven searches. Searchable maintains an AI Usage Policy that emphasizes editorial standards and guidelines for generative AI use.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '12', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/222bcbda-ee47-4fb5-ba4a-70530da2e528.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', null, null, null), ('2458', 'Statuo', 'Statuo Ltd', 'https://statuo.co.uk', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/statuo', 'We are Statuo, an independent agency specialising in Brand, Web & Marketing.We''re a team of Designers, Developers, Marketers and Strategists with the skills & passion to turn your ideas into phenomenal results. Based in a brand new refurbished farmhouse in Bolton (just outside of Manchester ) We''ve created a studio which is spacious, fun, flexible and packed full of creative ideas, and the latest technology to implement them.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/acee49f6-5c22-4e68-9344-6bda62869b5b.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', null, null, null), ('2459', 'Weco AI', 'Weco AI Ltd', 'https://www.weco.ai', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/weco-ai', 'AI Assistant for Machine Learning', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/0fa6e919-23f0-4ee7-bdc5-427ae63e31b3.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', 'breezy', 'weco', null), ('2460', 'Zeta Global', 'Zeta Global Ltd', 'https://zetaglobal.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/zetaglobal', 'Zeta Global is an AI-powered marketing cloud platform founded in 2007 by David A. Steinberg and John Sculley. Headquartered in New York City, the company is publicly traded on the New York Stock Exchange under the ticker symbol ZETA. With a workforce of over 1,700 employees, Zeta is recognized as a leading provider of omnichannel data-driven marketing technology.The Zeta Marketing Platform (ZMP) is the core of Zeta''s offerings. It integrates identity, intelligence, and omnichannel activation into a unified solution, leveraging advanced AI and extensive consumer data. The platform supports personalized marketing across various channels, including email, social media, and connected TV, enabling enterprises to effectively acquire, grow, and retain customers. Zeta serves over 450 enterprise customers, including nearly half of the Fortune 100 companies, and has a global presence with offices in multiple cities worldwide.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '1', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/1fb378bb-2cb9-4790-b9d5-18fc6a6f3a29.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', null, null, null), ('2461', 'Aerogel Core Ltd', 'AEROGEL CORE LIMITED', 'https://grafaero.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/aerogel-core-ltd', 'Aerogel Core Ltd is a UK-based manufacturer specializing in ultra-lightweight, graphene-based aerogel materials. Founded in 2022 as a spin-out from the University of Bath, the company focuses on creating next-generation structures for aerospace, automotive, and marine applications. It combines expertise in material science with innovative research to develop products that enhance performance while reducing environmental impact.The company designs and manufactures a range of graphene-based structures, including foils, aerogels, prepregs, and metamaterial-based products. These materials are engineered for applications such as acoustic management, thermal management, and weight reduction, offering significant advantages like reduced density and lower carbon emissions. Aerogel Core Ltd aims to automate its manufacturing processes to scale production and meet the growing demands of its target markets, particularly in aerospace and automotive sectors.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/84923db9-ee6e-406e-9440-ae3fb6f0a3d8.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', null, null, null), ('2462', 'Barron McCann', 'Barron McCann Limited', 'https://barronmccann.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/barronmccann', 'Barron McCann (BMc) is a technology company that specializes in field services engineering and IT solutions for distributed markets. Founded in 1977 and headquartered in Derby, UK, the company has over 46 years of experience serving various sectors, including retail, hospitality, leisure, government, and corporate clients. With a workforce of 295 employees, Barron McCann reported a turnover of £29.3 million and net assets of £18.4 million as of March 2024.The company offers a wide range of services, including field services engineering, IT maintenance, installation and deployment of IT technology, digital signage, fraud prevention solutions, and electric vehicle charging infrastructure. Barron McCann is committed to service excellence and operates with a customer-centric approach, ensuring consistent support throughout the service lifecycle. In 2024, the company expanded its capabilities by welcoming Retail Assist and establishing an Innovation Hub to enhance service development.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/ac1afaa6-e409-4418-8675-5fcc21d8bd19.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', 'smartrecruiters', 'barronmccann', null), ('2463', 'Bud Systems', 'Bud Systems Ltd', 'https://bud.co.uk', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/budsystemslimited', 'Bud Systems is a UK-based software development company that specializes in enhancing the delivery of apprenticeships and vocational training. Founded in 2016 and located in Bristol, the company leverages 30 years of apprenticeship expertise alongside software development skills. With a team of approximately 60-71 employees, Bud Systems generates $15.2 million in revenue.The Bud platform is an integrated apprenticeship management system that focuses on three main areas: learning, managing, and compliance and administration. It maximizes learner engagement with accessible learning plans, drives consistency through unique workflows, and simplifies evidence capture to ensure regulatory compliance. Initially designed for the Apprenticeship Levy, the platform has been adapted to support various training courses funded by different educational budgets.Bud Systems serves independent training providers, universities, colleges, and employers, helping them deliver effective apprenticeships and skills training. Customers have reported benefits such as reduced administrative tasks, improved compliance, and enhanced operational efficiency.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/99fa6baf-fc2f-4ed1-afeb-0a700e3a6d87.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', 'bamboohr', 'bud', null), ('2464', 'BXR Group', 'BXR Advisory Partners LLP', 'https://bxrgroup.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/bxr-partners-llp', 'BXR Advisory Partners is an investment advisor to BXR Group, primarily responsible for:identifying suitable investment opportunities;structuring and executing acquisitions disposals and financings; andproviding strategic guidance and financial expertise to portfolio companies.BXR Advisory Partners comprises advisory entities with offices in London and Budapest, and an affiliated office in Singapore.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/2b9af282-c6e1-4f6e-b701-2a0425875271.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', null, null, null), ('2465', 'Convex Energy', 'Convex Energy Limited', 'https://www.convex-energy.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/convexenergy', 'Convex Energy is an energy trading house based in Berlin, founded in 2017. The company combines skilled traders with advanced technology to operate in European commodities markets. With a team of 51-200 employees, including traders, data scientists, and software developers, Convex Energy promotes a collaborative culture that values creativity and transparency.The company employs a unique dual setup where traders and developers work together to create value. Convex Energy has been profitable since its inception and trades across three locations. Its operations include processing vast amounts of data for quick trading decisions, developing proprietary trading models, and utilizing advanced technology for executing trades. Additionally, Convex Energy offers educational resources on various energy trading topics, enhancing knowledge in areas such as power trading and market operations.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/4f2afbcd-27ac-4d2a-a133-4db8957d53c7.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', null, null, null), ('2466', 'Midnite', 'Dribble Media Limited', 'https://www.midnite.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/midnite', 'Midnite is a UK-based online gambling platform founded in 2018 by Nick Wright and Daniel Qu. It specializes in sports betting, with a strong emphasis on esports and traditional sports, as well as casino games and horse racing. The company aims to attract digitally native, younger users by offering a modern app experience that competes with established brands in the industry.The platform features a sportsbook as its core offering, which has expanded into a comprehensive betting service. Midnite''s team includes engineers, quants, designers, and marketers who are passionate about esports, sports, and gaming. The company focuses on seamless onboarding and has partnered with GBG for identity verification, enhancing player pass rates and driving revenue growth. Midnite is currently in a growth phase, working towards becoming a leading gambling brand.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '6', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/866aab61-d0ca-4f43-8aa5-d8cb291f8698.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', 'workable', 'midnite', null), ('2467', 'Independence Products', 'Independence Products Ltd', 'https://ipl.uk.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/independence-products-ltd', 'At Independence Products Ltd, we specialise in supporting people with long-term health needs by designing and delivering innovative solutions that promote safe, dignified, and independent living.We offer a unique all-in-one service focused on improving vascular access line care for individuals living with chronic conditions. Our tailored range of products and support is specifically developed to meet the needs of those with PICC, Hickman, and central venous (CVC) lines. By streamlining line care and offering practical tools that support both patients and clinicians, we help reduce infection risk, improve comfort, and enhance overall quality of life.Our team works in close collaboration with healthcare professionals and end users to ensure every product is effective, intuitive, and grounded in real-world use. From product development through to education and distribution, our integrated approach ensures better continuity of care and better patient outcomes.At Independence Products Ltd, everything we do is guided by one purpose: Empowering Independence.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/7301a0db-2db4-416e-8eaa-cd9437cbd06b.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', null, null, null), ('2468', 'NLPatent', 'Legalicity (UK Operations) Ltd T/A NLPatent', 'https://www.nlpatent.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/nlpatent', 'NLPatent is an AI-powered platform designed for patent research and intelligence, catering to IP professionals, R&D teams, and legal experts. Founded by IP attorney Stephanie and engineer James, the platform utilizes advanced AI techniques, including natural language processing and machine learning, to enhance patent searches and analysis. It enables users to conduct searches 5-10 times faster than traditional methods, addressing inefficiencies in outdated tools.The core offerings of NLPatent include modules for searching and analyzing patents, monitoring technologies and competitors, and visualizing portfolio insights. Users can perform assessments for patentability, invalidity, and infringement risks, among other tasks. The platform features customizable alerts, detailed reporting, and real-time AI analysis, ensuring users can refine their searches effectively. NLPatent is trusted by Fortune 500 companies, Am Law 100 firms, and research universities, with users highlighting its speed and precision in various patent workflows.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '1', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/1f96986e-23c7-478a-a8e5-72bfaef1a771.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', null, null, null), ('2469', 'Metris Energy', 'Metris Energy Ltd', 'https://www.metrisenergy.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/metrisenergy', 'Metris Energy AI is an AI-powered workspace platform tailored for asset managers in the renewable energy sector. It aims to enhance productivity and streamline daily operations by integrating various functionalities into a single solution for managing renewable energy projects, including solar.The platform features a centralized project database and document management system, allowing users to quickly access key information through AI-powered search capabilities. Metris also offers SLA tracking and KPI monitoring, converting static agreements into live performance indicators. Additional services include automated billing for Power Purchase Agreements, smart ticketing for fault detection, and an AI-powered scheduling assistant that facilitates seamless project management. Users can automate workflows and generate reports effortlessly, making project commissioning faster and more efficient.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/36fdbc56-ddc5-4e8d-9cf1-23ddbd252405.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', null, null, null), ('2470', 'Ringover', 'Ringover Ltd', 'https://www.ringover.co.uk/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/ringover-uk', 'Ringover is the go-to cloud phone system platform for UK staffing, recruitment and revenue-first teams. It''s built to help you call, message, track, and analyse every candidate and client conversation, without the extra admin.We combine AI-powered insights, omnichannel communication, and seamless integrations to help recruiters work smarter, not harder.Our platform helps you:• Improve placement rates by reaching the right candidates faster with intelligent communication tools• Boost recruiter productivity with automation, smart workflows, and native ATS syncing• Scale your agency with full visibility into team performance and client engagementWith 15+ global data centres and over 14,000 customers worldwide, our London-based team is here to help you optimise your tech stack and grow your recruitment business.🔗 Learn more at ringover.co.uk', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/0b6e9084-b31d-4fad-a245-681492f8aa02.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', null, null, null), ('2471', 'Standing on Giants', 'Standing on Giants Ltd.', 'https://www.standingongiants.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/standing-on-giants', 'Standing on Giants is a London-based agency founded in 2012 by Robbie Hearn and Vincent Boon. The agency specializes in building, managing, and scaling brand-owned online communities for global businesses. It emerged from the founders'' experience at giffgaff, where they developed a community-driven business model. Standing on Giants is recognized as the world''s first agency dedicated to this purpose and became a Certified B Corporation in August 2020, highlighting its commitment to creating positive impacts for people and the planet.The agency offers a comprehensive "Complete Community Solution" that includes expert consultancy, outsourced community management, and a custom platform designed for community engagement. With a global team from over 14 countries, Standing on Giants has successfully managed communities with over 1 million members and has collaborated with major brands like Airbnb, Google, and Heineken. The company emphasizes employee wellbeing and sustainability, operating as a 100% employee-owned entity since June 2025.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/2999b351-a20d-462b-913a-293c2f7eeca4.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', null, null, null), ('2472', 'The Place To Be', 'The Place To Be', 'https://www.theplacetobeagency.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/theplacetobeagency', 'The Place To Be Agency Limited is a recruitment agency based in Leeds, specializing in placing talent within marketing, digital, and creative teams across UK agencies. Founded in 2021, the agency focuses on high-quality, culture-driven recruitment services. It aims to build strong relationships with clients and candidates, ensuring successful job placements that align with the culture of both parties.The agency offers specialized recruitment services for senior roles in the creative sector, including digital, PR, social, content, and technical marketing positions. Their key offerings include exclusive search services, culture-matching to enhance recruitment processes, and a focus on senior hires. The team consists of specialists with extensive experience in agency life, ensuring a deep understanding of the needs of both clients and candidates.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/f1e5d844-920a-42ae-87ea-f7d2c9edb93f.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', null, null, null), ('2473', 'Titania', 'Titania Limited', 'https://www.titania.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/titania-ltd', 'Titania Ltd is a UK-based cybersecurity company founded in 2009 and headquartered in Worcester. The company specializes in proactive network security software focused on auditing, vulnerability management, and compliance assurance for network infrastructure, including routers, switches, and firewalls. Titania has developed solutions that enhance network readiness, recoverability, and resilience, transitioning clients from risk-based vulnerability management to continuous threat exposure management.Titania''s software offers accurate vulnerability detection, automated compliance reporting, and risk-prioritized views of non-compliance. Key features include continuous analysis of configuration changes, up-to-date configuration repositories for disaster recovery, and proactive attack surface monitoring. The company supports scalable deployment options and integrates with various tools to enhance operational readiness. Titania is trusted by over 30 US federal agencies, the US Department of Defense, and various global organizations across sectors such as finance, retail, and utilities, contributing to improved network security in critical environments.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/fc973ae4-ec13-4ec0-a7e2-8097a006b812.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', 'teamtailor', 'titania', null), ('2476', 'Relm Insurance', 'RELM INS UK LTD', 'https://relminsurance.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/relm-insurance-ltd', 'Relm Insurance is a Bermuda-based specialty insurance carrier founded in 2019. The company focuses on providing tailored insurance solutions for emerging industries such as digital assets, Web3, AI, fintech, biotech, alternative medicine, and the space economy. Relm obtained its general business license from the Bermuda Monetary Authority and became the first commercial insurer in Bermuda to secure Innovative Insurer – General Business authorization.Relm designs industry-specific insurance products to address unique risks in these sectors. Their offerings include a dedicated product suite for Web3 and digital assets, extended cyber technology coverage, and new products for the space economy. The company emphasizes financial strength and responsible growth, maintaining an exceptional Financial Stability Rating from Demotech. In 2024, Relm expanded its operations with a Managing General Agent in the US and opened an office in London, further enhancing its reach in innovative markets.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/721a307e-6673-43e3-8531-ffb0877fe569.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', 'greenhouse', 'relminsuranceukltd', null), ('2477', 'Braingaze', 'Braingaze Ltd', 'https://braingaze.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/braingaze', 'Braingaze is a technology-driven healthcare company focused on the early detection, diagnosis, treatment, and monitoring of neurodevelopmental and neurocognitive disorders, including ADHD, Autism Spectrum Disorder (ASD), Dyslexia, and cognitive diseases like Alzheimer’s. Founded in 2013 as a spin-off from the University of Barcelona, Braingaze is headquartered in Mataró, Spain, with an office in Surrey, UK. The company employs fewer than 25 people and has reported approximately $5.4 million in revenue.Braingaze offers two main products that utilize patented eye-tracking technology. The BGaze Clinic is a diagnostic support system that assesses attention through computerized games, providing ADHD probability and severity scores with over 90% accuracy. The BGaze Focus is a suite of mobile-friendly, gaze-controlled games designed for therapeutic relief in ADHD, ASD, and Dyslexia. Braingaze is also working on early detection methods for Autism Spectrum Disorder and Alzheimer’s, along with gamified digital treatments to enhance cognitive health. The company holds worldwide patents and complies with various medical standards, ensuring its solutions are both effective and reliable.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/0664fc5e-1193-4cc1-a047-5130dda288f3.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', null, null, null), ('2478', 'Everllence', 'Everllence UK Limited', 'https://www.everllence.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/everllence', 'Everllence SE is a German engineering company based in Augsburg, focusing on propulsion, decarbonization, and efficiency solutions for shipping, energy, and industry. The company aims to reduce hard-to-abate emissions under the motto "Moving big things to zero." With a history of 260 years in industrial innovation, Everllence was formerly known as MAN Energy Solutions and rebranded in 2025. It is wholly owned by the Volkswagen Group and employs around 15,000 people across more than 140 locations worldwide.Everllence develops a wide range of advanced engineering solutions, including diesel and gas engines, turbomachinery, and decarbonization technologies. Their offerings also include hydrogen production systems and after-sales services. The company reported sales of approximately 4.3 billion euros in 2024 and aims for over 50% of its business to consist of sustainable technologies by 2030. Everllence has received recognition for its sustainability efforts, including the 16th National German Sustainability Award in 2023.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/7422cb72-8975-4b6a-916a-dd3ec47e3045.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', null, null, null), ('2479', 'FlixBus', 'Flixbus UK Limited', 'https://www.flixbus.co.uk', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/flixbus', 'Flix, operating as FlixBus and under the parent company FlixMobility, is a global travel-tech company founded in 2013 in Munich, Germany. It specializes in sustainable and affordable long-distance bus and train services across more than 40 countries on five continents. Flix utilizes an asset-light business model, partnering with regional small and medium enterprises to manage fleets and services, while focusing on technology, network planning, and operations.The company offers extensive route networks connecting thousands of cities, with both day and night services available. Its innovative tech platform and mobile app facilitate booking, real-time tracking, and personalized travel experiences. Flix emphasizes sustainability through features like CO2 offset options and modern green fleets. With over 500 million travelers served and 350,000 daily connections to more than 2,000 destinations, Flix is committed to providing budget-conscious travelers with eco-friendly travel alternatives.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/b703fcc0-f69c-41b1-88c0-a416032d33ac.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', null, null, null), ('2480', 'LLC Global', 'LONDON LUXURY CHAUFFEURING LTD', 'https://www.llccars.co.uk/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/london-luxury-chauffeuring', 'London Luxury Chauffeuring offers a premier chauffeur service tailored to meet the needs of executives, VIPs, and discerning clients. With a fleet of world-class vehicles, we ensure every journey is an experience in comfort, style, and safety. Whether for airport transfers, corporate events, or special occasions, our professional chauffeurs provide seamless service across London and beyond. Experience luxury at its finest with London Luxury Chauffeuring—where elegance meets precision.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/8bbc3725-fb84-402a-b3f8-d9db668b0f23.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', 'smartrecruiters', 'llc', null), ('2483', 'Redgrave', 'Redgrave Search Ltd', 'https://redgravesearch.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/redgrave-search', 'Redgrave LLP is a law firm established in August 2010, specializing in legal issues at the intersection of law and technology. The firm focuses on areas such as eDiscovery, information governance, data privacy, data security, AI governance, and cybersecurity. Redgrave LLP provides innovative and cost-effective legal solutions to corporations, individuals, and Am Law 100 law firms, with attorneys practicing in state and federal courts across the United States. The firm serves a diverse range of industries, including healthcare, technology, insurance, and retail.The firm offers a wide array of services that combine legal expertise with technology and business insights. These include eDiscovery and litigation support, information governance, data privacy and security consulting, and advanced technology solutions like AI and machine learning. Redgrave LLP emphasizes a collaborative approach, focusing on thought leadership and the validation of new technologies to meet client needs during crises, investigations, and compliance challenges.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/b918c534-9c3a-436b-be93-6afb213b35f3.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', null, null, null), ('2484', 'Palm', 'Palm Technologies Limited', 'https://usepalm.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/usepalm', 'Palm is a financial technology company that offers a platform designed to enhance cash and liquidity management. The company focuses on providing real-time visibility into cash flows by connecting fragmented accounts and systems. This allows businesses to monitor their financial data in a unified manner, helping them understand fund movements and optimize liquidity.The platform features connected visibility, which aggregates data from various accounts into a single dashboard, and trusted forecasting that utilizes explainable AI for accurate cash flow predictions. These tools support treasury and finance teams in making informed decisions about cash balances, investments, and debt management. Palm''s solutions aim to reduce idle cash and improve financial planning by adapting to the specific context of each business.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/418c37d2-c2c0-45e4-b7d4-4731605810a2.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', null, null, null), ('2485', 'Pliant', 'Pliant Payments Limited', 'https://www.getpliant.com/en/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/getpliant', 'Pliant is a European fintech company based in Berlin, Germany, founded in 2020. It specializes in providing an API-first platform for B2B payment solutions. Pliant enables businesses to issue both physical and virtual credit cards, track spending, and integrate financial data into their systems.The company offers a range of products designed to optimize payment processes and enhance financial operations. Key offerings include customizable payment apps, a Pro API for scalable operations, a Cards-as-a-Service platform for issuing branded credit cards, and a Card OS solution for banks to launch innovative credit card programs. Pliant''s modular platform supports seamless integration with existing finance stacks, making it a smart choice for businesses looking to streamline their payment processes.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/295a653e-413a-48f0-bb30-151897151f8c.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', 'bamboohr', 'pliant', null), ('2486', 'Cantifix', 'Cantifix Limited', 'https://www.cantifix.co.uk', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/cantifix-ltd', 'Cantifix Ltd is a UK-based specialist in architectural glazing and structural glass, founded in 1986. Originally starting as a conservatory business, it evolved into a leader in innovative glazing solutions from the 1990s. The company is headquartered in London, with additional locations in Somerset and a showroom in Clerkenwell as a premium partner of Sky-Frame.Cantifix focuses on bespoke glazing solutions, offering services that range from design consultation and fabrication to installation and aftercare. Their core products include custom rooflight systems, various types of doors, glass walls, glass structures, glass roofs, and glass floors. The company emphasizes high-performance coatings and laminates to meet diverse needs, including solar, acoustic, and security requirements. With over 1,000 completed projects and a commitment to quality and collaboration, Cantifix serves a wide range of clients, including architects, designers, contractors, and homeowners across the UK.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/ad803962-70af-4030-9167-c40b7bee6720.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', null, null, null), ('2487', 'Copyright Agent', 'COPYRIGHT AGENT UK LTD', 'https://www.copyrightagent.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/copyrightagent', 'Copyright Agent is a global service provider focused on protecting intellectual property rights, particularly for images and digital content. The company offers automated infringement detection, enforcement, and resolution services at no upfront cost to clients, charging fees only upon successful outcomes. Founded on August 27, 2019, and formerly known as Visual Rights Group, Inc., Copyright Agent is headquartered in Denmark and has offices in the US, UK, Denmark, and Belgium.As an Intellectual Property Rights as a Service (IPRaaS) platform, Copyright Agent utilizes advanced software to scan the internet for unauthorized use of clients'' content. Their services include automated image search and infringement detection, comprehensive case resolution, and enforcement in multiple languages. The company serves a diverse clientele, including stock photo agencies, press agencies, and top photographers, and is recognized for its legal expertise and understanding of the image industry.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/bf30a117-3642-4ca3-99c4-43c31a85a7d7.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', null, null, null), ('2488', 'Inperio', 'Inperio (Services) Limited', 'https://inperio.co.uk', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/inperio-limited', 'Inperio (London) Limited is an independent managing general agent (MGA) based in London, specializing in niche insurance sectors. Established on October 16, 2017, the company focuses on providing specialist underwriting products backed by A-rated capacity. Inperio operates from its registered office at 5 Lloyd''s Avenue and is known for its commitment to client service and expert negotiation.As a full-service MGA, Inperio offers professional indemnity and terrorism insurance underwriting for clients across the United Kingdom. The company leverages the expertise of experienced risk advisors to deliver innovative insurance solutions tailored to complex demands. Inperio emphasizes strong partnerships with A-rated capacity providers, ensuring financial protection and exceptional service for its clients in niche areas of insurance and risk transfer.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/c5dc6d36-f5e7-4de1-9f7e-60205d69c49e.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', null, null, null), ('2489', 'OpenDialog AI', 'OpenDialog AI Limited', 'https://opendialog.ai', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/opendialogai', 'OpenDialog AI is an AI Agent Management System focused on regulated industries. Founded in 2017 and based in London, the company specializes in building, managing, and scaling autonomous AI agents with a strong emphasis on safety, compliance, and transparency. With a team of 32 employees, OpenDialog offers an enterprise-grade Conversational AI platform that automates customer interactions using advanced Generative AI and Large Language Models.The platform can automate up to 90% of interactions through natural language conversations across multiple channels, available 24/7. Key features include AI agent training, workflow management, compliance support, multi-channel deployment, and extensive analytics for continuous improvement. OpenDialog provides specialized autonomous AI agents, such as Selma, an AI sales agent for insurance, Jamie, an AI Policy Expert, and Rhea, an agent for completing abandoned transactions. The company serves industries like healthcare, insurance, financial services, and cybersecurity, helping organizations enhance customer experiences and streamline operations.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/34815e3c-1e52-478e-a8a4-2ddb328ee6eb.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', null, null, null), ('2490', 'ROCO', 'Roco9 Ltd', 'https://roco9.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/roco9-ltd', 'ROCO (Roco9 Ltd.) is a family-owned manufacturer of crushing and screening equipment based in Northern Ireland. Established in 2020, the company has roots in the industry dating back to 1978 through its parent company, the Ballytrain Group. ROCO is known for being Ireland''s only all-electric mobile crushing and screening manufacturer, focusing on innovation and sustainability.The company produces a variety of equipment, including fuel-efficient jaw crushers, high-output impactors for construction and demolition, and mobile scalpers for pre-screening. ROCO also offers custom solutions tailored to specific industry needs. Its equipment features dual-powered hybrid electric technology, providing cleaner and quieter operations. ROCO serves the recycling, demolition, and quarrying industries, with a global network of dealer partnerships across Europe and North America. The company emphasizes building strong relationships with customers and designing machines that meet real-world job site requirements.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/256da0d1-a30a-44ec-808c-6a3cf270486b.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', null, null, null), ('2491', 'Visualist', 'Visualist Technologies Ltd', 'https://www.visualistapp.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/visualist', 'Our mission is to build tools that delight, inspire and innovate, so that we enable every creative pro* to love what they do and scale but stay bespoke.*P.S. If you''re a creative, you can grow to be a pro.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/c32b7b0c-e613-415d-bc7e-73f9e4f0a4c7.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', null, null, null), ('2492', 'Intropy', 'Intropy AI Ltd', 'https://www.intropy.ai', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/intropyai', 'A new operating system for the parts and equipment industries', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/8cabf205-0348-4bee-8107-42d7807c8d57.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', null, null, null), ('2493', 'Upwind Security', 'Upwind Security UK Ltd', 'https://www.upwind.io', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/upwindsecurity', 'Upwind Security is a cloud security company founded in September 2022, specializing in a runtime-powered platform that secures cloud infrastructures, applications, and deployments in real-time. The company utilizes technologies like eBPF for continuous monitoring and threat detection. Established by the team behind Spot.io, Upwind combines expertise in DevOps and cloud infrastructure optimization to tackle challenges in modern cloud and AI environments.The core offering is a runtime security platform that provides real-time monitoring of cloud workloads, applications, and Kubernetes clusters. Key features include continuous threat detection, root-cause analysis for security issues, API security, and identity security. The platform supports multi-cloud and hybrid setups, integrating various tools for comprehensive visibility and compliance. Upwind has gained recognition as one of The Information’s 50 Most Promising Startups for 2024 and has received awards for its innovative solutions. The company serves hundreds of enterprises globally, including notable clients like Wix, Bill.com, and Booking.com.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/705ba4d0-9ce2-4559-bd45-8731f682abcb.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', null, null, null), ('2496', 'Big Orange Media', 'BIG ORANGE MEDIA LTD', 'https://bigorangemedia.co.uk', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/bigorangeuk', 'Big Orange Media Ltd is a UK-based integrated marketing and creative agency that specializes in advertising services. Founded in May 2016, the agency is headquartered in Tunbridge Wells, with a presence in London. It employs between 11 to 50 people and generates approximately $4 million in revenue. The company focuses on bold, cohesive strategies that amplify brands and drive business growth through tailored, outcome-based solutions.The agency offers a range of services, including web design, digital marketing, social media, branding, and integrated marketing campaigns. Its "Build, Grow, and Accelerate" packages are designed to align with clients'' business phases and goals. Big Orange Media emphasizes creativity combined with strategy to enhance audience engagement and brand visibility across various platforms. The agency is committed to delivering holistic campaigns that resonate with target audiences, incorporating innovative elements like podcasts and events.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/fed1cab3-273b-4124-8a35-15ea1a5e919c.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', null, null, null), ('2497', 'brown + company', 'Brown & Company Architects Ltd', 'https://www.brownandcompany.uk', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/brownandcouk', 'Brown & Co is a UK-based firm that specializes in agency, professional, and consultancy services across rural, commercial, and residential property sectors, as well as agriculture and environmental services. Established in 1993, the company has expanded its operations with offices primarily in East Anglia, the Midlands, and the Yorkshire and Humber regions, along with some international presence.The firm offers a wide range of services, including agency services for property transactions, professional consultancy in agriculture and land management, and environmental services related to property management. Brown & Co emphasizes strong, long-term relationships with its clients, which include private landowners, commercial property owners, and corporate clients. The company combines local knowledge with technical expertise to meet diverse client needs effectively.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/6af9bb9e-b63e-4e2c-818a-afb5cb9ef0eb.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', 'smartrecruiters', 'brown', null), ('2498', 'casual fitters', 'Casual Fitters Ltd', 'https://www.casualfitters.co.uk', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/casual-fitters', 'The tailor for a modern man. Our range of customisable/bespoke products includes; trousers, shirts, Suits and Blazers. All products have been created to solve a very common problem among men to finding clothes that fit well. Custom made suiting, trousers, blazers & shirts. Made-to-measure suiting, trousers, blazers & shirts3 London Locations, 1 Midtown Studio NYC', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/f3b277b0-1371-4720-8a20-aacbbf5aa57e.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', null, null, null), ('2499', 'Deducta', 'Deducta Ltd', 'https://deducta.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/deducta-ai', 'Deducta unifies multiple ERPs and disjointed systems to create a single source of truth. Easily uncover hidden synergies and standardize terms across the entire organization. Trust your data so you can make more informed decisions.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/964083d4-3bed-4e4d-b502-56619cfcf4e7.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', null, null, null), ('2500', 'ePass', 'ePass', 'https://epass.tech', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/epass-tech', 'ePass provides a modern, secure, and scalable approach to digital licencing — allowing admins to easily customise every part of the approval process:- Configuration: adjusting application requirements and user flows to comply with changing legislation.- Application: ensuring prospective licensees receive guidance and support.- Enforcement: supporting officers so they can plan, track, and report on compliance. With access to mapping functionality and historical records, ePass creates meaningful data that empowers decision-making and facilitates continuous engagement and education once a licence is granted.Find out more at https://www.civtech.scot/demo-day-9-epass.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/9a3eb712-a52b-4214-8e79-bc015fae7a49.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', null, null, null), ('2501', 'ExePay', 'EXEPAY LTD', 'https://www.exepay.co.uk', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/exepay-uk', 'ExePay is a digital-first fintech platform and Principal Member of Visa and Mastercard which gives you access to a UK and European IBAN account, international investment options, and premium lifestyle support services to help you better manage your financial and lifestyle needs.We provide:- Secure B2B business accounts- Multi-currency payment management- International financial operationsTo learn more check ⟶ exepay.co.uk', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/6ddd21da-d6f8-46d5-93fe-2869396fd69a.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', null, null, null), ('2502', 'Ionic Technologies', 'Ionic Technologies International Limited', 'https://ionictechnologies.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/ionic-technologies', 'Ionic Technologies is a UK-based company focused on permanent magnet recycling, particularly in recovering rare earth elements (REEs) from spent neodymium-iron-boron (NdFeB) magnets. Founded in 2016 as a spin-out from Queen''s University Belfast, the company utilizes patented hydrometallurgical technology to produce high-purity separated rare earth oxides (REOs) with over 99.9% purity. Headquartered in Belfast, Ionic operates a demonstration-scale plant and technical center dedicated to magnet recycling and heavy REE separation.The company''s core offering is its ionic liquid-based hydrometallurgical process, which efficiently extracts and refines individual REEs from spent magnets. This technology supports the production of essential materials for electric vehicles, wind turbines, and other advanced applications. Ionic Technologies collaborates with various stakeholders in the supply chain, including recycling companies and alloy producers, to promote sustainable practices and enhance the availability of recycled materials for critical industries.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/74ff384e-5dce-457e-a768-54f1905536ca.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', null, null, null), ('2503', 'JNE Partners LLP', 'JNE Partners LLP', 'https://www.jnepartners.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/jne-partners-llp', 'JNE Partners LLP is a London-based investment manager.  We are European-focused, fundamental value investors, investing in public andprivate equities and credit.  We manage a concentrated portfolio and invest in the best risk-adjusted opportunities at a given time, irrespective of asset class.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/9a988e95-0916-4acc-9779-b916a6fcc279.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', 'bamboohr', 'jne', null), ('2504', 'JVA Brokers', 'JVA Brokers', 'https://jvabrokers.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/jva-brokers-ltd', 'JVA is a specialist commodities brokerage firm offering voice and electronic execution services in exchange cleared Futures and Options listed on the London Metal Exchange (LME), Chicago Mercantile Exchange (CME), and The New York Mercantile Exchange (NYMEX).JVA operates on the simple principle that our clients'' interests are paramount. We act purely as broker, taking no proprietary risk and therefore eliminating any potential for conflicts of interest. JVA Brokers Limited is a Registered Intermediating Broker (RIB) of the London Metal Exchange (LME). Through this membership, JVA can arrange trades for ferrous (steel scrap and rebar), LMEprecious (gold and silver), traded options, cobalt, molybdenum, aluminium alloy, NASAAC and new products.The advice and help we provide are based on our principals'' experience, over more than a decade, in the commodity markets. JVA is able to offer clients the bespoke service, unconflicted advice and in-depth understanding they are seeking in today''s challenging markets. Our clients include a number of the world''s leading hedge funds, institutional asset managers, investment banks, corporations and commodity trading houses.JVA places the client first and foremost in every transaction and trade we undertake. This is at the heart of how we manage and maintain our client relationships. We adhere at all times to the highest professional and ethical standards, preserving client confidences and managing our own and our clients'' resources cost-effectively.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/45b3e35a-c567-4f48-91ca-3acf33919d4a.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', null, null, null), ('2505', 'Matoha', 'Matoha Instrumentation Ltd.', 'https://www.matoha.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/matoha', 'Matoha is a UK-based startup founded in 2017 by scientists and entrepreneurs from Imperial College London. The company specializes in affordable, handheld material identification devices that utilize near-infrared (NIR) spectroscopy and cloud-based machine learning. These devices are designed to enhance waste management and recycling by enabling efficient sorting of plastics and textiles on-site, without the need for lab analysis.Headquartered in London, Matoha operates in the environmental technology sector, focusing on supporting a circular economy. Their patent-pending devices, such as PlasTell for plastics and FabriTell for textiles, are portable and can be deployed in resource-limited areas, including Material Recovery Facilities (MRFs). Matoha''s technology has the potential to divert significant amounts of waste from landfills and has received several awards, including the IOP Startup Innovation Award and recognition in Forbes 30 under 30 (Europe 2023 Cohort). The company collaborates with partners like Ampere Computing and OCI to enhance its cloud and AI capabilities.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/ef004660-d2c9-4422-b610-e49433af37d6.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', null, null, null), ('2506', 'Unbox', 'Unbox Commerce Ltd', 'https://www.unbox.social', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/unbox-commerce', 'Unbox helps brands supercharge their growth in social commerce, with advanced analytics & insights to help merchants leverage the power of shoppable content to drive sustainable, profitable growth.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/f58e76f9-060f-41bf-9494-934ec258522f.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', null, null, null), ('2507', 'Cancer Research UK (CRUK)', 'Cancer Research UK', 'https://www.cancerresearchuk.org', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/cancer-research-uk', 'Cancer Research UK (CRUK) is the largest independent cancer research charity in the world, based in the UK and Isle of Man. Established on February 4, 2002, through the merger of the Cancer Research Campaign and the Imperial Cancer Research Fund, CRUK has over a century of expertise in cancer research. Its mission is to reduce cancer deaths by funding research, raising public awareness, and influencing health policy.CRUK funds research through grants to over 4,500 scientists, doctors, and nurses across various UK institutes. The organization focuses on key areas such as enhancing research leadership, improving early detection, and ensuring equitable access to treatment. It has significantly contributed to advancements in cancer treatment and prevention, including the development of important drugs and insights into genetic cancer. Additionally, CRUK provides valuable cancer information resources and runs awareness campaigns to engage the public and advocate for health system reforms.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '14', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/73e9290d-a2b2-49a5-9266-0fa2a975c54f.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', 'workday', 'External_Careers', null), ('2508', 'Farrans Construction', 'Farrans Limited', 'https://www.farrans.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/farrans-construction', 'Farrans Construction is a prominent civil engineering and building contractor based in Glasgow, Scotland. Established in 1854, the company specializes in innovative and sustainable solutions across the UK and Ireland. With a workforce of over 600 employees, Farrans operates from multiple offices and manages over 45 active sites.The company provides high-quality engineering and construction services across eight core sectors, including aviation, energy, water, transportation, commercial, industrial, public sector, and marine. Farrans also offers repurposing, refurbishment, and interiors services through its Fado division. With nearly 30 years of experience in renewable energy, Farrans has successfully completed over 1GW of windfarms, contributing significantly to sustainable power generation. The company is committed to social responsibility and aims to positively impact the communities it serves.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/d17f6381-de7f-456d-af54-8f38c7825b49.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', null, null, null), ('2509', 'Focused.io', 'Focused Labs UK Ltd', 'https://focused.io', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/focused-dot-io', 'Focused Labs is a technology consulting and custom software development firm that specializes in collaborative and agile solutions. They focus on digital transformation, legacy modernization, incremental innovation, and AI-driven technologies. Positioned as a partner to their clients, they emphasize extreme collaboration and aim to empower client teams to maintain and evolve software independently.The company offers a range of services, including technology consulting, custom software development, legacy modernization, and advanced AI solutions. Their approach involves needs assessment, solution design, implementation, and ongoing learning, ensuring minimal disruption during projects. Focused Labs is known for delivering production-ready software quickly, such as their agent blueprints, which can be completed in just three weeks. They work with cross-functional teams to drive rapid, feedback-driven iterations, adapting to the unique needs of various industries, including fintech and automotive.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '4', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/1d5a3264-a8d3-4c12-818e-46a916f6ca49.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', 'greenhouse', 'focused', null), ('2510', 'MatNex', 'Materials Nexus Limited', 'https://www.matnex.ai', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/matnex', 'MatNex, also known as Materials Nexus Ltd., is an AI-driven materials discovery company based in London, England. Founded in 2020, MatNex utilizes artificial intelligence and quantum mechanics to accelerate the discovery and design of new materials, significantly reducing the time required for development from decades to months. The company aims to create materials that lower environmental, economic, and social costs for essential items.The core technology of MatNex includes an AI platform that searches for new elemental compositions to address critical material challenges. This platform has screened over 100 million compositions, combining first-principles physics with machine learning to design sustainable, high-performance materials. MatNex focuses on net-zero technologies, including renewable energy generation, energy storage, transport, and sustainable computing, while also addressing the environmental impact of material extraction and processing.Notably, MatNex has developed rare-earth-free magnets through its "MagNex" initiative, significantly shortening discovery timelines. The company has also partnered with Viridien to enhance its computational capacity and scale its innovation pipeline for new material discoveries. MatNex has a team of 23 employees and has raised $2.68 million in funding.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/39066cb0-ac8f-4c0d-9cfe-7ff0d1447c1a.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', null, null, null), ('2511', 'Model ML', 'ModelML Limited', 'https://www.modelml.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/model-ml', 'Model ML is an AI-powered workspace platform tailored for financial services firms, focusing on automating tasks in investment banking, private equity, and consulting. Founded in 2023 by Chaz and Arnie Englander, the company is based in London and has around 50 employees. It emerged from stealth in early 2025, securing $12 million in initial funding and later raising $75 million in a Series A round to support its expansion in the Asia-Pacific region.The platform features contextually aware AI agents that streamline financial workflows by processing large datasets, conducting research, and automating analysis. Key functionalities include industry research, portfolio monitoring, and document review, which significantly reduce the time spent on manual tasks. Model ML integrates advanced technologies, such as OpenAI''s GPT-4.1 and Microsoft Azure, to enhance its capabilities and improve operational efficiency for its clients, which include leading investment banks and private equity firms.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/81adb13b-2b7f-4e3c-8f85-dab48045cd53.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', null, null, null), ('2512', 'Archer Humphryes Architects', 'Archer Humphryes International Ltd', 'https://www.archerhumphryes.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/archer-humphryes-ltd-', 'Archer Humphryes Architects is a Design company located in London, United Kingdom.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/fa72a9ca-23ce-42e3-bae8-a676043b2bbe.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', 'greenhouse', 'archer', null), ('2513', 'DistilleryVFX', 'DISTILLERY VFX LONDON LIMITED', 'https://www.distilleryvfx.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/distilleryvfx', 'Distillery VFX is an Emmy Award-winning boutique visual effects studio based in Vancouver, British Columbia, Canada. Established in 2019, the studio specializes in high-end environments, FX, compositing, and full-service VFX for feature films and television. With a team of experienced compositors and 3D generalists, Distillery VFX focuses on creative and technical problem-solving to deliver high-quality visuals efficiently.The studio emphasizes a proprietary pipeline and cross-disciplined talent, allowing it to handle large-scale projects with agility and quick iteration. Distillery VFX has around 70-95 employees and has seen significant growth in recent years. The company has credits on over 52 IMDb titles, showcasing its impressive body of work in the industry. Recently, it expanded its operations by incorporating Distillery VFX London Limited in the UK for motion picture production activities.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/b197cc14-f922-48e9-a665-0531b5f9525e.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', null, null, null), ('2514', 'BRYANT', 'Jack Bryant Productions Ltd T/A BRYANT', 'https://www.bryantprojects.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/bryantprojects', 'Founded in 2017, BRYANT excels at conceptualising and executing events at scale.We believe spaces are transformed into catalysts for cultural exchange when creative vision and technical craft work as one. Our purpose is to unite thinking and doing so in ways that break down barriers between brands and audiences, creating moments where meaningful interactions naturally flourish.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/716c47e4-4756-4f5e-826a-b72b29c6288e.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', null, null, null), ('2515', 'LSTC Group', 'LSTC Group Ltd', 'https://www.lstc.co.uk', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/lstc-group', 'LSTC Group is a UK-based engineering consultancy that specializes in survey, design, and technical services for the electricity transmission and distribution sector. Established in 2001, the company has its roots in Line Surveys, which dates back to 1954. LSTC Group is headquartered in Little Driffield, East Yorkshire, and has additional offices in Surrey, Flintshire, Derbyshire, and Scotland, allowing it to serve clients across the UK and internationally.The company offers a wide range of engineering services, including overhead transmission and distribution line design, cable route design, and asset inspection. They also provide geotechnical investigations, environmental surveys, and GIS mapping. LSTC Group emphasizes sustainability and innovation, delivering full turnkey solutions that enhance network reliability and efficiency. With a team of around 100-122 professionals, LSTC Group is committed to meeting the needs of the electricity, rail, and building industries while adhering to regulatory standards.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/2e953092-7177-47e8-b3c4-372501a608cd.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', null, null, null), ('2516', 'ClearRoute', 'Clearroute UK Limited', 'https://www.clearroute.io', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/clearroute', 'ClearRoute is a global platform engineering consultancy that specializes in Quality Cloud Engineering (QCE). The company helps enterprises accelerate software delivery by addressing complexities in cloud platforms, quality engineering, and developer experience throughout the end-to-end path to production. With a team of under 30 employees, ClearRoute employs a proprietary QCE framework that integrates Quality Assurance, DevOps, and Cloud Engineering to enhance efficiency and product quality.The consultancy offers a range of services, including end-to-end cloud strategy, test automation, performance testing, and developer experience enhancements. Their tools, such as Golden Paths, provide pre-built templates and resources to streamline development processes. ClearRoute focuses on fostering scalable transformation and collaboration, aiming to improve productivity and reduce time-to-market for its clients. The company emphasizes innovation and human connections as core values, driving impactful changes in complex environments.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '1', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/f6662410-d2a4-4ea1-91ba-29d86b332177.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', 'teamtailor', 'clearroute', null), ('2517', 'Founders Forum Group', 'Founders Forum Events LLP', 'https://ff.co', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/foundersforumgroup', 'Founders Forum Group is a global community established in 2005, dedicated to supporting entrepreneurs at every stage of their ventures. Headquartered in London, the organization connects founders, investors, and industry leaders through networking, education, professional services, investment, and philanthropy. It has hosted over 40 forums in more than 20 cities worldwide, including major hubs like Los Angeles, Tel Aviv, and Hong Kong.The company offers a range of services tailored to the startup ecosystem. This includes networking platforms like Grip, educational programs through 01 Founders, and professional services such as executive search and legal support via Founders Keepers and Founders Law. Additionally, Founders Forum Group provides investment opportunities through Founders Factory and firstminute capital, a significant seed fund. The organization also engages in philanthropic efforts through initiatives like The Centre for Entrepreneurs and Founders Pledge, fostering a supportive environment for entrepreneurial growth.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/f986a45b-7464-430a-8edc-1fc5633dac68.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', 'workable', 'foundersforum', null), ('2520', 'Captur', 'Captur Limited', 'https://www.captur.ai', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/captur-ai', 'Captur is a London-based AI startup founded by Charlotte Bax, specializing in an AI-driven image platform that utilizes computer vision and Edge AI for real-time image verification and quality control automation in mobile applications. The company offers a policy-aware photo capture layer and an intelligent camera SDK that integrates seamlessly into mobile apps, allowing teams to conduct instant image analysis, compliance checks, and fraud mitigation without the need for custom models.The Captur platform processes AI computations locally, enabling decisions in under three seconds. It targets complex operations in logistics, transportation, automotive, micro-mobility, and delivery across markets in the US, Europe, and APAC. With easy-to-implement APIs and SDKs, Captur enhances user experience and scalability while significantly reducing fraud and damage claims. The company has raised £2.2 million to expand its services and employs around 25-36 people, utilizing technologies such as JavaScript and HTML.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/b7136865-cfb2-4ea7-89bd-e90cfbe3153e.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', null, null, null), ('2521', 'Dan Pearson Studio', 'Dan Pearson Studio', 'https://www.danpearsonstudio.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/dan-pearson-studio', 'Dan Pearson Studio is a London-based landscape design practice founded in 1987 by Dan Pearson. The studio specializes in creating sophisticated gardens and landscapes that highlight naturalistic planting and a strong connection to the environment. With a team of 14 designers and landscape architects, the studio focuses on projects that blend artistic vision with practical craftsmanship.The studio offers a structured design process that includes site analysis, concept design, detailed design, and assistance with contractor selection. They work on a variety of projects, from small urban courtyards to large public parks and therapeutic gardens. Their portfolio features notable works such as the Chatsworth Estate masterplan and various Chelsea Flower Show gardens. Dan Pearson Studio collaborates with a diverse range of clients, including high-profile individuals and architectural firms, to create spaces that foster a deep connection to nature.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/ca7d309d-3e4b-4e6f-be77-c2e5406d09c2.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', 'bamboohr', 'dan', null), ('2522', 'Antaia', 'ESG360 Risk Management Ltd', 'https://www.antaia.io', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/86040680/', 'Navigating the complexities of sustainability reporting can be daunting.   Our platform empowers organisations to embed governance, establish clear data lineage, ensure compliance, and focus on strategic decision-making.  We help businesses to integrate cutting-edge AI technology with expert-led support to optimise sustainability and other regulation driven data collection, governance, and reporting. This combination reduces manual work, improves accuracy, and ensures readiness for evolving regulations. We provide a single source of truth of data for enterprises.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/895f2f0c-4bea-4034-814b-64a51844508a.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', null, null, null), ('2523', 'FTAI Aviation', 'FTAI AirOpCo UK Ltd', 'https://www.ftaiaviation.com/p/1', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/ftai-aviation-llc', 'FTAI Aviation is a global supplier specializing in high-quality CFM56 and V2500 engines, modules, and related materials for the aviation industry. The company plays a significant role in the aviation supply chain, focusing on providing premium components for commercial aircraft engines.FTAI Aviation supplies CFM56 and V2500 engines, which are commonly used in narrow-body commercial aircraft like the Boeing 737 and Airbus A320 families. In addition to engines, the company offers engine modules that are essential for maintenance, repair, and overhaul activities, as well as specialized materials that support engine maintenance and operations.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/3eea4246-4192-4c38-8618-e9eefcb62b10.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', null, null, null), ('2524', 'geoSurge', 'GEOSURGE LIMITED', 'https://geosurge.ai', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/geosurge-ai', 'Shape AI to reflect your brand, with geoSurge.The way people discover information is changing faster than ever. Large language models don''t just index - they remember. Brands are no longer competing for clicks - they''re competing to be recalled.geoSurge helps organisations future-proof their presence inside AI systems, turning memory into visibility. Today is the latest you can act.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/5296a6a0-f3a9-4c48-84cf-e5c40c982b6a.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', null, null, null), ('2525', 'Lawson West Solicitors', 'Lawson West Solicitors', 'https://www.lawson-west.co.uk', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/lawson-west-commercial', 'Lawson West Solicitors Limited is a licensed body law practice based in Leicester, England. Established in 2011, the firm has over 40 years of experience in providing expert legal advice to clients in Leicester, Leicestershire, and nearby areas. It operates from its office at 4 Dominus Way, Meridian Business Park, Leicester.The firm is dedicated to building friendly and supportive relationships with clients, positioning itself as a "Legal Partner For Life." Lawson West emphasizes core values such as being welcoming, confident, knowledgeable, and dependable. It offers professional legal services tailored to both personal and business needs, helping clients navigate various legal challenges. The firm has earned a reputation for personalized and award-winning legal support from its offices in Leicester and Market Harborough.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/02a3fd5b-eeba-44a4-9283-0fccc28c08b0.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', 'bamboohr', 'lawson', null), ('2526', 'Maji', 'Maji Financial Wellbeing Ltd', 'https://maji.io', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/maji-financial-wellbeing-ltd', 'Maji Financial Wellbeing Ltd is a UK-based provider focused on enhancing financial wellbeing. Founded in 2019 and headquartered in Beckenham, Maji offers a hyper-personalized digital platform that combines financial education, one-on-one coaching, and intuitive money management tools. The company aims to help employees reduce financial stress, improve productivity, and achieve long-term financial security.Maji''s platform features personalized financial coaching, tailored learning journeys, and various money management tools, including budget planners and savings goals. It also provides employer insights through data analytics to help organizations track employee financial health and refine benefits strategies. Maji serves UK employers and pension providers, emphasizing a people-first approach built on trust and impartiality. The company has raised $1.85 million in funding and operates with a small team, focusing on delivering meaningful benefits that support employee engagement and wellbeing.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/498edfc0-b107-4908-b239-eb10433bcd7e.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', null, null, null), ('2527', 'Neuberger Berman', 'Neuberger Berman Europe Limited', 'https://www.nb.com/en/global/home', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/neuberger-berman', 'Neuberger Berman is a private, independent investment management firm founded in 1939. It is 100% employee-owned and focuses on delivering long-term investment results through fundamental research and innovative strategies. The firm is headquartered in New York and operates in 19 countries, managing approximately $558 billion in client assets as of November 2025.Originally established to manage funds for high-net-worth individuals, Neuberger Berman has expanded its offerings to include a wide range of investment strategies across public and private markets. These include value-oriented and growth equity funds, fixed income investments, private equity, hedge funds, and multi-asset class solutions. The firm emphasizes a collaborative culture and has significantly grown its non-U.S. assets over the years, serving a diverse clientele that includes institutions, advisors, and intermediaries globally.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '13', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/00b7d43e-1186-47b0-b67c-1e57170ac6ff.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', 'workday', 'nb/NBCareers', null), ('2528', 'Pinnacom', 'Pinnacom Ltd', 'https://www.pinnacom.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/pinnacom', 'Pinnacom is a leading provider in Internet technologies to Businesses, Events and Broadcasters.  Pinnacom Limited offers telecoms, connectivity and IT services for both short term events and to our own long term customer base, offering a fully managed service from order to delivery.Pinnacom specialises in providing telephony and data services in remote locations for events and outside broadcasts etc. In doing this work the company has built considerable expertise in getting communications services to remote sites. Pinnacom has relationships with many carriers and data providers across the UK that allows the provision of data services to remote locations as well as cities, and operates as an Internet Service Provider to provide appropriate support levels for mission critical services.The Pinnacom team has experience of deploying telephone systems from 2 handsets to 500 handsets at multiple locations for events lasting from one day to several months.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/65597933-0c52-4772-9fbd-4015e14c27c1.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', null, null, null), ('2529', 'Woodrow', 'Woodrow Communications Ltd', 'https://woodrowcommunications.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/woodrowcommunications', 'Woodrow Communications Ltd is an independent strategic communications consultancy based in London, with additional offices in New York and Nairobi. Founded in February 2020, the firm specializes in public relations and communications, focusing on influential communications for modern economies and societies. Woodrow aims to tackle complexity through industry expertise and emphasizes building advisory services based on relationships and results.The company offers strategic communications consultancy services that help organizations lead discussions, simplify challenges, and drive agendas. Its core offerings include positioning clients to influence global issues and enhancing clarity in communications for multinationals, trade bodies, institutions, and high-growth businesses. Woodrow is dedicated to facilitating high-stakes conversations among various stakeholders to shape agendas and build trust.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/63be63ff-7f44-48a5-8907-4fd1b1714202.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', null, null, null), ('2530', 'Mitratech', 'Mitratech HotDocs (UK) Ltd.', 'https://mitratech.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/mitratech', 'Mitratech is a U.S.-based enterprise software company founded in 1987 and headquartered in Austin, Texas. The company specializes in legal technology, workflow automation, and governance, risk, and compliance (GRC) solutions for corporate legal, risk, compliance, and human resources professionals worldwide. Mitratech provides a unified platform that enhances transparency, reduces risk exposure, and ensures compliance across various functions.The company offers a comprehensive portfolio of software solutions, including legal management and automation tools for corporate legal departments, GRC solutions for risk monitoring and regulatory compliance, and human resources compliance tools for immigration onboarding and risk management. Mitratech''s innovative approach integrates specialized acquisitions, such as ClusterSeven, to address shadow IT and data privacy risks. With over 7,000 enterprise customers in more than 160 countries, including Fortune 1000 firms and top global financial institutions, Mitratech is recognized for its ability to streamline operations and improve decision-making across industries.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '1', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/de26e57c-b4e3-4efc-9baf-dd97bb8db6d8.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', 'greenhouse', 'mitratech', null), ('2531', 'Spectro Cloud', 'Spectro Cloud, UK Limited', 'https://www.spectrocloud.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/spectro-cloud', 'Spectro Cloud is a cloud-native infrastructure company based in San Jose, California. It focuses on making Kubernetes manageable at scale for enterprises across various environments, including public cloud, private cloud, bare metal, data centers, and edge computing. Founded by former employees of CliQr, Spectro Cloud offers a SaaS platform that emphasizes scalable, policy-based cluster management for Kubernetes, catering to platform engineering, IT operations, and DevOps teams.The company''s flagship product, Palette, provides full-stack automation and built-in security for multicluster management. It enables organizations to deploy and manage Kubernetes with flexibility and control. Key services include Kubernetes-as-a-Service, bare metal Kubernetes provisioning, and solutions for edge computing and modernizing legacy VM applications. Palette is available through AWS Marketplace and supports the deployment of containers and VMs in diverse environments.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/ccb78ee1-f79b-4a2d-bcfb-f64b59893fc5.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', null, null, null), ('2532', 'Candy Kittens', 'Longaim Ltd', 'https://candykittens.co.uk/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/candy-kittens', 'Candy Kittens is a London-based confectionery company founded in 2012 by Jamie Laing and Ed Williams. The company specializes in gourmet vegan sweets made from plant-based ingredients, ensuring no animal gelatine, artificial flavors, or palm oil are used. With a focus on creating a premium, ethical alternative to traditional sweets, Candy Kittens aims to appeal to adults seeking flavorful and guilt-free snacking options.The company opened its first sweet shop on King''s Road and later expanded to Selfridges. In 2018, Candy Kittens transitioned to a fully vegan range, becoming the first B Corp certified sweets brand in October 2022. This certification highlights their commitment to sustainability and social responsibility. Their product lineup includes eight flavors of gourmet vegan sweets, such as Wild Strawberry and Sour Watermelon, as well as a new vegan chocolate line called TREETS. Candy Kittens emphasizes natural ingredients and rich flavors, making their products appealing for those who prioritize quality and ethical consumption.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/b6621a10-bfc5-4b44-9d17-614bf360c809.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', 'teamtailor', 'candykittens', null), ('2533', 'Shield Space', 'Shield Space Limited', 'https://www.shieldspace.co.uk', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/shield-space', 'We''re here to redefine space security by harnessing the lessons of modern drone warfare. Instead of enormous monolithic satellites, we envision agile, networked clusters of smaller spacecraft capable of manoeuvring, inspecting, and, if necessary, disrupting threats on a tactical timeline. Through focused R&D, targeted prototyping, and collaboration with trusted partners, we plan to deliver orbital defence solutions that are both flexible and cost-effective. Our ultimate aim is to empower decision-makers with real-time, autonomous oversight of critical orbits, turning space from a vulnerable frontier into a domain where sovereign control can be swiftly asserted.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/a3c39e0f-60a9-404c-884f-6dd2929247bc.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', 'greenhouse', 'shield', null), ('2534', 'ABM UK', 'ABM AVIATION UK LIMITED', 'https://www.abm.co.uk', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/abmuk', 'ABM is a leading provider of integrated facility, engineering, and infrastructure solutions, employing over 100,000 team members worldwide and generating more than $8 billion in annual revenue. Founded in 1909, the company has evolved from a small window cleaning business into a multinational organization. In the UK and Ireland, ABM operates with over 2,600 team members across more than 1,600 sites, offering customized facilities solutions across various sectors.ABM provides a wide range of services, including facility management, technical solutions, cleanroom services, energy management, and integrated workforce programs. The company serves diverse industries such as healthcare, manufacturing, life sciences, and transportation. ABM is committed to a people-centered culture, focusing on workforce equity and inclusion, and aims to make a positive impact every day through its dedicated team. Recent strategic acquisitions have further enhanced its capabilities, particularly in the semiconductor sector.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '218', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/6f495f33-5185-4483-bfda-0acd2a988242.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', 'workable', 'abm-careers', null), ('2535', 'EGYM', 'EGYM UK Limited', 'https://uk.egym.com/en-gb', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/egym-global', 'EGYM is a global fitness technology company based in Munich, Germany, founded in 2010. It specializes in intelligent gym equipment, software, and digital solutions designed to enhance workout experiences for users and drive success for fitness facilities, health clubs, and corporate wellness programs. With over 700 employees and operations in 25 countries, EGYM serves around 18,000 fitness centers and reaches approximately 6 million users monthly.The company offers a comprehensive fitness ecosystem that includes connected gym equipment, digital solutions, and AI-powered tools. Its smart strength machines automatically adjust settings for personalized training, while its cloud-based platform provides apps for tracking progress and creating customized workout plans. EGYM also supports corporate wellness initiatives, offering subscription-based programs that give employees access to various fitness facilities and resources. The company emphasizes data-driven health outcomes and member motivation, ensuring dedicated support for its partners in the fitness industry.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '1', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/bf5459e3-576a-46ea-924b-72899ed37db2.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', null, null, null), ('2536', 'La Nouvelle Garde', 'Nouvelle Garde Limited', 'https://lanouvellegarde.com/en/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/lanouvellegarde', 'La Nouvelle Garde is a French restaurant group established in 2019 by Charles Perez and Victor Dubillot. The group aims to revitalize traditional Parisian brasseries by combining modern design with responsible French cuisine and the art of French living. Operating under France''s 2019 Pacte Law, La Nouvelle Garde is committed to transparent socio-environmental goals and has been a Certified B Corporation since May 2025.The group operates traditional brasseries that emphasize high-quality, on-site cuisine featuring locally sourced ingredients. Their offerings include simple yet flavorful dishes served in vibrant, design-forward spaces that encourage community and shared values. Notable locations include Brasserie Bellanger and Brasserie Dubillot in Paris. La Nouvelle Garde tracks its impact on food sourcing and professional development, aiming for high local sourcing rates and internal promotion within its teams.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/688c685a-390e-47e9-8501-70ff19a0907e.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', 'teamtailor', 'app', null), ('2537', 'Grind', 'Grind Holdings Ltd', 'https://grind.co.uk', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/shoreditch-grind', 'Grind is a London-based coffee company founded in 2011, known for its commitment to sustainability. It started in Shoreditch when founder David Abrahamovitch transformed a mobile phone store into the first Grind café, which operates as a coffee shop by day and a cocktail bar by night. Over the years, Grind has expanded to 14 locations across London, offering all-day dining, specialty coffee, and cocktails.The company produces a range of coffee products, including roast-to-order beans, ready-to-drink coffee cans, and the UK''s first home-compostable coffee pods compatible with Nespresso machines. Grind also offers a subscription service for direct-to-consumer delivery of its coffee products. As a global coffee supplier to Soho House and a partner with brands like Oatly and Brewdog, Grind serves hundreds of thousands of customers worldwide while emphasizing quality and sustainability in its offerings.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/6f7937be-9d0a-4f89-8b68-38c81bfe58da.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', null, null, null), ('2538', 'British Electronic Payments Institution', 'BEPI LTD', 'https://bepi.uk', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/britishpayments', 'BEPI (British Electronic Payments Institution) is a UK-based Electronic Money Institution (EMI), authorised and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority (FCA).We deliver modern financial infrastructure that empowers fintechs, marketplaces, SaaS platforms, and cross-border enterprises to move money globally — securely, efficiently, and in full regulatory alignment.As a trusted FCA-licensed partner, BEPI provides banking, acquiring, and card-issuing solutions that power the next generation of financial products.Our mission is simple: to make global finance smart, compliant, and scalable.Our solutions include:•	Multi-currency IBAN accounts — dedicated or pooled for international operations•	Virtual corporate cards — advanced controls, real-time visibility, and flexible spend management•	Payment acquiring & processing — SEPA, SWIFT, Faster Payments, and CHAPS•	Tiered FX conversion — competitive, transparent currency exchange rates•	Seamless API integration — automate payouts, reconciliation, and workflows•	Premium onboarding & KYC — fast activation with embedded compliance•	Dedicated client success — proactive service orchestration and tailored supportSince obtaining its EMI authorisation in 2020, BEPI has powered borderless finance for companies that require reliability, scalability, and trust in every transaction.We''re not just simplifying payments — we''re redefining how financial infrastructure should work: compliant by design, scalable by default, and global from day one.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/e8b57d71-74b4-4185-8361-481b4944c7e3.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', null, null, null), ('2539', 'Fidenda', 'Fidenda Limited', 'https://www.fidenda.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/fidenda', 'Fidenda is an independent consultancy based in London, specializing in Integrated Business Planning (IBP) using Anaplan. The firm focuses on helping complex organizations adopt IBP to enhance collaboration across departments, enabling faster, data-driven decision-making. With a team of approximately 25 employees, Fidenda emphasizes a client-first approach, ensuring that its services are tailored to meet the unique needs of each organization.Fidenda offers a range of services centered around Anaplan, including expert guidance for developing tailored IBP strategies, implementation and integration of custom Anaplan setups, and training and support for both new and existing users. The firm addresses common challenges in IBP adoption, providing practical solutions to connect reporting, forecasting, and strategic decisions. By leveraging its deep expertise in Anaplan, Fidenda aims to deliver quick, effective outcomes for its clients.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/cb74567c-9395-4399-8351-1af63b8f3077.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', 'bamboohr', 'fidenda', null), ('2540', 'FreshBritain', 'Fresh Design and Marketing Limited', 'https://www.freshbritain.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/freshbritain', 'FreshBritain is a UK-based brand design agency and brand strategy consultancy founded in 1999. The company focuses on creating emotional connections between brands and their audiences to enhance brand vision, simplify strategy, and improve overall performance. With a team of 10-49 employees, FreshBritain operates from Welwyn Garden City and Godalming, England.The agency offers a range of services, including brand creation and activation, brand strategy and design, and consultancy offerings such as Brand Masterclass and Brand Events. FreshBritain has extensive experience in designing over 200 global brands, emphasizing the importance of subconscious decision-making in branding. The company has worked with notable clients like Levi''s, Burberry, and Adidas Terrex, showcasing its ability to elevate brand identity and market presence.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/e60031e4-0217-4773-9517-e4cc478e015e.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', null, null, null), ('2541', 'Quvara Medical', 'Quvara Medical Limited', 'https://quvaramedical.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/quvara-medical', 'Part of the Buckland Group, Quvara Medical represents decades of proven precision, compliance, and scale — delivering smarter device manufacturing with speed, trust, and global regulatory strength. We''re a new brand, but our foundations are anything but new: our Swindon hub has been manufacturing millions of devices every year for one of the world''s largest med-tech companies.What''s in a name? It''s everything we stand for: - QU = Quality- VA = Validation- RA = Regulatory ApprovalTogether, they represent our core pillars: precision, compliance, and trust.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/1e3a673b-668a-4046-9904-da3df6523c5f.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', null, null, null), ('2542', 'Resource Experts', 'Resource Experts Ltd', 'https://resource-experts.co.uk', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/resource-experts-ltd-1', 'Resource Experts Ltd offers expert consultancy in Project Planning, tender planning, and claim consultancy services for the construction industry in the UK.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/41720139-71e2-4a6e-8549-29e459c97e1b.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', null, null, null), ('2543', 'Antithesis', 'Antithesis UK Limited', 'https://antithesis.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/antithesis-operations', 'Antithesis is an autonomous software testing platform based in Vienna, Virginia, founded in 2018. The company specializes in continuous reliability testing for complex distributed systems, enabling engineering teams to confidently ship software by autonomously detecting, reproducing, and debugging bugs that traditional methods may overlook. Launched in 2024, Antithesis employs between 51 and 200 people.The platform operates in a cloud-based environment, running customer software in a deterministic simulated setting that mirrors production conditions. It utilizes an AI-driven engine for autonomous testing, generating test cases based on desired outcomes. Key features include intelligent exploration, fault injection, and perfect reproducibility, allowing for the simulation of various production scenarios. Antithesis targets industries that require high reliability, such as financial services, automotive, healthcare, and more, and serves notable clients like Palantir, MongoDB, and Ethereum.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '5', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/740a83f1-6c8f-42c8-9292-b466f80d215b.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', 'ashby', 'https://api.ashbyhq.com/posting-api/job-board/antithesis', null), ('2544', 'Options', 'OPTIONS FOR SUPPORTED LIVING', 'https://optionsempowers.org.uk', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/optionsempowers', 'At Options, we believe in a world where people with disabilities can contribute as unique and valued members of dynamic communities.We aim to support, empower and enable people with disabilities to live their lives to the full, embracing everything that this means.Our talented and dedicated team challenge traditional social care norms, whilst working collaboratively with families, carers, partners and our communities to offer genuine person-centred support.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/4830330f-282a-41b2-90c2-85035623dcd2.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', 'smartrecruiters', 'options', null), ('2545', 'CAVU Aerospace UK', 'CAVU Aerospace UK Tech Ltd.', 'https://cavuaerospace.uk', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/cavu-aerospace-uk', 'CAVU Aerospace UK is subsidiary of CAVU Aerospace Inc. focused on Space sector.We manufacture satellite & Launch vehicle components. Core business is Command & Data Handling, OnBoard Computers.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/ee7448a4-833e-437a-81ac-fe2ea7fddafd.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', 'bamboohr', 'cavu', null), ('2546', 'CF Psychology', 'CF Psychology Group Limited', 'https://cfpsychology.co.uk', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/cfpsychology', 'CF Psychology is an educational psychology practice comprising a team of highly skilled educational psychologists who are experts in assessing the learning needs of children, young people, and adults. We provide services to individuals, families, schools, universities and employers.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/02ba15b4-83fa-42ef-a541-af02c77ae253.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', null, null, null), ('2547', 'Mike Kogan Consulting', 'MKC Hospitality Ltd', 'https://mikekoganconsulting.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/mikekoganconsulting.com', 'Mike Kogan Consulting is a company specializing in hospitality renovation. This privately held company located in Point Pleasant, NJ, has projects ongoing throughout the United States.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/a71655e7-6947-444c-be77-e06c2a64f727.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', 'smartrecruiters', 'mike', null), ('2548', 'Phoenix Equity Partners', 'Phoenix Equity Partners Limited', 'https://phoenix-equity.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/phoenix-equity-partners', 'Phoenix Equity Partners is a private equity firm based in London, established in 2001. The firm specializes in growth capital investments ranging from £10 million to £80 million in established, founder-led businesses in the UK and Ireland. Phoenix focuses on mid-market companies and targets sectors across Western Europe and North America. With a commitment to a people-first approach, the firm aims to nurture entrepreneurs and their teams, emphasizing collaboration and shared growth.The firm concentrates on three main thematic areas: Data & Analytics, Technology & Specialist Services, and Health & Wellbeing. Phoenix has a strong track record, having completed 63 unique partnerships since its inception, and it combines deep sector expertise with hands-on support to help businesses achieve their goals. The firm has managed 11 closed funds, with its latest closures in 2024, and celebrates entrepreneurial milestones alongside its partners. Key personnel include experienced professionals in origination, finance, and investment management.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/5be7eb27-4dd1-46d6-9d14-7e31ec93cdc2.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', 'breezy', 'phoenix', null), ('2549', 'The Angelou Centre', 'The Angelou Centre', 'https://angelou-centre.org.uk', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/the-angelou-centre', 'The Angelou Centre is a Black-led, women-run charity located in the North East of England. For over 30 years, it has provided a safe and confidential space for women, children, and young people from Black and minoritised communities who are recovering from violence, abuse, or discrimination. The Centre offers holistic and culturally sensitive support, including refuge housing, counseling, therapy, advocacy, and skills development programs aimed at fostering independence and raising awareness of rights.As a Wellbeing Hub in Newcastle, the Angelou Centre creates a welcoming environment with amenities like hot drinks and free Wi-Fi. Its services are tailored specifically for Black, Asian, minority ethnic, and refugee women, focusing on areas such as domestic abuse, sexual violence, and economic independence. The Centre also facilitates group activities and personal development opportunities, promoting a society free from inequality and discrimination.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/ee631f62-a10c-4148-ad0d-fe2057f421c5.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', null, null, null), ('2550', 'TreQ', 'TreQ Global Ltd', 'https://treq.tech', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/treq-tech', 'TreQ is a quantum systems engineering and manufacturing company that designs, manufactures, and operates custom quantum computing systems for organizations globally. Founded in 2023, TreQ is headquartered in the United Kingdom and has operations in the United States. The company recently raised over $5 million in seed funding to enhance its team and manufacturing capabilities.TreQ offers complete turnkey quantum computing solutions, including design, installation, operation, and maintenance. Their deployment models include on-premises solutions for clients to host systems at their facilities and cloud-based access through their facilities in the UK and US. The company''s flagship product, the Compass SG25B, is an open-architecture quantum computing system that integrates technologies from leading quantum ecosystem providers. TreQ focuses on modularity and interoperability, allowing for tailored solutions that meet specific client needs while minimizing supply chain risks. With a commitment to advancing scientific discovery and economic prosperity, TreQ serves researchers, developers, and organizations looking to build quantum-ready infrastructure.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/84422c02-977f-485f-adac-16700f3c40ee.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', null, null, null), ('2551', 'Figment', 'Figment Europe Ltd', 'https://www.figment.io', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/figment-io', 'Figment is an independent provider of staking infrastructure for blockchain networks, focusing on Proof-of-Stake (PoS) protocols. The company helps institutional clients earn rewards on digital assets while securing networks. With a global network of PoS validators, Figment supports staking across over 40 protocols, including Ethereum and Solana, managing $17 billion in assets under stake.Headquartered in Ontario, Canada, Figment operates as a remote-first company with a presence in 23 countries and employs between 201-500 people. The company aims to advance the digital asset ecosystem by offering secure, audited services with slashing protection and industry-leading service level agreements. Figment provides a comprehensive staking solution for institutions, including non-custodial staking infrastructure, a DataHub platform for developers, and tailored staking strategies. It serves over 1000 institutional clients, including asset managers, exchanges, wallets, and foundations, emphasizing risk reduction and optimized rewards.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/0659e1d9-2ab3-42aa-88c8-fa5f6b94596b.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', 'greenhouse', 'figment', null), ('2552', 'Bosch', 'Bosch Global Software Technologies Private Limited', 'https://www.bosch.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/bosch', 'Bosch, officially known as Robert Bosch GmbH, is a leading German multinational engineering and technology company founded in 1886. With operations in over 150 countries and a workforce of approximately 440,000 associates, Bosch focuses on innovation, sustainability, and social responsibility. The company invests significantly in research and development, employing around 87,000 associates across 136 global locations.Bosch operates in four main business sectors: Mobility Solutions, Industrial Technology, Consumer Goods, and Energy and Building Technology. It is recognized as the world''s largest automotive supplier, offering a range of products including fuel injection systems, ABS, and electrification solutions. In the consumer goods sector, Bosch is known for its home appliances, such as washing machines and kitchen machines. The company also develops precision tools and connectivity-driven products, emphasizing user-friendly technology across various industries.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '1', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/9e7723a8-165f-4a34-8291-64fc9f1bc6a1.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', null, null, null), ('2553', 'Chase Buchanan', 'Chase Buchanan Consulting Ltd', 'https://chasebuchanan.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/chase-buchanan-ltd', 'Chase Buchanan Private Wealth Management is a regulated wealth management firm that specializes in providing financial advice to expats around the world. With offices across Europe and a dedicated team in the US, the firm offers tailored investment, tax planning, and retirement services. Chase Buchanan is committed to delivering high-quality, unbiased advice that aligns with clients'' best interests, focusing on building long-term relationships and providing ongoing support.The firm offers a range of comprehensive services, including investment management with customized portfolios, tax-efficient strategies for compliance with international regulations, and retirement planning that optimizes various pension schemes. Additionally, they provide estate and succession planning to help clients structure their estates effectively. Chase Buchanan emphasizes the importance of using only regulated products and providers, ensuring that clients receive trustworthy and compliant financial solutions. Their target clientele includes global expats, particularly British and international clients residing in the United States.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/6015a0cd-153c-437a-9135-a27cb8bf8bd9.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', 'smartrecruiters', 'chase', null), ('2554', 'Seesaw Learning', 'Global Learning Europe Ltd', 'https://seesaw.com/en-gb/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/seesaw-learning', 'Seesaw Learning is a prominent learning experience platform tailored for elementary education, serving PreK-6th grade. Founded in 2013 and based in San Francisco, California, Seesaw connects teachers, students, administrators, and families to enhance student learning and engagement. The platform is utilized by over 25 million users across more than 130 countries.Seesaw offers a comprehensive suite of products, including a learning management system with AI, interactive lessons, digital portfolios, and tools for two-way communication. The platform also features assessment tools and school-wide management analytics, all designed to improve teacher efficiency and provide insights into student progress. Seesaw emphasizes accessibility and has received multiple certifications for its evidence-based design, supporting various educational frameworks. The company serves a diverse range of users, including teachers, students, families, and school administrators.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/913f339f-2a6e-4dba-94ae-5dfaac20d794.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', 'greenhouse', 'seesaw', null), ('2555', 'SB Laboratories', 'SB LABORATORIES LIMITED', 'https://sblabs.co.uk', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/s-b-uk-ltd', 'SB Laboratories, based in Manchester, specializes in the design, manufacture, and installation of laboratory furniture systems and fume cupboards. With over five decades of experience, the company has established itself as a leading provider in the UK. Founded in 2006, SB Laboratories employs around 29 people and offers comprehensive project management services throughout the laboratory development lifecycle.The company’s product range includes free-standing furniture systems, service walls, advanced fume cupboards, and integrated laboratory systems. SB Laboratories caters to a diverse clientele, including schools, colleges, universities, research and development facilities, healthcare institutions, and various industrial sectors. The company is recognized for its excellence, holding the Queen''s Award for Enterprise: International Trade and maintaining memberships with several professional organizations.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/1656cd7e-30f4-437c-8465-d365b46bffaf.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', null, null, null), ('2556', 'Scottish Legal Complaints Commission', 'Scottish Legal Complaints Commission', 'https://www.scottishlegalcomplaints.org.uk', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/scottish-legal-complaints-commission', 'The Scottish Legal Complaints Commission (SLCC) is an independent public body in Scotland that manages complaints against legal practitioners, including solicitors, advocates, and licensed conveyancers. Established in 2008 under the Legal Profession and Legal Aid (Scotland) Act, the SLCC aims to provide a fair and accessible service to the public, funded by an annual levy on legal professionals.The SLCC investigates service complaints and can award compensation up to £20,000. For serious conduct complaints, it refers cases to relevant professional bodies for further investigation. The organization also promotes best practices in the legal sector, oversees complaint handling by professional bodies, and conducts data analysis to identify trends in complaints. Its services are free for consumers, ensuring that everyone has access to a fair complaint resolution process.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/35d47244-89d5-4b74-baa7-4c4a9d693db7.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', null, null, null), ('2557', 'SURE Solutions', 'Sure Energy Solutions Ltd', 'https://suresol.co.uk', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/sure-solutions-refrigeration', 'SURE Solutions is a family-owned industrial refrigeration company, established in 2016 and based in Birkenhead, UK. The company specializes in energy-efficient refrigeration solutions using natural refrigerants like ammonia and CO2. With a team that boasts over 500 years of collective industry experience, SURE Solutions serves clients across the UK, offering flexibility by collaborating with preferred suppliers and subcontractors.The company provides comprehensive turnkey solutions in areas such as meat processing, dairy, food and beverage, and cold storage. Their services include design, installation, commissioning, and maintenance of refrigeration systems, along with a catalogue of OEM spares and refrigerants. SURE Solutions is committed to sustainability and operational excellence, holding multiple ISO accreditations and engaging in green initiatives. They also offer 24/7 technical support and have received industry recognition for their innovative projects and practices.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/9721138f-6bc8-4a78-a70d-cc8b5bbad0b3.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', 'lever', 'sure', null), ('2558', 'TMX Group', 'TMX Exchange Services Limited', 'https://www.tmx.com/en', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/tmx-group', 'TMX Group is a Canadian-based global information and financial services company that operates integrated capital markets platforms. Established on May 1, 2008, through the merger of the Montreal Exchange and the Toronto Stock Exchange, TMX Group has a rich history dating back to 1852. The company is headquartered in Toronto, Ontario, and is publicly traded on the TSX under the symbol "X."TMX Group offers a range of services across multiple marketplaces. The Toronto Stock Exchange (TSX) provides trading for public equities, while the TSX Venture Exchange supports companies at various development stages. The Montreal Exchange specializes in derivatives trading, including futures and options contracts. Additionally, TMX Group facilitates capital raising through TSX Private Markets and offers environmental products via the Montreal Climate Exchange. The company has made significant investments in advanced trading technology, enhancing its electronic trading capabilities and real-time market data services for both institutional and retail investors.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/9bf3d061-94b4-4fcf-a013-f8916c4d6052.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', 'workday', 'tmx/TMX_Careers', null), ('2559', 'Wasted Talent', 'Wasted Talent LTD', 'https://www.wastedtalent.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/wastedtalent', 'Wasted Talent is a global media company based in London, UK, that operates influential music, culture, and entertainment platforms, including Mixmag, Kerrang!, and The Face. The company focuses on creating authentic stories and branded content solutions aimed at engaging a global youth audience. Wasted Talent was formed as the parent company of key editorial platforms, originally linked to the acquisition of Kerrang! magazine in 2017. It has expanded its operations to include a New York office, enhancing its ability to produce US-centric content and events. The company''s flagship platforms deliver a range of editorial content, events, and awards, with a strong emphasis on music genres such as rock, punk, and electronic music. In addition to its media properties, Wasted Talent offers branded content creation and marketing solutions, helping brands connect with youth audiences through storytelling, partnerships, and custom content strategies.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/381b1a9b-f61e-46d6-aeab-6c6931faac4d.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', null, null, null), ('2560', 'InterDigital', 'InterDigital Europe Ltd', 'https://www.interdigital.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/interdigital-communications', 'InterDigital, Inc. is a global research and development company based in Wilmington, Delaware, specializing in wireless, video, and artificial intelligence technologies. Founded in 1972, the company operates primarily through intellectual property licensing, boasting an extensive patent portfolio of approximately 30,000 patents and applications. InterDigital is recognized for its contributions to 3G, 4G/LTE, and 5G technologies, as well as advancements in video and Wi-Fi standards.The company has established strategic licensing agreements with major technology firms, including Apple, Samsung, Huawei, LG, Xiaomi, and Nokia. InterDigital''s commitment to fair licensing practices has made it a trusted partner in the mobile ecosystem. With a focus on innovation, InterDigital continues to play a significant role in shaping the future of wireless communication and related technologies.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '5', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/1cb5c7ac-714f-43a6-9ac9-70091f8ae83a.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', 'workday', 'InterDigital_Career', null), ('2563', 'The Place', 'London Contemporary Dance (The Place) Limited', 'https://theplace.org.uk', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/theplace', 'The Place is a prominent creative hub for contemporary dance located in London. It operates as a trading name of London Contemporary Dance (The Place) Limited and has been a key institution since its founding in 1969. The organization is home to the London Contemporary Dance School (LCDS), which offers undergraduate and postgraduate programs in dance education. The Place is dedicated to fostering creativity and engagement through various dance-related services, including weekly classes for all ages and abilities, and a Centre for Advanced Training for young dancers.The Place supports emerging artists through development programs and live performances, encouraging innovative artistic expression. It has a rich history of leadership and collaboration, engaging with a diverse community of artists, students, and audiences both onsite and online. The organization emphasizes risk-taking and pedagogy, making it a vital part of the contemporary dance landscape in Europe.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/e9af283d-1614-4d6c-a79a-1b2cc944b9e8.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', null, null, null), ('2564', 'Amtest UK', 'Amtest UK Ltd', 'https://amtest.uk', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/amtest-uk', 'Amtest UK Ltd specialises in assessing the quality, durability, and performance of concrete materials used in construction projects, supported by in-house concrete technology consultants. Our highly qualified technicians provide testing, monitoring and surveying services for soils, aggregates, concrete, asphalt and core sampling, delivered on- and off-site.Our London-based laboratory provides comprehensive testing and analysis of various construction materials, including cementitious products, chemical admixtures, concrete, aggregates, and soils. With our dedicated Research and Development facility, we offer expert support through lab trials and durability tests like Chloride Migration and Water Penetration, ensuring projects are optimised from the start.Get in touch today to begin your partnership with us.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/d5e87198-a238-4336-a37e-3db3da932944.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', null, null, null), ('2565', 'Pluto Data Analytics', 'Pluto Data Analytics Limited', 'https://www.plutodata.co.uk', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/pluto-data-analytics', 'Pluto Data Analytics Limited is a UK-based company founded on February 18, 2020. It specializes in predictive sports analytics and data consultancy, operating from Brighton, England. The company focuses on transforming raw data into actionable insights using AI, machine learning, and advanced analytics, particularly in sports forecasting and betting markets. With around 9 employees, Pluto operates as a micro-entity and is classified under SIC code 63110 for data processing and related activities.Headquartered in London, Pluto Data Analytics offers AI-powered predictive analytics validated in real-world betting scenarios across various sports. Their services include predictive sports analytics for game forecasting and player behavior, as well as advanced analytics for fraud detection and betting pattern analysis. The company emphasizes the use of deep datasets and advanced machine learning models, providing tools for sports clubs to enhance player shortlisting and transfer decisions. Pluto aims to optimize operations and improve customer experiences through comprehensive data-driven solutions.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/8ca9ccb7-54e6-4d53-9dc2-7e154b8e9c53.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', 'bamboohr', 'pluto', null), ('2566', 'Quadrant Harmon', 'QUADRANT HARMON CONSULTING LIMITED', 'http://www.quadrantharmon.co.uk/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/quadrant-harmon-consulting-limited', 'Quadrant Harmon Consulting Ltd is a firm of Consulting Civil and Structural Engineers based in Central London.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/fbf68875-85a5-4151-8b10-508aa2e31fbb.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', null, null, null), ('2567', 'Vysus Group', 'Vysus Group', 'https://www.vysusgroup.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/vysus-group', 'Vysus Group is an independent engineering and technical consultancy that specializes in asset performance, risk management, and project management for complex industrial and energy assets. With headquarters in Houston, Texas, and a legal residence in Spain, the company operates globally and employs around 483 people. Vysus Group aims to help clients manage risk and enhance performance through technical expertise and innovative solutions for large-scale energy projects.The company offers digitally enabled consultancy services across various sectors, including energy, power, and infrastructure. Key services include asset performance management, real-time risk management using their PromapsTM software, project management for large-scale energy projects, and offshore subsurface surveys. Vysus Group is recognized for its significant contributions to offshore wind projects and its extensive experience in grid connection consultancy, particularly in Australia. The firm emphasizes collaboration and creativity to address challenges in energy market transitions and digital transformation.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/8efc5953-eb5d-4ae8-aadf-8b5d069415a1.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', null, null, null), ('2568', 'WCL Infrastructure', 'WCL Infrastructure Ltd', 'https://wclinfrastructure.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/wcl-infrastructure', 'WCL is an agile and fast-growing consultancy firm, developing and delivering major works for customers across the infrastructure sector. We work with large corporates and SMEs, bringing together the best minds in planning, programming, engineering and management. WCL specialises in integrated solutions for complex projects, complementing our customer''s existing team with specialist services and hand-picked experts. We provide tailored insights and support, unlocking exceptional outcomes in challenging circumstances. WCL serves a growing range of clients across the globe, from Clients such as Network Rail to Tier 1 suppliers, as well as operators at every level. We currently operate in the UK, New Zealand and Canada.We operate across 4 main service areas:•	Project and programme management•	Engineering and construction•	Commercial management•	Integration and controlsGet in touch to discuss your project requirements and find out how we can help.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/67db6265-9723-4d16-acfd-b5ae97eea556.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', null, null, null), ('2569', 'Finova', 'Finova', 'https://www.finova.tech', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/finova-tech', 'Finova is a UK-based technology provider that specializes in modular, SaaS-based, cloud-native software solutions for the mortgage, lending, and savings sectors. Founded in 1996 and headquartered in London, the company employs around 350 people and generates approximately $73.5 million in revenue. Finova''s technology helps banks, building societies, specialist lenders, equity release providers, and brokers streamline operations and automate processes.The company offers a flexible, API-driven platform that simplifies lending and savings operations, enabling clients to manage significant loan originations and assets. Finova''s suite includes solutions for origination, servicing, decisioning, and broker tools, all from a single adaptable platform. Key offerings include its flagship MSO platform for mortgages, a whole-market solution for various lending products, and tools for savings accounts. Finova aims to be a leading partner in the UK lending and savings market, focusing on efficiency and growth for its clients.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '7', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/9cb34c69-3a28-4fb9-a44f-c5a119de55b1.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', 'breezy', 'finova', null), ('2570', 'ARC marine', 'ARC marine', 'https://arcmarine.co.uk', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/arc-marine-ltd', 'ARC marine is an eco-engineering company dedicated to enhancing marine biodiversity through innovative, nature-inclusive solutions. Based in Devon and Cornwall, UK, the company was established in 2015 and has gained recognition for its science-led approach to reef creation and marine infrastructure. ARC Marine''s mission focuses on restoring and protecting ocean biodiversity by providing sustainable solutions for offshore and coastal developments.The company offers a comprehensive range of services, including the design, manufacture, and installation of nature-based solutions. They assist with obtaining necessary permits and licenses, ensuring compliance with regulations, and managing stakeholder relationships. ARC Marine''s product lineup features Reef Cubes, Reef Mats, and Reef Walls, all designed to protect marine infrastructure while promoting ecological health. Their Marine Matts are a notable innovation, replacing traditional concrete mattresses with a carbon-negative, plastic-free alternative that supports marine life.ARC Marine holds several industry accreditations, including B-Corp certification and ISO standards for quality and environmental management. The company is committed to advancing the UN Sustainable Development Goals and has received investment from Mercuria to further its mission of increasing marine biodiversity globally.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/463c4786-0df7-4011-99d6-c5af73bb53c5.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', 'bamboohr', 'arc', null), ('2571', 'Bowcliffe Wealth Management', 'Bowcliffe Wealth Management', 'https://www.bowcliffewm.co.uk', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/bowcliffe-wealth-management', 'Bowcliffe Wealth Management is a Senior Partner Practice of St. James''s Place Wealth Management, offering bespoke Chartered Financial Planning advice from the beautiful surroundings of Bowcliffe Hall near Wetherby.Clients are well placed and receive exceptional service as we help meet their personal/business needs.Bowcliffe Wealth Management offers personal face to face advice to clients throughout the country."In an age where technology plays a vital role, here at Bowcliffe Wealth Management we embrace this. However, we never fail to appreciate the importance of face to face advice, and although the principles of wealth management haven''t changed since joining the industry some 16 years ago, the need for personal financial planning advice has never been more important than now."Adrian Brook, Director of Bowcliffe Wealth Management.As a Senior Partner Practice of St. James''s Place, we are able to deliver exceptional service with access to market leading research and World leading fund managers.We would like to welcome you to Bowcliffe Wealth Management, and look forward to developing a long lasting relationship.Bowcliffe Wealth Management Ltd is an Appointed Representative of and represents only St. James''s Place Wealth Management plc (which is authorised and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority). The ''St. James''s Place Partnership'' and the titles ''Partner'' and ''Partner Practice'' are marketing terms used to describe St. James''s Place representatives.SJP Approved 16/9/2025', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/fede31b0-6174-4828-b797-b9eab78e6f0e.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', null, null, null), ('2572', 'Clarity Sensors', 'Clarity Sensors Ltd', 'https://www.claritysensors.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/claritysensors', 'At Clarity Sensors, our aim is to transform medical imaging by developing cutting-edge semiconductor-based X-ray detector that will advance early disease detection, expand access to preventative disease screening, and enhance patient safety through ultra-low dose, high-resolution X-ray imaging.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/e725d50c-180d-4ccc-898a-126d3eea04c6.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', 'greenhouse', 'clarity', null), ('2573', 'Ellidore', 'Ellidore Events Limited', 'https://www.ellidore.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/ellidore', 'Ellidore is a luxury lifestyle concierge and membership service company founded in 2010 and based in London, England. With a focus on high-net-worth individuals, Ellidore provides a wide range of services, including personalized travel planning, full-service event organization, fashion services, and exclusive access to premium events. The company also offers comprehensive lifestyle concierge services and exclusive membership programs that enhance clients'' experiences.Ellidore prides itself on reliability, discretion, and personalized service, ensuring that clients receive exceptional attention and professionalism. The company targets successful and adventurous individuals, including business leaders and entrepreneurs, who seek unique lifestyle experiences. With offices in London, Dubai, Dallas, and Los Angeles, Ellidore is expanding its presence in the United States, aiming to become a leading luxury lifestyle service globally within the next five years.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/2096a12b-2269-47b0-bd2c-797611667e2b.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', null, null, null), ('2574', 'Jeen.ai', 'Jeen AI Technologies UK Ltd', 'https://jeen.ai', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/jeen-ai', 'Jeen.ai is an Israeli enterprise AI platform established in July 2024 as a spin-off from One Technologies. Based in Tel Aviv, the company provides a secure, unified AI workspace designed for customizing and deploying generative AI solutions tailored to business needs. Jeen.ai offers deployment options in cloud, on-premises, or hybrid environments, focusing on simplifying AI adoption for large organizations.The core offering is the Enterprise AI Workspace, which integrates various tools such as intelligent chat, Retrieval-Augmented Generation (RAG), AI agents, and financial operations management. Key features include real-time voice interaction capture and transcription, as well as custom generative AI solutions for corporate chat, digital assistants, and customer-facing AI bots. Jeen.ai serves a range of industries, including finance, technology, government, and defense, and is trusted by leading enterprises that prioritize security and performance.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/f5b9582c-4dc2-44ca-869b-91a6491f2000.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', null, null, null), ('2575', 'Sustainable Energy', 'Sustainable Energy Ltd', 'https://www.sustainable-energy.co.uk', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/sustainable-energy-ltd', 'Sustainable Energy Ltd is a UK-based engineering and consulting firm that has been operating since 1998. The company specializes in renewable, low-carbon, decentralized energy systems and district heat networks. With a team of engineers, designers, project managers, and finance experts, it provides independent advice and support throughout the project lifecycle, focusing on feasibility studies, design, implementation, and management of renewable energy projects.The firm has successfully completed over 300 renewable heating projects, delivering more than 100MW of biomass, heat pump, and solar capacity in the UK. It has also developed over 50MW of electrical capacity from biomass power and biogas CHP. Sustainable Energy Ltd is known for its involvement in high-profile district heating networks and innovative projects, including an on-site wind turbine and a solar PV farm. The company emphasizes practical, cost-effective solutions tailored to the needs of public sector clients and large utility companies.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/4fbbb77c-a569-4f58-bfd2-465dcec2f06b.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', null, null, null), ('2576', 'Air Aware Labs', 'Air Aware Labs Ltd', 'https://www.airawarelabs.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/airawarelabs', 'Air Aware Labs is a London-based technology startup founded in 2024. The company focuses on providing personalized air quality insights using artificial intelligence and real-time data. Their mission is to make clean air accessible and to enhance public awareness of air pollution''s health impacts.The flagship product, AirTrack, launched in April 2025, offers real-time air pollution modeling and personalized exposure data based on user location and activity. It features route optimization to identify high-exposure areas and integrates with fitness platforms like Strava and Apple Health. Additionally, AirTrack Enterprise provides organizations with insights into employee air pollution exposure as part of wellness programs.Air Aware Labs has quickly gained traction, reaching 1,000 users within its first year without advertising. The company collaborates with notable partners, including Google for Startups and the World Economic Forum''s Clean Breath Alliance, to further its mission of improving air quality awareness and health outcomes.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/29c70d5e-ee14-42e6-953a-84aea07969dd.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', null, null, null), ('2577', 'Lumivero', 'Lumivero UK Limited', 'https://lumivero.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/lumivero', 'Lumivero is a software company based in Denver, Colorado, founded in 1995. It specializes in data analysis, management, and collaboration tools, utilizing expert methodologies and AI-powered workflows. The company helps professionals gain insights from various data types, including qualitative, quantitative, and unstructured data, supporting research, decision-making, and experiential learning. Lumivero operates globally, with offices in Australia and Europe, and employs around 270 people, generating approximately $65.8 million in revenue.The company offers a range of software solutions tailored for academic and business professionals. Key products include NVivo, a leading qualitative analysis software; @RISK and DecisionTools Suite for risk management and decision-making; XLSTAT for advanced statistical analysis in Excel; and AI-powered reference management tools. Additionally, Lumivero provides experiential learning software that streamlines student placements and enhances program success. Its tools facilitate data organization, analysis, and collaboration, making them valuable across various sectors, including academia, healthcare, and financial services.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '3', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/c4fd0bf2-8daa-4e2d-9682-0fd5f6e468a9.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', 'lever', 'lumivero', null), ('2578', 'Nevis', 'NEVIS WEALTH TECHNOLOGY LTD', 'https://www.neviswealth.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/neviswealth', 'Nevis is an AI platform based in New York City, focused on wealth management. Founded by former Revolut executives, the company aims to automate operational workflows for Registered Investment Advisors (RIAs) and wealth management firms. Nevis emerged from stealth in late 2025, securing $40 million in funding, including a $5 million seed round and a $35 million Series A led by Sequoia Capital.The platform is designed to streamline administrative tasks, allowing advisors to concentrate on client service and business growth. Nevis integrates data from various systems into a unified AI-powered operating system, automating processes such as meeting preparation, task generation, and client onboarding. It supports RIAs managing over $50 billion in client assets and is gaining traction among wealth management firms, enhancing productivity and client experiences.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '9', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/81e16707-9ed2-4d9f-9719-601d2e5ee1ca.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', null, null, null), ('2579', 'AlbR Capital', 'ALBR CAPITAL LTD', 'https://albrcapital.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/albr-capital-limited', 'Further to the announcement of 1 July 2025, we are delighted to announce that Peterhouse Capital Limited ("Peterhouse") and AlbR Capital Limited ("AlbR") have combined their Capital Markets business under the new name of AlbR Capital Limited ("AlbR") effective from 1 October 2025. The teams from Peterhouse and AlbR are excited about the resources that the business will have and the services it is able to offer, bringing together each Firm''s Corporate Finance/Advisory and Corporate Broking businesses, along with AlbR''s Private Growth Capital team.  AlbR is located at 80 Cheapside, London EC2V 6EE.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/4411e166-bd77-4815-9750-fb7fc9288612.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', null, null, null), ('2580', 'Ann Squared Events', 'ANN SQUARED LTD', 'https://weareannsquared.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/ann-squared', 'Ann Squared Events is a full-service events and experiential agency based in the UK, established in 2016. The agency specializes in event creation, production, management, and staffing, focusing on delivering detailed experiences for brands and agencies. Headquartered in London, Ann Squared operates as ANN Squared Ltd and provides both discreet, white-label support and comprehensive end-to-end solutions to ease the pressures of event organization.The agency offers a range of services tailored to meet the needs of clients in creative, communications, PR, and field services sectors. Their offerings include custom roadshows, exhibitions, and experiential events, along with full event management and staffing solutions. Ann Squared Staffing provides access to a vetted pool of trusted staff across London and the South West, ensuring flexible shifts and dedicated support for logistics and communications. With a commitment to client success, Ann Squared positions itself as a reliable partner that prioritizes attention to detail and competitive pricing.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/f27d1036-c93d-4106-a2c5-051279fd43f6.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', 'bamboohr', 'ann', null), ('2581', 'Apollo Global Management, Inc.', 'Apollo Enterprise Strategies UK Ltd', 'https://www.apollo.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/apollo-global-management-inc', 'Apollo Global Management, Inc. is a prominent global alternative asset manager based in New York City. Founded in 1990 by former executives of Drexel Burnham Lambert, the firm manages over $188 billion in assets and employs more than 2,900 people across North America, Europe, and Asia. Apollo focuses on generating risk-adjusted returns through innovative capital solutions for both institutions and individuals.The company offers a range of services in alternative asset management, including private equity, credit, real estate, and retirement solutions. Its private equity division engages in leveraged buyouts and distressed investments, while its credit services include middle-market direct lending and high-yield portfolios. Apollo also invests in commercial real estate and provides insurance and retirement solutions through its subsidiary, Athene. The firm serves a diverse clientele, including institutional investors and high-net-worth individuals, and supports over 190 portfolio companies across various sectors.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/a3eb6a5a-0d68-4240-a874-776ed6923770.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', 'workday', 'Apollo_Careers', null), ('2582', 'AUTODOC', 'Autodoc Operations UK Limited', 'https://autodoc.group/en/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/autodoc', 'AUTODOC is Europe''s largest digital platform in the automotive aftermarket, founded in 2008 in Berlin. The company has established itself as a significant e-commerce player, generating €1,555 million in revenue in 2024. With around 6,000 employees from 52 nationalities, AUTODOC operates in 27 European countries and processes approximately 50,000 orders daily.The company offers a vast catalog of automotive parts and accessories, featuring 6.7 million products from 2,500 brand manufacturers. It supports 85,000 model configurations across various vehicle types, including cars, trucks, and motorbikes. AUTODOC also provides extensive customer support in 23 languages, along with over 20,700 PDF car repair guides and 4,300 car repair tutorials on YouTube. The company operates a hybrid B2B and B2C model, focusing on building long-term relationships with suppliers and ensuring high accessibility for customers.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/83207d23-f7b4-4e35-be7d-c6896e201635.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', null, null, null), ('2583', 'Cosine', 'Buildt AI Limited t/a Cosine', 'https://cosine.sh', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/cosine-ai', 'Cosine is a San Francisco-based AI company founded in 2022, originally known as Buildt. The company develops agentic AI software engineering tools designed to automate and enhance software development workflows. Its main product, Genie, is an AI model that utilizes human reasoning to assist with various coding tasks, including code generation, refactoring, bug fixing, and security improvements.Cosine specializes in multi-agent reasoning systems that facilitate asynchronous collaboration and task management across popular project management tools like Jira, Trello, and GitHub. The company benchmarks its technology using SWE-Lancer, demonstrating strong performance in real-world development tasks. Cosine focuses on delivering security-compliant code fixes, analyzing legacy repositories, and providing auto-generated documentation, all aimed at improving developer productivity and project efficiency.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '4', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/7cfcd85a-f916-4a4d-a58b-ba898c9df7ef.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', 'ashby', 'https://api.ashbyhq.com/posting-api/job-board/cosine', null), ('2584', 'Contec, Inc.', 'CONTEC CLEANROOM (UK) LIMITED', 'https://emea.contecinc.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/contecinc', 'Contec, Inc. is a prominent manufacturer of contamination control products, specializing in critical cleaning solutions for cleanroom and manufacturing environments. Founded in 1988 in Spartanburg, South Carolina, the company quickly transitioned from distribution to manufacturing, launching its first presaturated wipes, PROSAT®, in 1992. Over the years, Contec has expanded its operations globally, with facilities in Spartanburg and Suzhou, China, and has established partnerships worldwide.The company offers a wide range of products, including knitted, woven, and nonwoven wipes, disinfectants, mops, and custom cleaning solutions. Contec serves various industries, such as pharmaceuticals, biotechnology, healthcare, and aerospace, providing essential tools for maintaining cleanliness and compliance in critical applications. With a focus on innovation and customer needs, Contec is dedicated to delivering high-quality solutions backed by technical support and a robust supply chain.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/8baf8529-c792-4f3d-82f9-040804e204f4.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', 'greenhouse', 'emea', null), ('2585', 'Danske Commodities', 'Danske Commodities UK Limited', 'https://danskecommodities.com/united-kingdom', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/danske-commodities', 'Danske Commodities is a Danish energy trading company founded in 2004, specializing in power, gas, and renewables trading across over 40 markets worldwide. Headquartered in Aarhus, Denmark, with an office in Stamford, Connecticut, the company manages more than 12,000 MW of renewable energy and operates a 24/7 trading setup with around 600 employees, most of whom hold advanced degrees. Danske Commodities focuses on short-term trading to facilitate the energy transition and enhance the market presence of renewables.The company has a rich history, starting with electricity trading between Germany and Denmark and expanding into various energy sectors, including intraday power trading and gas trading. Backed by Equinor, Danske Commodities employs innovative technology, such as algorithmic trading, to optimize its operations. Its strategies aim to lead in renewables and flexibility trading while providing comprehensive risk management across various domains. The company reported strong financial performance in 2024, with a gross turnover of €19.5 billion, driven by its robust trading activities.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/1468c500-4fbd-472e-adc4-b907ba69eed7.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', null, null, null), ('2586', 'HENGE', 'Henge UK Ltd', 'https://www.henge07.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/henge-official', 'Henge is an Italian luxury furniture and design brand founded in 2011 by Paolo Tormena in the Veneto region. The company specializes in handcrafted furniture, lighting, home accessories, kitchens, and fragrances, using rare materials such as Breccia Medicea dell’Acqua Santa marble, petrified wood, and volcanic stone. Henge focuses on creating "objects with a soul," blending meticulous material research with innovative craftsmanship to enhance everyday spaces.The brand collaborates with local Italian workshops and renowned designers, employing advanced technologies to transform natural materials. Henge''s product range includes high-end furniture like sofas, tables, and cabinetry, as well as refined lighting and home accents. Their H-Fragrance collection draws inspiration from craftsmanship and nature. Henge operates globally, with flagship showrooms in 70 countries, including a new location in Dubai, and offers bespoke interior solutions through projects like "Unwritten Streets."', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/f7eb4333-4452-46c5-8d74-790cb615f63d.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', null, null, null), ('2587', 'J Goodwin & Co', 'J Goodwin & Co LLP', 'https://www.jgoodwinandco.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/j-goodwin-co-llp', 'J Goodwin & Co is an independent merchant bank focused on being Europe''s leading growth partner for the most significant players in the technology, media, and creative industries.Our mission is to create opportunities for our clients, providing them with expert advice, and investing alongside them, to nurture their growth and success.We leverage our unrivalled network, deep industry expertise and love for walking alongside the highest-performing entrepreneurs, to help shape our clients'' leadership of their relevant sector.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/a78fbd4d-c109-4393-83b3-838a18cd4d44.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', null, null, null), ('2588', 'Medly AI', 'Medly AI Limited', 'https://www.medlyai.com/uk', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/medly-ai', 'Medly AI is an EdTech startup founded by two doctors who transitioned from the NHS to enhance access to personalized education. Established on September 1, 2023, and based in London, Medly focuses on addressing the achievement gap in traditional education systems through innovative educational support services.The company offers AI-powered tutoring platforms tailored for both the UK and US markets. In the UK, Medly provides personalized tutoring for GCSE, A-Level, and IB subjects, featuring modes for learning, practice, and exam preparation. For the US market, it offers SAT tutoring that adapts to individual learning styles, complete with strategy instruction and progress visualization. Medly''s platform utilizes advanced AI technology and proven teaching methods to deliver personalized learning experiences, ensuring students receive instant feedback and support tailored to their needs.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/06221252-a086-4e7b-bbb2-f9d4f48610ff.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', null, null, null), ('2589', 'OpenTrade', 'Open Trade Technology Ltd', 'https://www.opentrade.io/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/opentrade-io', 'OpenTrade is a fintech company based in Altrincham, United Kingdom, founded in 2023. It offers an institutional-grade platform for real-world asset-backed stablecoin lending and yield products. The platform enables fintechs, Web2/Web3 companies, and institutional investors to provide white-labeled, embedded yield solutions supported by high-quality financial assets.The OpenTrade platform features a web application, a powerful API, and an EVM-compatible blockchain protocol. It connects blockchain-based assets like USDC and EURC with traditional banking infrastructure, delivering "yield-as-a-service" through secure structures. OpenTrade''s offerings include treasury management, bespoke yield products, and developer tools, all designed to enhance customer experiences and create new revenue streams. The company currently manages $47 million in assets and has processed nearly $200 million in transactions, with backing from notable investors such as a16z Crypto and Circle.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/466a0df1-19c0-4377-9ef5-56d25edb07f1.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', null, null, null), ('2590', 'Peer Group plc', 'Peer Group PLC', 'https://peergroup.co.uk', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/peer-group-plc', 'Peer Group is a private limited company specialising in commercial and residential real estate. It owns and manages a wide-ranging portfolio in the office, retail, industrial and residential sectors.Operating under the Chairmanship of Martin Birrane, during the last four decades, has built a portfolio of UK property which it manages in-house.The Group''s strategy is to secure growth through the considered asset management of the existing portfolio and the acquisition of carefully chosen investment and development opportunities.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/109f1958-dec0-4815-b3c4-80c4f9b6ea65.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', null, null, null), ('2591', 'SEFE', 'SEFE Marketing & Trading Limited', 'https://www.sefe.eu/en/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/sefemt', 'SEFE Marketing & Trading Ltd is an international energy company based in the United Kingdom, specializing in the trading, sales, transport, and storage of gas, power, and renewable energy products. Established in 1999 and headquartered in London, SEFE is owned by the Federal Government of Germany and has grown into a significant player in the European energy market.The company sells around 200 terawatt hours of gas and power annually, serving the energy needs of over 11 million German households. SEFE controls approximately 25% of Germany''s total gas storage capacity and employs a workforce of around 500 to 2,000 people globally. Its operations encompass the origination and trading of energy products, sales to a diverse customer base, and the provision of infrastructure and services in gas, power, hydrogen, and clean energy. SEFE is committed to supporting the transition to a low-carbon future through investments in renewable electricity and low-carbon gases.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/4b62d914-ed2c-43bf-a54b-b62611ef55e4.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', null, null, null), ('2592', 'The Big House', 'The Big House Theatre Company', 'https://thebighouse.uk.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/the-big-house-theatre-company', 'The Big House is a charity working with care leavers and at risk young people using drama. We stage high profile theatre and film productions.The Lie - 19th November - 6th December - Get your tickets now! http://bit.ly/3WCNEAR"I''ve seen quite a lot of this sort of work with young people, but rarely anything so passionately or so brilliantly acted, and even more rarely so beautifully staged" Michael Coveney on PHOENIX.What''s On Stage"Visceral storytelling. Shot through with moments of pure theatre, graced with vivid, moving performances by an excellent young cast. A stirring opening statement from this exciting new theatre company." Jez Butterworth (Writer of Jerusalem and Mojo)The Rt.Hon Jeremy Corbyn MP said "Within all of us there is a poem, within all of us there is a painting, within all of us there is a novel, within all of us there is a real expression of what we want to see of the world. And what The Big House does is open it up and bring it out. It''s wonderful." In 2014 The Big House won the Born To Be Award from the Centre for Social Justice in recognition of their impact - helping young people fulfil their potential.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/b246211a-4c31-4a96-986b-931a85aee575.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', null, null, null), ('2593', 'Urban Green', 'Urban Green Space Ltd T/A Urban Green', 'https://weareurbangreen.co.uk', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/weareurbangreen', 'Urban Green is a multidisciplinary design and environmental consultancy based in Manchester, established in 2010. The company specializes in landscape architecture, urban design, landscape planning, biodiversity net gain, and arboriculture. With a team of 40 to 74 specialists, Urban Green works on projects throughout the UK, focusing on creating positive impacts on people, places, and the environment.The firm adopts an integrated approach, collaborating closely with clients from the initial planning stages to project delivery. Urban Green''s services include innovative designs for public spaces, schools, residential developments, and infrastructure projects. Their expertise also extends to ecology and tree management, ensuring comprehensive support for environmental enhancement strategies. The team is led by experienced professionals with backgrounds in various sectors, contributing to the firm''s commitment to delivering optimal solutions.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/e6691417-f5b6-4172-85b6-ef54fea9a0c3.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', 'bamboohr', 'urban', null), ('2595', 'Wonder Studios', 'Rabbit Hole Labs Limited', 'https://wonderstudios.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/wearewonderstudios', 'Wonder Studios is a London-based creative studio founded in 2025 that utilizes AI technology and a global network of talent to produce films, advertising, and original content efficiently. Co-founded by CEO Xavier Collins and Chief Creative Officer Justin Hackney, the studio combines extensive experience in film and advertising with innovative AI workflows. Recently, it raised $12 million in funding to enhance AI-driven production capabilities.The studio operates as a two-sided agency, offering services that include commercials, music videos, documentaries, and indie features, all produced with a focus on cinematic quality and cost-effectiveness. Wonder Studios also develops original intellectual property, such as anthology films and animated adaptations, while emphasizing a hybrid approach that integrates human creativity with AI efficiency. The Wonder App serves as a talent marketplace, connecting emerging creatives with brands and fostering grassroots storytelling.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '1', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/2f72db21-5da9-4e0b-9e64-868ff77bbd32.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', 'greenhouse', 'wonderstudios', null), ('2596', 'Wonder', 'Wonder London Limited', 'https://wearewonder.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/wonder-london', 'Wonder is a global B2B and B2E events agency based in London. The agency specializes in creating innovative business experiences that connect brands with their audiences through audience-first strategies. Wonder operates worldwide, focusing on humanizing corporate events and challenging