8ea59.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', null, null, null), ('2598', 'Antare', 'Antare Technology Limited', 'https://antare.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/antare-technology', 'The team founded Antare in 2024 comprising product designers and engineers - some of whom have worked together for over 15 years. Together, the companies we have built have been collectively acquired for billions of dollars: we have a genuine level of success under our belts that you could help to contribute to. Today, we’re a small, hands-on team spanning product design, finance, hardware, and software engineering.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '4', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/969ad34e-8923-4b0f-ab76-824641907ca5.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', 'teamtailor', 'antaretechnology', null), ('2599', 'Crosure Inc.', 'Crosure Limited', 'https://crosure.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/crosure-uk', 'Crosure is a provider of digital insurance solutions to the global insurance industry. Delivered as Software as a Service, Crosure''s range of digitalization solutions is designed to help our clients to transform their businesses and accelerate their growth by extending their reach to new personal and commercial customers via innovative technology, efficient distribution, and lower costs', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/2dd6aa56-51bf-4236-9454-7796306345d7.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', null, null, null), ('2600', 'Finimize', 'Finimize Limited', 'https://finimize.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/finimize', 'Finimize is a London-based financial media and education company founded in 2016 by Max Rofagha and Scott Tindle. The company aims to democratize financial information by providing jargon-free content tailored for modern investors, particularly millennials. With a community of over 1 million members, Finimize offers a daily newsletter that delivers a concise, 3-minute digest of global finance news.The company also features a mobile app that serves as a community-driven platform for financial insights, analysis, and investment education. In addition to its core offerings, Finimize hosts events like the Modern Investor Summit, featuring industry leaders. The Finimize for Business service helps financial firms engage with modern investors through customized content and communication strategies. Finimize has partnered with over 300 brands, including notable firms like BlackRock and CFA, showcasing its commitment to enhancing client engagement in the financial sector.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/f15e7b05-6c3a-49c5-9acb-4095c1cdbd49.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', null, null, null), ('2601', 'Guildmore', 'Guildmore Ltd', 'https://guildmore.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/guildmore-ltd-', 'Guildmore Ltd is a family-owned main contractor based in the UK, established in 1998. With over 130 employees and an annual turnover exceeding £80 million, the company operates nationwide, focusing on construction, cladding remediation, decarbonisation, and planned property improvements. Guildmore has dedicated offices in Leicester and Manchester, with its headquarters in Bromley, Greater London.The company offers a range of services through its specialist business units, including new build developments, refurbishment projects, and cladding remediation. Guildmore is committed to sustainability, aiming for Net Zero by 2040, and emphasizes quality, reliability, and long-term partnerships in both public and private sectors. Under the leadership of Engin, Guildmore fosters a collaborative culture that prioritizes employee development and corporate responsibility, with a goal of achieving 70% of its turnover from repeat business.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/44497a8b-d81b-4c6e-bb7a-977fe500cea6.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', null, null, null), ('2602', 'Haskoning', 'Haskoning UK Ltd', 'https://www.haskoning.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/haskoning', 'Haskoning is an independent international engineering consultancy firm based in Amersfoort, Netherlands. With over 6,800 employees in more than 25 countries, the company focuses on providing engineering, design, consultancy, software, and technology solutions aimed at sustainable development. Founded in 1881, Haskoning has a rich history of involvement in civil engineering and has expanded its expertise to various sectors, including aviation, energy, infrastructure, and urban development.The firm is recognized for its world-leading capabilities in maritime and industrial projects, optimizing port facilities and providing solutions for manufacturers in sectors such as food and beverage, pharmaceuticals, and automotive. Haskoning is committed to addressing challenges related to energy transition, digitization, and climate change. It also develops digital solutions for asset design and predictive maintenance, with notable innovations like Kaumera, a bio-based resource derived from sludge treatment.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/d22dbe3f-6236-46df-8287-23931d3e3339.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', null, null, null), ('2603', 'Spinal', 'Spinal Technologies Limited', 'https://www.withspinal.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/withspinal', 'Spinal builds intelligent finance operations.Our AR agent automates your entire contract-to-cash cycle—reading contracts, generating invoices, and collecting payment.What used to take 20+ hours per week now happens automatically.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/0c9bea0e-bebc-464d-ae23-6ab9871ef6ec.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', null, null, null), ('2604', 'Brompton Technology', 'Brompton Technology Ltd', 'https://www.bromptontech.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/brompton-technology-limited', 'Brompton Technology Limited is a global leader in LED video processing, based in London, UK. Founded in 2011, the company designs and manufactures advanced video processing products tailored for live events and creative industries. With a dedicated team of around 75 employees, Brompton Technology has built a strong reputation as a reliable technology partner across various sectors.The company''s flagship product, the Tessera platform, is a cutting-edge LED processing system that supports some of the largest live events worldwide. Brompton Technology also offers free software updates, technical support, training, and consulting services, emphasizing a commitment to longevity and sustainability in their designs. Their technology is utilized in diverse applications, including live events, virtual production, broadcast, and corporate AV, serving notable clients like Taylor Swift and Ed Sheeran. In 2025, Brompton Technology was honored with a King''s Award for Enterprise for Innovation, recognizing its contributions to the industry.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/8d141033-5d33-4849-a7bf-773be8a3dbd9.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', null, null, null), ('2605', 'Camfil', 'Camfil Ltd', 'https://www.camfil.com/en-gb', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/camfil-india', 'For more than half a century, Camfil has been helping people breathe cleaner air. As a leading manufacturer of premium clean air solutions, we provide commercial and industrial systems for air filtration and air pollution control that improve worker and equipment productivity, minimize energy use, and benefit human health and the environment.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/327f2899-2752-430c-81bf-d74a58aab9fa.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', null, null, null), ('2606', 'Careberry', 'Careberry Software Ltd', 'https://www.careberry.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/careberrysoftware', 'Careberry is an all-in-one care management platform designed by a care provider to eliminate the need for multiple systems. Over 100 care managers and carers contributed to its development, and it was used to deliver more than 60,000 hours of care before being offered to others.Key features include rostering, recruitment, care planning, mileage, expenses, invoicing, automated timesheets and medication management. To help businesses go paperless, admins, carers, and families can upload documents, photos, and videos, which are securely stored in client or carer profiles. The platform is accessible to office teams, care managers, carers, clients, and their families through a web-based portal and mobile apps.One standout feature is Careberry''s integration with the NHS medicines database, automatically populating MAR charts and reducing errors. We also offer links for customers to manage recruitment directly through the platform or their own websites.Our platform uses advanced security, ensuring the same high level of protection across web and mobile apps. Users can customise security settings, while we monitor data security based on user behaviour, devices, and locations—protection that''s typically out of reach for small care companies.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/ee457ab8-e1f7-4a53-b427-65721e3325a2.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', null, null, null), ('2607', 'Coppice Lifestyle', 'Coppice Garden Centre Ltd', 'https://www.coppicegc.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/coppice-garden-centre-limited', 'Coppice Garden Centre is a retail and hospitality setting just outside Middleton near Tamworth and Sutton Coldfield. It is home to The Fig & Olive restaurant and bar, where diners can enjoy the sun-soaked terrace in the day and the warmth of the candlelights by night.Joined by Forage Food Hall, Coppice strives to provide inspiration for a different and refreshing way of life. With a focus on fresh food and all things in style, Coppice is the place to be when it comes to reinventing your home, garden and lifestyle.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/c9e8f43e-4ccb-4ca6-a1ba-4aca1096afa8.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', null, null, null), ('2608', 'Cyril Leonard', 'https://www.cyrilleonard.com/our-people/careers-opportunities/', 'https://www.cyrilleonard.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/cyril-leonard', 'We are market-leading professionals providing forward thinking, proactive real estate solutions since 1934.Our MissionTo create and enhance value for our Clients through our comprehensive knowledge base, creativity and intelligent execution.We are one of very few owner-led multidisciplinary surveying practices in central London. A firm that uniquely combines capital markets & leasing, project & building consultancy and property & asset management – providing Clients with outstanding advice and delivery in all the major markets, property sectors and transaction forms.This structure, coupled with our in-depth understanding of real estate fundamentals, allows us to deliver on our promises in order to meet the precise needs of our Clients. Above all, we are a discreet and trusted advisor that prioritises long-term Client relationships.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/a37aaa79-6b26-4695-8574-ee69ee5e7029.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', null, null, null), ('2609', 'Digital Travel Marketing Group (DTMG)', 'DIGITAL TRAVEL MARKETING GROUP LIMITED', 'https://www.digitaltravel.io', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/digital-travel-summit', 'Digital Travel Marketing Group (DTMG) is a technology company based in Liverpool, UK, focused on providing digital solutions for travel brands, particularly in the cruise and tourism sectors. The company develops a range of products, including travel apps, websites, and customer engagement tools, aimed at enhancing customer connections and loyalty. DTMG serves over 65 businesses globally, from large corporations to startups.Key offerings include engaging apps and websites designed for travel agents, cruise booking engines, and the CruiseAppy app, which helps both customers and agents sell more cruise holidays. DTMG also provides a fast search and booking platform tailored for the leisure travel industry. The company partners with various organizations to integrate top infrastructure and content, ensuring deep digital customer engagement. With a team experienced in travel, DTMG supports travel agencies, cruise specialists, and tourism projects effectively.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/6f9fdc22-45bb-4e3c-bc72-981f64e65f36.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', null, null, null), ('2610', 'Dye & Durham', 'Dye & Durham (UK) Limited', 'https://dyedurham.co.uk', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/dyedurham-uk', 'Dye & Durham UK is a leading provider of legal technology solutions for law firms in the United Kingdom. As part of Dye & Durham Limited, it specializes in cloud-based software and information services that streamline practice management, conveyancing due diligence, corporate services, and compliance. The company operates from London and is recognized as a Strategic Partner of the Law Society of England and Wales.The company offers a range of services, including its Unity® software for practice management, comprehensive property information services, and tools for corporate transactions. It also provides compliance solutions such as KYC/AML checks and identity verification. With a focus on operational efficiency and regulatory compliance, Dye & Durham UK serves over 60,000 clients globally, including more than 80 of the top 100 UK law firms.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/ef260fbe-df6a-4728-b63c-e7cc378e2340.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', null, null, null), ('2611', 'ROXFIT', 'ROXFIT LIMITED', 'https://www.roxfit.app', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/roxfitapp', 'ROXFIT is a UK-based fitness technology company that focuses on hybrid athletes, particularly those in the HYROX community. The company offers the ROXFIT app, which allows users to create, modify, complete, and track personalized multi-modal workouts. The app provides real-time data and insights, making it a valuable tool for training and competition.Founded by Ben Wilson and Joey Allott, ROXFIT operates as a hybrid fitness platform. The app features a workout creation library, real-time tracking and guidance on devices like Apple Watch and Garmin, and detailed post-session analytics. Users can access a variety of workout formats, set targets, and share their progress socially. The app has seen significant organic growth, with thousands of downloads shortly after its launch.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/4f6e8814-a9e3-4874-8fb2-24dd3c218866.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', null, null, null), ('2612', 'Sable Bio', 'SableBio Limited', 'https://sablebio.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/sable-bio', 'Sable Bio is a London-based biotechnology startup founded in 2023. The company develops an AI-powered platform that provides predictive safety insights for drug targets, focusing on toxicology to enhance drug discovery and reduce clinical trial failures. Sable Bio leverages advanced AI, large language models, and domain expertise to analyze various biomedical data sources, addressing challenges in drug development such as safety assessments and data overload.The core offering is the Sable Target Intelligence platform, which extracts signals from diverse data sources to deliver interpretable predictions and actionable recommendations on drug safety. This platform supports pharmaceutical companies, biotech firms, researchers, and drug discovery teams in evaluating drug target safety. Sable Bio generates revenue through subscriptions, licenses, and potentially consulting services, while actively seeking partnerships with other companies and academic institutions to further its mission.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/fff038ee-048f-4842-babc-ac51b621fb77.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', null, null, null), ('2613', 'Sponsicore', 'SPONSICORE LIMITED', 'https://sponsicore.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/sponsicore', 'We offer a comprehensive solution tailored for companies to efficiently maintain records and ensure compliance, from managing documentation to meeting regulatory requirements.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/f208722c-1fec-4cdd-a3c8-d63f9d12d961.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', null, null, null), ('2614', 'Your.Online', 'Your.online Cirrus', 'https://your.online', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/youronline', 'Your.Online is a decentralized operational growth engine that collaborates with entrepreneurs to build and scale online brands. It focuses on three key segments: Presence, Performance, and Trust. The company provides capital, expertise, and access to a global network to help accelerate growth while maintaining the founders'' local identity and autonomy.Operating under the umbrella of Your.World and supported by Strikwerda Investments, Your.Online fosters a founder-first ecosystem. It emphasizes long-term reinvestment and collaboration to create strong local brands. The platform connects online entrepreneurs and leading brands worldwide, boasting impressive metrics such as over 5 million products, 1.3 million customers, and €300 million in revenue. Your.Online is dedicated to identifying and supporting ambitious entrepreneurs, inviting them to explore partnership opportunities.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/8b158764-f4cc-4399-9c4f-566774a9d914.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', null, null, null), ('2615', 'Catalyst Event Production Services', 'Catalyst Event Production Services Limited', 'https://catalyst-eps.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/catalyst-event-production-services', 'Catalyst Event Production Services is a creative-led technical production company based in Perth, Scotland. Founded in 2004, it specializes in designing, producing, and delivering dynamic global events using innovative technology. The company operates from a 12,000 sq ft scenic workshop in Edinburgh, where it creates custom builds for exhibitions and scenic joinery.Catalyst offers comprehensive event production services, including design and technical production, full event management, and advanced audio-visual solutions. Their in-house design team crafts immersive experiences that integrate sound, video, lighting, and staging. The company also provides equipment hire and custom fabrication, ensuring tailored solutions for events of all sizes across the UK, Europe, and beyond. With a focus on client collaboration, Catalyst aims to exceed expectations and deliver unforgettable events.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/6e975067-3c8e-4f32-845d-063e7ce658eb.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', 'smartrecruiters', 'catalyst', null), ('2616', 'Compact Syngas Solutions', 'Compact Syngas Solutions Limited', 'https://www.syngas-solutions.co.uk', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/compact-syngas-solutions-limited', 'Compact Syngas Solutions supply modular gasification technology for the production of hydrogen, power, heat and carbon credits', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/d1a04cd5-6188-4f3f-bb87-6c5c359e0191.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', 'smartrecruiters', 'compact', null), ('2617', 'Odfjell Drilling', 'Deep Sea Rig (UK) Ltd', 'https://www.odfjelldrilling.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/odfjell-drilling', 'Odfjell Drilling is a prominent offshore drilling services provider, established in 1973 and headquartered in Aberdeen, United Kingdom. The company specializes in harsh environment and deepwater operations, boasting a modern fleet of semi-submersible rigs. With roots tracing back to 1914, Odfjell Drilling has evolved significantly, marking its 50th anniversary in 2023 and showcasing advancements from the first Norwegian-built drilling rig to advanced 6th-generation rigs.The company offers a range of services, including mobile offshore drilling units for exploration, production, and platform drilling. Odfjell Well Services provides well intervention and tubular running services across various regions, including Europe and the Middle East. Odfjell Drilling is committed to sustainability, focusing on energy-efficient operations and zero-emission drilling, while also investing in technology and automation to enhance operational efficiency. With a workforce of over 1,600 employees, Odfjell Drilling emphasizes a strong culture of quality, health, safety, security, and environmental stewardship.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/3fa3ce47-50d3-4756-a1fd-38f86aa84946.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', null, null, null), ('2618', 'dmg events', 'Dmg Events (UK) Limited', 'https://www.dmgevents.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/dmgevents', 'dmg events is a global exhibition and publishing company based in Dubai, UAE, established in 1989. The company organizes 80 to 95 large-scale face-to-face events each year across various industries, including energy, construction, hospitality, interiors, food, mining, transport, coatings, and trade. With a strong focus on in-person events, dmg events attracts over 425,000 visitors annually and operates 10 to 13 offices worldwide, including locations in Saudi Arabia, Egypt, South Africa, the UK, Canada, Singapore, and India.The company specializes in B2B exhibitions, conferences, and publishing, offering services that enhance networking, business matching, and learning opportunities. Their portfolio includes notable events such as The Big 5 for construction, ADIPEC for energy, and The Hotel Show for hospitality. dmg events emphasizes adapting flagship events to new regions and integrating physical and digital platforms to support growth in both emerging and mature markets.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '2', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/243e6127-61b2-4f82-8306-a6efeb2242de.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', 'greenhouse', 'dmgevents', null), ('2619', 'DRIVE Represents', 'Drive Represents Limited', 'https://www.driverepresents.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/driverepresents', 'DRIVE is a future-thinking agency with community, connection, true representation and power at its core. Founded by Sofie Geradin, DRIVE represents a cherry-picked list of leading stylists, creative consultants and casting directors working with brands in the luxury fashion arena. Having been immersed in the fashion and creative industries for over 15 years, through DRIVE, Geradin builds mutual, meaningful and personal relationships with artists who are driven by a shared passion to strive for visionary work and success.Committed to a hands on dialogue that''s creative, honest and inspiring, DRIVE fosters creativity and mentors both new and established talent, acting as a community within which its artists are able to grow and succeed, with long term milestones in mind.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/f9488afe-b618-4ae7-9ba3-8f9dabefc28e.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', null, null, null), ('2620', 'Edgewing', 'Edgewing Systems Limited', 'https://www.edgewing.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/edgewingltd', 'Edgewing is an international joint venture formed by BAE Systems, Leonardo, and Japan Aircraft Industrial Enhancement Co. Ltd. (JAIEC). Established on June 20, 2025, the company focuses on the design and development of a next-generation combat air system as part of the Global Combat Air Programme (GCAP). Headquartered in Reading, United Kingdom, Edgewing operates facilities in the UK, Italy, and Japan, promoting collaboration among its partner nations.The primary goal of Edgewing is to deliver a sixth-generation crewed fighter jet by 2035, with a product lifecycle extending beyond 2070. Each parent company holds an equal share, and the leadership is headed by Marco Zoff, the former managing director of Leonardo’s aircraft division. Edgewing emphasizes values such as trust, unity, and innovation to enhance national security and strategic partnerships with the UK, Italy, and Japan.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/7aec3476-413e-4b9c-9f49-004d5fb1b994.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', null, null, null), ('2621', 'IN8INITY', 'IN8INITY GLOBAL LIMITED', 'https://in8inity.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/infinity-infinity', 'In8inity — a global communication operator. We offer solutions in the areas of data storage and transmission, IP and classical telephony, Internet access, content delivery, colocation and other telecommunication services in several countries of the world.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/3c52ef03-1b03-4cf1-8b44-4993d35dd1b2.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', null, null, null), ('2622', 'loyalBe', 'LoyalBe Ltd', 'https://loyalbe.io', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/loyalbe', 'loyalBe is a Belfast-based company founded in 2017 that specializes in card-linked offers (CLO) within the commerce media sector. The company connects brands with shoppers through bank cards, enabling targeted marketing campaigns that offer cashback rewards both in-store and online. loyalBe operates a data-driven platform that enhances customer engagement and loyalty by leveraging payment data to drive repeat sales and minimize wasted ad spend.The company''s core offerings include a CLO platform that drives incremental revenue through precision targeting and personalized campaigns. It also provides custom rewards and loyalty programs for banks and FinTechs, as well as targeted marketing campaigns for retailers. With access to over 300 million potential customers through banking and FinTech partners, loyalBe supports customer acquisition and retention while delivering real-time insights and metrics to measure sales impact. The company has raised $1.48M in funding and continues to grow its presence in the financial services, retail, and restaurant tech sectors.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/067e46a9-5f8c-4922-98b7-7c7ab93abb35.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', null, null, null), ('2623', 'Norgine UK & Ireland', 'Norgine Pharmaceuticals Limited', 'https://norgine.co.uk', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/norgine-uk-ireland', 'Norgine is a prominent European specialist pharmaceutical company based in the Netherlands, with a history dating back to 1906. The company operates in 14 European countries, including the UK and Ireland, as well as Australia and New Zealand, employing over 1,300 people across various operational sites. Norgine has a fully integrated pharmaceutical infrastructure that allows it to acquire, develop, manufacture, and commercialize innovative products.The company focuses on gastroenterology and hepatology, with significant expertise in bowel preparation products. Norgine''s product portfolio includes MOVICOL®, a leading treatment for constipation in Europe, and PLENVU®, a unique bowel preparation product. In addition to pharmaceuticals, Norgine offers digital and analog services to support healthcare professionals and patients. Norgine Ventures, a complementary business, provides financing to innovative healthcare companies in Europe and the US. The company is dedicated to improving patient outcomes and enhancing healthcare systems through its innovative solutions.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/537a30ed-8c25-4caa-a218-88722939421e.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', 'smartrecruiters', 'norgine', null), ('2624', 'Novus Power', 'Novus Power Limited', 'https://www.novus-power.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/novus-poweruk', 'Novus Power is a UK-based company that specializes in grid connections and high voltage infrastructure for large-scale solar and battery energy storage projects. They focus on providing comprehensive turnkey solutions, emphasizing innovative designs and efficient project management.The company offers a range of services, including design, project management, procurement, and health and safety. Their expert team creates tailored designs to meet project requirements and oversees all aspects of delivery to ensure timely and cost-effective results. Novus Power prioritizes health and safety through strict protocols and continuous training, fostering safe working environments for their projects.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/7d74f515-357d-4693-9f3d-a541bdbd3204.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', 'smartrecruiters', 'novus', null), ('2625', 'Showcase', 'Showcase Group Limited', 'https://www.showcase.co', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/28171726/', 'We work with the world''s leading brands to bring our customers exclusive access to the luxury sample sales in London and nationwide.  We are also passionate supporters of young British talent and provide a platform for the brightest and the best to share the spotlight.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/ec3189de-edf3-4758-aec5-c11b6414ae2d.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', 'teamtailor', 'showcase', null), ('2626', 'Sina Medical Glass', 'SINA Medical Glass Ltd', 'https://sinamedicalglass.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/sinamedicalglass', 'Made in Britain. Designed for life.Sina Medical Glass specialises in precision-engineered borosilicate glass vials and cartridges for the world''s pharmaceutical industry. Based in St Helens, Great Britain, we combine engineering excellence with cutting-edge technology to deliver ISO- compliant quality and reliability.With Sustainability underpinning every step of our process, we deliver performance without compromise and without limits.Exhibiting at CPHI - Frankfurt 28th-30th October. Come and meet the team Stand 8.OC51', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/8354b59c-a0eb-4790-9595-874dd0ec884c.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', null, null, null), ('2627', 'Alpha & Omega Semiconductor', 'Alpha and Omega Semiconductor (UK) Limited', 'https://www.aosmd.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/alpha-&-omega-semiconductor', 'Alpha and Omega Semiconductor Limited (AOS) is a global supplier and developer of a wide range of power semiconductor devices. The company specializes in discrete power devices, wide bandgap power devices, power management integrated circuits (ICs), and modules. AOS integrates advanced semiconductor process technology and product design to create high-performance power management solutions.AOS offers a diverse portfolio of products, including Power MOSFETs, Silicon Carbide (SiC), Gallium Nitride (GaN), Insulated Gate Bipolar Transistors (IGBT), Intelligent Power Modules (IPM), and more. These products are designed for high-volume applications across various sectors, such as personal computers, data centers, automotive electronics, and consumer devices. The company operates with a focus on innovation and customer responsiveness, supported by its in-house wafer fabrication facility in Hillsboro, Oregon.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/1aa27f16-4fe7-4f80-bbc2-62ed517de046.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', 'smartrecruiters', 'alpha', null), ('2628', 'Atlas Holdings LLC', 'Atlas FRM (UK) Ltd', 'https://www.atlasholdingsllc.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/atlas-holdings-llc', 'Atlas Holdings LLC is a private equity firm based in Greenwich, Connecticut, founded in 2002 by Andrew Bursky and Tim Fazio. The firm specializes in controlling investments in manufacturing and distribution industries. It has grown significantly, now owning 30 companies that employ around 75,000 people across 1,200 facilities worldwide.Atlas focuses on acquiring companies that are facing financial or operational challenges. The firm employs a strategy that includes disciplined entry valuation and investing in sectors where it has expertise. Its diverse portfolio spans various industries, including automotive components, building materials, energy, and food processing. Notable companies in its portfolio include Bovis, De La Rue, and The ODP Corporation. Atlas has made significant acquisitions, including a recent $1 billion deal for The ODP Corporation, and reports annual revenue of $9.9 billion.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/2ec4f499-24da-4fca-bdb9-e7e48117edad.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', 'bamboohr', 'atlas', null), ('2629', 'BIP', 'BIP CONSULTING UK LIMITED', 'https://www.bip.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/bip-global', 'BIP is the international consultancy for the 21st century with over 5,000 consultants globally daring to make a difference.  Operating at the intersection of business and technology BIP design, develop, and deliver sustainable solutions at pace and scale creating greater value for your customers, employees, shareholders and society.   Real world, real work, and real value, that’s the BIP commitment on every transformation we do. We deliver good-sense, human-centred strategies, that produce the results. We understand the possibilities can seem endless. Challenges are complex, technology ever evolving, and business goals pressurised and diverse.  As a Certified B Corporation, we believe in conducting business for the greater good. We embrace all aspects of corporate social responsibility in a way that permeates everything we do, including not only the way we interact with our own people but with our various communities as well as the environment.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/220551c4-b2df-4349-8917-a4357364e198.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', null, null, null), ('2630', 'Boskalis', 'Boskalis Subsea Services Limited', 'https://boskalis.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/boskalis', 'Royal Boskalis Westminster N.V. is a prominent global provider of dredging, offshore contracting, and maritime services, based in Papendrecht, Netherlands. Established in 1910, the company has grown to operate in over 75 countries with a workforce of more than 8,000 employees and a fleet of over 300 vessels. Boskalis has played significant roles in major projects such as the Dutch Delta Works and the Hong Kong International Airport land reclamation.The company is organized into three main divisions: Dredging & Inland Infra, Offshore Energy, and Towage & Salvage. It offers a wide range of services, including port development, land reclamation, offshore installation, and heavy marine transportation. Boskalis serves a diverse clientele, including governments, port operators, oil companies, and international project developers, addressing key global trends such as trade growth, energy demand, and climate change through its integrated maritime solutions.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '12', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/15cc0d44-9e03-4c13-9aaf-d33074eb5378.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', 'smartrecruiters', 'boskalis', null), ('2631', 'Kinetic AI', 'Kinetic AI Limited', 'https://kineticai.co.uk/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/kinetic-ai-limited', 'KineticAI is building a team of AI specialists, roboticists, and computational designers while forging partnerships with architecture firms, developers, and research institutions.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/b28b95dc-32f3-4bc7-b539-0c1eb81e7a38.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', 'bamboohr', 'kinetic', null), ('2632', 'Ruuby', 'RUUBY LIMITED', 'https://ruuby.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/ruuby-limited', 'Ruuby is a digital beauty concierge platform founded in 2015 or 2016, headquartered in London, United Kingdom. The company connects users with professionally vetted beauty, spa, and wellness professionals for on-demand services delivered directly to homes, offices, hotels, or event locations. Ruuby operates across multiple regions, including the United Kingdom, United Arab Emirates, Switzerland, and the South of France.The core offering is an app that allows users to book a variety of beauty, spa, and wellness treatments from five-star providers. Services are available for private clients, corporate events, luxury hotels, and special occasions like weddings. Ruuby partners with top spas in London to provide access to spare appointments and extends its services through mobile professionals. The platform emphasizes convenience and high-quality treatments, making it a leading choice in the personal care industry.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/6604e0f5-356a-4b4f-ae99-338a56ebaf88.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', null, null, null), ('2633', 'ZITON A/S', 'Ziton Ltd', 'https://ziton.eu', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/ziton-a-s', 'ZITON A/S is a Danish company based in Horsens, specializing in operations and maintenance (O&M) services for the offshore wind industry since 2007. Originally founded as Dansk Bjergning og Bugsering A/S, the company rebranded in 2016 and has since become a leader in its field, operating a fleet of six dedicated jack-up vessels. ZITON has expanded its operations significantly, growing from one vessel to six through strategic acquisitions and financing.The company offers comprehensive turnkey O&M solutions for offshore wind farm owners and turbine manufacturers. Their services include major component exchanges, strategic planning to reduce O&M costs, and technician services. ZITON also provides tools and equipment for component replacements and specializes in decommissioning services with a focus on safety and environmental impact. With a strong presence in northern European waters, ZITON supports various ports and has established long-term partnerships with major industry players like Vestas, Siemens Gamesa Renewable Energy, Ørsted, and Vattenfall.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/e2863c94-1a55-4e55-b75d-a0cb9de8dc77.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', null, null, null), ('2634', 'Clear Treasury', 'Clear Treasury (UK Trading) Limited', 'https://www.cleartreasury.co.uk', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/clear-treasury', 'We remove the complexity of international payments. Our expertise brings you insight and stability in an uncertain financial environment.In a market as dynamic and unpredictable as foreign exchange, our aim is to help reduce that risk for our clients and partners.FX StrategyWe help protect your bottom line from unpredictability of currency markets using spot, forward contracts and structured products.PaymentsInternational Payments are a daily necessity for many business. We remove the complexity from the process using a combination of both our expertise and technology.IntegrationsOur services can be seamlessly integrated into your systems or product via our various APIs.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/324e1a86-8ee2-4d0d-8104-9c875336a62b.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', 'greenhouse', 'clear', null), ('2635', 'Geoquip Marine', 'Geoquip Marine Services PLC', 'https://www.geoquip-marine.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/geoquip-marine', 'Geoquip Marine is a leading company in offshore geotechnical site investigations, focusing on heave-compensated drilling, sampling, and in-situ testing for water depths up to 3,500 meters. Established in 2010-2011 and headquartered in Sankt Gallen, Switzerland, the company operates a large fleet of specialized geotechnical drilling vessels, providing reliable seabed data for various offshore projects globally.The company offers a range of services, including site investigations, geophysical surveys, and specialized drilling for shallow gas and deep-water mineral exploration. Geoquip Marine also develops advanced equipment, such as deep-water drill rigs and in-house testing systems. With a commitment to supporting marine geotechnical engineering, Geoquip Marine serves clients in offshore renewables, oil and gas, infrastructure, and scientific research, ensuring effective data acquisition and project planning across multiple regions.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/5a6e27d2-26c3-4571-9006-2f308a330091.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', null, null, null), ('2636', 'Kesmalea Therapeutics', 'Kesmalea Therapeutics Limited', 'https://kesmalea.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/kesmalea-therapeutics', 'Kesmalea Therapeutics is a biotechnology company based in London, founded in 2020. The company specializes in targeted protein degradation (TPD) therapeutics, focusing on developing novel treatments that address challenges associated with traditional bifunctional protein degraders. Using its proprietary SELFTAC® platform, Kesmalea transforms these degraders into small molecules, enhancing their effectiveness and ability to penetrate the central nervous system.The company is dedicated to in-house drug discovery in oncology and CNS disorders, aiming to create orally available, CNS-penetrant protein degraders for chronic diseases with unmet medical needs. Kesmalea has successfully raised significant funding, including £25 million in a Series A round co-led by Syncona Ltd and Oxford Science Enterprises. With a commitment to fostering a collaborative culture, Kesmalea Therapeutics is focused on advancing its innovative pipeline of therapeutics.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/ec0934c0-3158-4712-8eb0-21c00bbc9379.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', null, null, null), ('2637', 'Landis+Gyr', 'Landis+Gyr Metering Solutions Limited', 'https://www.landisgyr.eu', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/landis/', 'At Landis+Gyr, we create a greener tomorrow through leading smart metering, grid edge intelligence and smart infrastructure technology.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/5d8cca10-fafd-4e8e-bef0-61880558a845.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', null, null, null), ('2638', 'Nammos Restaurants', 'Nammos Mayfair Limited', 'https://www.nammos.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/nammos-world', 'Nammos is a luxury hospitality and lifestyle brand that began as a small fish tavern on Psarou beach in Mykonos in the mid-1960s. Founded by Kyriakos Angeletakis and his wife Eleni, it has transformed into a renowned global dining and resort destination. The company was officially established as Nammos World SARL in 2003 and is based in Monaco.Nammos is celebrated for its Mediterranean-inspired cuisine with Asian influences, featuring fresh seafood, premium sushi, and innovative cocktails. The Mykonos location offers a luxury beach club experience, complete with private cabanas, a shisha lounge, and a spa. Additionally, Nammos operates a luxury village with high-fashion boutiques and art galleries. The brand is expanding its hospitality offerings with plans for Nammos Hotel Mykonos and future resorts in the Maldives and Abu Dhabi. With locations in Dubai, Cannes, Limassol, and Qatar, Nammos caters to high-net-worth individuals seeking exclusive culinary and lifestyle experiences.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/03a486cb-2bc6-40c9-8e86-316c40afeb05.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', null, null, null), ('2639', 'Natural Innovations', 'Natural Innovations Limited', 'https://naturalinnovations.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/naturalinnovations', 'Natural Innovations is a UK-based food manufacturer that specializes in bespoke, plant-led ingredients and menu solutions for global food brands. Founded in 2002 and rebranded from Freshcut Foods in 2025, the company is headquartered in Beeston, Nottingham. It focuses on transforming natural ingredients into high-quality, ready-to-eat products that prioritize bold flavors, health, and sustainability.The company develops custom plant-led ingredients, including chargrilled, roasted, and blanched vegetables, as well as carbohydrates and ready-to-eat meals. Natural Innovations emphasizes chef-led menu solutions that cater to foodservice, manufacturing, and recipe box providers. With a commitment to research and development, the company adapts to changing consumer demands, such as the rise of flexitarian diets. In 2023, Natural Innovations reported a turnover exceeding £42.4 million, reflecting its growth and market leadership in bespoke ingredients.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/91406800-16c7-46ce-a0b2-395b2511dfe2.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', null, null, null), ('2640', 'PeopleCert', 'PeopleCert UK Ltd', 'https://www.peoplecert.org', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/peoplecert-group', 'PeopleCert is a global leader in the assessment, certification, and accreditation of professional skills and language competencies. Founded in 2000 and headquartered in London, the company has grown from a Greek examination provider to a multinational organization, delivering millions of exams in over 200 countries. With a workforce of around 862-1,000 employees from 40 nationalities, PeopleCert generates approximately $147.9 million in annual revenue.The company offers a range of certifications and exams based on global standards, including ITIL® for IT service management, PRINCE2® for project management, and LANGUAGECERT® for language proficiency. PeopleCert also provides online proctored exams and assessment technology, supporting multiple languages and countries. Its services empower career advancement and organizational training, benefiting a significant number of Fortune 500 companies and government organizations worldwide.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/0cc5a76a-5e99-4096-a091-c7f1dbe286d7.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', 'bamboohr', 'peoplecert', null), ('2641', 'Walker Morris LLP', 'Walker Morris LLP', 'https://www.walkermorris.co.uk', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/walker-morris', 'Walker Morris LLP is a commercial law firm based in the UK, located in Leeds. Established in 1988, the firm specializes in providing strategic legal advice to a wide range of clients, including multinational companies, public and private entities, banks, financial institutions, SMEs, and high-profile individuals. With around 450 employees, Walker Morris emphasizes high-quality, partner-led services and fosters a collaborative culture.The firm offers expertise in various areas, including corporate law, finance, real estate, and dispute resolution. They handle mid-market corporate transactions, corporate financing, property finance, and contentious matters, with a focus on efficiency and alignment with client goals. Walker Morris has strong sector knowledge in areas such as retail, energy, technology, healthcare, and manufacturing, allowing them to effectively navigate commercial risks and drivers for their clients.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/60e539cc-dc6e-4586-b9a7-600da9e1829b.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', 'smartrecruiters', 'walker', null), ('2642', 'Act Build Change', 'Act Build Change Ltd', 'https://actbuildchange.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/actbuildchange', 'Act Build Change Ltd is a UK-based organization focused on training individuals and collectives to act collectively, build power, and drive transformative change. Founded in 2018 by Ricky Wong and Stephanie Wong, the company aims to make community organizing training more accessible, particularly for those facing oppression. It operates in the fields of information services and education.The organization offers training programs and support for collectives to enhance their skills in community organizing, group facilitation, and coaching. Act Build Change provides insights through stories and news on topics like solidarity and new curricula, such as "Everyone Can Organise." The team includes experienced professionals in social justice and project management, dedicated to fostering partnerships for a better future.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/f03bae08-c071-4a60-afda-7a13215eb8e9.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', 'lever', 'act', null), ('2643', 'Alaris Antennas', 'ALARIS THE RF TECHNOLOGY GROUP LTD', 'https://alaris.tech/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/alaris-antennas', 'Alaris Antennas is a South African company specializing in defense and security-focused antenna and RF technology. Founded in 1990, it transitioned from a consultancy to a manufacturing entity in 2002. The company is headquartered in Centurion, Gauteng, and operates as part of Alaris Holdings, which includes several subsidiaries across multiple countries.Alaris Antennas designs and manufactures a wide range of high-quality antennas and antenna systems that operate within the 9kHz to 18GHz frequency range. Their product offerings include log periodic dipole arrays, active array antennas, and customized RF and microwave electronics. The company also provides comprehensive in-house design and engineering services, including simulation design, CAD modeling, and antenna customization. Alaris Antennas serves various sectors, including defense, homeland security, and scientific communities, with a strong focus on custom-designed solutions that foster customer loyalty.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/5ed88deb-9f05-4f59-823a-96896908f83e.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', 'smartrecruiters', 'alaris', null), ('2644', 'BNVT Capital', 'BNVT Capital Ltd', 'https://bnvtcapital.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/bnvt-capital', 'BNVT Capital Ltd is a London-based global venture capital firm established in 2023. The company specializes in early-stage investments in AI-first and tech-driven startups that address systemic challenges such as energy, financial inclusion, and enterprise transformation. It operates as a private limited company and is registered with the UK Financial Conduct Authority.The firm has launched a $150 million debut fund aimed at supporting startups that tackle significant societal issues through technology and artificial intelligence. BNVT Capital''s leadership team includes experienced professionals based in London and Riyadh, enhancing its reach and expertise in the venture capital landscape.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/f937e92e-56fd-4dea-83c3-6c537261c10e.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', null, null, null), ('2645', 'CNBC', 'CNBC (UK) Limited', 'https://www.cnbc.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/cnbc', 'CNBC is a global business news media company owned by NBCUniversal, specializing in live television programming, digital content, and events focused on financial markets and economic news. Launched in 1989, CNBC has grown to reach over 450 million consumers worldwide each month, establishing itself as a leader in business news.The company offers 23 hours of live TV programming daily across the U.S., Europe, and Asia, featuring popular shows like *Squawk Box* and *American Greed*. CNBC operates international channels, including CNBC Europe and CNBC Asia, and provides 24/7 digital streaming services. It also hosts various business events and has partnerships for content exchange with organizations like Dow Jones. With a strong emphasis on delivering award-winning journalism, CNBC continues to impact viewers'' lives and finances through its comprehensive coverage and insights.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/08193348-1a0e-4261-aeee-507269a171b7.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', 'smartrecruiters', 'v1', null), ('2646', 'eEnergy', 'eEnergy Services UK Limited', 'https://www.eenergy.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/eenergyplc', 'eEnergy is a UK-based leader in B2B digital energy services, focusing on Energy-as-a-Service (EaaS) solutions. The company helps organizations achieve their Net Zero goals with zero upfront costs through funded projects in energy efficiency, generation, and management. eEnergy is listed on the London Stock Exchange under the ticker EAAS and has over a decade of experience in the industry.The company provides a comprehensive range of services, including LED lighting and controls, solar PV installations, EV charging infrastructure, and energy analytics through its MY ZeERO platform. eEnergy''s approach involves detailed audits, tailored proposals, phased implementation, and ongoing maintenance to ensure continuous improvement. It serves various sectors, including education, healthcare, public, and commercial & industrial, helping clients reduce energy waste, cut costs, and lower carbon emissions. With a commitment to making Net Zero achievable for all organizations, eEnergy is trusted by over 1,000 customers across the UK for their energy upgrades.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/32b19eb1-176a-4311-a4dc-83251ee727c5.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', 'teamtailor', 'eenergy', null), ('2647', 'Rivington Energy', 'Rivington Energy (Management) Limited', 'https://rivingtonenergy.co.uk', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/rivington-energy', 'A sustainable energy specialist developing and managing renewable energy solutions for UK residents and commercial clients.  Our in-house team of experts have delivered over 1GW of consented solar and battery projects.  Our core business pillars include: Project development; Commercial energy solutions; Project Management; Data Centres; and Ventures.  Rivington Energy is majority-owned by Federated Hermes Limited.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/9fdafaf3-a2af-4e37-9531-db4a66a3e708.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', null, null, null), ('2648', 'Ten Health & Fitness', 'TEN HEALTH HOLDINGS LIMITED', 'https://www.ten.co.uk/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/tenhealthfitness', 'Ten Health & Fitness is a boutique fitness and rehabilitation provider based in London, founded in 2007 by Joanne Mathews. The company specializes in holistic services, including Dynamic Reformer Pilates, physiotherapy, personal training, and massage therapy. With a focus on enhancing movement, strength, and overall well-being, Ten Health & Fitness operates 10 studios across London and employs over 160 staff.The company offers a range of services designed for all fitness levels, including group classes and one-on-one sessions. Their "Circle of Care" approach integrates rehabilitation and fitness, ensuring a supportive environment for clients. Additionally, Ten Health & Fitness provides educational programs for health professionals, offering courses in Pilates Reformer use and personal training. The brand is known for its welcoming atmosphere and commitment to helping clients achieve their fitness goals.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/abb86141-19bb-406b-9a01-e6695c184d63.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', 'breezy', 'ten', null), ('2649', 'Andersen Lab', 'ANDERSENLAB LTD', 'https://andersenlab.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/andersen-softwaredev', 'Andersen is a global software development company based in Krakow, Poland, with over 18 years of experience in digital transformation. Founded in 2007, Andersen has grown to employ more than 3,500 experts across over 16 locations worldwide, including development centers in the USA, UK, Germany, and several other countries. The company has successfully completed over 1,000 projects and is recognized among the world''s Top 1,000 B2B service providers.Andersen offers a wide range of end-to-end IT services, including custom software development, mobile app development, web development, API integration, legacy modernization, UI/UX design, cloud development, quality assurance, IT consulting, cybersecurity, and data analytics. The company serves various industries, such as financial services, healthcare, logistics, automotive, e-commerce, and public sector. Andersen is committed to client satisfaction and sustainability, promoting responsible practices in its operations.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/01dbb492-75b4-4ab2-bb06-8e37e19c57a4.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', 'breezy', 'andersen', null), ('2650', 'Blam Pictures', 'Blam Pictures Ltd', 'https://www.blampictures.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/blam-pictures', 'A multiple award-winning media production company specializes in CGI Animation, VFX and Motion Graphics intense projects.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/ffa9a35c-af66-4ee1-8d80-c8fa7e36a399.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', null, null, null), ('2651', 'Brexa International', 'Brexa International Limited', 'https://brexa-international.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/brexa-international', 'Brexa International, acquired by Bain Capital in 2024, consists of group of companies operating in the staffing, recruitment, HR services, BPO outsourcing, and debt management industries serving a diverse set of customer sectors. Revenues of 3bn euro, 65,000 employees, and operating across Europe, Latin America, and Oceania.Some of our larger companies and brands are:OTTO Workforce (Netherlands & Poland), CPL Group (Ireland & UK), Orizon (Germany), CDER (UK), Liberata (UK), Jobs In Time Medical (Germany), GrupoExpro (Chile, Peru and Colombia), Bluefin Resources (Australia), HOBAN (Australia), Kinetic (New Zealand), and many more.Brexa International is part of Brexa Holdings Inc (www.brexa.com), formerly known as Outsourcing Inc, a global staffing and recruitment group with headquarters in Japan.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/4188f133-df8a-45d1-9898-b54a6bc2249f.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', null, null, null), ('2652', 'Cake Industries', 'Cake Industries Ltd', 'https://cakeindustries.co.uk', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/cakeindustries', 'Cake Industries Ltd is a London-based design, engineering, and fabrication firm that specializes in creating high-quality, custom-made objects. Founded in 2012, the company offers a range of services including design, structural engineering, fabrication, and installation. Their portfolio features sculptures, staircases, bridges, furniture, cabinetry, and small buildings or pavilions.The team at Cake Industries is composed of skilled craftspeople, designers, makers, engineers, and installers. They work closely with architects, artists, private clients, and corporations to deliver bespoke items using premium materials. The firm is committed to quality and excellence in all their projects, serving clients across the UK and Europe.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/aaa655ad-1002-441d-8cc9-3aaf68a94390.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', null, null, null), ('2653', 'Clinical Outcomes Solutions', 'Clinical Outcomes Solutions Limited', 'https://www.clinoutsolutions.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/clinoutsolutions', 'Clinical Outcomes Solutions (COS) is a global consultancy founded in 2013, focusing on patient-centered research and strategic consulting in Clinical Outcome Assessments (COA). The company aims to integrate the patient voice into drug development for pharmaceutical and biotechnology sponsors. COS provides comprehensive support across all aspects of COA research, helping clients make data-driven decisions that enhance patient care value in health economics and outcomes research.COS operates with a cross-functional Business Unit model, which includes dedicated units for Clinical Outcome Assessments, Quantitative Science, and Prospective Studies. This structure promotes specialization and innovation, allowing COS to deliver tailored, high-quality solutions throughout the drug development process. The company emphasizes regulatory compliance and employs advanced methodologies to capture patient perspectives effectively. COS has established itself as an industry leader through strong partnerships with top biopharma companies, clinicians, and policymakers, and it maintains offices in the UK and the US.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/e1bc4048-349c-4948-83de-d78a0824d097.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', null, null, null), ('2654', 'Cranswick', 'Cranswick PLC', 'https://cranswick.plc.uk', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/cranswick-country-foods-plc', 'Cranswick Country Foods PLC is a prominent food producer based in Hessle, United Kingdom. Established in 1975, the company has evolved from a single mill producing pig feed to one of the largest food producers in the UK. It operates as a public limited company and is known for its diverse range of high-quality food products.The company manufactures fresh and processed meats, including pork and chicken, as well as gourmet items like premium sausages and artisan foods. Cranswick also offers convenience foods, ready-to-eat meals, olive oil, and pet food. With its own farming operations and milling facilities, Cranswick oversees the entire value chain from production to distribution. It serves grocery retailers, the food service industry, and other food producers, distributing products across the UK and internationally.Cranswick reported a revenue of £1.56 billion for the end of 2023, reflecting a 5.5% growth from the previous year. The company is committed to sustainably produced food and collaborates with artisan food experts to uphold traditional production methods.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/c6d10ee0-fcb3-48c0-8a22-50f39c0afb6c.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', null, null, null), ('2655', 'Creo Clinic', 'Creo Health Ltd', 'https://creoclinic.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/creo-clinic', 'The CREO Clinic is a specialised plastic surgery clinic, offering expert cosmetic procedures for exceptional results. Our core principles, expertise and transparency, are reflected in every aspect of our clinical direction. Starting with our surgeons, who have mastered their respective fields and operate with the utmost attention to our clients'' desires.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/373ba519-d2e6-47fb-88c0-6a5fa463146f.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', null, null, null), ('2656', 'Dalgety', 'Dalgety Ltd', 'https://dalgetyuk.co.uk', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/dalgety-ltd', 'Dalgety Limited is a UK-based private limited company that specializes in the cultivation and production of pharmaceutical-grade medical cannabis. Established on July 12, 2016, the company is committed to GMP-certified processes and emphasizes innovation in biochemistry and horticulture. Headquartered at East Midlands Airport in Derbyshire, Dalgety aims to transform medical cannabis into a trusted treatment option for patients globally, focusing on quality, transparency, and patient-first innovation.The company assembles a team of industry leaders and regulatory specialists to advance medical cannabis production using advanced technology. Its mission is to empower prescribers and improve patient outcomes while shaping the future of medical cannabis in the UK and beyond. Dalgety offers services that include regulatory strategy, facility construction and operation, and the supply of high-quality cannabis medicines, all while maintaining a commitment to transparency and patient care.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/f4a1943a-aa7a-4ddd-b14b-22475d645c56.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', null, null, null), ('2657', 'DISAUTHORITY', 'Disauthority Ltd', 'https://disauthority.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/disauthority', 'Run by passionate (borderline obsessive) people. Based in South London / Suite 6, Metropolitan House, 38-40 High St, CR0 1YB, CroydonAt DISAUTHORITY, we believe that passionate filmmakers with good ideas should be given the opportunity to see their project develop and reach wide audiences.And that''s where we come in. We break the wall between ideas and production and help emerging filmmakers take their projects to the screen – with the highest, industry-level standards.We champion every project that matters to us, from development to post-production. We strive for perfection in the visual and the creative and push for projects big or small that come through our doors to become world class.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/a33c9bd1-46c8-4b50-a473-01c5e8fb01c2.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', null, null, null), ('2658', 'genei', 'Genie Technology Limited', 'https://www.genei.io', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/genei', 'genei is an AI-powered summarization and research tool that helps users extract key insights from webpages, PDFs, and documents. The company is part of Y Combinator and has received recognition, including a prize in Oxford University''s "All Innovate" startup competition. The platform offers a range of features, including automatic summarization, keyword extraction, sentiment analysis, and document management. Users can store documents in customizable projects, cross-reference multiple resources, and take cloud-based notes. genei integrates with major cloud storage and productivity platforms like Google Drive, Dropbox, and Microsoft SharePoint. It operates on a flat-rate subscription model starting at £4.99 per month and serves a variety of customers, including freelancers, small businesses, and enterprises across industries such as research and healthcare. User satisfaction is high, with 95% of users reporting increased productivity and time savings. Customer support is available through email, FAQs, and a knowledge base.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/45fb1331-1ece-4d9c-b260-db71bc3652df.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', null, null, null), ('2659', 'Matthew Allchurch Architects (MAA)', 'Matthew Allchurch Architects Limited', 'https://www.maa-architects.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/matthew-allchurch-architects-limited', 'Matthew Allchurch Architects (MAA) is an architectural practice established in 2000, based in the Boathouse Design Studio, a Grade II listed building by the Thames at Teddington Lock. As a RIBA Chartered Practice and ISO 9001 accredited, MAA is dedicated to enhancing the built environment through a collaborative and supportive culture among its team of architectural professionals.The firm offers a range of tailored architectural services, including concept design and planning, technical design and tendering, and construction delivery. MAA works closely with clients to develop project briefs, coordinate planning applications, and ensure quality during construction. Their diverse project portfolio includes residential developments, co-living spaces, commercial and mixed-use buildings, industrial storage solutions, and hospitality projects.MAA is also a founding member of The Boathouse Design Studio, promoting collaboration among local businesses. The practice emphasizes universal design and sustainability, aiming to create environments that support wellbeing and community engagement.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/bd7b51b8-c631-4685-9142-6f8ff47cefff.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', null, null, null), ('2660', 'Semarion', 'Semarion Ltd', 'https://www.semarion.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/semarion', 'Semarion is a spin-out company from the Cambridge University Cavendish Laboratory, established in 2018. It specializes in microfabrication technology that integrates materials engineering with cell biology. The company focuses on innovating adherent cell assays to accelerate *in vitro* drug discovery, aiming to produce better data more quickly.The core offering of Semarion is the SemaCyte® platform, which includes mobile, barcoded microcarriers designed to enhance cell-based assays. These microcarriers support cell movement and can be integrated into existing workflows, improving flexibility and efficiency in drug screening processes. The platform features various components, such as the SemaCyte® Cell Assaying Microcarriers and the SemaCyte® Multiplexing Platform, which facilitate high-throughput screening and high-content imaging while maintaining cell morphology. Semarion''s technology is compatible with a range of cell lines and imaging techniques, making it a valuable asset in drug discovery workflows.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/c4be675f-683d-44c3-89ef-dc70cbc4b6d1.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', null, null, null), ('2661', 'SPAICE', 'SPAICE TECHNOLOGY LTD', 'https://www.spaice.tech', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/spaicetech', 'SPAICE is a technology company specializing in spatial-AI autonomy software for aircraft, drones, and satellites. Their software is designed to enable autonomous operations in complex 3D environments, addressing challenges in navigation, pose estimation, and environmental monitoring.The company is led by a skilled team, including CEO Matteo Cuccorese, who has a strong background in aerospace engineering and AI, and CTO Guillem Garrofé Montoliu, an expert in computer science and robotics. SPAICE is focused on innovation in spatial AI and is actively seeking talent to join their mission-driven team.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '4', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/f2c3e9d8-3242-43e0-96ad-5bd99c58c0e3.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', null, null, null), ('2662', 'THDP', 'The Hickson Design Partnership Limited', 'https://www.thdpdesign.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/thdp', 'THDP is a luxury interior design and architecture practice with locations in London and Milan. The firm specializes in high-end hospitality and residential projects across Europe and internationally. As a chartered RIBA practice and a member of SBID and NEWH, THDP takes a comprehensive 360° approach to design, from initial concepts to project completion. They create evocative designs that incorporate local culture and client visions for hotels, bars, restaurants, and spas.The company offers a wide range of services, including architecture, interior design, procurement, project management, and site supervision. Their architecture services cover feasibility studies, brand consultancy, and detailed building design. In interior design, they focus on space planning, design development, and the curation of furniture, fixtures, and equipment. THDP also manages public improvement programs and provides marketing materials design, ensuring a cohesive vision throughout each project. Their work emphasizes luxury interiors that reflect the essence of each property and its location.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/c5c9db02-1de7-4d10-86e4-dd65fc1f6abe.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', null, null, null), ('2663', 'Varkey Foundation', 'The Varkey Foundation', 'https://www.varkeyfoundation.org', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/varkeyfoundation', 'The Varkey Foundation is a global not-for-profit organization established in 2010 by Sunny Varkey. It aims to improve the quality of education by enhancing the status and skills of teachers worldwide, ensuring that every child has access to a good teacher. The foundation operates across all five continents, focusing on underprivileged children and underserved communities through policy advocacy, program implementation, and partnerships.Key initiatives include the Global Teacher Prize, which honors exceptional teachers with a $1 million award, and the Global Student Prize, recognizing innovative students. The foundation also hosts the Global Education and Skills Forum, an annual event for education policy discussions. It runs various teacher training programs, such as the Programa de Liderazgo e Innovación Educativa in Argentina, and has developed platforms like Comunidad Atenea to support teachers during challenges like COVID-19. The Varkey Foundation collaborates with organizations such as UNESCO, UNICEF, and the Clinton Global Initiative to further its mission.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/06d591a2-8a59-44a2-ba27-04fafadb763b.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', null, null, null), ('2665', 'tor&co', 'TORANDCO LIMITED', 'https://www.torandco.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/torandco', 'tor&co is a planning, design, and environmental consultancy located in Bournemouth, Dorset, with additional offices in London and Birmingham. Originally founded as Terence O''Rourke, the firm rebranded to tor&co in 2023 as part of its transition to an Employee Ownership Trust structure. Established in 1985, the company employs around 67 people and is led by a team of 10 directors with expertise in planning, architecture, and landscape architecture.The consultancy offers a wide range of services, including strategic planning advice, urban design for large-scale projects, integrated landscape architecture, heritage consultancy, environmental impact assessments, architectural design, and strategic communications. tor&co focuses on building long-term relationships with clients in both public and private sectors, employing an interdisciplinary approach to address various challenges with insight and foresight.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/e8f6313f-b32b-4847-b58a-52c0ef37087b.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', null, null, null), ('2666', 'WCM', 'WCM Europe Ltd', 'https://www.wcm.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/wcm-europe-ltd', 'WCM (World Class Manufacturing) is an engineering and manufacturing group specializing in automotive solutions for global brands. The company combines its engineering and manufacturing expertise to deliver comprehensive product development services. Its six divisions focus on creating innovative parts, assemblies, and systems tailored for the automotive market.WCM offers end-to-end solutions that emphasize rapid and efficient production. Their services include full-cycle product development and advanced manufacturing processes designed to support OEMs and Tier 1 suppliers. The company is committed to high-volume, high-quality output, ensuring that it meets the demands of the automotive industry effectively.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/b3685fd3-96e7-44f6-aa23-c52d5cdf7d7d.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', null, null, null), ('2667', 'Decagon', 'Decagon AI UK Ltd', 'https://decagon.ai', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/decagon-ai', 'Decagon is a San Francisco-based AI startup founded in 2023 by Jesse Zhang and Ashwin Sreenivas. The company specializes in generative AI agents designed for enterprise customer support and customer experience (CX) automation. With a team of around 100-200 employees, Decagon has raised approximately $200-231 million in funding, achieving unicorn status within 18 months.Decagon offers a cloud-based SaaS platform that enables businesses to build and scale conversational AI agents. These agents provide continuous support by automating tasks such as resolving support tickets, answering product inquiries, and managing subscriptions. The platform features context-aware responses, true omnichannel automation, and analytics tools that help enterprises enhance customer engagement and loyalty while reducing costs. Decagon''s technology is built on large language models and integrates seamlessly across various communication channels, making it a robust solution for modern customer experience challenges.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '10', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/cff218cb-62cf-4176-81ee-7441b175bd24.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', 'ashby', 'decagon', null), ('2668', 'Edgway', 'Edgway Limited', 'https://www.edgway.co.uk', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/edgway', 'Implementation Partners for Microsoft Power Platform Solutions and Copilot Studio.As a Microsoft Solutions Partner for business applications, we specialise in Power Platform and Copilot Studio, helping organisations achieve real business value through intelligent automation. We are a team of Power Platform experts dedicated to designing and delivering solutions that transform operations. By combining deep technical knowledge with a practical understanding of business needs, we help organisations work smarter, make faster decisions, and unlock the full potential of digital transformation.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/829c1abf-a2dc-44ca-80ae-1898f9aae964.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', null, null, null), ('2669', 'OpenInfo', 'Gold Mountain Labs Ltd', 'https://www.open-info.co.uk', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/open-info', 'OpenInfo builds AI and eCommerce solutions for food and drink wholesalers.Drive growth and deliver better customer service through one automated platform.Lightning-fast eCommerce. Automated manual order processing. Improved customer service. Dynamic supplier advertising. The trusted AI partner for food and drink wholesalers.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/1b8ec443-2de7-4c3d-9799-c911c74bf1e4.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', null, null, null), ('2670', 'Whisper', 'WHISPER FILMS LIMITED', 'https://whisper.tv', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/whispertv', 'Whisper is a UK-based production company that specializes in high-end sports broadcast production, unscripted entertainment, branded content, factual television, documentaries, esports, and live events. Founded in 2010, Whisper operates from offices in London, Cardiff, Manchester, and Auckland, employing over 200 team members. The company became part of Sony Pictures Television in February 2020 and has received recognition as a Broadcast Best Place to Work for multiple years.Whisper excels in various production services, including live sports coverage, documentary production, and quick-turnaround highlights. The company has produced notable content for major events such as Formula One, NFL, UEFA, and the Women''s EURO, which won a BAFTA. Whisper also creates entertainment programming, including game shows like Jeopardy! and Wheel of Fortune. The company partners with major broadcasters like BBC, ITV, and Amazon Prime, emphasizing a collaborative approach to delivering engaging and impactful content across multiple genres.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '2', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/9ae8dfe4-099e-4305-af1c-697d2b9719bc.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', 'bamboohr', 'thewhispergroup', null), ('2671', 'Zelt', 'Zelt Ltd', 'https://zelt.app', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/zelthq', 'Zelt is a UK-based HR technology company that offers an all-in-one people operations platform designed to streamline the employee lifecycle from onboarding to offboarding. The platform integrates HR, payroll, IT, and related functions, helping businesses reduce manual work and improve efficiency. Zelt''s user-friendly features include self-service options, drag-and-drop interfaces, and real-time data insights, supported by responsive customer service.The company provides four modular plans—People, Money, Tech, and Growth—each with Core and Pro tiers. Key offerings include HR management, payroll automation, time off and attendance tracking, and IT device management. Zelt also supports expense approvals, benefits management, recruitment tracking, and compliance automation. The platform is designed for fast-growing companies looking to unify their tech stacks and enhance the employee experience.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/5142b6e1-7609-4b25-b2cb-363138f10cc2.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', null, null, null), ('2672', 'Alcoa', 'Alcoa Services UK Limited', 'https://www.alcoa.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/alcoa', 'Alcoa is a global leader in bauxite, alumina, and aluminum products, with a rich history dating back to its founding in 1888. The company was established to commercialize the Hall–Héroult process, which made aluminum production more cost-effective. In 2016, Alcoa restructured into two independent corporations, with one continuing under the Alcoa name, focusing on mining and aluminum processing.Headquartered in Pittsburgh, Pennsylvania, and New York City, Alcoa operates in over 350 locations across 42 countries, employing approximately 129,000 people. The company offers a wide range of products, including aerospace and automotive components, packaging materials, aluminum forged wheels, cast products, and construction materials. Alcoa serves various industries such as aerospace, automotive, packaging, and building and construction, maintaining a strong presence in high-technology sectors and consumer goods.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '1', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/456b56d4-1fa5-4f09-b3fe-7431a65ecd91.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', 'workday', 'alcoa/Careers', null), ('2673', 'Alumni Ventures', 'ALUMNI VENTURES UK, LLP', 'https://alumniventures.co.uk', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/alumniventures', 'Alumni Ventures (AV) is a venture capital firm based in Manchester, New Hampshire, founded in 2014 by Mike Collins and Luke Antal. The firm focuses on democratizing access to venture investments for accredited individual investors and institutions, managing around $1.5 billion in assets. AV is recognized as America''s largest VC firm for individual investors, with a strong track record of over 1,600 investments across various sectors, including health, AI, and deep tech.AV operates with a unique investment approach, co-investing in pre-seed to later-stage companies without leading rounds or taking board seats. The firm offers approximately 45 funds, including general and focused funds, as well as tailored institutional portfolios for wealth managers and corporations. Investors can participate with a minimum investment of $10,000, benefiting from rigorous diligence and exclusive services. AV also supports a vibrant community of over 850,000 members, providing resources and networking opportunities for both investors and founders.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '7', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/bbdc338b-5301-4041-80b7-abe5c7009ac9.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', 'greenhouse', 'alumniventures', null), ('2674', 'Avolution', 'Avolution UK', 'https://www.avolutionsoftware.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/avolution', 'Avolution is a global software company founded in 2001, based in North Sydney, Australia. The company specializes in enterprise architecture tools, with its flagship product, ABACUS, being a leading modeling platform used by over 2,000 organizations in more than 100 countries. Avolution has a strong presence in America, Asia-Pacific, and Europe, supported by a global partner network.ABACUS is a flexible, graph-based tool designed for roadmapping, modeling, collaboration, and analysis. It allows users to integrate and manage data from various sources, build diagrams and models, and generate insights through customizable analytics. The software supports a range of frameworks and notations, making it adaptable to different organizational needs. Avolution also offers tailored programs and extended services, including consulting and implementation support, to enhance the use of ABACUS for various applications, such as digital transformation and risk monitoring.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/9f69097b-7d65-4302-8f41-8f5a0c777ddd.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', 'workable', 'avolution', null), ('2675', 'BOXRAW', 'BOXRAW Ltd', 'https://uk.boxraw.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/boxraw-ltd', 'BOXRAW is a UK-based boxing lifestyle brand founded in 2017 by Ben Amanna. The brand aims to represent boxing as a way of life, offering a range of products including premium boxing clothing, sportswear, fitness apparel, equipment, and accessories for all skill levels. BOXRAW ships its products to over 55 countries each month and has experienced significant growth, expanding into a 7-figure e-commerce business by 2022.The company emphasizes community and respect, and it operates the BOXRAW Foundation, a registered charity that uses boxing to promote discipline and mindfulness among underserved youth through sustainable gyms worldwide. BOXRAW collaborates with professional boxers and athletes, ensuring its products are developed with athlete feedback for optimal functionality and quality. The brand is also working on innovations like Boxraw Labs, an AI-powered system for analyzing punch statistics to enhance fight analysis.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/6da695e7-4cf7-4d3f-97b5-8369f36de45a.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', null, null, null), ('2676', 'Finster AI', 'Finster AI, UK', 'https://finster.ai', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/finster-ai', 'Finster AI is an AI-native platform based in London, founded in 2023 by Sid Jayakumar, a former Google DeepMind researcher. The company specializes in creating purpose-built AI tools for investment research, analysis, and workflows in the financial sector. It primarily serves investment banks, asset managers, and institutional investors, addressing challenges such as data overload and accuracy demands.The core offering, the Finster AI Platform, is currently in beta and enhances investment research through automated workflows and AI agents that synthesize financial data. Key features include research enhancement, workflow automation, and thesis refinement, all designed to save time and improve decision-making. The platform is built on a robust technical foundation, ensuring security and compliance for complex financial decisions. Finster AI has secured funding to expand its operations and form strategic partnerships, further solidifying its presence in the financial industry.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '6', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/e6918452-8892-447a-9718-a4bd924e0b0e.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', 'greenhouse', 'finsterai', null), ('2677', 'Healthtech 1', 'HEALTHTECH 1 LTD', 'https://www.healthtech1.uk', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/healthtech-1', 'Healthtech-1, officially known as HEALTHTECH 1 LTD, is a London-based healthtech startup founded in 2021. The company focuses on automating repetitive administrative tasks in UK primary care, primarily for the National Health Service (NHS). By streamlining these processes, Healthtech-1 aims to save staff time and enhance efficiency in healthcare settings.The company has developed several automation solutions for NHS primary care practices. Their key products include Automated Registrations, which processes new patient registrations with same-day efficiency, and Automated Lab Filing, which simplifies lab report processing. Additionally, they have introduced Automated GP2GP Filing for transferring patient records between GP systems. Healthtech-1 is recognized as an NHS-approved supplier and has expanded its reach to over 1,400 GP practices across England, significantly reducing administrative burdens and improving patient care. The company has received accolades, including the Digital Solutions Provider of the Year at the 2024 GP Practice Awards.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '8', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/d566aebd-8924-4646-9bec-6bee32ab23a9.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', 'ashby', 'Healthtech-1', null), ('2678', 'ID-Pal', 'ID-Pal UK Limited', 'https://www.id-pal.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/id-pal', 'ID-Pal is a Dublin-based company that offers an ISO27001 certified SaaS+ identity verification and compliance platform. Founded in 2016, ID-Pal enables businesses to verify customer identities and comply with AML/KYC regulations remotely. The platform is powered by AI and features a range of capabilities, including instant identity document verification, biometric facial matching, and ongoing compliance monitoring.The solution is designed for quick deployment, allowing businesses to implement it in less than a day. ID-Pal serves various sectors, including fintech, banking, and credit unions, providing customizable workflows to meet specific business needs. The company has established partnerships, such as with Certa, to enhance real-time identity verification processes. With a focus on security, ID-Pal ensures zero access to customer data and employs robust encryption methods to protect sensitive information.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/33b8f6da-1579-4ffd-a37c-3042a3688346.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', null, null, null), ('2679', 'Knox Digital', 'Knox Digital Limited', 'https://knoxdigi.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/knoxdigital', 'Knox Digital is a global digital communications consultancy based in the United Kingdom. The company focuses on influencing public opinion through innovative digital strategies. With a team experienced in working with high-profile clients, including Presidents and international businesses, Knox Digital emphasizes a modern approach to communications.The firm offers a range of services, including strategic consulting, branding, social media management, audience analysis, paid advertising, and digital infrastructure training. Their approach combines data-driven insights with creative execution to effectively engage target audiences. Knox Digital is registered as a private limited company and has been active since its incorporation on June 7, 2024.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/051833f5-7316-4aa4-81c9-a040855e0830.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', null, null, null), ('2680', 'Periodic Labs', 'Periodic Labs UK, Ltd', 'https://periodic.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/periodic-labs', 'Periodic Labs is an early-stage AI company dedicated to advancing scientific discovery through the development of AI scientists and autonomous laboratories. The company focuses on the physical sciences and materials research, aiming to enhance research capabilities by combining intelligent AI systems with hands-on experimentation. Their innovative approach involves generating new knowledge through hypothesis testing and analyzing high-volume experimental data.Founded by a team with extensive experience in AI and scientific projects, Periodic Labs is supported by notable investors, including a16z, Felicis, and NVIDIA’s venture capital arm, NVentures. The company is committed to building AI systems that can conjecture models, conduct experiments, and learn from results, with a particular emphasis on materials discovery and industry applications. They also provide tailored solutions for specific industry challenges, such as assisting semiconductor manufacturers with data analysis and design iteration.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/baccd742-4209-4caa-8b41-5f1176bdd2d5.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', null, null, null), ('2681', 'The Earth Build Project', 'The Earth Build Project Limited', 'https://www.earthbuildproject.co.uk', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/earthbuildproject', 'The Earth Build Project is a pioneering co-operative intent on researching and developing a new zero-carbon construction method.  Combining cutting edge 3D printing technology with a traditional ''cob'' mix of earth and organic fibre, we are working towards constructing the UKs first 3D printed buildings from the earth on which they stand.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/c9075c95-b0ef-402c-a8c9-9772f8f8c60e.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', null, null, null), ('2682', 'Thomas Miller', 'Thomas Miller (UK) Holdings Company Ltd', 'https://www.thomasmiller.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/thomasmiller', 'Thomas Miller is a global provider of insurance services, established in 1885. With a presence in 19 countries and 31 offices, the company employs over 900 people. It specializes in managing complex issues and developing innovative solutions within the insurance sector.The core services offered by Thomas Miller include management services for transport and professional indemnity insurance mutuals, managing general agency operations, and professional services such as technical, legal, captive, and claims management. The company also provides investment management for its own entities and other institutions. A key focus area is marine insurance, particularly Protection & Indemnity (P&I) services, through its Specialty Underwriting Agency.Thomas Miller emphasizes building long-term relationships with clients, ensuring that their culture and governance prioritize client needs. The company''s mutual management businesses are central to its operations, supported by owned businesses that enhance service offerings and generate returns for shareholders.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/c10609b7-bef3-4982-ba39-933efd933191.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', 'breezy', 'thomas', null), ('2683', 'Titan Research', 'Titan Research Ltd', 'https://www.titanresearch.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/titan-research', 'As a domain name data company, Titan Research offers a Domain Name Intelligence API that provides businesses and organisations with up-to-date intelligence on any domain name. Our Domain Name Management Service provides a comprehensive solution for streamlining the management of large domain name portfolios.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/151308ac-a2e2-4ea8-afe2-205192db3f01.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', 'bamboohr', 'titan', null), ('2684', 'Village', 'VILLAGE SOCIAL LTD', 'https://www.villagesocial.app', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/villagesocialapp', 'AI native and emotionally intelligent social for busy professionals. Share life''s ups and downs and get helpful reminders when it matters, never miss an important detail, stay close despite lack of time or distance.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/31e92d1c-b140-4b70-86e1-408dcd5e33e0.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', 'greenhouse', 'village', null), ('2685', 'Asymmetric Security', 'DeepResponse Ltd', 'https://www.asymmetricsecurity.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/asymmetric-security', 'Asymmetric Security is the first full-stack AI Digital Forensics and Incident Response company. We respond to cyber incidents for our customers, using AI tools built in-house. Drawing on these real-world incidents, we build realistic evaluations and reinforcement learning environments to advance our own AI cyberdefense capabilities and those of frontier AI labs.Our mission is to accelerate AI''s defensive cybersecurity capabilities. We believe accelerating AI cyberdefense is critical to meet the security challenges of the AGI era. Our team includes alumni from Oxford, Stanford, Cambridge, RAND, Palo Alto Networks, Crowdstrike, and beyond.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/3e0bc2b2-cf70-4940-9788-b996cd854d1b.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', null, null, null), ('2686', 'Diesta', 'Diesta Limited', 'https://diesta.co.uk', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/diestaltd', 'Diesta Limited is a UK-based insurtech company founded in 2022. It specializes in an intelligent platform designed to automate premium reconciliation, distribution, and processing for the intermediated insurance industry. The company primarily serves insurers and brokers in the United Kingdom, focusing on compliance, regulatory support, and ancillary accountancy services within the insurance value chain.Diesta''s premium processing platform connects internal systems, brokers, and insurers to a unified financial ledger. Key features include automated reconciliation of premium records, a credit control module for faster payment collection, and integration with systems like Whitespace for reliable policy administration data. The platform aims to enhance cash flow and efficiency in the insurance sector, with upcoming features designed to unlock capital and improve liquidity. Diesta is also compliant with SOC 1, SOC 2, and GDPR standards, ensuring secure operations in the financial services space.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/ef4a793b-15ff-461f-9d02-a1381056f25c.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', null, null, null), ('2687', 'Hines', 'Hines Europe Real Estate Investments Limited', 'https://www.hines.com/locations/europe', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/hines', 'Hines is a global real estate investment, development, and management firm founded in 1957 by Gerald D. Hines in Houston, Texas. The company has grown from a one-man operation to a major player in the real estate sector, with a presence in 384 cities across 30 countries. Hines has developed over 163 million square feet of office space and more than 119 million square feet of non-office space, focusing on landmark projects and sustainability initiatives.The firm offers a range of real estate services, including investment management, development, acquisitions and dispositions, asset management, and property management. Hines works across various sectors, such as office, retail, industrial, multifamily, and mixed-use projects. The company is known for creating architecturally significant buildings and has a strong commitment to sustainability, having pioneered features like LEED Platinum buildings and energy management practices. With approximately $144 billion in assets under management, Hines continues to emphasize quality investments and functional environments.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '2', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/7455f972-011d-4716-b8d6-abb3d0aa6896.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', 'icims', 'hines', null), ('2688', 'Shelftrak', 'ShelfTrak Ltd', 'https://www.shelftrak.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/shelftrak-ltd', 'We are a team of retail experts with 50+ years of combined experience, united by a mission to help brands and retailers make faster, smarter decisions about their in-store execution.Frustrated by the limitations of traditional retail tracking, we embraced AI to transform how execution and compliance are measured in real time. Shelftrak was born—a high-performance commercial technology company delivering unmatched precision, speed, and scale.Our proprietary AI-powered image recognition analyses thousands of retail fixture images with better-than-human accuracy. The result? Rapid insights into category share, price, promotion, and execution trends that empower our clients to act quickly and strategically.We serve leading FMCG brands and retailers across the globe, covering the key channels of travel retail, domestic markets and hospitality venues. Clients and projects include Nestlé, Mondelez, Hershey, Lindt, Diageo, Remy-Cointreau, Brown-Forman, Pernod Ricard, Lindt and JTI.𝗢𝘂𝗿 𝗰𝗼𝗿𝗲 𝘀𝗲𝗿𝘃𝗶𝗰𝗲𝘀:𝗚𝗹𝗼𝗯𝗮𝗹 𝗧𝗿𝗮𝘃𝗲𝗹 𝗥𝗲𝘁𝗮𝗶𝗹 𝗧𝗿𝗮𝗰𝗸𝗶𝗻𝗴 𝗦𝗲𝗿𝘃𝗶𝗰𝗲Three cycles per year across 50 airports and 75 stores, delivering SKU-level insights on share of shelf and competitor execution.𝗦𝗵𝗲𝗹𝗳𝘁𝗿𝗮𝗸 𝗖𝗼𝗺𝗽𝗹𝗶𝗮𝗻𝗰𝗲 𝗔𝗽𝗽Our mobile tool allows in-store teams and field agents to collect, upload, and analyse retail execution data instantly using AI-driven "Click & Go" tracking.𝗕𝗲𝘀𝗽𝗼𝗸𝗲 𝗖𝗼𝗻𝘀𝘂𝗹𝘁𝗮𝗻𝗰𝘆Tailored analysis and strategic reporting that drive category growth, execution improvement, and competitive advantage.Shelftrak brings together retail know-how, smart tech, and a relentless focus on execution performance. We turn retail visibility into actionable intelligence—so your brand is always shelf-ready.www.shelftrak.com | info@shelftrak.com', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/a6184f00-f401-4034-b156-c5b0345a192d.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', null, null, null), ('2689', 'Sunbird', 'Sunbird Solar Solutions (UK) Limited', 'https://www.sunbird.eu', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/sunbirdeu', 'Sunbird is a Pan-European and UK solar PV developer led by an experienced team of Commercial and Industrial (C&I) specialists with decades of experience in developing, financing, designing, constructing, and maintaining solar and battery energy storage assets. We offer tailored solar and energy storage solutions for shopping malls, industrial properties, logistics warehouses, and office parks, including a turnkey approach covering design, regulatory, procurement, construction, and ongoing operation and maintenance for rooftop, ground mount, and car park solar PV systems.We offer:Flexible Customer Engagement Models:- Co-investing joint ventures for enhanced collaboration- Tailor engagement strategies to meet individual client needsBorderless Operations:- Expertise in managing multi-country solar portfolios- Navigating diverse regulatory environmentsProven Track Record:- Our team has successfully installed 300 MW and have 500 MW in development across Europe- Demonstrated capability in delivering resultsMaximizing Income Potential:- Dedicated sales team monetizes excess roof space and power- Third-party power sales boost property owner revenueScalability and Efficiency:- Seamless growth through technology and established processes- Implement tried-and-tested systems for optimal performanceLong-Term Partnerships:- View clients as partners on a renewable energy journey- Transforming buildings into power producersInnovative Energy Strategies:- Explore both onsite and offsite energy sales- Flexible lease terms Localized Support:- Ground teams ensure standardized equipment, installation, and maintenance- Reporting across European jurisdictions for transparency and complianceSolutions to Address Rising Costs:- As energy prices continue to rise, our solutions become even more relevant.- We pave the way toward achieving net zero energy consumption, benefiting both the environment and our clients.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/ae3810d2-a928-429f-8d75-ee34172149e9.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', null, null, null), ('2690', 'The Helicopter Girls', 'THE HELICOPTER GIRLS LIMITED', 'https://thehelicoptergirls.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/the-helicopter-girls', 'The next generation of aerial cinematography.Established 2011, we are the UK''s most comprehensive and experienced provider of drone cinematography. Bringing the world''s best talent together with leading-edge technology to make the impossible possible.Recent projects include Wicked, Stuntman, Wonka, Fast X, Paddington in Peru, The Diplomat, The Witcher and many more.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/775c4ab8-8ddf-486f-af01-127c0bbf0662.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', null, null, null), ('2691', 'Fifth Dimension', 'Fifth Dimension AI Ltd', 'https://www.fifthdimensionai.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/5dai', 'Fifth Dimension AI is a London-based technology company founded in 2023, focusing on generative AI solutions for the real estate industry. The company aims to enhance productivity by automating repetitive tasks such as data analysis, document review, and content creation. Its headquarters is located at Huckletree, 213 Oxford Street, London.The core product, Ellie, is a generative AI assistant designed specifically for real estate professionals. Ellie automates high-volume tasks, including reading and analyzing complex documents, extracting insights with high accuracy, and generating content in the user''s brand tone. The platform features tailored AI toolkits, integration with various systems, and over 50 AI models to support real estate operations. Fifth Dimension AI emphasizes collaboration between humans and AI, ensuring that professionals are empowered rather than replaced. The company has experienced significant growth, with notable clients like Grainger, Canary Wharf Group, Allsop, and Hamptons adopting Ellie into their operations.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/ce594bbc-344f-4853-8bfb-547e3a0b0799.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', 'teamtailor', 'app', null), ('2692', 'London EV Company (LEVC)', 'London EV Company Limited', 'https://www.levc.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/levc', 'London EV Company (LEVC) is a British automotive manufacturer based in Ansty Park, Coventry, specializing in zero-carbon mobility solutions. Founded in 1908, LEVC has a rich history in urban transport, originally known as The London Taxi Corporation. The company rebranded in 2017 to focus on electric vehicle production, supported by significant investments from Chinese automaker Geely.LEVC produces innovative electric and range-extended vehicles designed for urban transport. Its flagship model, the TX London Taxi, is recognized as the world''s cleanest taxi, featuring a battery electric powertrain with a gasoline range extender. The VN5 electric van and the L380, a fully electric vehicle, are also part of its lineup. The company is committed to expanding its offerings with new electric models that enhance space, charging capabilities, and digital features.With a state-of-the-art factory in Coventry, LEVC emphasizes smart, green, and safe mobility solutions. The company is dedicated to advancing lightweight vehicles and zero-emission technology, positioning itself as a leader in the e-mobility sector.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/ba044fd8-def7-4d1b-a58d-22cb12c49366.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', 'teamtailor', 'app', null), ('2693', 'Matternet', 'Matternet UK Ltd', 'https://www.matternet.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/matternet-inc', 'Matternet is a drone technology company based in Mountain View, California, founded in December 2011. The company specializes in autonomous aerial delivery systems, focusing on the efficient delivery of goods, particularly medical supplies, in urban and road-deficient areas. Matternet aims to improve logistics through decentralized networks of drones, landing stations, and cloud-based software.The company has developed the Matternet M2 drone system, which is the first delivery drone to receive FAA Type Certification and Production Certification, allowing it to operate in U.S. airspace. The M2 drone can carry payloads of up to 2 kg over distances of 20 km. Matternet also offers automated landing stations for secure payload exchanges and a cloud-based software platform for managing drone networks. Their services include end-to-end autonomous aerial delivery for healthcare, e-commerce, and humanitarian aid, with a strong emphasis on contactless deliveries. Matternet has completed over 20,000 commercial flights and has established partnerships with organizations like UPS and Doctors Without Borders.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/2b812836-e49c-4397-9c3a-424584d60db4.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', 'workable', 'matternet', null), ('2694', 'Proteintech', 'Proteintech Europe Limited', 'https://www.ptglab.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/proteintech-group', 'Proteintech Group is a biotechnology company founded in 2001 by scientists, including CEO Dr. Jason Li. The company focuses on developing high-quality antibodies and related reagents for protein research, aiming to cover all human gene products and support reproducible scientific discovery. Proteintech originated from NIH-funded research and emphasizes a "scientists for scientists" approach, ensuring originality and quality by producing its own antibodies using a "whole protein approach."The company offers a wide range of research tools, primarily antibodies, immunoassays, and proteins, all manufactured in-house. Proteintech provides antibodies against 12,000 human targets, over 100 sandwich ELISA kits, and more than 4,000 recombinant fusion proteins. They also offer custom services for polyclonal antibody production and additional reagents for research protocols. With products cited in over 20,000 publications, Proteintech is recognized for its reliability and performance in proteomics, immunology, and related fields, supporting scientists in their research endeavors.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/1c9d43ca-10d7-4d1a-9ded-9ea3611e265b.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', null, null, null), ('2695', 'Ampa', 'AMPA Holdings LLP', 'https://ampa.co.uk', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/ampa-group-legal-professional-services', 'Ampa Holdings LLP is a leading legal and professional services group based in Birmingham, UK. Founded in March 2021, it operates as a "House of Brands," uniting various specialized brands under a collaborative model. Ampa is committed to sustainable growth and has been certified as a B Corporation since January 2023, emphasizing a balance between profit and responsibility towards people, communities, and the environment.The group includes several distinct brands, such as Shakespeare Martineau, Mayo Wynne Baxter, Lime Solicitors, Marrons, Corclaim, CSS Assure, and Coadax. These brands provide a range of services, including legal advice, town planning, loss recovery, cyber security, and corporate finance. With over 1,200 employees across more than 20 office locations, Ampa fosters a culture of collaboration, trust, and inclusion, and is recognized as a top company for employee engagement in the UK.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/87bab891-8281-4d6d-ac59-ba4a3babffd7.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', 'pinpoint', 'app', null), ('2696', 'Appier', 'Appier UK Co., LTD', 'https://www.appier.com/en/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/appier', 'Appier Group, Inc. is an AI-native SaaS company based in Taipei, Taiwan, founded in 2012. The company specializes in AdTech and MarTech solutions, providing businesses with AI-driven marketing, customer engagement, and decision-making tools. Appier''s mission is to make AI accessible and measurable, helping over 2,000 customers worldwide achieve better marketing outcomes through predictive analytics and personalized experiences.With a global presence that includes 17 offices across Asia, the US, and Europe, Appier has made significant strides since its inception. The company offers a range of products, including Ad Cloud for advertising campaigns, Personalization Cloud for tailored customer interactions, and Data Cloud for analytics and insights. Their solutions cater to various industries, including e-commerce, finance, and travel, enabling businesses to analyze consumer behavior and enhance ROI. Appier continues to grow, reporting a 26% year-over-year revenue increase and expanding its customer base significantly.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '1', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/7cd0f74f-a012-44f2-863d-7a1e45bf0a16.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', 'greenhouse', 'appier', null), ('2697', 'Clay', 'Clay Labs UK Ltd', 'https://www.clay.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/grow-with-clay', 'Clay is a sales and marketing technology company based in Brooklyn, New York, founded in 2017. The company offers an AI-powered platform designed for data enrichment, outbound marketing automation, and growth workflows. Clay helps teams identify, research, and engage high-intent customers by aggregating data from over 100 premium sources, including public databases and social media.The platform streamlines revenue operations by automating personalized outbound campaigns and lead generation. It allows users to conduct complex growth experiments that traditionally required larger teams, significantly reducing manual research efforts. Clay''s services include real-time intent data tracking, multi-channel lead sourcing, and seamless CRM integration. The company supports a range of clients, from solo founders to large enterprises, with tiered pricing plans and a 14-day trial option. Notable clients include OpenAI and Canva, who have benefited from enhanced data-driven outbound strategies.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '9', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/9ea8b26d-0593-4a37-99f2-ac644223e66d.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', 'ashby', 'claylabs', null), ('2698', 'DBX Commodities', 'DBX Commodities Ltd', 'https://www.dbxcommodities.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/dbx-commodities', 'DBX Commodities is a London-based analytics software company founded in 2020. It specializes in providing real-time data and insights for dry bulk commodity trading, utilizing satellite imagery, AI, and machine learning. The company emerged from Signal Ventures'' incubation program and officially launched in 2021.DBX offers a software platform that delivers real-time intelligence on supply, demand, inventories, and flows for dry bulk commodities. Key features include satellite technology and analytics for tracking vessel movements and cargo, as well as visualizations tailored for commodity market professionals. The platform enhances trading opportunities and supply chain efficiency across various sectors, including coal, iron ore, bauxite, alumina, copper, steel, and agriculture. DBX primarily serves physical and financial traders, including commodity producers, banks, and hedge funds.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/6ca7d165-0f9c-4b08-803d-7f48dcee9f18.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', null, null, null), ('2699', 'Infoshare+', 'Infoshare+ Ltd', 'https://infoshareplus.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/infoshareuk', 'Infoshare+ is a UK-based data and software company that specializes in providing mission-critical solutions for the public sector, particularly local government. Founded in 1993, the company has over 30 years of experience in enhancing service efficiency, data accuracy, asset management, and decision-making through data analytics and digital tools. Infoshare+ operates under a buy-and-build strategy, acquiring complementary govtech providers to create a scalable platform for public sector digitization and resource optimization.The company offers tailored data and digital solutions that address various public sector challenges, including social care, finance, and property management. Key offerings include data analytics for improved performance insights, digital front doors for self-assessment tools, and asset management systems compliant with accounting standards. Infoshare+ is committed to operational streamlining and integrated services, focusing on data quality and governance. It serves hundreds of public sector organizations, including over 200 local government and emergency service entities, positively impacting thousands of individuals.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/57bf4a97-0805-47ed-b9cc-f8e3ff8ccf48.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', null, null, null), ('2700', 'ScienceMachine', 'Science Machine Ltd', 'https://www.sciencemachine.ai', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/sciencemachine', 'ScienceMachine is a London-based AI startup founded in 2024, led by CEO Lorenzo Sani and a team including Benjamin Tenmann, Henry E. Miller, Matthew Greenig, and Bo Wang. The company specializes in developing AI-driven bioinformatics platforms aimed at enhancing scientific research through rapid and cost-effective data analysis.The core product, Sam, is an autonomous AI agent that automates end-to-end workflows in biotech and biomedical data analysis. It processes raw data, generates reports, and integrates seamlessly with existing client tools and databases. Sam is designed to handle various tasks, including flow cytometry data analysis, mass spectrometry, RNA-seq visualization, and image segmentation. ScienceMachine emphasizes security, ensuring that client data remains private and encrypted.In July 2025, ScienceMachine raised $3.5 million in pre-seed funding, positioning itself as a leader in AI automation for biotech. The company operates on a subscription-based model, offering customized AI solutions and enterprise features that include expert human support and a free demo option.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/0fe3e73b-04e3-4d42-9845-c4b198b1fdcc.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', null, null, null), ('2701', 'Spectris', 'Spectris Limited', 'https://www.spectris.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/spectris-limited', 'Spectris plc is a global leader in precision instrumentation and controls, specializing in measurement, testing, and analysis solutions that enhance productivity across various industries. The company operates through two main segments: Spectris Scientific and Spectris Dynamics. Spectris Scientific focuses on advanced measurement and materials characterization, while Spectris Dynamics provides sensing, data acquisition, and analysis solutions for product development.Founded in 1915 as the Fairey Aviation Company, Spectris has evolved significantly over the years, transitioning from aviation to precision instrumentation. The company has expanded through strategic acquisitions, including the notable purchase of Malvern Instruments in 2002, which bolstered its scientific capabilities. Spectris serves a diverse range of sectors, including life sciences, automotive, electronics, and academic research, and reported a revenue of £1.44 billion in 2022, reflecting strong growth.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '14', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/60459153-ce8d-4c1c-89e7-25cfd6c88def.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', 'workday', 'spectris/Malvern_Panalytical_Careers', null), ('2702', 'DAHER', 'DAHER AEROSPACE LTD', 'https://www.daher.com/en/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/daher', 'Daher is a French family-owned industrial conglomerate founded in 1863, specializing in aircraft manufacturing, logistics, and industrial services across various sectors, including aerospace, defense, nuclear, and automotive. With over 14,000 employees in 15 countries, Daher generates approximately $2 billion in annual sales.The company has a rich history, originally starting as a shipping company before expanding into energy logistics and global transport. Daher is recognized as the world''s oldest continuously operating aircraft manufacturer, producing high-performance aircraft such as the TBM series of single-engine turboprops and the Kodiak series of utility turboprops. Additionally, Daher manufactures aerospace structures and components for major aircraft like the Dassault Falcon 7X and Airbus A350.Daher also offers integrated logistics and industrial services, supporting aerospace and energy sectors with expertise in shipping, oversized transport, and supply chain management. The company collaborates with leading firms like Airbus and Rolls-Royce, showcasing its commitment to innovation and quality in the aerospace industry.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/8dff5353-bc42-4841-8722-763b32590094.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:01.557015+00', null, null, null), ('2703', 'Institute of Directors (IoD)', 'Institute of Directors', 'https://www.iod.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/school/institute-of-directors', 'The Institute of Directors (IoD) is the UK''s oldest organization for professional business leaders, established in 1903 and granted a Royal Charter in 1906. It represents a diverse membership of directors, senior business leaders, and entrepreneurs, with a focus on promoting free enterprise and setting standards for corporate governance. The IoD serves between 20,000 to 35,000 members, including a significant portion from FTSE 100 companies and small to medium-sized enterprises (SMEs). The organization emphasizes professionalism and good governance, aiming for "better directors for a better world."The IoD offers a variety of professional development, networking, and advocacy services. Members can connect with peers across different sectors, participate in training programs, and gain insights into directorship issues. The organization also actively represents members'' views to government and media, influencing policy on key business matters. With a global presence, the IoD provides courses and resources internationally, supporting directors in fulfilling their leadership responsibilities and fostering entrepreneurial activity.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/b1efc7b6-17e5-4154-9efa-66a564d8c627.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', null, null, null), ('2706', 'Swap', 'Swap Commerce Limited', 'https://www.swap-commerce.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/sw-ap', 'Swap Commerce is a UK-based software company that specializes in an agentic commerce operating system designed for e-commerce brands, particularly those using Shopify. Founded in October 2021, Swap Commerce streamlines global compliance, returns, inventory management, logistics, and operations into a single dashboard. This integration helps over 600 businesses in retail, apparel, fashion, and food & beverages save time and reduce costs while focusing on growth.The platform offers a comprehensive suite of services, including DDP shipping, automated returns management, global tax compliance, and AI-enabled inventory analytics. Users benefit from features like real-time insights, automated processing, and enhanced customer experiences. Swap Commerce has demonstrated significant results, such as an average 8% revenue boost and a 111% year-over-year sales increase for some clients. The company emphasizes sustainability through responsible returns disposal and eco-conscious practices, making it a valuable partner for scaling e-commerce operations.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '35', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/c16583b9-2276-4053-868d-c12a55634369.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', 'greenhouse', 'swapecommerce', null), ('2707', 'Verdant Specialty Solutions', 'Verdant Specialty Solutions Halifax Ltd', 'https://www.verdantspecialty.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/verdant-specialty-solutions', 'Verdant Specialty Solutions is a global specialty chemicals company based in Houston, Texas. Founded in 2021, it has roots dating back to the 1970s as McIntyre Group. The company specializes in surfactants and specialty chemicals for various sectors, including personal care, home care, hygiene, industrial cleaning, and energy. Verdant was acquired by Samyang Holdings in December 2023.The company employs around 300 people and serves over 1,000 customers worldwide, generating annual revenue of about USD 210 million. Verdant operates production sites in the US, UK, and Germany, along with labs and distribution networks globally. Its product portfolio includes a range of surfactants and specialty chemicals, such as amphoteric and cationic surfactants, emulsifiers, and anti-foaming agents. Verdant focuses on providing sustainable and high-performance solutions that enhance product quality and environmental impact, catering to both consumer brands and industrial processes.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/10d95f77-bccb-411f-a63b-2e771fd2a6a5.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', 'bamboohr', 'verdant', null), ('2708', 'Liberty Global', 'Liberty Global Europe Ltd', 'https://www.libertyglobal.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/liberty-global', 'Liberty Global plc is a multinational telecommunications company formed in 2005 through the merger of Liberty Media International and UnitedGlobalCom. With headquarters in London, Amsterdam, and Denver, the company operates as a group of operators and investors across three platforms: Liberty Telecom, Liberty Growth, and Liberty Services. It focuses on providing converged broadband, video, mobile services, and strategic investments in technology, media, and infrastructure.Liberty Global serves approximately 80 million connections, delivering next-generation broadband internet, video, mobile communications, and telephony through advanced fibre and 5G networks. Its core platform, Liberty Telecom, includes well-known brands such as Virgin Media-O2 in the UK and VodafoneZiggo in the Netherlands. The company also invests in around 70 companies in various sectors, including technology and media, and offers innovative technology and finance services through its Liberty Services platform.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '60', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/221f121c-eec6-4db5-9ab9-6e9cfeaf6cdf.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', 'workday', 'Liberty_Global_Careers', null), ('2709', 'Cap10 Partners LLP', 'CharlesII Partners LLP', 'https://cap10partners.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/cap10-partners-llp', 'Cap10 Partners is a private equity firm based in London, England, founded in 2021 by experienced financial entrepreneurs. The firm specializes in long-term investments in European mid-market companies, aiming to bring large-cap sophistication and innovation to this sector.The firm employs a thematic investment strategy across five business sectors, focusing on high-potential businesses that may be overlooked by others. Cap10 integrates Environmental, Social, and Governance (ESG) principles as a key value driver in its portfolio, supporting business leaders to create meaningful change and enhance value for stakeholders. To date, Cap10 Partners has completed three acquisitions, including the notable purchase of Sureserve Group in July 2023 for £214 million, marking a significant milestone as a first-time fund completing a Public-to-Private transaction.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/fe56560f-1b09-4c0a-9bc6-bdba9a383afb.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', null, null, null), ('2710', 'COGA AI', 'COGA AI Limited', 'https://coga.ai', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/coga-ai', 'COGA AI', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/7d603634-7b40-46c1-8137-5c5fae31fd86.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', null, null, null), ('2711', 'Compleo Health', 'COMPLEO HEALTH LIMITED', 'https://www.compleohealth.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/compleohealth', 'Compleo Health Ltd. is a UK-based healthcare company that specializes in diagnostic imaging services, particularly MRI and CT scanning. Founded in February 2021, the company is headquartered in Manchester and serves the NHS, Independent Healthcare Providers, and other facilities across the UK and Europe.Compleo Health offers a range of services, including mobile and relocatable MRI and CT scanning, equipment rental, expert staffing solutions, and comprehensive managed services. Their focus on sustainability is evident through the use of helium-free scanners and practices that reduce carbon footprints. The company supports both long-term and short-term models for clinics, hospitals, and community diagnostic centers.Compleo Health collaborates with various healthcare providers, including NHS Trusts and private hospitals, and has received positive feedback for its tailored solutions and reliable support. The company is committed to enhancing patient care through innovative and sustainable diagnostic solutions.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '1', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/7227e6a6-6b2d-4d45-99ad-b8d536d6f893.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', 'recruitee', 'compleohealth', null), ('2712', 'Ohm Space', 'OHMSPACE LTD', 'https://ohm.space', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/ohmspace', 'Ohm Space is a UK-based aerospace startup founded in 2021, specializing in high-temperature resistojet propulsion systems for spacecraft. The company develops innovative solutions for a range of platforms, from nanosatellites to large geostationary satellites, using safe and low-cost propellants like water and noble gases. This approach enhances thrust and specific impulse, achieving up to 70% higher performance compared to competitors while promoting sustainability by reducing hazardous chemicals.Headquartered in Southampton, OhmSpace builds on extensive research from the University of Southampton. The company secured a €2.5M seed round in 2023 to support its mission, which includes plans for In-Orbit Demonstration missions in 2026. OhmSpace''s core product is a modular, scalable electric propulsion system that utilizes patented 3D-printed metal heaters for efficient propellant use. The company also offers engineering model assembly, mission design support, and plans for in-house manufacturing in Rome to ensure quality and scalability. Its technology targets space agencies, satellite operators, and LEO constellation providers, focusing on enhancing mission capabilities and sustainability in the aerospace sector.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/337a6241-6502-4a56-8db9-d38eac904b42.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', null, null, null), ('2713', 'Rumbl', 'Rumbl Ltd', 'https://rumbl.co.uk', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/rumbl-ltd', 'We''re a tight-knit team of creatives, developers and digital strategists with over 40 years'' combined commercial experience.We work remotely with businesses all over the country, creating beautiful brands, conversion-focused websites and digital marketing strategies that generate leads. Our clients come in all shapes and sizes and from many different industries, all with the common goal of finding solutions to their problems and ensuring they stand out against their competitors.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/c4f5619f-04ff-434e-8497-9a4df021861b.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', null, null, null), ('2714', 'Teciem', 'TCMI UK LTD', 'https://teciem.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/teciem', 'Teciem is a treasury and capital markets software provider that became an independent company in February 2026, after spinning off from Finastra. Headquartered in London, Teciem leverages 35 years of industry expertise and serves over 340 financial institutions across 85 countries, including 70 of the world''s top 100 banks. The company is led by CEO Wissam Khoury, who has extensive experience in financial technology.Teciem''s mission is to deliver essential treasury, capital markets, risk management, regulatory compliance, and investment management solutions. Their software suite includes several key products: Kondor, a cloud-enabled treasury solution; Summit, a platform for OTC derivatives; Opics, a treasury solution for banks; Sophis, a platform for managing derivatives; Fusion Invest, an investment management platform; and Fusion Risk, a risk and compliance platform. Teciem collaborates with a wide range of financial institutions, focusing on enhancing trading efficiency and regulatory compliance through innovative technology and a strong partner network.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '1', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/56aa5f2a-c860-449e-a938-286214553ea1.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', 'workday', 'finastra/Teciem', null), ('2715', 'AQA', 'AQA Education', 'https://www.aqa.org.uk', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/aqa', 'AQA (Assessment and Qualifications Alliance) is the UK''s largest exam board and a non-profit education charity. It sets and marks over half of all GCSEs and A-levels taken by more than 1 million students across 92% of UK schools. Established in 1998, AQA operates from Manchester and focuses on general secondary education, technical and vocational education, and other educational services.With a history spanning over 120 years, AQA has evolved from earlier examination bodies to provide a range of qualifications, including GCSEs, AS and A-levels, Extended Project Qualifications, and Technical Awards. The organization also offers resources such as past paper questions, differentiated tests, and online teacher support through its community platform, Teachit. AQA is committed to advancing education by reinvesting its income into educational activities and support for disadvantaged youth.In addition to assessment services, AQA leads in educational research and policy, providing expertise to inform curriculum development. The organization supports teachers through qualification development and custom assessments, ensuring that educational resources meet the needs of students and educators alike.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '9', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/fc2074f8-06e2-421b-acec-636138c87880.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:00.376782+00', 'workday', 'AQA', null), ('2716', 'The Linux Foundation', 'Linux Foundation UK Limited', 'https://www.linuxfoundation.org', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/the-linux-foundation', 'The Linux Foundation (LF) is a non-profit organization established in 2000, originally as Open Source Development Labs. It focuses on supporting Linux kernel development and promoting open-source software. Headquartered in San Francisco, California, the LF serves as a collaborative hub for developers, companies, and communities, facilitating projects across various technologies, including cloud, networking, and blockchain.The LF''s mission is to support, promote, protect, and standardize Linux and open-source technologies. It provides essential infrastructure, legal frameworks, and funding through memberships and crowdfunding. The foundation hosts significant events like the Linux Kernel Developers Summit and Open Source Summit, fostering collaboration and addressing ecosystem challenges. With a diverse range of hosted projects, the LF plays a crucial role in advancing technologies that impact industries globally.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/9e0b5c18-c14a-402f-ad3d-a5f50cb7e9ef.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:04.042781+00', 'smartrecruiters', 'linuxfoundation', null), ('2717', 'Oak Engage', 'OAK ENGAGE LIMITED', 'https://www.oak.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/oakengage', 'Oak Engage is a UK-based company founded in 2017 that specializes in modern intranet software and employee engagement solutions. The company aims to enhance internal communications and connect various types of workers, including frontline and remote employees, through a mobile-first platform. Oak Engage operates as OAK ENGAGE LIMITED and has its headquarters in Newcastle Upon Tyne.The company offers an award-winning employee app and intranet platform designed to boost productivity and engagement. Key features include mobile access, seamless integrations with tools like Microsoft 365 and Google Workspace, social and cultural tools for peer recognition, and feedback mechanisms such as polls and surveys. The platform is customizable, allowing organizations to create tailored experiences that improve information access and foster workplace culture. Oak Engage has partnered with notable brands like Aldi, ITV, and Burger King, demonstrating its commitment to supporting diverse workforces.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/b05b4315-58ca-4bf4-a406-8af2769e09a8.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:02.529791+00', 'workable', 'oakengage', null), ('2718', 'RTS Wind UK', 'RTS Wind Ltd', 'https://www.rts-wind.co.uk', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/rts-wind-ltd', 'RTS Wind UK (RTS Wind Ltd) is a specialist in wind turbine services for the onshore and offshore renewables industry. Based in Middlesbrough, North Yorkshire, the company is part of the global RTS Wind Group and has over 20 years of experience in turbine maintenance and project solutions. Founded in 2005, RTS Wind has expanded its operations internationally, with a presence in 44 countries across five continents.The company offers a wide range of turnkey solutions, including blade repair, inspection, maintenance, resource management, and high voltage services. RTS Wind is committed to safety and sustainability, aligning its operations with UN goals for affordable and clean energy. With a focus on quality and rapid response, RTS Wind UK supports wind turbine projects worldwide, backed by a certified and culturally aware team operating from a 24/7 control center.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', '4', '0', 'https://jbuikhbssecxhfunkaol.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/a4e974a7-0201-4fe9-8137-08ea8d8ef77a.png', 'true', null, '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', '2026-03-03 15:44:03.25189+00', null, null, null), ('2719', 'IslaCare', null, 'https://apply.workable.com/islacare/', null, null, null, null, '1', null, 'true', null, '2026-03-04 20:10:12.734078+00', '2026-03-04 20:10:12.734078+00', 'workable', 'islacare', null), ('3000', 'Jaja Finance', null, null, null, null, null, null, '10', null, 'true', null, '2026-03-06 16:28:45.83961+00', '2026-03-06 16:28:45.83961+00', 'bamboohr', 'jajafinance', null), ('3002', 'Economic Modeling', 'Economic Modeling Specialists Intl. Ltd', 'https://www.lightcast.io', null, null, 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', null, '1', null, 'true', null, '2026-03-06 17:03:02.551666+00', '2026-03-06 17:03:02.551666+00', 'lever', 'economicmodeling', null), ('3003', 'Nouvelle Garde Groupe', 'Nouvelle Garde Groupe', 'https://www.nouvellegardegroupe.com', null, null, 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', null, '38', null, 'true', null, '2026-03-06 17:03:03.674304+00', '2026-03-06 17:03:03.674